      "text":
          "Wa-izaa laqul lazeena aamanoo qaalooo aamannaa wa-izaa khalaa ba'duhum ilaa ba'din qaalooo atuhaddisoonahum bimaa fatahal laahu 'alaikum liyuhaajjookum bihee 'inda rabbikum, afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Awalaa ya'lamoona annal laaha ya'lamu maa yusirroona wa-maa yu'linoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Wa-minhum ummiyyoona laa ya'lamoonal kitaaba illaaa amaaniyya wa-in hum illaa yazunnoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Fawailul lillazeena yaktuboonal kitaaba bi-aidihim summa yaqooloona haazaa min 'indil laahi liyashtaroo bihee samanan qaleela(n); fawailul lahum mimaa katabat aydeehim wa-wailul lahum mimmaa yaksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo lan tamassanan Naaru illaaa ayyaamam ma'doo-dah,(tan) qul attakhaztum 'indal laahi 'ahdan falain yukhlifal laahu 'ahdah(ooo); am taqooloona 'alal laahi maa laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Balaa man kasaba sayyi'atanw wa-ahaatat bihee khateee'atuhoo fa-ulaaa'ika As-haabun Naar(i); hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aamanoo wa-'amilus saalihaati ulaaa'ika As-haabul Janna(ti); hum feeha khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz akhaznaa meesaaqa Baneee Israaa'eela laa ta'budoona illal laaha wa-bil waalidaini ihsaana(nw) wa-zil qurbaa walyataamaa walmasaakeeni wa-qooloo linnaasi husna(nw) wa-aqeemus salaata wa-aatuzZakaat(a) summa tawallaitum illaa qaleelam minkum wa-antum mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz akhaznaa meesaa-qakum laa tasfikoona dimaaa'akum wa-laa tukhrijoona anfusakum min diyaarikum summa aqrartum wa-antum tashhadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Summa antum haaa'ulaaa'i taqtuloona anfusakum wa-tukhrijoona fareeqam minkum min diyaarihim tazaaharoona 'alaihim bil-ismi wal'udwaani wa-in yaatookum usaaraa tufaadoohum wahuwa muharramun 'alaikum ikhraajuhum, afatu'-mi-noona biba'dil Kitaabi wa-takfuroona biba'd,(in) famaa jazaaa'u mai yaf'alu zaalika minkum illaa khizyun fil hayaatid dunyaa; wa-yawmal qiyaamati yuraddoona ilaaa ashaddil 'azaab:(i) wa-mal laahu bighaafilin 'ammaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeenash tarawul hayaatad dunyaa bil-aakhira(ti); falaa yukhaffafu 'anhumul 'azaabu wa-laa hum yunsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Moosal Kitaaba wa-qaffainaa mim ba'dihee bir-Rusul(i); wa-aatainaa 'Eesab- na- Maryamal baiyinaati wa-ayyadnaahu bi-Roohil Qudus:(i) afakullamaa jaaa'akum Rasoolum bimaa laa tahwaaa anfusukumus takbartum fafareeqan kazzabtum wa-fareeqan taqtuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo quloobunaa ghulf,(um) bal la'anahumul laahu bikufrihim faqaleelam maa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa jaaa'ahum Kitaabum min 'indil laahi musaddiqul limaa ma'ahum wa-kaanoo min qablu yastaftihoona 'alal lazeena kafaroo falammaa jaaa'ahum maa 'arafoo kafaroo bih,(ee) fala-'natul laahi 'alal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Bi'samash taraw biheee anfusahum ai yakfuroo bimaaa anzalal laahu baghyan ain yunazzilal laahu min fadlihee 'alaa mai yashaaa'u min ibaadi(hee); fabaaa'oo bighadabin 'alaa ghadab,(in) wa-lilkaafireena 'azaabum muheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahum aaminoo bimaaa anzalal laahu qaaloo nu'minu bimaaa unzila 'alainaa wa-yakfuroona bimaa waraaa'ahoo wa-huwal haqqu musaddiqal limaa ma'ahum: qul falima taqtuloona Ambiyaaa'al laahi min qablu in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "^Wa-laqad jaaa'akum Moosa bilbaiyinaati summat takhaztumul 'ijla mim ba'dihee wa-antum zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz akhaznaa meesaaqakum wa-rafa'naa fawqakumut Toora khuzoo maaa aatainaakum biquwwatinw wasma'oo; qaaloo sami'naa wa-'asainaa wa-ushriboo fee quloobihimul 'ijla bikufrihim, qul bi'samaa yaamurukum biheee eemaanukum in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Qul in kaanat lakumud Daarul Aakhiratu 'indal laahi khaalisatam min doonin naasi fatamannawul mawta in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Wa-lai yatamannawhu abadam bimaa qaddamat aideehim: wallaahu 'aleemum bizzaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Wa-latajidannahum ahrasannaasi 'alaa hayaatinw wa minal lazeena ashrakoo, yawaddu ahaduhum lau yu'ammaru alfa sana(tinw) wa-maa huwa bi-muzahzihihee minal 'azaabi ai yu'ammar:(a) wallaahu baseerum bimaa ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Qul man kaana 'aduwwal li-Jibreela fa-innahoo nazzalahoo 'alaa qalbika bi-iznil laahi musaddiqal limaa baina yadaihi wa-hudanw wa-bushraa lilmu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Man kaana 'aduwwal lillaahi wa-malaaa'ikatihee wa-Rusulihee wa-Jibreela wa-Meekaala fa-innal laaha 'aduwwul lilkaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad anzalnaaa ilaika Aayaatim baiyinaat(inw); wa-maa yakfuru bihaaa illal faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Awa-kullamaa 'aahadoo ahdan nabazahoo fareequm minhum, bal aksaruhum laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa jaaa'ahum Rasoolum min 'indil laahi musaddiqul limaa ma'ahum nabaza fareequm minal lazeena ootul Kitaaba Kitaabal laahi waraaa'a zuhoorihim ka-annahum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Wattaba'oo maa tatlush Shayaateenu 'alaa mulki Sulaimaan(a); wamaa kafara Sulaimaanu walaakinnash Shayatteena kafaroo yu'al-limoonan naasas sihra wa-maaa unzila 'alal malakaini bi-Baabila Haaroota wa-Maaroot, wa-maa yu'allimaani min ahadin hattaa yaqoolaaa innamaa nahnu fitnatun falaa takfur; fayata'al-lamoona minhumaa maa yufarriqoona bihee bainal mar'yee wa-zawjih,(i) wa-maa hum bidaaarreena bi-hee min ahadin illaa bi-iznil llah,(i) wa-yata'allamoona maa yadurruhum wa-laa yanfa'uhum, wa-laqad 'alimoo lamanish taraahu maa lahoo fil Aakhirati min khalaaq,(in) wa-labi'sa maa sharaw biheee anfusahum, lau kaanoo ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Wa-law annahum aamanoo wattaqaw lamasoobatum min 'indil laahi khair(un); lau kaanoo ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa taqooloo raa'inaa wa-qoolun zurnaa wasma'oo: wa-lilkaafireena 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Maa yawaddul lazeena kafaroo min ahlil kitaabi wa-lal mushrikeena ai-n yunazzala 'alaikum min khairim mir Rabbikum: wallaahu yakhtassu birahmatihee mai-n yashaaa,(u) wallaahu zul fadlil 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "^Maa nansakh min aayatin aw nunsihaa na-ti bikhairim minhaaa aw mislihaaa: alam ta'lam annal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Alam ta'lam annal laaha lahoo mulkus samaawaati wal-ard:(i) wa-maa lakum min doonil laahi minw waliyyinw wa-laa naseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Am tureedoona an tas'aloo Rasoolakum kamaa su'ila Moosa min qabl:(u) wa-mai-n yatabaddalil kufra bil-eemaani faqad dalla sawaaa'as sabeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Wadda kaseerum min ahlil kitaabi lau yaruddoo-nakum mim ba'di eemaanikum kuffaaran hasadam min 'indi anfusihim mim ba'di maa tabaiyyana lahumul haqq(u); fa'foo wasfahoo hattaa yaa-tiyal laahu bi-amrih:(ee) innal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Wa-aqeemus salaata wa-aatuz zakaah,(ta) wa-maa tuqaddimoo li-anfusikum min khairin tajidoohu 'indal laah:(i) innal laaha bimaa ta'maloona baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo lai-n yadkhulal jannata illaa man kaana Hoodan aw Nasaaraa: tilka amaaniyyuhum: qul haatoo burhaa-nakum in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "Balaa man aslama wajhahoo lillaahi wa-huwa muhsinun falahooo ajruhoo 'inda rabbihee wa-laa khawfun 'alaihim wa-laa hum yahzanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalatil Yahoodu laisatin Nasaaraa 'alaa shai'inw wa-qaalatin Nasaaraaa laisatil Yahoodu 'alaa shai'inw 'wa-hum yatloonal Kitaab:(a) kazaalika qaalal lazeena la ya'lamoona misla qawlihim, fallaahu yahkumu bainahum Yawmal Qiyaamati feemaa kaanoo feehi yakhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 114,
      "text":
          "Wa-man azlamu mimmam mana'a masaajidal laahi ai-n yuzkara feehas muhoo wa-sa'aa fee kharaabihaaa, ulaaa'ika maa kaana lahum ai-n yadkhuloohaaa illaa khaaa'ifeen,(a) lahum fid dunyaa khizyunw wa-lahum fil aakhirati 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahil mashriqu walmaghrib,(u) fa-aynamaa tuwalloo fasamma wajhul laah,(i) innal laaha waasi'un Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalut takhazal laahu walada:(n) subhaana(hoo); bal lahoo maa fis samaawaati wal-ard(i); kullul lahoo qaanitoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Badeee'us samaawaati wal-ard(i); wa-izaa qadaaa amran fa-innamaa yaqoolu lahoo kun fayakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 118,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena laa ya'lamoona lau-laa yukallimunal laahu au taateenaaa aaya:(tun) kazaalika qaalal lazeena min qablihim misla qawlihim. tashaabahat quloobuhum: qad baiyannal aayaati liqawmin-y yooqinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 119,
      "text":
          "Innaaa arsalnaaka bilhaqqi basheeranw wa-nazeera(nw); wa-laa tus'alu 'an As-haabil Jaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 120,
      "text":
          "Wa-lan tardaa 'ankal Yahoodu wa-lan Nasaaraa hattaa tattabi'a millatahum: qul inna hudal laahi huwal hudaa: wa-la'init taba'ta ahwaaa'ahum ba'dal lazee jaaa'aka minal 'ilmi maa laka minal laahi minw waliyyinw wa-laa naseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 121,
      "text":
          "Allazeena aatainaahumul Kitaaba yatloonahoo haqqa tilaawatiheee ulaaa'ika yu'minoona bih:(ee) wa-mai-n yakfur bihee fa-ulaaa'ika humul khaasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 122,
      "text":
          "Yaa-Baneee Israaa'eelaz kuroo ni'matiyal lateee an'amtu 'alaikum wa-annee faddaltukum 'alal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 123,
      "text":
          "Wattaqoo yawmal laa tajzee nafsun 'an nafsin shai-'anw wa-laa yuqbalu minhaa 'adlunw wa-laa tanfa'uhaa shafaa-'atunw wa-laa hum yunsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 124,
      "text":
          "^Wa-izib talaaa Ibraaheema Rabbuhoo bi-Kalimaatin fa-atammahun(na); qaala Innee jaa'iluka linnaasi Imaama(n); qaala wa-min zurriyyatee; qaala laa yanaalu 'ahdiz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 125,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz ja'alnal Baita masaabatal linnaasi wa-amna-nw wattakhizoo mim Maqaami Ibraaheema musallaaa; wa-'ahidnaaa ilaaa Ibraaheema wa-Ismaa'eela an tahhiraa Baitiya littaaa'ifeena wal'aakifeena warrukka'is sujood"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 126,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaala Ibraaheemu Rabbij 'al haazaa baladan aaminanw warzuq ahlahoo minas samaraati man aamana minhum billaahi wal-yawmil aakhir(i); qaala wa-man kafara fa-umatti'uhoo qaleelan summa adtarruhooo ilaa 'azaabin Naar(i); wa-bi'sal maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 127,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz yarfa'u Ibraaheemul qawaa'ida minal Baiti wa-Ismaa'eelu Rabbanaa taqabbal minnaa; innaka Antas Samee'ul Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 128,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaa waj'alnaa muslimaini laka wa-min zurriyyatinaaa ummatam muslimatal laka wa-arinaa manaasikanaa wa-tub 'alainaa; innaka antat Tawwaabur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 129,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaa wab'as feehim Rasoolam minhum yatloo 'alaihim aayaatika wa-yu'allimuhumul Kitaaba wal-Hikmata wa-yuzakkeehim, innaka Antal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 130,
      "text":
          "Wa-mai-n yarghabu 'am Millati Ibraaheema illaa man safiha nafsah,(u) wa-laqadi astafainaahu fid dunyaa; wa-innahoo fil aakhirati laminas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 131,
      "text":
          "Iz qaala lahoo Rabbuhooo aslim; qaala aslamtu li-Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 132,
      "text":
          "Wa-wassaa bihaaa Ibraaheemu baneehi wa-Ya'qoobu, yaa-baniyya innal laahas tafaa lakumud deena falaa tamootunna illaa wa-antum muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 133,
      "text":
          "Am kuntum shuhadaaa'a iz hadara Ya'qoobal mawtu iz qaala libaneehi maa ta'budoona mim ba'dee qaaloo na'budu ilaahaka wa-ilaaha aabaaa'ika Ibraaheema wa-Ismaa'eela wa-Ishaaqa Ilaahanw waahidanw wa-nahnu lahoo muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 134,
      "text":
          "Tilka ummatun qad khalat; lahaa maa kasabat wa-lakum maa kasabtum; wa-laa tus'aloona 'ammaa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 135,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo koonoo Hoodan aw Nasaaraa tahtadoo: qul bal Millata Ibraaheema Haneefa(nw); wa-maa kaana minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 136,
      "text":
          "Qoolooo aamannaa billaahi wa-maaa unzila ilainaa wa-maaa unzila ilaaa Ibraaheema wa-Ismaa'eela wa-Ishaaqa wa-Ya'qooba wal-Asbaati wa-maa ootiya Moosa wa-'Eesaa wa-maaa ootiyan Nabiyyoona mir Rabbihim laa nufarriqoo baina ahadim minhum wa-nahnu lahoo muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 137,
      "text":
          "Fa-in aamanoo bimisli maaa aamantum bihee faqadih tadaw; wa-in tawallau fa-innamaa hum fee shiqaaq(i); fasayak-feekahumul laah,(u) wa-Huwas Samee'ul Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 138,
      "text":
          "Sibghatal laah(i); wa-man ahsanu minal laahi sibgha(tanw); wa-nahnu lahoo 'aabidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 139,
      "text":
          "Qul atuhaaajjoonanaa fil laahi wa-Huwa Rabbunaa wa-Rabbukum wa-lanaa a'maalunaa wa-lakum a'maalukum wa-nahnu lahoo mukhlisoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 140,
      "text":
          "Am taqooloona inna Ibraaheema wa-Ismaa'eela wa-Ishaaqa wa-Ya'qooba wal-asbaata kaanoo Hoodan aw Nasaaraa: qul 'a-antum a'lamu amil laah:(u) wa-man azlamu mimman katama shahaadatan 'indahoo minal laah:(u) wa-mal laahu bighaafilin 'ammaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 141,
      "text":
          "Tilka ummatun qad khalat; lahaa maa kasabat wa-lakum maa kasabtum; wa-laa tus'aloona 'ammaa kaano ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 142,
      "text":
          "^Sayaqoolus sufahaaa'u minan naasi maa wallaahum 'an Qiblatihimul latee kaanoo 'alaihaa, qul lillaahil mashriqu walmaghrib,(u) yahdee mai yashaaa'u ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 143,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika ja'alnaakum ummatanw wasatal litakoonoo shuhadaaa'a 'alan naasi wa-yakoonar Rasoolu 'alaikum shaheedaa: wa-maa ja'alnal qiblatal latee kunta 'alaihaaa illaa lina'lama mai yattabi'ur Rasoola mimmai yanqalibu 'alaa 'aqibaiyh,(i) wa-in kaanat lakabeeratan illaa 'alal lazeena hadal laah:(u) wa-maa kaanal laahu liyudee'a eemaanakum, innal laaha binnaasi la-Ra'oofur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 144,
      "text":
          "Qad naraa taqalluba wajhika fis samaaa'(i); fala-nuwalliyannaka qiblatan tardaahaa, fawalli wajhaka shatral Masjidil haaraam,(i) wa-haisu maa kuntum fawalloo wujoohakum shatrah: wa-innal lazeena ootul Kitaaba laya'lamoona annahul haqqu mir Rabbihim: wa-mal laahu bighaafilin 'ammaa ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 145,
      "text":
          "Wa-la'in ataital lazeena ootul kitaaba bikulli aayatim maa tabi'oo Qiblatak, wa-maaa anta bitaabi'in Qiblatahum, wa-maa ba'duhum bitaabi'in Qiblata ba'd,(in) wa-la'init taba'ta ahwaaa'ahum mim ba'di maa jaaa'aka minal 'ilmi innaka izal laminaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 146,
      "text":
          "Allazeena aatainaahumul kitaaba ya'rifoonahoo kamaa ya'rifoona abnaaa'ahum; wa-inna fareeqam minhum layaktumoonal haqqa wa-hum ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 147,
      "text": "Alhaqqu mir Rabbik(a); falaa takoonana minal mumtareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 148,
      "text":
          "Wa-likullinw wijhatun huwa muwalleehaa; fastabiqul khairaat,(i) ayna maa takoonoo ya`ti bikumul laahu jamee'aa,(n) innal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 149,
      "text":
          "Wa-min haisu kharajta fawalli wajhaka shatral Masjidil Haraam(i); wa-innahoo lalhaqqu mir Rabbik: wa-mal laahu bighaafilin 'ammaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 150,
      "text":
          "Wa-min haisu kharajta fawalli wajhaka shatral Masjidil Haraam,(i) wa-haisu maa kuntum fawalloo wujoohakum shatrahoo li'allaa yakoona linnaasi 'alaikum hujjatun illal lazeena zalamoo minhum falaa takhshawhum wakhshawnee wa-li-utimma ni'matee 'alaikum wa-la'allakum tahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 151,
      "text":
          "kamaaa arsalnaa feekum Rasoolam minkum yatloo 'alaikum aayaatina wa-yuzakkeekum wa-yu'alli-mukumul kitaaba wal-hikmata wa-yu'allimukum maa lam takoonoo ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 152,
      "text": "Fazkurooneee azkurkum washkuroo lee wa-laa takfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 153,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal laazeena aamanus ta'eenoo bissabri was-Salaah,(ti) innal laaha ma'as saabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 154,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taqooloo limai-n yuqtalu fee sabeelil laahi amwaat,(um) bal ahyaaa'unw wa-laakil laa tash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 155,
      "text":
          "Wa-lanablu-wannakum bishai'im minal khawfi waljoo'i wa-naqsim minal amwaali wal-anfusi was-samaraat:(i) wa-bashshiris saabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 156,
      "text":
          "Allazeena izaaa asaabathum museebatun qaalooo innaa lillaahi wa-innaaa ilaihi raaji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 157,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika 'alaihim salawaatum mir Rabbihim wa-rahma(tum); wa-ulaaa'ika humul muhtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 158,
      "text":
          "^Innas Safaa wal-Marwata min sha'aaa'iril laah(i); faman hajjal Baita awi'tamara falaa junaaha 'alaihi ai yattawwafa bihimaa, wa man tatawwa'a khairan fa-innal laaha Shaakirun 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 159,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yaktumoona maaa anzalnaa minal baiyinaati walhudaa mim ba'di maa baiyannaahu linnaasi fil kitaab(i) ulaaa'ika yal'anuhumul laahu wa-yal'anuhumul laa-'inoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 160,
      "text":
          "Illal lazeena taaboo wa-as-lahoo wa-baiyanoo fa-ulaaa'ika atoobu 'alaihim, wa-Anat Tawwaabur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 161,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo wamaa-too wa-hum kuffaar(un) ulaaa'ika 'alaihim la-'natul laahi walmalaa'ikati wannaasi ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 162,
      "text":
          "khaalideena feeha; laa yukhaffafu 'anhumul 'azaabu wa-laa hum yunzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 163,
      "text":
          "Wa-ilaahukum illaahunw waahid(ul); laaa ilaaha illaa Huwar Rahmaanur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 164,
      "text":
          "Inna fee khalqis samaawaati wal-ardi wakhtilaafil laili wannahaari walfulkil latee tajree fil bahri bimaa yanfa'un naasa wa-maaa anzalal laahu minas samaaa'i mim maaa'in fa-ahyaa bihil arda ba'da mawtihaa wa-bas-sa feehaa min kulli daaabbatinw wa-tasreefir riyaahi was-sahaabil musakhkhari bainas samaaa'i wal-ardi la-aayaatil liqawminy ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 165,
      "text":
          "Wa-minan naasi mai yattakhizu min doonil laahi andaadai-n yuhibboonahum kahubbil laah(i); wallazeena aamanooo ashaddu hubbal lillah: wa-lau yaral lazeena zalamoo iz yarawnal 'azaaba annal quwwata lillaahi jamee'a(nw) wa-annal laaha shadeedul 'azaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 166,
      "text":
          "Iz tabarra-al lazeenat tubi'oo minal lazeenat taba'oo wa-ra-awul 'azaaba wa-taqatta'at bihimul as-baab"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 167,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeenat taba'oo lau anna lanaa karratan fanatabarra-a minhum kamaa tabarra'oo minnaa: kazaalika yureehimul laahu a'maalahum hasaraatin 'alaihim; wa-maa hum bikhaarijeena minan Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 168,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhan naasu kuloo mimmaa fil ardi halaalan taiyyiba(nw) wa-laa tattabi'oo khutu-waatish Shaitaan,(i) innahoo lakum 'aduwwum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 169,
      "text":
          "Innamaa yaa`murukum bis-sooo'i walfah-shaaa'i wa-an taqooloo alal laahi maa laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 170,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahumut tabi'oo maaa anzalal laahu qaaloo bal nattabi'u maaa alfainaa 'alaihi aabaaa'anaaa: awa-lau kaana aabaaa'hum laa ya'qiloona shai'anw wa-laa yahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 171,
      "text":
          "Wa-masalul lazeena kafaroo kamasalil lazee yan'iqu bimaa laa yasma'u illaa du'aaa'anw wa-nidaaa'aa,(n) summum bukmun 'umyun fahum laa ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 172,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo kuloo min taiyibaati maa razaqnaakum washkuroo lillaahi in kuntum iyyaahu ta'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 173,
      "text":
          "Innamaa harrama 'alaikumul maitata waddama wa-lahmal khinzeeri wa-maaa uhilla bihee lighairil laah(i); famanid turra ghaira baaghinw wa-laa 'aadin falaaa isma 'alaih,(i) innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 174,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yaktumoona maaa anzalal laahu minal kitaabi wa-yashtaroona bihee samanan qaleel(an) ulaaa'ika maa yaakuloona fee butoonihim illan Naar(a) wa-laa yukallimu-humul laahu Yawmal Qiyaamati wa-laa yuzakkeehim wa-lahum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 175,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeenash tarawud dalaalata bilhudaa wal'azaaba bilmaghfirah,(ti) famaaa as-barahum 'alan Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 176,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bi-annal laaha nazzalal kitaaba bilhaqq: wa-innal lazee-nakh talafoo fil kitaabi lafee shiqaaqim ba'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 177,
      "text":
          "^Laisal birra an tuwalloo wujoohakum qibalal mashriqi walmaghribi wa-laakinnal birra man aamana billaahi wal-yawmil aakhiri wal-malaaa'ikati wal-kitaabi wan-nabiyyeena wa-aatal maala 'alaa hubbihee zawil qurbaa walyataa-maa walmasaakeena wabnas sabeeli wassaaa'ileena wa-fir riqaabi wa-aqaamas salaata wa-aataz zakaata walmoofoona bi-ahdihim izaa 'aahadoo; wa-saabireena fil baasaaa'i waddarraaa'i wa-heenal baas:(i) ulaaa'ikal lazeena sadaqoo; wa-ulaaa'ika humul muttaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 178,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo kutiba alaikumul qisaasu fil qatlaa; alhurru bilhurri wal'abdu bil'abdi wal-unsaa bil-unsaa, faman 'ufiya lahoo min akheehi shai'un fattibaa'um bilma'roofi wa-adaaa'un ilaihi bi-ihsaan:(in) zaalika takhfeefum mir rabbikum wa-rahmah:(tun) famani' tadaa ba'da zaalika falahoo 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 179,
      "text":
          "Wa-lakum fil qisaasi hayaatuin yaaa-ulil albaabi la'allakum tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 180,
      "text":
          "Kutiba 'alaikum izaa hadara ahadakumul mawtu in taraka khairanil wasiyyatu lilwaalidaini wal-aqrabeena bil-ma'roof(i); haqqan 'alal muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 181,
      "text":
          "Famam baddalahoo ba'da-maa sami'ahoo fa-innamaaa ismuhoo 'alal lazeena yubaddi-loonah,(u) innal laha Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 182,
      "text":
          "Faman khaafa mim moosin janafan aw isman fa-aslaha bainahum falaaa ismaa 'alayh,(i) innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 183,
      "text":
          "Yaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo kutiba 'alaikumus Siyaamu kamaa kutiba 'alal lazeena min qablikum la'allakum tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 184,
      "text":
          "Ayyaamam ma'doodaat,(in) faman kaana minkum mareedan aw' alaa safarin fa'iddatum min ayyaamin ukhar,(a) wa-'alal lazeena yuteeqoonahoo fidyatun ta'aamu miskeen(in); faman tatawwa'a khairan fahuwa khairul lah,(oo) wa-an tasoomoo khairul lakum; in kuntum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 185,
      "text":
          "Shahru Ramadaanal lazeee unzila feehil Qur'aanu hudal linnaasi wa-baiyinaatim minal hudaa wal-furqaan,(i) faman shahida minkumush shahra fal-yasum(hu); wa-man kaana mareedan aw 'alaa safarin fa'iddatum min ayyaamin ukhar:(a) yureedul laahu bikumul yusra wa-laa yureedu bikumul 'usra wa-litukmilul 'iddata wa-litukabbirul laaha 'alaa maa hadaakum wa-la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 186,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa sa-alaka 'ibaadee 'annnee fa-innee qareeb(un); ujeebu da'watad daa'i izaa da'aan(i); falyastajeeboo lee wal-yu'minoo bee la'allahum yarshudoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 187,
      "text":
          "Uhilla lakum laylatas Siyaamir rafasu ilaa nisaaa'ikum, hunna libaasul lakum wa-antum libaasul lahunn:(a) 'alimal laahu annakum kuntum takhtaanoona anfusakum fataaba 'alaikum wa'afaa 'ankum; fal'aana baashiroo-hunna wabtaghoo maa katabal laahoo lakum, wa-kuloo washraboo hattaa yatabaiyana lakumul khaitul abyadu minal khaitil aswadi minal fajr(i); summa atimmus Siyaama ilal layl,(i) wa-laa tubaashiroo-hunna wa-antum 'aakifoona fil masaajid:(i) tilka hudoodul laahi falaa taqraboohaa: kazaalika yubaiyinul laahu aayaatihee linnaasi la'allahum yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 188,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taakuloo amwaalakum bainakum bilbaatili wa-tudloo bihaaa ilal hukkaami litaakuloo fareeqam min amwaalin naasi bil-ismi wa-antum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 189,
      "text":
          "^Yas'aloonaka 'anil ahilla(ti); qul hiya mawaaqeetu linnaasi wal-Hajj:(i) wa-laisal birru bi-an ta'tul buyoota min zuhoorihaa wa-laakinnal birra manit taqaa: wa'tul buyoota min abwaa-bihaa, wattaqul laaha la'allakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 190,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaatiloo fee sabeelil laahil lazeena yuqaatiloonakum wa-laa ta'tadooo, innal laaha laa yuhibbul mu'tadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 191,
      "text":
          "Waq-tuloohum haisu saqif-tumoohum wa-akhrijoohum min haisu akhrajookum, walfitnatu ashaddu minal qatl,(i) wa-laa tuqaa-tiloohum 'indal Masjidil Haraami hattaa yuqaatilookum feeh(i); fa-in qaata-lookum faq-tuloohum: kazaalika jazaaa'ul kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 192,
      "text": "Fa-i'ninn tahau fa-innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 193,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaatiloohum hatta laa takoona fitnatunw wa-yakoonad deenu lillaah(i); fa-inin tahau falaa 'udwaana illaa 'alaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 194,
      "text":
          "Ash-Shahrul Haraamu bish-Shahril Haraami wal-hurumaatu qisaas,(un) famani' tadaa 'alaikum fa'tadoo 'alaihi bimisli ma' tadaa 'alaikum, wattaqul laaha wa'lamooo annal laaha ma'al muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 195,
      "text":
          "Wa-anfiqoo fee sabeelil laahi wa-laa tulqoo bi-aydeekum ilat tahluka'( ti) wa - ahsinoo' innal laaha yuhibbul muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 196,
      "text":
          "Wa-atimmul Hajja wal-Umarata lillaah,(i) fa-in uhsirtum famas taisara minal had(yi); walaa tahliqoo ru'oosakum hatta yablughal hadyu mahilla,(hu) faman kaana minkum mareedan aw biheee azam mir ra'sihee fafidyatum min Siyaamin aw sadaqatin aw nusuk,(in) fa-izaaa amintum faman tamatta'a bil-'Umrati ilal Hajji famas taisara minal had,(yi) famal lam yajid fa-Siyaamu salaasti ayyaamin fil Hajji wa-sab'atin izaa raja'tum: tilka 'asharatun kaamilah:(tun) zaalika limal lam yakun ahluhoo haadiril Masjidil Haraam,(i) wattaqul laaha wa'lamoo annal laaha shadeedul 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 197,
      "text":
          "Al-Hajju ashhurum ma'-loomaat,(tun) faman farada feehinnal hajja falaa rafasa wa-laa fusooqa wa-laa jidaala fil Hajj:(i) wa-maa taf'aloo min khairien ya'lamhul laah:(u) wa-tazawwadoo fa-inna khairaz zaadit taqwaa, wattaqooni yaaa-ulil albaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 198,
      "text":
          "Laisa 'alaikum junaahun an tabtaghoo fad-lam mir rabbikum, fa-izaaa afadtum min 'Arafaatin fazkurul laaha 'indal Mash'aril Haraam(i); waz-kuroohu kamaa hadaakum wa-in kuntum min qablihee laminad daaalleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 199,
      "text":
          "Summa afeedoo min haisu afaadan naasu wastagh firullaah,(a) innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 200,
      "text":
          "Fa-iza qadaitum manaa-sikakum fazkurul laaha kazikrikum aabaaa'akum aw ashadda zikraa:(n) faminan naasi ma-ien yaqoolu Rabbanaaa aatinaa fid dunyaa wa-maa lahoo fil Aakhirati min khalaaq"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 201,
      "text":
          "Wa-minhum maien yaqoolu rabbanaaa aatina fid dunyaa hasanatanw wa-fil aakhirati hasanatanw wa-qinaa azaaban Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 202,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika lahum naseebum mimmaa kasaboo, wal-laahu saree'ul hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 203,
      "text":
          "^Wazkurul laaha feee ayyaamin ma'doodaat,(in) faman ta'ajjala fee yawmaini falaaa ismaa 'alaihi wa-man ta-akhara falaaa isma 'alayh,(i) limanit taqaa: wattaqul laaha wa'lamooo annakum ilaihi tuhsharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 204,
      "text":
          "Wa-minan naasi mai yu'jibuka qawluhoo fil hayaatid dunyaa wa-yushhidul laaha 'alaa maa fee qalbihee wa-huwa aladdul khisaam"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 205,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa tawallaa sa'aa fil-ardi liyufsida feeha wa-yuhlikal harsa wannasl:(a) wal laahu laa yuhibbul fasaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 206,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahut taqil laaha akhazathul izzatu bil-ism,(i) fahasbuhoo jahannam,(u) wa-labi'sal mihaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 207,
      "text":
          "Wa-minan naasi maien yashree nafsahub tighaaa'a mardaatil laah,(i) wallaahu ra'oofum bil'ibaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 208,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanud khuloo fis silmi kaaaffa(tanw) wa-laa tattabi'oo khutuwaatish Shaitaan,(i) innahoo lakum 'aduwwum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 209,
      "text":
          "Fa-in zalaltum min ba'di maa jaaa'atkumul baiyinaatu fa'lamoo annal laaha 'Azeezun hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 210,
      "text":
          "Hal yanzuroona illaaa a-ien ya'tiya-humul laahu fee zulalim minal ghamaami walmalaaa'ikatu wa-qudiyal amr,(u) wa-ilal laahi turja'ul umoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 211,
      "text":
          "Sal Banee Israaa'eela kam aatainaahum min aayatim baiyinah:(tin) wa-mai yubaddil ni'matal laahi mim ba'di maa jaaa'athu fa-innal laaha shadeedul 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 212,
      "text":
          "Zuyyina lillazeena kafarul hayaatud dunyaa wa-yas-kharoona minal lazeena aamanoo wallazeenat taqaw fawqahum yawmal Qiyaamah:(ti) wallaahu yarzuqu ma-ien yashaaa'u bighairi hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 213,
      "text":
          "Kaanan naasu ummatanw waahidatan fab'asal laahun Nabiyyeena mubashshireena wa-munzireen(a) wa-anzala ma'ahumul kitaaba bilhaqqi liyahkuma bainan naasi feemakh talafoo feeh,(i) wa-makh talafa feehi 'illal lazeena ootoohu mim ba'di maa jaaa'athumul baiyinaatu baghyam bainahum; fahadal laahul lazeena aamanoo limakh talafoo feehi minal haqqi bi-iznih:(i) wallaahu yahdee ma-ien yashaaa'u ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 214,
      "text":
          "Am hasibtum an tadkhulul jannata wa-lammaa yaa-tikum masalul lazeena khalaw min qablikum; massathumul baasaaa'u waddarraaaa'u wa-zulziloo hattaa yaqoolar Rasoolu wallazeena aamanoo ma'ahoo mataa nasrul laah:(i) alaaa inna nasral laahi qareeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 215,
      "text":
          "Yas'aloonaka maazaa yunfiqoon(a); qul maaa anfaqtum min khairin falil-waalidaini wal-aqrabeena walyataamaa wal-masaakeeni wabnis sabeel:(i) wa-maa taf'aloo min khairin fa-innal laaha bihee 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 216,
      "text":
          "Kutiba alaikumul qitaalu wa-huwa kurhul lakum; wa'asaaa an takrahoo shai'anw wa-huwa khairul lakum; wa'asaaa an tuhibbo shai'anw wa-huwa sharrul lakum: wallaahu ya'lamu wa-antum laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 217,
      "text":
          "Yas'aloonaka 'anish Shahril Haraami qitaalin feeh(i); qul qitaalun feehi kabeer(unw); wa-saddun 'an sabeelil laahi wa-kufrum bihee wal-Masjidil Haraam(i) wa-ikhraaju ahlihee minhu akbaru 'indal laah,(i) wal-fitnatu akbaru minal qatl:(i) wa-laa yazaaloona yuqaatiloonakum hatta yaruddookum 'an deenikum inis tataa'oo, wa-ma-ien yartadid minkum 'an deenihee fayamut wahuwa kaafirun fa-ulaaa'ika habitat a'maaluhum fid dunyaa wal-aakhira(ti); wa-ulaaa'ika as-haabun Naar(i); hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 218,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo wallazeena haajaroo wa-jaahadoo fee sabeelil laahi ulaaa'ika yarjoona rahmatal laah,(i) wallaahu Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 219,
      "text":
          "^Yas'aloonaka 'anil khamri walmaisir(i); qul feehimaaa ismun kabeerunw wa-manaafi'u linnaasi wa-ismuhumaa akbaru min naf'ihimaa: wa-yas'aloonaka maaza yunfiqoona qulil 'afuw:(a) kazaalika yubaiyinul laahu lakumul aayaati la'allakum tatafakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 220,
      "text":
          "Fid dunyaa wal-aakhirah:(ti) wa-yas'aloonaka 'anil yataamaa; qul islaahul lahum khayr(un); wa-in tukhaalitoohum fa-ikhwaanukum, wallaahu ya'lamul mufsida minal muslih,(i) wa-law shaaa'al laahu la-a'natakum, innal laaha 'Azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 221,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tankihul mushrikaati hattaa yu'minn,(a) wa-la-amatum mu'minatun khairum mim mushrikatinw wa-lau a'jabatkum: wa-laa tunkihul mushrikeena hattaa yu'minoo, wa-la'abdum mu'minun khairum mim mushrikinw wa-lau 'ajabakum: ulaaa'ika yad'oona ilan Naar(i); wallaahu yad'ooo ilal Jannati wal-maghfirati biiznih(ee); wa-yubaiyinu Aayaatihee linnaasi la'allahum yatazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 222,
      "text":
          "Wa-yas'aloonaka 'anil maheed(i); qul huwa aza(n) fa'tazilun nisaaa'a fil maheed(i); wa-laa taqraboo-hunna hattaa yathurn(a); fa-izaa tatah-harrna faatoohunna min haisu amarakumul laah,(u) innal laaha yuhibbut Tawwaabeena wa-yuhibbul mutatahhireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 223,
      "text":
          "Nisaaa'ukum harsul lakum faatoo harsakum annaa shi'tum; wa-qaddimoo li-anfusikum, wattaqul laaha wa'lamooo annakum mulaaqooh:(u) wa-bash-shiril mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 224,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taj'alul laaha 'urdatal li-aymaanikum an tabarroo wa-tattaqoo wa-tuslihoo bainan naas:(i) wallaahu Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 225,
      "text":
          "Laa yu'aakhi-zukumul laahu billaghwi feee aymaa-nikum wa-laakien yu'aakhi-zukum bimaa kasabat quloo-bukum: wallaahu Ghafoorun Haleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 226,
      "text":
          "Lillazeena yu'loona min nisaaa'ihim tarabbusu arba'ati ashhur(in); fa-in faaa'oo fa-innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 227,
      "text": "Wa-in 'azamut talaaqa fa-innal laaha Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 228,
      "text":
          "Walmutallaqaatu yatarab-basna bi-anfusi-hinna salaasata qurooo',(in) wa-laa yahillu lahunna aien yaktumna maa khalaqal laahu feee arhaami-hinna in kunna yu'minna bil-laahi wal-yawmil aakhir,(i) wa-bu'oola-tuhunna ahaqqu biraddi-hinna fee zaalika in araadooo islaa-haa,(n) wa-lahunna mislul lazee alaihinna bilma'roof,(i) wa-lir-rijjaali 'alaihinna daraja:(tun) wallaahu 'Azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 229,
      "text":
          "Attalaaqu marrataan(i); fa-imsaakum bima'roofin aw tasreehum bi-ihsaan:(in) wa-laa yahillu lakum an taakhuzoo mimmaaa aataitumoohunna shai'an illaaa aien yakhaafaaa alla yuqeemaa hudoodal lah(i); fa-in khiftum allaa yuqeemaa hudoodal laahi falaa junaaha 'Alaihimaa feemaf tadat bih:(ee) tilka hudoodul laahi falaa ta'tadoohaa, wa-maien yata'adda hudoodal laahi fa-ulaaa'ika humuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 230,
      "text":
          "Fa-in talla-qahaa falaa tahillu lahoo mim ba'du hattaa tankiha zawjan ghairah:(u) fa-in tallaqahaa falaa junaaha 'alaihimaaa aien yata-raaja'aaa in zannaaa aien yuqeemaa hudoodal laah:(i) wa-tilka hudoodul laahi yubai-yyinuhaa liqawmien ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 231,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa tallaq-tumun nisaaa'a faba-laghna ajala-hunna fa-amsi-koohunna bima'roofin aw sarrihoo-hunna bima'roof,(in) wa-laa tumsikoo-hunna diraa-ral lita'tadoo, wa-maien yaf'al zaalika faqad zalama naf-sah,(u) wa-laa tat-takhizooo aayaatil laahi huzuwaa,(nw) wazkuroo ni'matal laahi 'alaikum wa-maaa anzala 'alaikum minal kitaabi wal-hikmati ya'izukum bih,(i) wattaqul laaha wa'lamooo annal laaha bikulli shai'in 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 232,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa tallaqtumun nisaaa'a fabalaghna ajalahunna falaa ta'duloo-hunna aien yankihna azwaaja-hunna izaa taraadaw bainahum bilma'roof:(i) zaalika yoo'azu bihee man kaana minkum yu'minu billaahi wal-yawmil aakhir:(i) zaalikum azkaa lakum wa-at-har:(u) wallaahu ya'lamu wa-antum laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 233,
      "text":
          "^Walwaa-lidaatu yurdi'na awlaada-hunna hawlaini kaamilain(i); liman araada a-ien yutimmar radaa'ah,(ta) wa-'alal mawloodi lahoo rizqu-hunna wa-kiswatuhunna bilma'roof,(i) laa tukallafu nafsun illaa wus'ahaa, laa tudaaarra waalidatum biwaladihaa wa-laa mawloodul lahoo biwaladih,(i) wa'alal waarisi mislu zaalik:(a) fa-in araadaa Fisaalan 'an taraadim minhumaa wa-tashaawurin falaa junaaha 'alaihim:(a) wa-in aradttum an tastardi'ooo awlaadakum falaa junaaha 'alaikum izaa sallamtum maaa aataitum bilma'roof:(i) wattaqul laaha wa'lamooo annal laaha bimaa ta'maloona baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 234,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yutawaffawna minkum-wa yazaroona azwaajaien yatarabbasna bi-anfusi-hinna arba'ata ashhurinw wa'ashra(n); fa-izaa balaghna ajalahunna falaa junaaha 'alaikum feemaa fa'alna feee anfusi-hinna bilma'roof:(i) wallaahu bimaa ta'maloona Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 235,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa junaaha 'alaikum feema 'arrad-tum bihee min khit-batin nisaaa'ee aw aknantum feee anfusikum, 'alimal laahu annakum sataz-kuroo-nahunna wa-laakil laa tuwaa'idoohunna sirran illaaa an taqooloo qawlam ma'roofaa,(n) wa-laa ta'zimoo 'uqdatan nikaahi hattaa yablughal kitaabu ajalah,(u) wa'lamooo annal laaha ya'lamu maa feee anfusikum fah-zarooh,(u) wa'lamooo annal laaha Ghafoorun Haleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 236,
      "text":
          "Laa junaaha 'alaikum in tallaq-tumun nisaaa'a maa lam tamassoo-hunna aw tafridoo lahunna fareedah,(tan) wa-matti'oohunna 'alal moosi'ee qadaruhoo wa-'alal muqtiri qadaruhoo matta'am bil-ma'roof(i); haqqan 'alal muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 237,
      "text":
          "Wa-in tallaqtumoo-hunna min qabli an tamassoo-hunna wa-qad farad-tum lahunna fareeda-tan fanis-fu maa farad-tum illaaa aien ya'foona aw ya'fuwal lazee biyadihee 'uqdatun nikaah,(i) wa-an ta'fooo aqrabu littaqwaa, wa-laa tansawul fadla bainakum, innal laaha bimaa ta'maloona Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 238,
      "text":
          "Haafizoo 'alas salawaati was-Salaatil Wustaa wa-qoomoo lillaahi qaaniteen"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 239,
      "text":
          "Fa-in khiftum farijaalan aw rukbaana(n); fa-izaaa amintum fazkurul laaha kamaa 'allamakum maa lam takoonoo ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 240,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yutawaf-fawna minkum wa-yazaroona azwaajanw wasiyyatal li-azwaajihim mataa'an ilal hawli ghaira ikhraaj,(in) fa-in kharajna falaa junaaha 'alaikum fee maa fa'alna feee anfusihinna min ma'roof:(in) wal-laahu Azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 241,
      "text":
          "Wa-lilmutallaqaati mataa'um bil-ma'roof(i); haqqan 'alal muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 242,
      "text": "Kazaalika yubaiyinul laahu lakum aayaatihee la'allakum ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 243,
      "text":
          "^Alam tara ilal lazeena kharajoo min diyaari-him wa-hum uloofun hazaral mawt(i) faqaaala lahumul laahu mootoo summa ahyaahum, innal laaha lazoo fadlin 'alan naasi wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa yashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 244,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaatiloo fee sabeelil laahi wa'lamooo annal laaha Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 245,
      "text":
          "Man zal lazee yuqridul laaha qardan hasanan fayudaa-'ifahoo lahoo ad'aafan kaseerah,(tan) wallaahu yaqbidu wa-yabsutu wa-ilaihi turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 246,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilal mala-i mim Baneee Israaa'eela mim ba'di Moosaaa iz qaaloo li-Nabiyyil lahumub 'as lanaa malikan nuqaatil fee sabeelil laah(i); qaala hal 'asaitum in kutiba 'alaikumul qitaalu allaa tuqaatiloo; qaaloo wa-maa lanaaa allaa nuqaatila fee sabeelil laahi wa-qad ukhrijnaa min diyaarinaa wa-abnaaa'inaa; falammaa kutiba 'alaihimul qitaalu tawallaw illaa qaleelam minhum: wallaahu 'aleemum bizzaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 247,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala lahum Nabiy-yuhum innal laaha qad ba'asa lakum Taaloota malikaa,(an) qaalooo annaa yakoonu lahul mulku 'alainaa wa-nahnu ahaqqu bilmulki minhu wa-lam yu'ta sa'atam minal maal,(i) qaala innal laahas tafaahu 'alaikum wa-zaadahoo bastatan fil 'ilmi waljism(i); wallaahu yu'tee mulkahoo maien yashaaa',(u) wallaahu Waasi'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 248,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala lahum Nabiyyuhum inna Aayata mulkiheee aien ya`atiya-kumut Taabootu feehi sakeenatum mir Rabbikum wa-baqiyyatum mimmaa taraka Aalu Moosa wa-Aalu Haaroona tahmi-luhul malaaa'ikah,(tu) inna fee zaalika la-Aayatal lakum in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 249,
      "text":
          "Falammaa fasala Taalootu biljunoodi qaala innal laaha mub-taleekum binahar(in) faman shariba minhu falaisa minnee wa-mal lam yat'amhu fa-innahoo minneee illaa manigh tarafa ghurfatam biyadih,(i) fashariboo minhu illaa qaleelam minhum, falammaa jaawazahoo huwa wallazeena aamanoo ma'ahoo qaaloo laa taaqata lanal yawma bi-Jaaloota wa-junoodih,(i) qaalal lazeena yazunnoona annahum mulaaqul laahi kam min fi'atin qaleelatin ghalabat fi'atan kaseeratam bi-iznil laah:(i) wallaahu ma'as saabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 250,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa barazoo li-Jaaloota wa-junoodihee qaaloo Rabbanaaa afrigh 'alainaa sabranw wa-sabbit aqdaamanaa wansurnaa 'alal qawmil kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 251,
      "text":
          "Fahaza-moohum bi-iznil laah(i) wa-qatala Daawoodu jaaloota wa-aataahul laahul mulka Wal-Hikmata wa'allamahoo mimmaa yashaaa':(u) wa-law-laa daf'ul laahin naasa ba'dahum biba'dil lafasadatil ard(u) wa-laakinnal laaha zoo fadlin 'alal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 252,
      "text":
          "Tilka Aayaatul laahi natloohaa 'alaika bilhaqq,(i) wa-innaka laminal mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 253,
      "text":
          "^Tilkar Rusulu faddalnaa ba'dahum 'alaa ba'd. minhum man kallamal laah(u); wa-rafa'a ba'dahum darajaat,(in) wa-aatainaa 'Eesab na Maryamal baiyinaati wa-ayyadnaahu bi-Roohil Qudus:(i) wa-law shaaa'al laahu maq tatalal lazeena mim ba'dihim mim ba'di maa jaaa'athumul baiyinaat(u) wa-laakinikh talafoo faminhum man aamana wa-minhum man kafar,(a) wa-law shaaa'al laahu maq tataloo wa-laakinnal laaha yaf'alu maa yureed"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 254,
      "text":
          "Yaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo anfiqoo mimmaa razaq-naakum min qabli aien ya`atiya yawmul laa bai'un feehee wa-la khullatunw wa-laa shafaa'ah:(tun) wal-kaafiroona humuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 255,
      "text":
          "Allahu laaa ilaaha illaa Huwal Haiyul Qaiyoom,(u) laa taakhuzuhoo sinatunw wa-laa nawm,(un) lahoo maa fis samaawaati wa-maa fil ard:(i) man zal lazee yashfa'u indahooo illaa bi-iznih,(i) ya'lamu maa baina aydeehim wa-maa khalfahum; wa-laa yuheetoona bishai'im min 'ilmihee illaa bimaa shaaa',(a) wasi'a Kursiyyuhus samaawaati wal-ard(a); wa-laa Ya'ooduhoo hifzuhum,(aa) wa-Huwal Aliyyul 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 256,
      "text":
          "Laaa ikraaha fid deen(i); qadt tabiyanar rushdu minal ghayy,(i) famai yakfur bit-Taaghooti wa-yu'mim billaahi faqadis tamsaka bil'urwatil wusqaa lan fisaama lah:(aa) wallaahu Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 257,
      "text":
          "Allaahu waliyyul lazeena aamanoo yukhrijuhum minaz zulumaati ilan noor(i); wallazeena kafarooo awliyaaa'uhumut Taaghootu yukhrijoo-nahum minan noori ilaz zulumaat:(i) ulaaa'ika As-haabun Naar(i); hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 258,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilal lazee Haaajja Ibraaheema fee Rabbiheee an aataahul laahul mulka iz qaala Ibraaheemu Rabbiyal lazee yuhyee wa-yumeetu qaala ana uhyee wa-umeet(u); qaala Ibraaheemu fa-innal laaha yaatee bishshamsi minal mashriqi faati bihaa minal maghribi fabuhital lazee kafar:(a) wallaahu laa yahdil qawmaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 259,
      "text":
          "Aw kallazee marra 'alaa qaryatinw wa-hiya khaawiyatun 'alaa 'urooshihaa qaala annaa yuhyee haazihil laahu ba'da mawtih(aa); fa-amaatahul laahu mi'ata 'aamin summa ba'a-sah(oo); qaala kam labist(a); qaala labistu yawman aw ba'da yawm(in); qaala bal labista mi'ata 'aamin fanzur ilaa ta'aamika wa-sharaabika lam yatasannah; wanzur ilaa himaarika wa-linaj'alaka Aayatal linnaas(i); wanzur ilal 'izaami kaifa nunshizuhaa summa naksoohaa lahmaa,(n) falammaa tabaiyyana lahoo qaala a'lamu annal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 260,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaala Ibraaheemu Rabbi arinee kaifa tuhyil mawtaa; qaala awa-lam tu'min; qaala balaa wa-laakil liyatma'inna qalbee; qaala fakhuz arab'atam minat tairi fasurhunna ilaika summaj 'al a'alaa kulli jabalim minhunna juz'a(n) summad'uu hunna ya`ateenaka sa'yaa,(n) wa'lam annal laaha 'Azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 261,
      "text":
          "Masalul lazeena yunfiqoona amwaalahum fee sabeelil laahi kamasali habbatin ambatat sab'a sanaabil(a) fee kulli sumbulatim mi'atu habbah:(tin) wallaahu yudaa'ifu limaien yashaaa:(oo) wallaahu Waasi'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 262,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yunfiqoona amwaalahum fee sabeelil laahi summa laa yutbi'oona maaa anfaqoo mann-anw wa-laaa azal lahum ajruhum 'inda Rabbihim; wa-laa khawfun 'alaihim wa-laa hum yahzanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 263,
      "text":
          "^Qawlum ma'roofunw wa-maghfiratun khairum min sadaqatien yatba'uhaaa azaa: wallaahu Ghaniyyun Haleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 264,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tubtiloo sadaqaatikum bilmanni wal-azaa kallazee yunfiqu maa-lahoo ri'aaa'an naasi wa-laa yu'minu billaahi wal-yawmil aakhir(i); fama-saluhoo kamasali safwaanin 'alaihi turaabun fa-asaabahoo waabilun fatara-kahoo saldaa(l); laa yaqdiroona 'alaa shai'im mimmaa kasaboo: wallaahu laa yahdil qawmal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 265,
      "text":
          "Wa-masalul lazeena yunfiqoona amwaalahu mubtighaaa'a mardaatil laahi wa-tasbeetam min anfusihim kamasali jannatim birabwatin asaa-bahaa waabilun fa-aatat ukulahaa di'faini fa-il lam yusibhaa waabilun fatal:(lun) wallaahu bimaa ta'maloona Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 266,
      "text":
          "Ayawaddu ahadukum an takoona lahoo jannatum min nakheelinw wa-a'naabin tajree min tahtihal anhaar(u) lahoo feehaa min kullis samaraati wa-asaa-bahul kibaru wa-lahoo zurriyyatun du'afaaa'(u) fa-asaabahaaa i'saarun feehi naarun fahtaraqat: kazaalika yubaiyinul laahu lakumul aayaati la'allakum tata-fakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 267,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-'ayyuhal lazeena aamanooo anfiqoo min taiyibaati maa kasabtum wa-mimmaaa akhrajna lakum minal ard(i); wa-laa tayammamul khabeesa minhu tunfiqoon(a) wa-lastum bi-aakhizeehi illaaa an tughmidoo feeh,(i) wa'lamooo annal laaha Ghaniyyun Hameed"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 268,
      "text":
          "Ash-Shaitaanu ya'idukumul faqra wa-ya'murukum bil-fahshaaa('i); wallaahu ya'idukum maghfiratam minhu wa-fadlaa:(n) wallaahu Waasi'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 269,
      "text":
          "Yu'til Hikmata maien yashaaa,('oo); wa-maien yu'tal Hikmata faqad ootiya khairan kaseeraa:(n) wa-maa yazzakkaru illaaa ulul albaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 270,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa anfaqtum min nafaqatin aw nazartum min nazrin fa-innal laaha ya'lamuh:(u) wa-maa liz-zaalimeena min ansaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 271,
      "text":
          "In tubdus sadaqaati fani'immaa hi(ya); wa-in tukhfoohaa wa-tu'toohal fuqaraaa'a fahuwa khayrul lakum, wa-yukaffiru 'ankum min saiyi-aatikum: wallaahu bimaa ta'maloona Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 272,
      "text":
          "^Laisa 'alaika hudaahum wa-laakinnal laaha yahdee maien yashaaa:('oo) wa-maa tunfiqoo min khairin fali-anfusikum, wa-maa tunfiqoona illab tighaaa'a wajhil laah,(i) wa-maa tunfiqoo min khairien yuwaffa ilaikum wa-antum laa tuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 273,
      "text":
          "Lil-fuqaraaa'il lazeena uh-siroo fee sabeelil laahi laa yastatee'oona darban fil ard(i)-yah sabuhumul jaahilu aghniyaaa'a minat ta'affufi ta'rifuhum biseemaahum laa yas'aloonan naasa ilhaafaa:(n) wa-maa tunfiqoo min khairin fa-innal laaha bihee 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 274,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yunfiqoona amwaalahum billaili wan-nahaari sirranw wa-'alaaniyatan falahum ajruhum 'inda Rabbihim wa-laa khawfun 'alaihim wa-laa hum yahzanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 275,
      "text":
          "Allazeena ya`akuloo`nar ribaa laa yaqoomoona illaa kamaa yaqoomul lazee yatakhabba-tuhush shaitaanu minal mass,(i) zaalika bi-annahum qaalooo innamal bai'u mislur ribaa: wa-ahallal laahul bai'a wa-harramar ribaa, faman jaaa'ahoo maw'izatum mir rabbihee fantahaa falahoo maa salafa wa-amruhooo ilal laah(i); wa-man 'aada fa-ulaaa-'ika As-haabun naar(i); hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 276,
      "text":
          "Yamhaqul laahur ribaa wa-yurbis sadaqaat:(i) wallaahu laa yuhibbu kulla kaffaarin aseem"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 277,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo wa-amilus saalihaati wa-aqaamus salaata wa-aata-wuz zakaata lahum ajruhum 'inda rabbihim wa-laa khawfun 'alaihim wa-laa hum yahzanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 278,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanut taqul laaha wa-zaroo maa baqiya minar ribaaa in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 279,
      "text":
          "Fa-il lam taf'aloo faa-zanoo biharbim minal laahi wa-Rasoolih(ee); wa-in tubtum falakum ru'oosu amwaalikum laa tazlimoona wa-laa tuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 280,
      "text":
          "Wa-in kaana zoo 'usratin fa-naziratun ilaa maisarah,(tinw) wa-an tasaddaqoo khairul lakum; in kuntum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 281,
      "text":
          "Wattaqoo yawman turja'oona feehi ilal laah(i); summa tuwaffaa kullu nafsim maa kasabat wa-hum laa yuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 282,
      "text":
          "Yaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo izaa tadaayantum bidaiynin ilaa ajalim musamman faktubooh,(u) walyaktub bainakum kaatibum bil'adl,(i) wa-laa yaaba kaatibun aien yaktuba kamaa 'allamahul laah,(u) falyaktub walyum-li-lil lazee 'alaihil haqqu walyattaqil laaha rabbah(oo) wa-laa yabkhas minhu shai'aa,(n) fa-in kaanal lazee 'alaihil haqqu safeehan aw da'eefan aw laa yastatee'u aien yumilla huwa falyumlil waliyyuhoo bil'adl,(i) wastash-hidoo shaheedaini mir rijaalikum; fa-il lam yakoonaa rajulaini farajulunw wamra-ataani mimman tardawna minash shuhadaaa'i an tadilla ihdaahumaa fatuzakkira ihdaahumal ukhraa, wa-laa yaabash shuhadaaa'u izaa maa du'oo, wa-laa tas'amooo an taktuboohu sagheeran aw kabeeran ilaaa ajalih,(i) zaalikum aqsatu 'indal laahi wa-aqwamu lish-shahaadati wa-adnaaa allaa tartaabooo; illaaa an takoona tijaaratan haadiratan tudeeroonahaa bainakum falaisa 'alaikum junaahun allaa taktuboo:(ha) wa-ash-hidooo izaa tabaaya'tum, wa-laa yudaaarra kaatibunw wa-laa shaheed,(un) wa-in taf'aloo fa-innahoo fusooqum bikum: wattaqul laah(a); wa-yu'allimu-kumul laah:(u) wallaahu bikulli shai'in 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 283,
      "text":
          "^Wa-in kuntum 'alaa safarinw wa-lam tajidoo kaatiban fari-haanum maqbooda(tun); fa-in amina ba'dukum ba'dan falyu'addil lazi tumina amaa-natahoo wal-yattaqil laaha Rabbah:(u) wa-laa taktumush shahaadah,(ta) wa-maien yaktumhaa fa-innahooo aasimun qalbuh:(u) wallaahu bimaa ta'maloona 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 284,
      "text":
          "Lillaahi maa fis samaawaati wa-maa fil ard:(i) wa-in tubdoo maa feee anfusikum aw tukhfoohu yuhaasibkum bihil laah(u); fayaghfiru li-maien yashaaa'u wa-yu'azzibu maien yashaaa:(oo) wallaahu 'alaa kulli shai-in qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 285,
      "text":
          "Aamanar Rasoolu bimaaa unzila ilaihi mir Rabbihee walmu'minoon,(a) kullun aamana billaahi wa-Malaaa'ikathihee wa-Kutubhihee wa-Rusulihee laa nufarriqu baina ahadim mir Rusulih,(i) wa-qaaloo sami'naa wa-ata'naa; ghufraanaka Rabbanaa wa-ilaikal maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "sura": 2,
      "aya": 286,
      "text":
          "Laa yukalliful laahu nafsan illaa wus'ahaa, lahaa maa kasabat wa'alaihaa mak tasabat: Rabbanaa laa tu'aakhiznaaa in naseenaaa aw akhta`naa, Rabbanaa wa-laa tahmil 'alainaaa isran kamaa hamaltahoo 'alal lazeena min qablinaa, Rabbanaa wa-laa tuhammilnaa maa laa taaqata lanaa bih(i); wa'fu 'annaa waghfir lanaa warhamnaa, Anta mawlaanaa fansurnaa 'alal qawmil kaafireen"
    },
    {"index": 294, "sura": 3, "aya": 1, "text": "Alif-Laam-Meeem"},
    {
      "index": 295,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Allaahu laaa ilaaha illaa Huwal Haiyul Qaiyoom"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Nazzala 'alaikal Kitaaba bilhaqqi musaddiqal limaa baina yadaihi wa-anzalat Tawraata wal-Injeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Min qablu hudal linnaasi wa-anzalal Furqaan:(a) innal lazeena kafaroo bi-Aayaatil laahi lahum 'azaabun shadeed:(unw) wallaahu 'azeezun zun tiqaam"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha laa yakhfaa 'alaihi shai'un fil ardi wa-laa fis samaaa'"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazee yusawwi-rukum fil arhaami kaifa yashaaa,('oo) laa ilaaha illaa Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazeee anzala 'alaikal Kitaaba minhu Aayaatum Muh-kamaatun hunna Ummul Kitaabi wa-ukharu Muta-shaabihaat(un); fa-ammal lazeena fee quloobihim zaiyghun fa-yattabi'oona ma tashaa-baha minhub tighaaa 'alfitnati wabtighaaa'a ta`weelih:(i) wa-maa ya'lamu ta`wee-lahooo illal laah:(u) war-raasi-khoona fil 'ilmi yaqooloona aamannaa bihee kullum min 'indi Rabbinaa: wa-maa yazzakkaru illaaa ulul albaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaa laa tuzigh quloobanaa ba'da iz hadaitanaa wa-hab lanaa mil ladunka rahmah,(tan) innaka antal Wahhaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaaa innaka jaami 'un-naasi li-Yawmil laa raiba feeh,(i) innal laaha laa yukhliful mee'aad"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo lan tughniya 'anhum am-waaluhum wa-laaa aw-laaduhum minal laahi shai'a(nw); wa-ulaaa'ika hum waqoodun Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Kada`abi Aali Fir'awna wallazeena min qablihim, kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa fa-akhaza-humul laahu bi-zunoo-bihim: wallaahu shadeedul 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Qul lillazeena kafaroo satugh-laboona wa-tuh`sharoona ilaa jahannam,(a) wa-bi'sal mihaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Qad kaana lakum Aayatun fee fi'atainil taqat(aa); fi'atun tuqaatilu fee sabeelil laahi wa-ukhraa kaafiratuien yaraw`nahum mis`laihim ra`ayal 'ayn,(i) wallaahu yu'ayyidu bi-nasrihee maien yashaaa':(u) innaa fee zaalika la-'ibratal li-ulil absaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Zuyyina linnaasi hubbush shahawaati minan nisaaa'i wal-baneena wal-qanaa-teeril muqan-tarati minaz zahabi wal-fiddati wal-khailil musaw-wamati wal-an'aami walhars:(i) zaalika mataa'ul hayaatid dunyaa; wallaahu 'indahoo husnul ma-aab"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "^Qul a'unabbi-'ukum bikhairim min zaalikum, lil-lazeenat taqaw 'inda Rabbihim jannaatun tajree min tah-tihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaa wa-azwaajum mutah-haratunw wa-ridwaanum minal laah:(i) wallaahu baseerum bil'ibaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yaqooloona Rabbanaaa innanaaa aamannaa faghfir lanaa zunoobanaa wa-qinaa 'azaaban Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Assaabireena wassaa-diqeena walqaaniteena walmunfiqeena walmus-taghfireena bil-as-haar"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Shahidal laahu annahoo laa ilaaha illaa Huwa wal-malaaa'ikatu wa-ulul 'ilmi qaaa'imam bilqist; laaa ilaaha illaa Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Innad deena 'indal laahil Islaam;(u) wamakh talafal lazeena ootul Kitaaba illaa mim ba'di maa jaaa'ahumul 'ilmu baghyam bainahum: wa-mai yakfur bi-Aayaatil laahi fa-innal laaha saree'ul hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Fa-in haaaj-jooka faqul aslamtu wajhiya lillaahi wa-manit taba'an:(i) wa-qul lillazeena ootul Kitaaba wal-ummiyyeena 'a-aslamtum, fa-in aslamoo faqadih tadaw; wa-in tawallaw fa-innamaa 'alaikal balaagh:(u) wallaahu baseerum bil-'ibaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yakfuroona bi-Aayaatil laahi wa-yaqtuloonan Nabiyyeena bighairi haqqinw wa-yaqtuloonal lazeena yaa`muroona bilqisti minan naasi fabash-shirhum bi'azaabin aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena habitat a'maaluhum fid dunyaa wal-Aaakhirah(ti) wa-maa lahum min naasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilal lazeena ootoo naseebam minal Kitaabi yud'awna ilaa Kitaabil laahi liyah-kuma bai-nahum summa yata-wallaa fareequm minhum wa-hum mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bi-annahum qaaloo lan tamassanan naaru illaaa ayyaamam ma'doodaat(inw); wa-gharrahum fee deenihim maa kaanoo yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Fa-kaifa izaa jama'naahum li-Yawmil laa raiba fee wa-wuffiyat kullu nafsim maa kasabat wa-hum laa yuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Qulil laahumma Maalikal Mulki tu'til mulka man tashaaa'u wa-tanzi'ul mulka mimman tashhaaa'u wa-tu'izzu man tashaaa'u wa-tuzillu man tashaaa'(u); biyadikal khair(u); innaka 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Toolijul laila fin nahaari wa-toolijun nahaara fil lail(i); wa-tukhrijul haiya minal maiy-yiti wa-tukhrijul maiy-yita minal haiy(yi); wa-tarzuqu man tashaaa'u bighari hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Laa yatta-khizil mu'minoonal kaafireena awliyaaa'a min doonil mu'mineen(a); wa-maien yaf'al zaalika falaisa minal laahi fee shai'in illaaa an tat-taqoo minhum tuqaah:(tan) wa-yuhazzi-rukumul laahu nafsah:(u) wa-ilal laahil maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Qul in tukhfoo maa fee sudoorikum aw tubdoohu ya'lamhul laah:(u) wa-ya'lamu maa fis samaawaati wa-maa fil ard:(i) wallaahu 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Yawma tajidu kullu nafsim maa 'amilat min khairim muh-dara(nw) wa-maa 'amilat min sooo'in tawaddu law anna baina-haa wa-baina-hooo amadam ba'eedaa:(an) wa-yuhazzi-rukumul laahu nafsah:(u) wallaahu ra'oofum bil'ibaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Qul in kuntum tuhib-boonal laaha fattabi'-oonee yuh`bib-kumul laahu wa-yaghfir lakum zunoobakum: wallaahu Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Qul atee'ul laaha war-Rasool(a); fa-in tawallaw fa-innal laaha laa yuhibbul kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "^Innal laahas tafaaa Aadama wa-Noohanw wa-Aala Ibraaheema wa-Aala Imraana 'alal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 34,
      "text": "Zurriyyatam ba'duhaa mim ba'd:(inw) wallaahu Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Iz qaalat im'ra-atu 'Imraana Rabbi innee nazartu laka maa fee batnee muhar-ra-ra(n) fataqabbal min(nee); innaka Antas Samee'ul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Fa-lammaa wada'at-haa qaalat Rabbi innee wada'tuhaaa unsaa wallaahu a'lamu bimaa wada'at wa-laisaz zakaru kalunsaa; wa-innee sammai-tuhaa Maryama wa-innee u'eezuhaa bika wa-zurriy-yatahaa minash Shaitaanir Rajeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Fata-qabba-lahaa Rabbuhaa biqaboolin hasaninw wa-ambatahaa nabaatan hasananw wa-kaffalahaa Zakariyyaa; kullamaa dakhala 'alaihaa Zakariyyal Mihraaba wajada 'indahaa rizqa(n); qaala yaa-Maryamu annaa laki haazaa; qaalat huwa min 'indil laah(i); innal laaha yarzuqu maien yashaaa'u bighairi hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Hunaaa-lika da'aa Zakariyyaa Rabbah(oo); qaala Rabbi hab lee mil ladunka zurriyyatan taiyiba(tan); innaka samee'ud du'aaa'"
    },
    {
      "index": 332,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Fanaadat-hul malaaa'ikatu wa-huwa qaaa'ee-muien yusallee fil Mihraabi annal laaha yubash-shiruka bi-Yahyaa musaddiqam bi-Kalimatim minal laah(i) wa-saiyidanw wa-hasooranw wa-Nabiyyam minas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 333,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbi annaa yakoonu lee ghulaamunw wa-qad bala-gha-niyal kibaru wam-raatee 'aaqir(un); qaala kazaa-likal laahu yaf'alu maa yashaaa'"
    },
    {
      "index": 334,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbij 'al leee Aayah(tan); qaala Aaayatuka allaa tukalliman naasa salaasata ayyaamin illa ramzaa:(an) wazkur Rabbaka kaseeranw wa-sabbih bil'ashiyyi wal-ib-kaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 335,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaa-latil malaaa'ikatu yaa-Maryamu innal laahas tafaaki wa-tah-haraki wastafaaki 'alaa nisaaa'il 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 336,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Yaa-Maryamu uq-nutee li-Rabbiki wasjudee warka'ee ma'ar raaki'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 337,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Zaalika min ambaaa'il ghaibi noo-heehi ilaik,(a) wa-maa kunta ladai`him iz yulqoona aq`laamahum ayyuhum yak-fulu Maryama wa-maa kunta ladai-him iz yakh-tasimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 338,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Iz qaa-latil malaaa'ikatu yaa-Maryamu innal laaha yubash-shiruki bi-Kalimatim minhus muhul Maseehu 'Eesab nu Maryama wajeehan fid dunyaa wal-Aakhirati wa-minal muqar-rabeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 339,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 46,
      "text": "Wa-yukallimun naasa fil mahdi wa-kahlanw wa-minas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 340,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Qaalat Rabbi annaa yakoonu lee waladunw wa-lam yamsa-snee bashar(un); qaala kazaa-likil laahu yakhluqu maa yashaaa',(oo) izaa qadaaa amran fa-innamaa yaqoolu lahoo kun fayakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 341,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 48,
      "text": "Wa-yu'allimuhul Kitaaba wal-Hikmata wat-Tawraata wal-Injeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 342,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Wa-Rasoolan ilaa Baneee Israaa'eela annee qad ji'tukum bi-Aayatim mir Rabbikum; annee akhluqu lakum minat teeni kahai'atit tairi fa-anfukhu feehi fayakoonu tairam bi-iznil laah(i); wa-ubri'ul akmaha wal-abrasa wa-uhyil mawtaa bi-iznil laah(i); wa-unabbi'ukum bimaa taa`kuloona wa-maa tadda-khiroona fee buyootikum, inna fee zaalika la-Aayatal lakum in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 343,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa-musaddiqal limaa baina yadaiy-yaa minat Tawraati wa-li-uhilla lakum ba'dal lazee hurrima 'alaikum, wa-ji'tukum bi-Aayatim mir Rabbikum fattaqul laaha wa-atee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 344,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha Rabbee wa-Rabbukum fa'budooh:(u) haazaa Siraatum Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 345,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "^Fa-lammaaa ahassa 'Eesaa min-humul kufra qaala man ansaaree ilal laah(i); qaalal Hawaariy-yoona nahnu ansaarul laahi aamannaa billaahi wash-had bi-annaa muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 346,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaaa aamannaa bimaaa anzalta wattaba'nar Rasoola faktubnaa ma'ash shaahideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 347,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 54,
      "text": "Wa-makaroo wa-makaral laah(u); wallaahu khairul maakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 348,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Iz qaalal laahu yaa-'Eesaaa innee mutawaffeeka wa-raafi'uka ilaiya wa-mutah-hiruka minal lazeena kafaroo wa-jaa'ilul lazeenat taba-ooka fawqal lazeena kafarooo ilaa Yawmil Qiyaama(ti); summa ilaiya marji'ukum fa-ahkumu bainakum feemaa kuntum feehi takh-taliifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 349,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Fa-ammal lazeena kafaroo fa-u'az-zibuhum 'azaaban shadeedan fid dunyaa wal-Aakhira(ti) wa-maa lahum min naasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 350,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Wa-ammal lazeena aamanoo wa-'amilus saalihaati fa-yuwaf-feehim ujoorahum: wallaahu laa yuhibbuz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 351,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 58,
      "text": "Zaalika natloohu 'alaika minal Aayaati wa-Zikril Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 352,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Inna masala 'Eesaa 'indal laahi kamasali Aadam(a); khala-qahoo min turaabin summa qaala lahoo kun fayakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 353,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 60,
      "text": "Alhaqqu mir Rabbika falaa takum minal mumtareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 354,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Faman haaaj-jaka feehi mim ba'di maa jaaa'aka minal 'ilmi faqul ta'aalaw nad'u abnaaa'anaa wa-abnaaa'akum wa-nisaaa'anaa wa-nisaaa'akum wa-anfusanaa wa-anfusakum summa nabtahil fanaj'al la'natal laahi 'alal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 355,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Innaa haazaa lahuwal qasasul haqq,(u) wa-maa min ilaahin illal laah,(u) wa-innal laahaa la-Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 356,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 63,
      "text": "Fa-in tawallau fa-innal laaha 'aleemun bil-mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 357,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Qul yaa-Ahlal Kitaabi ta'aalau ilaa Kalimatin sawaaa'im bainanaa wa-bainakum allaa na'buda illal laaha wa-laa nushrika bihee shai'anw wa-laa yat-takhiza ba'dunaa ba'dan arbaabam min doonil laah,(i) fa-in tawallau faqoo-lush hadoo bi-annaa muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 358,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-Ahlal Kitaabi limaa tuhaaaj-joona feee Ibraaheema wa-maaa unzilatit Tawraatu wal-Injeelu illaa mim ba'dih,(ee) afala ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 359,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Haaa-antum haaa'ulaaa'i haa-jajtum feemaa lakum bihee 'ilmun falima tuhaaaj-joonaa feemaa laisa lakum bihee 'ilm,(un) wal-laahu ya'lamu wa-antum laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 360,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Maa kaana Ibraaheemu Yahoodiy-yanw wa-laa Nasraa-niyyanw wa-laakin kaana Haneefam Muslima(nw) wa-maa kaana minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 361,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Innaa awlan naasi bi-Ibraaheema lallazeenat taba-'oohu wa-haazan nabiyyu wallazeena aamanoo: wallaahu waliyyul mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 362,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Waddat taaa'ifatum min Ahlil Kitaabi lau yudil-loonakum wa-maa yudilloona illaaa anfusa-hum wa-maa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 363,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-Ahlal Kitaabi lima takfuroona bi-Aayaatil laahi wan-antum tashadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 364,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-Ahalal Kitaabi lima talbisoonal haqqa bilbaatili wa-taktumoonal haqqa wa-antum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 365,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalat taaa'ifatum min Ahlil Kitaabi aaminoo billazeee unzila 'alal lazeena aamanoo waj-han nahaari wak-furooo aakhirahoo la'alla-hum yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 366,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tu'minooo illaa liman tabi'a deenakum qul innal hudaa hudal laahi aien yu'taaa ahadum misla maaa ooteetum auw yuhaaaj-jookum 'inda Rabbikum: qul innal fadla biyadil laahi yu`teehi maien yashaaa':(u) wal-laahu Waasi'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 367,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Yakhtassu birahmatihee maien yashaaa':(u) wal-laahu zul fadlil 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 368,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "^Wa-min Ahlil Kitaabi man in taa`manhu biqintaarien yu'addihee ilaika wa-minhum man in taamanhu bideenaaril laa yu'addiheee ilaika illaa maa dumta 'alaihi qaaa'ima:(n) zaalika bi-annahum qaaloo laisa 'alainaa fil ummiyyeena sabeel(unw) Wa-yaqooloona 'alal laahil kaziba wa-hum ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 369,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Balaa man awfaa bi'ahdihee wattaqaa fa-innal laaha yuhibbul muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 370,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yashtaroona bi'ahdil laahi wa-aymaanihim samanan qaleelan ulaaa'ika laa khalaaqa lahum fil Aakhirati wa-laa yukallimu-humul laahu wa-laa yanzuru ilaihim Yawmal Qiyaamati wa-laa yuzakkeehim wa-lahum 'azabun 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 371,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Wa-inna minhum lafaree qaien yalwoona alsinatahum bil Kitaabi litah-saboohu minal Kitaab, Wa-maa huwa minal Kitaabi Wa-yaqooloona huwa min 'indillaahi Wa-maa huwa min 'indillaah(i) Wa-yaqooloona 'alal laahil kaziba Wa-hum ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 372,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Maa kaana li-basharin aien yu'tiyahul laahul Kitaaba walhukma wan-Nubuwwata summa yaqoola linnaasi koonoo 'ibaadal lee min doonil laahi Wa-laakin koonoo rabbaaniyeena bimaa kuntum tu'allimoonal Kitaaba Wa-bimaa kuntum tadrusoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 373,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa ya`murakum an tat-takhizul malaaa-'ikata wan-Nabiyyeena arbaaba:(n) a`yaamurukum bilkufri ba'da iz antum muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 374,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz akhazal laahu meesaaqan Nabiyyeena lamaaa aataitukum min Kitaabinw Wa-Hikmatin summa jaaa'akum Rasoolum musaddiqul limaa ma'akum latu'minunna bihee Wala-tan-surunnah,(u) qaala 'aaqrartum Wa-akhaztum alaa zaalikum isree; qaalooo aqrarnaa, qaala fashhadoo Wa-ana ma'akum minash shaahideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 375,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 82,
      "text": "Faman tawallaa ba'da zaalika fa-ulaaa'ika humul faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 376,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Afaghaira deenil laahi yab-ghoona Wa-lahooo aslama man fis samaawaati wal-ardi taw'anw Wa-karhanw Wa-ilaihi yurja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 377,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Qul aamannaa billaahi Wa-maaa unzila 'alainaa Wa-maaa unzila 'alaaa Ibraaheema Wa-Ismaa'eela Wa-Iss-haaqa Wa-Ya'qooba wal-Asbaati Wa-maaa ootiya Moosaa Wa-'Eesaa wan-Nabiyyoona mir Rabbihim laa nufarriqu baina ahadim minhum Wa-nahnu lahoo muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 378,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yabtaghi ghairal Islaami deenan falaien yuqbala minhu Wa-huwa fil Aakhirati minal khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 379,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Kaifa yahdil laahu qawman kafaroo ba'da eemaanihim Wa-shahidooo annar Rasoola haqqunw Wa-jaaa'ahumul baiyinaat,(u) wal-laahu laa yahdil qawmaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 380,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika jazaaa'uhum anna 'alaihim la'natal laahi walmalaaa'ikati wannaasi ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 381,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Khaalideena feehaa laa yukhaffafu 'anhumul 'azaabu Wa-laa hum yunzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 382,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Illal lazeena taaboo mim ba'di zaalika Wa-aslahoo fa-innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 383,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo ba'da eemaanihim summaz daadoo kufral lan tuqbala tawbatuhum Wa-ulaaa'ika humud daaalloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 384,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo Wa-maatoo Wa-hum kuffaarun falaien yuqbala min ahadihim mil'ul ardi zahabanw Wa-la-wif tadaa bih:(ee) ulaaa'ika lahum 'azaabun aleemunw Wa-maa lahum min naasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 385,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Lan tanaalul birra hattaa tunfiqoo mimmaa tuhibboon,(a) Wa-maa tunfiqoo min shai'in fa-innal laaha bihee 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 386,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "^Kullut ta'aami kaana hillal li-Baneee Israaa'eela illaa maa harrama Israaa'eelu 'alaa nafsihee min qabli an tunazzalat Tawraah:(tu) qul faa`too bit-Tawraati fatloohaaa in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 387,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Famanif taraa 'alal laahil kaziba mim ba'di zaalika fa-ulaaa'ika humuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 388,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Qul sadaqal laah:(u) fattabi'oo Millata Ibraaheema Haneefanw Wa-maa kaana minal mush-rikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 389,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Inna awwala Baitinw wudi'a linnaasi lallazee bi-Bakkata mubaarakanw Wa-hudal lil-'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 390,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Feehi Aayaatum baiyinaatum Maqaamu Ibraaheem(a); Wa-man dakha-lahoo kaana aamina:(n) Wa-lillaahi 'alan naasi Hijjul Baiti manis tataa'a ilaihi sabeela,(n) Wa-man kafara fa-innal laaha ghaniyyun 'anil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 391,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Qul yaaa-Ahlal Kitaabi lima takfuroona bi-Aayaatil laahi wallaahu shaheedun 'alaa maa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 392,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Qul yaaa-Ahlal Kitaabi lima tasuddoona 'an sabeelil laahi man aamana tab-ghoo-nahaa 'iwajanw Wa-antum shuhadaaa':(u) Wa-mal laahu bighaafilin 'ammaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 393,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo in tutee'oo fareeqam minal lazeena ootul Kitaaba yaruddookum ba'da eemaanikum kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 394,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Wa-kaifa takfuroona Wa-antum tutlaa 'alaikum Aayaatul laahi Wa-feekum Rasooluh:(u) Wa-maien ya'tasim bil-laahi faqad hudiya ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 395,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanut taqul laaha haqqa tuqaatihee Wa-laa tamootunna illaa Wa-antum muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 396,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Wa'tasimoo bi-Hablil laahi jamee'anw Wa-laa tafarraqoo, wazkuroo ni'matal laahi alaikum iz kuntum a'daaa'an fa-allafa baina quloobikum fa-asbah-tum bini'matiheee ikhwaana(nw) Wa-kuntum 'alaa shafaa hufratim minan Naari fa-anqazakum minh:(a) kazaalika yubaiyinul laahu lakum aayaatihee la'allakum tahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 397,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Waltakum minkum ummatuien yad'oona ilal khairi Wa-ya'muroona bil-ma'roofi Wa-yan-hawna 'anil munkar,(i) Wa-ulaaa'ika humul muflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 398,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa takoonoo kallazeena tafarraqoo wakhtalafoo mim ba'di maa jaaa'ahumul baiyinaat,(u) Wa-ulaaa'ika lahum 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 399,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Yawma tabi-yaddu wujoohunw Wa-taswaddu wujooh,(un) fa-ammal lazeenas waddat wujoo-hum akafartum ba'da eemaanikum fazooqul 'azaaba bimaa kuntum takfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 400,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Wa-ammal lazeena bi-yaddat wujoohuhum fafee rahmatil laahi hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 401,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Tilka Aayaatul laahi natloohaa 'alaika bilhaqq:(i) Wa-mal laahu yureedu zulmal lil'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 402,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahi maa fis samaawaati Wa-maa fil ard:(i) Wa-ilal laahi turja'ul umoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 403,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Kuntum khaira ummatin ukhrijat linnaasi ta'muroona bilma'roofi Wa-tanhawna 'anil munkari Wa-tu'minoona billaah:(i) Wa-law aamana Ahlul Kitaabi lakaana khairal lahum, minhumul mu'minoona Wa-aksaru-humul faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 404,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Laien yadurrookum 'illaaa aza(nw); Wa-ien yuqaa-tilookum yuwal-lookumul adbaara summa laa yunsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 405,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "Duribat 'alaihimuz zillatu aina maa suqifooo illaa bihablim minal laahi Wa-hablim minan naasi Wa-baaa'oo bighadabim minal laahi Wa-duribat 'alaihimul maskanah,(tu) zaalika bi-annahum kaanoo yakfuroona bi-Aayaatil laahi Wa-yaqtuloonal Ambiyaaa'a bighairi haqq,(in) zaalika bimaa 'asaw Wa-kaanoo ya'tadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 406,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "^Laisoo sawaaa'a:(n) min Ahlil Kitaabi ummatun qaaa'ima-tuien yatloona Aayaatil laahi aanaaa'al laili Wa-hum yasjudoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 407,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 114,
      "text":
          "Yu'minoona billaahi wal-Yawmil Aakhiri Wa-ya'muroona bilma'roofi Wa-yanhawna 'anil munkari Wa-yusaari'oona fil khairaat(i) Wa-ulaaa'ika minas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 408,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa yaf'aloo min khairin falaien yukfarooh:(u) wal-laahu 'aleemun bil-muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 409,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo lan tughniya 'anhum amwaaluhum Wa-laaa awlaaduhum minal laahi shai'a(nw); Wa-ulaaa'ika As-haabun Naar,(i) hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 410,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Masalu maa yunfiqoona fee haazihil hayaatid dunyaa kamasali reehin feehaa sirrun asaabat harsa qawmin zalamooo anfusahum fa-ahlakath,(hu) Wa-maa zalamahumul laahu Wa-laakin anfusahum yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 411,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 118,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tat-takhizoo bitaa-natam min doonikum laa ya'loonakum khabaala(nw) waddoo maa 'anittum qad badatil baghdaaa'u min afwaahihim; Wa-maa tukhfee sudooruhum akbar,(u) qad baiyannaa lakumul Aayaat(i); in kuntum ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 412,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 119,
      "text":
          "Haaa-antum ulaaa'i tuhib-boonahum Wa-laa yuhib-boonakum Wa-tu'minoona bil-kitaabi kullihee Wa-izaa laqookum qaalooo aamannaa Wa-izaa khalaw 'addoo 'alaikumul anaa-mila minal ghaiz,(i) qul mootoo bighai-zikum: innal laaha 'aleemum bizaatis sudoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 413,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 120,
      "text":
          "In tamsaskum hasanatun tasu'hum Wa-in tusibkum saiyyi'a-tuien yafrahoo bih(aa); Wa-in tasbiroo Wa-tattaqoo laa yadurrukum kaiduhum shai'a:(n) innal laaha bimaa ya'maloona muheet"
    },
    {
      "index": 414,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 121,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz ghadawta min ahlika tubawwi'ul mu'mineena maqaa'ida lilqitaal:(i) wal-laahu samee'un 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 415,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 122,
      "text":
          "Iz hammat taaa'ifataani minkum an taf-shalaa wal-laahu waliyyuhum:(a) Wa-'alal laahi fal-yatawak-kalil mu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 416,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 123,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad nasarakumul laahu bi-Badrinw Wa-antum azilla(tun); fattaqul laaha la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 417,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 124,
      "text":
          "Iz taqoolu lil-mu'mineena alaien yakfiyakum aien yumiddakum Rabbukum bi-salaa-sati aalaafim minal malaaa'ikati munzaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 418,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 125,
      "text":
          "Balaaa, in tasbiroo Wa-tattaqoo Wa-ya'tookum min fawrihim haazaa yumdidkum Rabbukum bi-khamsati aalaafim minal malaaa'ikati musawwimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 419,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 126,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa ja'alahul laahu illaa bushraa lakum Wa-litatma'inna quloobukum bih:(i) Wa-man nasru illaa min 'indil laahil 'Azeezil Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 420,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 127,
      "text":
          "Liyaqta'a tarafam minal lazeena kafarooo auw yakbitahum fayan-qaliboo khaaa'ibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 421,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 128,
      "text":
          "Laisa laka minal amri shai'un auw yatooba 'alaihim auw yu'az-zi-bahum fa-innahum zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 422,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 129,
      "text":
          "Wa-lilaahi maa fis samaawaati Wa-maa fil ard,(i) yaghfiru limaien yashaaa'u Wa-yu'azzibu maien yashaaa',(u) wallaahu Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 423,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 130,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanoo la takulu ribaaa ad'aafam mudaa'afa(tanw); wattaqul laaha la'allakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 424,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 131,
      "text": "Wattaqun Naaral lateee u'iddat lilkaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 425,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 132,
      "text": "Wa-atee'ul laaha war-Rasoola la'allakum turhamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 426,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 133,
      "text":
          "^Wa-saari'ooo ilaa maghfiratim mir Rabbikum Wa-Jannatin ar-duhas samaawaatu wal-ardu u'iddat lilmuttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 427,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 134,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yunfiqoona fis sarraaa'i wad-darraaa'i wal-kaazimeenal ghaiza wal-aafeena 'anin naas:(i) wal-laahu yuhibbul muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 428,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 135,
      "text":
          "Wal-lazeena izaa fa'aloo faa-hishatan aw zalamooo anfusahum zakarul laaha fastagh-faroo li-zunoobihim; Wa-maien yaghfiruz zunooba illal laahu Wa-lam yusirroo 'alaa maa fa'aloo Wa-hum ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 429,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 136,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika jazaaa'uhum maghfiratum mir Rabbihim Wa-Jannaatun tajree min tah-tihal anhaaru khaalideena feeha, Wa-ni'ma ajrul 'aamileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 430,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 137,
      "text":
          "Qad khalat min qablikum sunann faseeroo fil ardi fanzuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqiba-tul mukazzibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 431,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 138,
      "text": "Haazaa bayaanul linnaasi Wa-hudanw Wa-maw'izatul lil-muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 432,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 139,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tahinoo Wa-laa tahzanoo Wa-antumul a'lawna in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 433,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 140,
      "text":
          "Iien yamsaskum qarhum faqad massal qawma qarhum misluh,(u) Wa-tilkal ayyaamu nudaa-wiluhaa bainan naasi Wa-liya'lamal laahul lazeena aamanoo Wa-yattakhiza minkum shuhadaaa:('a) wal-laahu laa yuh-ibbuz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 434,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 141,
      "text": "Wa-liyumah-hisal laahul lazeena aamanoo Wa-yamhaqal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 435,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 142,
      "text":
          "Am hasibtum an tadkhulul Jannnata Wa-lammaa ya'lamil laahul lazeena jaahadoo minkum Wa-ya'lamas saabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 436,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 143,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad kuntum tamann-nawnal mawta min qabli an tal-qawhu faqad ra-aitu-moohu Wa-antum tanzuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 437,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 144,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa Muhammadun illaa Rasoolun qad khalat min qablihir Rusul,(u) afa'im maata auw qutilan qalabtum 'alaaa a'qaabikum, Wa-maien yanqalib 'alaa aqibaihi falaien yadurral laaha shai'a:(n) Wa-sayajzil laahush shaakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 438,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 145,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana linafsin an tamoota illaa bi-iznil laahi kitaabam mu'ajjala:(n) Wa-maien yurid sawaabad dunyaa nu'tihee minhaa Wa-maien yurid sawaabal Aakhirati nu'tihee minhaa, Wa-sanaj-zish shaakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 439,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 146,
      "text":
          "Wa-ka-aiyim min Nabiyyin qaatala ma'ahoo ribbiy-yoona kaseerun famaa wahanoo limaaa Asaabahum fee sabeelil laahi Wa-maa da'ufoo Wa-mas takaanoo: wallaahu yuhibbus saabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 440,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 147,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana qawlahum illaa an qaaloo Rabbanagh fir lanaa zunoobanaa Wa-israafanaa feee amrinaa Wa-sabbit aqdaamanaa wansurnaa 'alal qawmil kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 441,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 148,
      "text":
          "Fa-aataahumul laahu sawaabad dunyaa Wa-husna sawaabil Aakhirah:(ti) wal-laahu yuhibbul muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 442,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 149,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-'aiyuhal lazeena aamanoo in tutee'ul lazeena kafaroo yarud-dookum 'alaaa a'qaabikum fatan-qaliboo khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 443,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 150,
      "text": "Balil laahu maw-laakum; Wa-Huwa khairun naasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 444,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 151,
      "text":
          "Sanulqee fee quloobil lazeena kafarur ru'ba bimaaa ashrakoo bil-laahi maa lam yunazzil bihee sultaana(nw); Wa-ma`wa-humun Naar,(u) Wa-bi'sa maswaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 445,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 152,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad sadaqakumul laahu wa'dahooo iz tahussoo-nahum bi-iznih(ee); hattaaa izaa fashiltum Wa-tanaaza'tum fil amri Wa-'asaitum mim ba'di maaa araakum maa tuhibboon,(a) minkum maien yureedud dunyaa Wa-minkum maien yureedul Aakhira(h),(ta) summa sarafakum 'anhum liyab-taliyakum; Wa-laqad 'afaa 'ankum: wal-laahu zoo fadlin 'alal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 446,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 153,
      "text":
          "^Iz tus'idoona Wa-laa talwoona 'alaaa ahadinw war-Rasoolu yad'ookum feee ukhraakum fa-asaabakum ghammam bighammil likailaa tahzanoo 'alaa maa faatakum Wa-laa maaa asaabakum: wal-laahu khabeerum bimaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 447,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 154,
      "text":
          "Summa anzala 'alaikum mim ba'dil ghammi amanatan nu'aasai yaghshaa taaa'-ifatam minkum; Wa-taaa'ifatun qad ahammat-hum an-fusuhum yazun-noona bil-laahi ghairal haqqi zannal jaahiliyya(ti); yaqooloona hal lanaa minal amri min shai':(in) qul innal amra kullahoo lillaah:(i) yukhfoona fee anfusihim maa laa yubdoona lak(a); yaqooloona law kaana lanaa minal amri shai'um maa qutilnaa haahun:(a) qul law kuntum fee buyootikum laba-razal lazeena kutiba 'alaihimul qatlu ilaa madaa-ji'ihim; Wa-liyab-taliyal laahu maa fee sudoorikum Wa-liyumah-hisa maa fee quloobikum: wallaahu 'aleemum bizaatis sudoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 448,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 155,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena tawallaw minkum yawmal taqal jam'aani innamas tazal-lahumush Shaitaanu biba'di maa kasaboo; Wa-laqad 'afal laahu 'anhum: innnal laaha Ghafoorun Haleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 449,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 156,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhul lazeena aamanoo laa takoonoo kallazeena kafaroo Wa-qaaloo li-ikhwaanihim izaa daraboo fil ardi auw kaanoo ghuzzal law kaanoo 'indanaa maa maatoo Wa-maa qutiloo liyaj'alal laahu zaalika hasratan fee quloobihim: wal-laahu yuhyee Wa-yumeet:(u) wallaahu bimaa ta'maloona Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 450,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 157,
      "text":
          "Wa-la'in qutiltum fee sabeelil laahi auw muttum la-maghfiratum minal laahi Wa-rahmatun khairum mimmaa yajma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 451,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 158,
      "text": "Wa-la'im muttum 'auw qutiltum la-ilal lahi tuhsharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 452,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 159,
      "text":
          "Fabimaa rahmatim minal laahi linta lahum; Wa-law kunta fazzan ghaleezal qalbi lan-faddoo min hawlik(a); fa'afu 'anhum wastaghfir lahum Wa-shaawir-hum fil amr(i); fa-izaa 'azamta fatawakkal 'alal laah,(i) innal laaha yuhibbul mutawak-kileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 453,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 160,
      "text":
          "Iien yansur-kumul laahu falaa ghaaliba lakum; Wa-ien yakh-zulkum faman zal lazee yan-surukum min ba'dih:(i) Wa-'alal laahi fal-yatawak-kalil mu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 454,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 161,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana li-Nabiyyin aien yaghull,(a) Wa-maien yaghlul ya'ti bimaa ghalla Yawmal Qiyaamah,(ti) summa tuwaffaa kullu nafsim maa kasabat Wa-hum laa yuz-lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 455,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 162,
      "text":
          "Afamanit taba'a Ridwaanal laahi kamam baaa'a bi-sakha-tim minal laahi Wa-ma'waahu Jahannam,(u) Wa-bi'sal maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 456,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 163,
      "text": "Hum darajaatun 'indal laah:(i) wallaahu baseerum bimaa ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 457,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 164,
      "text":
          "Laqad mannal laahu 'alal mu'mineena iz ba'asa feehim Rasoolam min an-fusihim yatloo 'alaihim Aayaa-tihee Wa-yuzak-keehim Wa-yu'allimu-humul Kitaaba wal-Hikma(ta) Wa-in kaanoo min qablu lafee dalaalim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 458,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 165,
      "text":
          "Awa-lammaaa asaa-batkum museebatun qad asabtum mislaihaa qultum annaa haazaa; qul huwa min 'indi anfusikum: innal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 459,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 166,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa asaabakum yawmal taqal jam'aani fabi-iznil laahi Wa-liya'lamal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 460,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 167,
      "text":
          "Wa-liya'lamal lazeena naafaqoo, Wa-qeela lahum ta'aalaw qaatiloo fee sabeelil laahi awid fa'oo; qaaloo law na'lamu qitaalal-lat taba'naakum: hum lilkufri yawma'izin aqrabu minhum lil-eemaan,(i) yaqooloona bi-afwaahi-him maa laisa fee quloobihim; wal-laahu a'lamu bimaa yaktumoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 461,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 168,
      "text":
          "Allazeena qaaloo li-ikhwaanihim Wa-qa'adoo law ataa'oonaa maa qutiloo: qul fadra'oo an anfusi-kumul mawta in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 462,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 169,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tahsabannal lazeena qutiloo fee sabeelil laahi amwaata,(m) bal ahyaaa'un 'inda Rabbihim yurzaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 463,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 170,
      "text":
          "Fari-heena bimaaa aataa-humul laahu min fadlihee Wa-yas-tabshiroona billazeena lam yalhaqoo bihim min khalfihim allaa khawfun 'alaihim Wa-laa hum yahzanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 464,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 171,
      "text":
          "^Yastabshiroona bini'matim minal laahi Wa-fad-linw Wa-annal laaha laa yudee'u ajral mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 465,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 172,
      "text":
          "Al-lazeenas tajaaboo lil-laahi war-Rasooli mim ba'di maaa asaa-bahumul qarh,(u) lil-lazeena ah-sanoo minhum wattaqaw ajrun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 466,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 173,
      "text":
          "Allazeena qaala lahumun naasu innan naasa qad jama'oo lakum fakh-shawhum fazaa-dahum emaana(nw) Wa-qaaloo hasbunal laahu Wa-ni'mal wakeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 467,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 174,
      "text":
          "Fan-qalaboo bini'matim minal laahi Wa-fadlil lam yam-sashum sooo'unw wattaba'oo rid-waanal laah:(i) wal-laahu zoo fadlin 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 468,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 175,
      "text":
          "In-namaa zaalikumush Shaitaanu yukhawwifu awliyaaa'ah(oo) falaa takhaa-foohum Wa-khaafooni in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 469,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 176,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yahzunkal lazeena yusaari'oona fil Kufr,(i) innahum laien yadurrul laaha shai'aa:(n) yureedul laahu allaa yaj'ala lahum hazzan fil Aakhira(ti); Wa-lahum 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 470,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 177,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeenash tarawul kufra bil-eemaani laien yadurrul laaha shai'anw Wa-lahum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 471,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 178,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yah-sabannal lazeena kafarooo annamaa numlee lahum khairulli an-fusihim, innamaa numlee lahum liyaz-daadooo isma,(nw) Wa-lahum 'azaabum muheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 472,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 179,
      "text":
          "Maa kaanal laahu liya-zaral mu'mineena 'alaa maaa antum 'alaihi hattaa yameezal khabeesa minat taiyyib:(i) Wa-maa kaanal laahu liyut-li'akum 'alal ghaib(i) Wa-laakinnal laaha yajtabee mir rusulihee maien yashaaa'(oo); fa-aaminoo billaahi Wa-Rusulih,(i) Wa-in tu-'minoo Wa-tattaqoo falakum ajrun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 473,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 180,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yah-sabannal lazeena yab-khaloona bimaa aataa-humul laahu min fadilhee huwa khairal lahum; bal huwa sharrul lahum; sayu-tawwa-qoona maa ba-khiloo bihee Yawmal Qiyaama(h):(ti) Wa-lillaahi meeraa-sus samaawaati wal-ard:(i) wal-laahu bimaa ta'maloona Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 474,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 181,
      "text":
          "Laqad sami'al laahu qawlal lazeena qaalooo innal laaha faqeerunw Wa-nahnu aghniyaaa'. Sanaktubu maa qaaloo Wa-qat-lahumul Ambiyaa'a bighairi haqq(inw) Wa-naqoolu zooqoo 'azaabal Hareeq"
    },
    {
      "index": 475,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 182,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bimaa qaddamat ai-deekum Wa-annal laaha laisa bi-zallaamil lil'abeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 476,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 183,
      "text":
          "Allazeena qaalooo innal laaha 'ahida ilainaaa allaa nu'mina li-Rasoolin hatta ya'tiyanaa biqurbaanin ta-kuluhun naar:(u) qul qad jaaa'akum Rusulum min qablee bil-baiyinaati Wa-billazee qultum falima qatal-tumoohum in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 477,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 184,
      "text":
          "Fa-in kaz-zabooka faqad kuz-ziba Rusulum min qablik(a) jaaa'oo bil-baiyinaati waz-Zuburi wal-Kitaabil Muneer"
    },
    {
      "index": 478,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 185,
      "text":
          "Kulu nafsin zaaa'iqatul mawt:(i) Wa-innamaa tuwaffawna ujoorakum Yawmal Qiyaama(ti); faman zuhziha 'anin Naari Wa-udkhilal Jannata faqad faaz:(a) Wa-mal hayaatud dunyaaa illaa mataa'ul ghuroor"
    },
    {
      "index": 479,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 186,
      "text":
          "^Latub-lawunna feee amwaalikum Wa-anfusikum Wa-latasma'unna minal lazeena ootul Kitaaba min qablikum Wa-minal lazeena ashrakooo azan kaseeraa,(n) Wa-in tasbiroo Wa-tattaqoo fa-inna zaalika min 'azmil umoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 480,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 187,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz akhazal laahu meesaa-qal lazeena ootul Kitaaba latu-baiyyi-nunna-hoo lin-naasi Wa-laa taktumoona(hoo- fanabazoohu waraaa'a zuhoorihim washtaraw bihee samanan qaleela(n); fabi'sa maa yashtaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 481,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 188,
      "text":
          "Laa tah-sabannal lazeena yaf-rahoona bimaaa ataw Wa-yuhibbona aien yuhmadoo bimaa lam yaf'aloo falaa tah-sa-bunnahum bima-faazatim minal 'azaab(i); Wa-lahum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 482,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 189,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahi mulkus samaawaati wal-ard:(i) wal-laahu 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 483,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 190,
      "text":
          "Inna fee khalqis samaawaati wal-ardi wakh-tilaafil laili wan-nahaari la-Aayaatil li-ulil albaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 484,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 191,
      "text":
          "Al-lazeena yaz-kuroonal laaha qiyaamanw wa-qu'oodanw wa-'alaa junoo-bihim Wa-yata-fakkaroona fee khalqis samaawaati wal-ard(i) Rabbanaa maa khalaqta haaza baatila(n) Subhaanaka faqinaa 'azaaban Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 485,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 192,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaaa innaka man tud-khilin Naara faqad akhzai-tah(oo); Wa-maa liz-zaalimeena min ansaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 486,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 193,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaaa innanaa sami'naa munaa-di-yaien yunaadee lil-eemaani an aaminoo bi-Rabbikum fa-aamannaa, Rabbanaa faghfir lanaa zunoobanaa Wa-kaffir 'annaa saiyi-aatina Wa-tawaffanaa ma'al abraar"
    },
    {
      "index": 487,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 194,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaa Wa-aatinaa maa wa'adt-tanaa 'alaa Rusulika Wa-laa tukhzinaa Yawmal Qiyaama(h):(ti) innaka laa tukhliful mee'aad"
    },
    {
      "index": 488,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 195,
      "text":
          "Fas-tajaaba lahum Rabbuhum annee laaa Udee'u 'amala 'aamilim minkum min zakarin aw unsaa; ba'dukum mim ba'd(in); fal-lazeena haajaroo Wa-ukhrijoo min diyaa-rihim Wa-oozoo fee sabeelee Wa-qaataloo Wa-qutiloo la-ukaf-firanna 'anhum saiyyi-aatihim Wa-la-ud-khilanna-hum Jannnatin tajree min tah-tihal anhaar(u) sawaabam min 'indil laah:(i) wal-laahu 'indahoo husnus sawaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 489,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 196,
      "text": "Laa yaghur-rannaka taqal-lubul lazeena kafaroo fil bilaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 490,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 197,
      "text": "Mataa'un qaleelun summa ma'waahum Jahannam,(u) Wa-bi'sal mihaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 491,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 198,
      "text":
          "Laakinil lazeenat taqaw Rabbahum lahum Jannnaatun tajree min tah-tihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaa nuzulam min 'indil laah:(i) Wa-maa 'indal laahi khairul lil-abraar"
    },
    {
      "index": 492,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 199,
      "text":
          "Wa-inna min Ahlil Kitaabi lamaien yu'minu billaahi Wa-maaa unzila ilaikum Wa-maaa unzila ilaihim khaashi'eena lillaahi laa yash-taroona bi-Aayaatil laahi samanan qaleelaa:(n) ulaaa'ika lahum ajruhum 'inda Rabbihim: innal laaha saree'ul hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 493,
      "sura": 3,
      "aya": 200,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanus biroo Wa-saabiroo Wa-raabitoo wattaqul laaha la'allakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 494,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhan naasut taqoo Rabbakumul lazee khalaqakum min nafsinw waahidatinw wa-khalaqa minhaa zawjahaa wa-bas-sa minhumaa rijaalan kaseeranw wa-nisaaa'aa; wattaqul laahal lazee tasaaa-'aloona bihee wal-arhaam; innal laaha kaana 'alaikum Raqeeba"
    },
    {
      "index": 495,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Wa-aatul yataamaaa amwaalahum wa-laa tatabad-dalul khabeesa bittaiyibi wa-laa taakulooo amwaalahum ilaaa amwaalikum; innahoo kaana hooban kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 496,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Wa-in khiftum allaa tuqsitoo fil yataamaa fankihoo maa taaba lakum minan nisaaa'i masnaa wa-sulaasa wa-rubaa'a fa'in khiftum allaa ta'diloo fawaahidatan aw maa malakat aimaanukum; zaalika adnaaa allaa ta'ooloo"
    },
    {
      "index": 497,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Wa-aatun nisaaa'a sadu-qaatihinna nihlah; fa-in tibna lakum 'an shai'im minhu nafsan fakuloohu hanee'am mareee'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 498,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tu'tus sufahaaa'a amwaalakumul latee ja'alal laahu lakum qiyaamanw warzuqoohum feehaa waksoohum wa-qooloo lahum qawlam ma'roofaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 499,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wabtalul yataamaa hattaaa izaa balaghun nikaaha fa-in aanastum minhum rushdan fad-fa'ooo ilaihim amwaalahum wa-laa taa-kuloohaaa israafanw wa-bidaaran ai yakbaroo; wa-mai kaana ghaniyyan falyasta'fif wa-mai kaana faqeeran falyaakul bilma'roof; fa-izaa dafa'tum ilaihim amwaalahum fa'ashhidoo 'alaihim; wa-kafaa billaahi Haseeba"
    },
    {
      "index": 500,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Lirrijaali naseebum mimmaa tarakal waalidaani wal-aqraboona wa-lin-nisaaa'i naseebum mimmaa tarakal waalidaani wal-aqraboona mimmaa qalla minhu aw kasur; naseebam mafroodaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 501,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa hadaral qismata ulul qurbaa walyataamaa walmasaakeenu farzuqoohum minhu wa-qooloo lahum qawlam ma'roofaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 502,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Walyakhshal lazeena law tarakoo min khalfihim zurriyyatan di'aafan khaafoo 'alaihim falyattaqul laaha walyaqooloo qawlan sadeedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 503,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yaakuloona amwaalal yataamaa zulman innamaa yaakuloona fee butoonihim Naaranw-wa sayaslawna sa'eeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 504,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Yooseekumul laahu fee awlaadikum liz-zakari mislu hazzil unsayayn(i); fa-in kunna nisaaa'an fawqas nataini falahunna sulusaa maa taraka wa-in kaanat waahidatan falahan nisf; wa-li-abawaihi likulli waahidim minhumas sudusu mimmma taraka in kaana lahoo walad; fa-il lam yakul lahu waladunw wa-warisahoo abawaahu fali-ummihis sulus; fa-in kaana lahoo ikhwatun fali-ummihis sudus; mim ba'di wasiyyatien yoosee bihaaa aw dayn; aabaaa'ukum wa-abnaaa'ukum laa tadroona ai-yuhum aqrabu lakum naf'aa; fareedatam minal laah; innal laaha kaana 'Aleeman Hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 505,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-lakum nisfu maa taraka azwaajukum il lam yakul lahunna walad; fa-in kaana lahunna waladun falakumur rubu'u mimmaa tarakna mim ba'di wasiyyatien yuseena bihaaa aw dayn; wa-lahunnar rubu'u mimmaa tarakum il lam yakul lakum walad; fa-in kaana lakum waladun falahunnas sumunu mimmaa taraktum; mim ba'di wasiyyatin toosoona bihaaa aw dayn; wa-in kaana raju-luin yoorasu kalaalatan awim ra-atunw wa-lahooo akhun aw ukhtun falikulli waahidim minhumas sudus; fa-in kaanooo aksara min zaalika fahum shurakaaa'u fis sulusi mim ba'di wasiyyatien yoosaa bihaaa aw dainin ghaira mudaaarr(in); wasiyyatam minal laah; wallaahu 'Aleemun Haleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 506,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Tilka hudoodul laah; wa-maien yuti'il laaha wa-Rasoolahoo yudkhilhu Jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaa; wa-zaalikal fawzul 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 507,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien ya'sil laaha wa-Rasoolahoo wa-yata'adda hudoodahoo yudkhilhu Naaran khaalidan feehaa wa-lahoo 'azaabum muheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 508,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wallaatee ya-teenal faahishata min nisaaa'ikum fastashhidoo 'alaihinna arba'atam minkum fa-in shahidoo fa-amsikoohunna fil buyooti hatta yatawaffaa-hunnal mawtu aw yaj'alal laahu lahunna sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 509,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wallazaani ya-tiyaanihaa minkum fa-aazoohumaa fa-in taabaa wa-aslahaa fa-a'ridoo 'anhumaaa; innal laaha kaana Tawwaabar Raheema"
    },
    {
      "index": 510,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Innamat tawbatu 'alallaahi lillazeena ya'maloonas sooo'a bijahaalatin summa yatooboona min qareebin faulaaika yatoobul laahu 'alaihim; wa kaanal laahu 'Aleeman Hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 511,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-laisatit tawbatu lillazeena ya'maloonas saiyiaati hattaaa izaa hadara ahadahumul mawtu qaala innee tubtul 'aana wa-lal lazeena yamootoona wa-hum kuffaar; ulaaa'ika a'tadnaa lahum 'azaaban aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 512,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa yahillu lakum an tarisun nisaaa'a karhan wa-laa ta'duloohunna litazhaboo biba'di maaa aataitumoohunna illaaa aien yaateena bifaa-hishatim mubaiyyinah; wa-'aashiroo-hunna bilma'roof; fa-in karihtumoohunna fa'asaaa an takrahoo shai'anw wa-yaj'alal laahu feehi khairan kaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 513,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-in arattumustib daala zawjim makaana zawjin wa-aataitum ihdaahunna qintaaran falaa taakhuzoo minhu shai'aa; ataakhuzoonahoo buhtaannanw wa-ismam mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 514,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-kaifa taakhuzoonahoo wa-qad afdaa ba'dukum ilaa ba'dinw wa-akhazna minkum meesaaqan ghaleezaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 515,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tankihoo maa nakaha aabaaa'ukum minan nisaaa'i illaa maa qad salaf; inahoo kaana faahishatanw wa-maqtanw wa-saaa'a sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 516,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Hurrimat 'alaikum umma-haatukum wa-bannaatukum wa-akhawaatukum wa-'ammaatukum wa-khaalaatukum wa-banaatul akhi wa-banaatul ukhti wa-ummahaatu kumul laateee arda'-nakum wa-akhawaatukum minarradaa'ati wa-ummahaatu nisaaa'ikum wa-rabaaa'i-bukumul laatee fee hujoorikum min nisaaa'ikumul laatee dakhaltum bihinna Fa-il lam takoonoo dakhaltum bihina falaa junaaha 'alaikum wa halaaa'ilu abnaaa'ikumul lazeena min aslaabikum wa-an tajma'oo bainal ukhtaini illaa maa qad salaf; innallaaha kaana Ghafoorar Raheema"
    },
    {
      "index": 517,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Walmuhsanaatu minan nisaaa'i illaa maa malakat aimaanukum kitaabal laahi 'alaikum; wa-uhilla lakum maa waraaa'a zaalikum an tabtaghoo bi-amwaali kum muhsineena ghaira musaa-fiheen; famastamta'tum bihee minhunna fa-aatoohunna ujoorahunna fareedah; wa-laa junaaha 'alaikum feemaa taraadaitum bihee mim ba'dil fareedah; innal laaha kaana 'Aleeman Hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 518,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-mal lam yastati' minkum tawlan ai yankihal muhsanaatil mu'minaati famimmaa malakat aimaanukum min fatayaatikumul mu'minaat; wallaahu a'lamu bi-eemaanikum; ba'dukum mim ba'd; fankihoohunna bi-izni ahlihinna wa-aatoohunna ujoorahunna bilma'roofi muhsanaatin ghaira musaafihaatinw wa-laa muttakhizaati akhdaan; fa-izaaa uhsinna fa-in ataina bifaahi-shatin fa'alaihinnna nisfu maa 'alal muhsanaati minal 'azaab; zaalika liman khashiyal 'anata minkum; wa an tasbiroo khairul lakum; wallaahu Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 519,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Yureedul laahu liyubai-yina lakum wa-yahdiyakum sunanal lazeena min qablikum wa-yatooba 'alaikum; wallaahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 520,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu yureedu ai yatooba 'alaikum wa-yureedul lazeena yattabi-'oonash shahawaati an tameeloo mailan 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 521,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Yureedul laahu ai yukhaffifa 'ankum; wa-khuliqal insaanu da'eefaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 522,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa taakulooo amwaalakum bainakum bilbaatili 'illaaa an takoona tijaaratan 'an taraadim minkum; wa-laa taqtulooo anfusakum; innal laaha kaana bikum Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 523,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Wa-mai yaf'al zaalika 'udwaananw wa-zulman fasawfa nusleehi Naaraa; wa-kaana zaalika 'alal laahi yaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 524,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "In tajtaniboo kabaaa'ira maa tunhawna 'anhu nukaffir 'ankum saiyiaatikum wa-nudkhilkum mudkhalan kareemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 525,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tatamannaw maa faddalal laahu bihee ba'dakum 'alaa ba'd; lirrijaali naseebum mimak tasaboo wa-linnisaaa'i naseebum mimmak tasabna; was'alu llaaha min fadlih; innal laaha kaana bikulli shai'in 'Aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 526,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-likullin ja'alnaa ma-waaliya mimmaa tarakal waalidaani wal-aqraboon; wallazeena 'aqadat aimaanukum fa-aatoohum naseebahum; innal laaha kaana 'alaa kulli shai'in Shaheedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 527,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Arrijaalu qawwaamoona 'alan nisaaa'i bimaa fad-dalal laahu ba'dahum 'alaa ba'dinw wa-bimaaa anfoqoo min amwaalihim; fassaalihaatu qaanitaatun haafizaatul lil-ghaibi bimaa hafizal laah; wallaatee takhaafoona nushu-zahunna fa-'izoohunna wahjuroohunna fil madaaji'i wadriboohunna fa-in ata'nakum falaa tabghoo 'alaihinna sabeelaa; innal laaha kaana 'Aliyyan Kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 528,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-in khiftum shiqaaqa baini-himaa fab'asoo haka-mam min ahlihee wa-hakamam min ahlihaa; iny yureedaaa islaah ai-yuwaffiqil laahu bainahumaa; innal laaha kaana 'Aleeman Khabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 529,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa'budul laaha wa-laa tushrikoo bihee shai'anw wa-bil-waalidaini ihsaananw wa-bizil qurbaa wal-yataamaa wal-masaakeeni wal-jaari zil-qurbaa wal-jaaril junubi was-saahibi biljambi wabnis sabeeli wa maa malakat aimaanukum; innal laaha laa yuhibbu man kaana mukhtaalan fakhooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 530,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yabkhaloona wa-ya-muroonan naasa bilbukhli wa-yaktumoona maaa aataahu-mul laahu min-fadlih; wa a'-tadnaa lilkaafireena 'azaabam muheenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 531,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yunfiqoona amwaalahum ri'aaa'an naasi wa-laa yu'minoona billaahi wa-laa bil-Yawmil Aakhir; wa-mai yakunish shaitaanu lahoo qareenan fasaaa'a qareenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 532,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wa-maazaa 'alaihim law aamanoo billaahi wal-Yawmil Aakhiri wa-anfaqoo mimmaa razaqahumul laah; wa kaanallaahu bihim Aaleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 533,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha laa yazlimu misqaala zarratinw wa-in taku hasanatany yudaa'ifhaa wa-yu'ti mil ladunhu ajran 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 534,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Fakaifa izaa ji'naa min kulli ummatim bishaheedinw wa ji'naabika 'alaa haaa'ulaaa-'i Shaheedan"
    },
    {
      "index": 535,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Yawma'iziny yawad dullazeena kafaroo wa'asawur Rasoola law tusawwaa bihimul ardu wa-laa yaktumoonal laaha hadeesaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 536,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa taqrabus Salaata wa-antum sukaaraa hatta ta'lamoo ma taqooloona wa-la junuban illaa 'aabiree sabeelin hatta taghtasiloo; wa-in kuntum mardaaa aw 'alaa safarin aw jaaa'a ahadum minkum minal ghaaa'iti aw laamastumun nisaaa'a falam tajidoo maaa'an fatayam-mamoo sa'eedan taiyiban famsahoo biwujoohikum wa-aideekum; innal laaha kaana 'Afuwwan Ghafooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 537,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilal lazeena ootoo naseebam minal Kitaabi yashtaroonad dalaalata wa-yureedoona an tadillus sabeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 538,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu a'lamu bi-a'daaa'i-kum; wa-kafaa billaahi waliyyanw wa-kafaa billaahi naseera"
    },
    {
      "index": 539,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Minal lazeena haadoo yuharrifoonal Kalima 'am mawaadi'ihee wa-yaqooloona sami'naa wa-'asainaa wasma' ghaira musma'inw wa-raa'inaa lai-yyam bi-alsinatihim wa-ta'nan fid deen; wa-law annahum qaaloo sami'naa wa-ata'naa wasma' wanzurnaa lakaana khairal lahum wa-aqwama wa-laakil la'anahumul laahu bikufrihim falaa yu'minoona illaa qaleela"
    },
    {
      "index": 540,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "yaaa aiyuha lazeena ootu Kitaaba aaminoo bimaa nazzalnaa musadiqallimaa ma'akum min qabli an natmisa wujoohan fanaruddahaa 'alaaa adbaarihaaa aw nal'anahum kamaa la'annaaa Ashaabas Sabt; wa-kaana amrul laahi maf'oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 541,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha laa yaghfiru ai yushraka bihee wa-yaghfiru maa doona zaalika limai yashaaa'; wa-mai yushrik billaahi faqadif taraaa isman 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 542,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilal lazeena yuzakkoona anfusahum; balil laahu yuzakkee mai yashaaa'u wa-laa yuzlamoona fateelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 543,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Unzur kaifa yaftaroona 'alal laahil kazib, wakafaa biheee ismamm mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 544,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilal lazeena 'ootoo naseebam minal kitaabi yu'minoona bil-Jibti wat-Taaghooti wa-yaqooloona lillazeena kafaroo haaa-ulaaa'i ahdaa minal lazeena aamanoo sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 545,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena la'ana-humul laahu wa-mai yal'anil laahu falan tajida lahoo naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 546,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Am lahum naseebum minal mulki fa-izal laa yu'toonan naasa naqeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 547,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Am yahsudoonan naasa 'alaa maaa aataahumul laahu min fadlihee faqad aatainaaa Aala Ibraaheemal Kitaaba wal-Hikmata wa-aatainaahum mulkan 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 548,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Faminhum man aamana bihee wa-minhum man sadda 'anh; wa-kafaa bi-Jahannama sa'eeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 549,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo bi Aayaatinaa sawfa nusleehim Naaran kullamaa nadijat julooduhum baddalnaahum juloodan ghairahaa liyazooqul 'azaab; innallaaha kaana 'Azeezan Hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 550,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aamanoo wa-'amilus saalihaati sanud-khiluum jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaaa abadaa, lahum feehaaa azwaajum mutahharatun wa-nudkhiluhum zillan zaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 551,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha yaamurukum an tu'addul amaanaati ilaaa ahlihaa wa-izaa hakamtum bainan naasi an tahkumoo bil-'adl; innal laaha ni'immaa ya'izukum bih; innal laaha kaana Samee'am Baseera"
    },
    {
      "index": 552,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanooo atee'ul laaha wa-atee'ur Rasoola wa-ulil amri minkum fa-in tanaaza'tum fee shai'in faruddoohu ilal laahi war-Rasooli in kuntum tu'minoona billaahi wal-yawmil Aakhir; zaalika khairunw wa-ahsanu taaweelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 553,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilal lazeena yaz'umoona annahum aarmanoo bimaa unzilaa ilaika wa-maaa unzila min qablika yureedoona aien yatahaakamooo ilat Taaghooti wa-qad umirooo aien yakfuroo bih, wa-yureedush Shaitaanu aien yudillahum dalaalam ba'eedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 554,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahum ta'aalaw ilaa maaa anzalal laahu Wa-ilar Rasooli ra-aital munaafiqeena yasuddoona 'anka sudoodaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 555,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Fakaifa izaaa asaabathum museebatum bima qaddamat aydeehim summa jaaa'ooka yahlifoona billaahi in aradnaaa illaaa ihsaananw Wa-tawfeeqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 556,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena ya'la mullaahu maa fee quloobihim Fa-a'rid 'anhum Wa-'izhum Wa-qul lahum feee anfusihim qawlam baleeghaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 557,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa arsalnaa mir Rasoolin illaa liyutaa'a bi-iznil laah; Wa-law annahum 'iz zalamooo anfusahum jaaa'ooka fastaghfarul laaha wastaghfara lahumur Rasoolu la-wajadul laaha Tawwaabar Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 558,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Falaa Wa-Rabbika laa yu'minoona hattaa yuhakkimooka feemaa shajara bainahum summa laa yajidoo fee anfusihim harajam mimmaa qadaita Wa-yusal-limoo tasleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 559,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Wa-law annaa katabnaa 'alaihim aniq tulooo anfusakum awikh rujoo min diyaarikum maa fa'aloohu illaa qaleelum minhum Wa-law annahum fa'aloo maa yoo'azoona bihee lakaana khairal lahum Wa-ashadda tasbeetaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 560,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 67,
      "text": "Wa-izal la-aatainaahum mil ladunnaaa ajran 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 561,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 68,
      "text": "Wa-lahadainaahum Siraatam mustaqeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 562,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yuti'il laaha war-Rasoola Fa-ulaaa'ika ma'al lazeena an'amal laahu 'alaihim minan nabiyyeena wassiddeeqeena washshuhadaaa'i wassaaliheen; Wa-hasuna ulaaa'ika rafeeqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 563,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 70,
      "text": "Zaalikal fadlu minal laah; Wa-kafaa billaahi 'Aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 564,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanoo khuzoo hizrakum fanfiroo subaain awin firoo jamee'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 565,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Wa-inna minkum lamal la-yubatti'anna Fa-in asaabatkum museebatun qaala qad an'amal laahu 'alaiya iz lam akum ma'ahum shaheeda"
    },
    {
      "index": 566,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-la-in asaabakum fadlum minal laahi la-yaqoolanna ka-al lam takum bainakum Wa-bainahoo mawaddatuien yaa-laitanee kuntu ma'ahum Fa-afooza fawzan 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 567,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Falyuqaatil fee sabeelil laahil lazeena yashroonal hayaatad dunyaa bil-Aakhirah; Wa-maien uqaatil fee sabeelil laahi Fa-yuqtal aw yaghlib fasawfa nu'teehi ajran 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 568,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa lakum laa tuqaatiloona fee sabeelil laahi walmustad'afeena minar rijaali wannisaaa'i walwildaanil lazeena yaqooloona Rabbanaaa akhrijnaa min haazihil qaryatiz zaalimi ahluhaa waj'al lanaa mil ladunka waliyanw waj'al lanaa mil ladunka naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 569,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Allazeena aamanoo yuqaatiloona fee sabeelil laahi wallazeena kafaroo yuqaatiloona fee sabeelit Taaghoot faqaatiloo awliyaaa'ash Shaitaan; inna kaidash Shaitaani kaana da'eefa"
    },
    {
      "index": 570,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilal lazeena qeela lahum kuffooo aidiyakum Wa-aqeemus Salaata wa-aatuz Zakaata falammaa kutiba 'alaihimul qitaalu izaa fareequm minhum yakhshawnnan naasa kakhashyatil laahi aw ashadda khashyah; Wa-qaaloo Rabbanaa lima katabta 'alainal qitaala law-laaa akhkhartanaa ilaaa ajalin qareeb; qul mataa'ud dunyaa qaleelunw wal-Aakhiratu khairul limanit taqaa Wa-laa tuzlamoona fateelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 571,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Ainamaa takoonoo yudrikkumul mawtu Wa-law kuntum fee buroojim mushaiy-yadah; Wa-in tusibhum hasanatuien yaqooloo haazihee min 'indil laahi Wa-in tusibhum saiyyi'atuien yaqooloo haazihee min 'indik; qul kullum min 'indil laahi famaali haaa-'ulaaa'il qawmi la yakaadoona yafqahoona hadeesaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 572,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Maaa asaabaka min hasanatin faminal laahi Wa-maaa asaaabaka min saiyi'atin famin nafsik; Wa-arsalnaaka linnaasi Rasoolaa; Wa-kafaa billaahi Shaheedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 573,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Man yuti'ir Rasoola faqad ataa'al laaha Wa-man tawallaa famaaa arsalnaaka 'alaihim hafeezaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 574,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaqooloona taa'antun Fa-izaa barazoo min 'indika baiyata taaa'ifatum minhum ghairal lazee taqoolu wallaahu yaktubu maa yubaiyitoona faa'rid 'anhum Wa-tawakkal 'alal laah; Wa-kafaa billaahi Wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 575,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Afalaa yatadabbaroonal Qur'aan; Wa-law kaana min 'indi ghairil laahi la-wajadoo feehi-kh tilaafan kaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 576,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa jaaa'ahum amrum minal amni awil khawfi azaa'oo bihee Wa-law raddoohu ilar Rasooli Wa-ilaaa ulil amri minhum la'alimahul lazeena yastambitoonahoo minhum; Wa-law-laa fadlul laahi 'alaikum Wa-rahmatuhoo lattaba'tumush Shaitaana illaa qaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 577,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Faqaatil fee sabeelil laahi laa tukallafu illa nafsaka Wa-harridil mu'mineena 'asal laahu aien yakuffa ba-sal lazeena kafaroo; wallaahu ashaddu ba-sanw Wa-ashaddu tankeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 578,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Maien yashfa' shafaa'atan hasanataien yakul lahoo naseebum minhaa Wa-maien yashfa' shafaa'tan saiyyi'ataien yakul lahoo kiflum minhaa; Wa-kaanal laahu 'alaa kulli shai'im Muqeetaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 579,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa huyyeetum bi-tahiy-yatin fahaiyyoo bi-ahsana minhaaa aw ruddoohaa; innal laaha kaana 'alaa kulli shai'in Haseeba"
    },
    {
      "index": 580,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Allaahu laaa ilaaha illaa huwa la-yajma'annakum ilaa Yawmil Qiyaamati laa raiba feeh; Wa-man asdaqu minal laahi hadeesaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 581,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Famaa lakum fil muna-fiqeena fi-ataini wallaahu arkasahum bimaa kasaboo; atureedoona an tahdoo man adallal laahu Wa-maien yudli-lil laahu falan tajida lahoo sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 582,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Wadoo law takfuroona kamaa kafaroo fatakoonoona sawaaa'an falaa tattakhizoo minhum awliyaaa'a hattaa yuhaajiroo fee sabeelil laah; Fa-in tawallaw Fa-khuzoohum waqtuloohum haisu wajadt-tumoohum Wa-laa tattakhizoo minhum waliyyanw Wa-laa naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 583,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Illal lazeena yasiloona ilaa qawmim bainakum Wa-bainahum meesaaqun aw jaaa'ookum hasirat sudooruhum aien yuqaatilookum aw yuqaatiloo qawmahum, Wa-law shaaa'al laahu lasallatahum 'alaikum falaqaatalookum; Fa-ini' tazalookum falam yuqaatilookum Wa-alqaw ilaikumus salama famaa ja'alal laahu lakum 'alaihim sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 584,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Satajidoona aakhareena yureedoona aien yaamanookum Wa-yaamanoo qawmahum kullamaa ruddooo ilal fitnati urkisoo feehaa; Fa-il lam ya'tazilookum Wa-yulqooo ilai kumus salama Wa-yakuffooo aidiyahum fakhuzoohum waqtuloohum haisu saqif-tumoohum; Wa-ulaaa'ikum ja'alnaa lakum 'alaihim sultaanam mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 585,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana limu'minin aien yaqtula mu'minan illaa khata'aa; waman qatala mu'minan khata'an fatahreeru raqabatim mu'minatyunw Wa-diyatum musallamatun ilaaa ahliheee illaaa aien yassaddaqoo; Fa-in kaana min qawmin 'aduwwil lakum Wa-huwa mu'minun fatahreeru raqabatim mu'minah; Wa-in kaana min qawmim bainakum Wa-bainahum meesaaqun fadiyatum musallamatun ilaaa ahlihee Wa-tahreeru raqabatim mu'minatin famal lam yajid Fa-Siyaamu shahraini mutataabi'aini tawbatam minal laah; Wa-kaanal laahu 'Aleeman hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 586,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yaqtul mu'minam muta'ammidan fajazaaa'uhoo Jahannamu khaalidan feehaa Wa-ghadibal laahu' alaihi Wa-la'anahoo Wa-a'adda lahoo 'azaaban 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 587,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Yaaa aiyuhal lazeena aamanoo izaa darabtum fee sabeelil laahi fatabaiyyanoo Wa-laa taqooloo liman alqaaa ilaikumus salaama lasta mu'minan tabtaghoona 'aradal hayaatid dunyaa fa'indal laahi maghaanimu kaseerah; kazaalika kuntum min qablu famannnal laahu 'alaikum fatabaiyyanoo; innallaaha kaana bimaa ta'maloona Khabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 588,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Laa yastawil qaa'idoona Minal mu'mineena ghairu ulid darari walmujaahidoona fee sabeelil laahi bi-amwaalihim Wa-anfusihim; faddalal laahul mujaahideena bi-amwaalihim Wa-anfusihim 'alal qaa'ideena darajah; Wa-kullanw wa'adal laahul husnaa; Wa-faddalal laahul mujaahideena 'alal qaa'ideena ajran 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 589,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Darajaatim minhu Wa-maghfiratanw Wa-rahmah; Wa-kaanal laahu Ghafoorar Raheema"
    },
    {
      "index": 590,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena tawaffaa-humul malaaa-ikatu zaalimeee anfusihim qaaloo feema kuntum qaaloo kunnaa mustad'afeena fil ard; qaalooo alam takun ardul laahi waasi'atan fatuhaajiroo feehaa; Fa-ulaaa'ika ma-waahum Jahannamu Wa-saaa-at maseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 591,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Illal mustad-'afeena minar rijaali wannisaaa'i walwildaani laa yastatee'oona heelatanw Wa-laa yahtadoona sabeela"
    },
    {
      "index": 592,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Fa-ulaaa'ika 'asal laahu aien ya'fuwa 'anhum; Wa-kaanal laahu 'Afuwwan Ghafooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 593,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yuhaajir fee sabeelil laahi yajid fil ardi muraaghaman kaseeranw Wa-sa'ah; Wa-maien yakhruj mim baitihee muhaajiran ilal laahi Wa-Rasoolihee summa yudrikhul mawtu faqad waqa'a ajruhoo 'alal laah; Wa-kaanal laahu Ghafoorar Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 594,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa darabtum fil ardi falaisa 'alaikum junaahun an taqsuroo minas Salaati in khiftum aien yaftinakumul lazeena kafarooo; innal kaafireena kaanoo lakum aduwwam mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 595,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa kunta feehim Fa-aqamta lahumus Salaata faltaqum taaa'ifatum minhum ma'aka walyaakhuzooo aslihatahum Fa-izaa sajadoo fal-yakoonoo mienw waraaa'ikum walta-ti taaa'ifatun ukhraa lam yusalloo falyusallo ma'aka walyaakhuzoo hizrahum Wa-aslihatahum; waddal lazeena kafaroo law taghfuloona 'an aslihatikum Wa-amti'atikum Fa-yameeloona 'alaikum mailatanw waahidah; Wa-laa junaaha 'alaikum in kaana bikum azam mim matarin aw kuntum mardaaa an tada'ooo aslihatakum Wa-khuzoo hizrakum; innal laaha a'adda lilkaafireena 'azaabam muheenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 596,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Fa-izaa qadaitumus Salaata fazkurul laaha qiyaamanw Wa-qu'oodanw Wa-'alaa junoobikum; Fa-izat ma-nantum Fa-aqeemus Salaah; innas Salaata kaanat 'alal mu'mineena kitaabam mawqootaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 597,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tahinoo fib tighaaa'il qawmi in takoonoo ta-lamoona Fa-innahum ya-lamoona kamaa ta-lamoona; Wa-tarjoona minal laahi maa laa yar-joon; Wa-kaanal laahu 'Aleeman Hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 598,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Innaaa anzalnaaa ilaikal Kitaaba bilhaqqi litahkuma bainan naasi bimaaa araakal laah; Wa-laa takul lilkhaaa'ineena khaseemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 599,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 106,
      "text": "Wastaghfiril laaha innal laaha kaana Ghafoorar Raheema"
    },
    {
      "index": 600,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tujaadil 'anil lazeena yakhtaanoona anfusahum; innal laaha laa yuhibbu man kaana khawwaanan aseemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 601,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Yastakhfoona minan naasi Wa-laa yastakh-foona minal laahi Wa-huwa ma'ahum iz yubaiyitoona maa laa yardaa minal qawl; Wa-kaanal laahu bimaa ya'maloona muheetaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 602,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Haaa-antum haaa'ulaaa'i jaadaltum 'anhum fil hayaatid dunyaa famaien yujaadilul laaha 'anhum Yawmal Qiyaamati am maien yakoonu 'alaihim wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 603,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien ya'mal sooo'an aw yazlim nafsahoo summa yastaghfiril laaha yajidil laaha Ghafoorar Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 604,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yaksib isman Fa-innamaa yaksibuhoo 'alaa nafsih; Wa-kaanal laahu 'Aleeman hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 605,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yaksib khateee'atan aw isman summa yarmi bihee bareee'an faqadih tamala buhtaananw Wa-ismam mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 606,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "Wa-law-laa fadlul laahi 'alaika Wa-rahmatuhoo lahammat taaa'ifatum minhum aien yudillooka Wa-maa yudilloona illaaa anfusahum Wa-maa yadurroonaka min shai'; Wa-anzalal laahu 'alaikal Kitaaba wal-hikmata wa-'allamaka maa lam takun ta'lam; Wa-kaana fadlul laahi 'alaika 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 607,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 114,
      "text":
          "laa khaira fee kaseerim min najwaahum illaa man amara bisadaqatin aw ma'roofin aw islaahim bainan naas; Wa-maien yaf'al zaalikab tighaaa'a mardaatil laahi Fa-sawfa nu'teehi ajran 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 608,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Wa-main yushaaqiqir Rasoola mim ba'di maa tabaiyyana lahul hudaa wa-yattabi' ghaira sabeelil mu'mineena nuwallihee ma tawallaa Wa-nuslihee Jahannama Wa-saaa'at maseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 609,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha laa yaghfiru aien yushraka bihee wayaghfiru maa doona zaalika limain yashaaa'; Wa-main yushrik billaahi faqad dalla dalaalam ba'eedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 610,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Iien yad'oona min dooniheee illaaa inaasanw wa-ien yad'oona illaa Shaitaanam mareedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 611,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 118,
      "text":
          "La'anahul laah; Wa-qaala la-attakhizanna min 'ibaadika naseebam mafroodaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 612,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 119,
      "text":
          "Wa-la-udillannahum Wa-la-umanni-yannnahum Wa-la-aamurannahum fala-yubat-tikunna aazaanal an'aami Wa-la-aamurannahum fala-yughaiy-yirunna khalqal laah; Wa-main yattakhizish Shaitaana waliyyam mmin doonil laahi faqad khasira khusraanam mubeena"
    },
    {
      "index": 613,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 120,
      "text":
          "Ya'iduhum Wa-yuman-neehim Wa-maa ya'iduhumush Shaitaanu illaa ghurooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 614,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 121,
      "text": "Ulaaa'ika ma'waahum Jahannamu Wa-laa yajidoona 'anhaa maheesaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 615,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 122,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati sanud-khiluhum Jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaaa abadaa; wa'dal laahi haqqaa; Wa-man asdaqu minal laahi qeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 616,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 123,
      "text":
          "Laisa bi-amaaniyyikum Wa-laaa amaaniyyi Ahlil Kitaab; main ya'mal sooo'aien yujza bihee Wa-laa yajid lahoo min doonil laahi waliyanw Wa-laa naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 617,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 124,
      "text":
          "Wa-main ya'mal minas saalihaati min zakarin aw unsaa Wa-huwa mu'minun fa-ulaaa'ika yadkhuloonal Jannata Wa-laa yuzlamoona naqeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 618,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 125,
      "text":
          "Wa-man ahsanu deenam mimmman aslama wajhahoo lillaahi Wa-huwa muhsinunw wattaba'a Millata Ibraaheema haneefaa; wattakhazal laahu Ibraaheema khaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 619,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 126,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahi maa fis samaawaati Wa-maa fil ard; Wa-kaanal laahu bikulli shai'im muheetaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 620,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 127,
      "text":
          "Wa-yastaftoonaka fin nisaaa'i qulil laahu yufteekum feehinna Wa-maa yutlaa 'alaikum fil Kitaabi fee yataaman nisaaa'il laatee laa tu'toonahunna maa kutiba lahunnna Wa-targhaboona an tankihoohunna wal-mustad'a-feena minal wildaani Wa-an taqoomoo lilyataamaa bilqist; Wa-maa taf'aloo min khairin fa-innal laaha kaana bihee 'Aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 621,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 128,
      "text":
          "Wa-inim ra-atun khaafat mim ba'lihaa nushoozan aw i'raadan falaa junaaha 'alaihi-maaa aien yuslihaa bainahumaa sulhaa; wassulhu khair; Wa-uhdiratil anfusush shuhh; Wa-in tuhsinoo Wa-tattaqoo fa-innal laaha kaana bimaa ta'maloona Khabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 622,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 129,
      "text":
          "Wa-lan tastatee'ooo an ta'diloo bainan nisaaa'i Wa-law harastum falaa tameeloo kullal maili fatazaroohaa kalmu'al-laqah; Wa-in tuslihoo Wa-tattaqoo fa-innal laaha kaana Ghafoorar Raheema"
    },
    {
      "index": 623,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 130,
      "text":
          "Wa-ien yatafarraqaa yughnil laahu kullam min sa'atih; Wa-kaanal laahu Waasi'an Hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 624,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 131,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahi ma fis samaawaati Wa-maa fil ard; Wa-laqad wassainal lazeena ootul Kitaaba min qablikum Wa-iyyaakum anit taqul laah; Wa-in takfuroo fa-inna lillaahi ma fis samaawaati Wa-ma fil ard; Wa-kaanal laahu Ghaniyyan hameedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 625,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 132,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahi ma fis samaawaati Wa-ma fil ard; Wa-kafaa billaahi Wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 626,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 133,
      "text":
          "Ien yasha yuzhibkum aiy-yuhan naasu Wa-ya'ti bi-aakhareen; Wa-kaanal laahu 'alaa zaalika Qadeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 627,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 134,
      "text":
          "man kaana yureedu sawaabad dunyaa fa'indal laahi sawaabud dunyaa wal-Aakhirah; Wa-kaanal laahu Samee'am Baseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 628,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 135,
      "text":
          "Yaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo koonoo qawwa-meena bilqisti shuhadaaa'a lillaahi Wa-law 'alaa anfusikum awil waalidaini wal-aqrabeen ien yakun ghaniyyan aw faqeeran fallaahu awlaa bihimaa falaaa tattabi'ul hawaaa an ta'diloo; Wa-in talwooo aw tu'ridoo fa-innal laaha kaana bimaa ta'maloona Khabeera"
    },
    {
      "index": 629,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 136,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanooo aaminoo billaahi Wa-Rasoolihee wal-Kitaabil lazee nazzala 'alaa Rasoolihee wal-Kitaabil lazeee anzala min qabl; Wa-main yakfur billaahi Wa-Malaaa'ikatihee Wa-Kutubihee Wa-Rusulihee wal-Yawmil Aakhiri faqad dalla dalaalam ba'eedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 630,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 137,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo summa kafaroo summa aamanoo summa kafaroo summaz daado kufral lam yakunil laahu liyaghfira lahum Wa-laa liyahdiyahum sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 631,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 138,
      "text": "Bash-shiril munaafiqeena bi-anna lahum 'azaaban aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 632,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 139,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yattakhizoo-nal kaafireena awliyaaa'a min doonil mu'mineen; a-yabtaghoona 'indahumul 'izzata fainnnal 'izzata lillaahi jamee'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 633,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 140,
      "text":
          "Wa-qad nazzala 'alaikum fil Kitaabi an izaa sami'tum Aayaatil laahi yukfaru bihaa Wa-yustahza-oo bihaa falaa taq'udoo ma'ahum hattaa yakhoodoo fee hadeesin ghairih; innakum izam misluhum; innal laaha jaami'ul munaafiqeena wal-kaafireena fee jahannama jamee'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 634,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 141,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yatarab-basoona bikum fa-in kaana lakum fath-hum minal laahi qaalooo alam nakum ma'akum Wa-in kaana lilkaafireena naseebun qaalooo alam nastah-wiz 'alaikum Wa-nammna'kum minal mu'mineen; fallaahu yahkumu bainakum Yawmal Qiyaamah; Wa-lain yaj'alal laahu lilkaafireena 'alal mu'mineena sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 635,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 142,
      "text":
          "Innal munaafiqeena yukhaadi'oonal laaha Wa-huwa khaadi'uhum Wa-izaa qaamooo ilas Salaati qaamoo kusaalaa yuraaa-oonan naasa Wa-laa yazkuroonal laaha illaa qaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 636,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 143,
      "text":
          "Muzab-zabeena baina zaalika laaa ilaa haaa-ulaaa-e Wa-laaa ilaa haaa'ulaaa'; Wa-main yudli-lil laahu falan tajida lahoo sabeela"
    },
    {
      "index": 637,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 144,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tattakhizul kaafireena awliyaaa'a min doonil mu'mineen; aturee-doona an taj'aloo lillaahi 'alaikum sultaanam mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 638,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 145,
      "text":
          "Innal munaafiqeena fid darkil asfali minan Naari Wa-lan tajida lahum naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 639,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 146,
      "text":
          "Illal lazeena taaboo Wa-aslahoo wa'tasamoo billaahi Wa-akhlasoo deenahum lillaahi faulaaa'ika ma'al mu'mineena Wa-sawfa yu'til laahul mu'mineena ajran 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 640,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 147,
      "text":
          "Ma yafa'lul laahu bi'azaabikum in shakartum Wa-aamantum; Wa-kaanal laahu Shaakiran 'Aleema"
    },
    {
      "index": 641,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 148,
      "text":
          "La yuhibbul laahul jahra bis-sooo'i minal qawli illaa man zulim; Wa-kaanal laahu Samee'an 'Aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 642,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 149,
      "text":
          "in tubdoo khairann aw tukhfoohu aw ta'foo 'an sooo'in fa-innal laaha kaana 'afuwwan Qadeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 643,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 150,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yakkfuroona billaahi Wa-Rusulihee Wa-yureedoona aien yufarriqoo bainal laahi Wa-Rusulihee Wa-yaqooloona nu'minu biba'dinw Wa-nakfuru biba'-dinw Wa-yureedoona aien yattakhizoo baina zaalika sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 644,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 151,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika humul kaafiroona haqqaaw; Wa-a'tadnaa lilkaafireena 'azaabam muheenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 645,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 152,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aamanoo billaahi Wa-Rusulihee Wa-lam yufarriqoo baina ahadim minhum ulaaa'ika sawfa yu'teehim ujoorahum; Wa-kaanal laahu Ghafoorar Raheema"
    },
    {
      "index": 646,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 153,
      "text":
          "Yas'aluka Ahlul Kitaabi an tunazzila 'alaihim Kitaabam minas samaaa'i faqad sa-aloo Moosaa akbara min zaalika faqaaloo arinal laaha jahratan fa-akhazat-humus saa'iqatu bizulmihim; summat takhazul 'ijla mim ba'di maa jaa'at-humul baiy-yinaatu fa'afawnaa 'ann zaalik; Wa-aatainaa Moosaa sultaanam mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 647,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 154,
      "text":
          "Wa-rafa'naa fawqahumut Toora bimeesaaqihim Wa-qulnaa lahumud khulu abaaba sujjadanw Wa-qulnaa lahum laa ta'doo fis Sabti Wa-akhaznaa minhum meesaaqan ghaleezaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 648,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 155,
      "text":
          "Fabimaa naqdihim meesaaqahum Wa-kufrihim bi-aayaatil laahi Wa-qatlihimul Ambiyaaa'a bighairi haqqinw Wa-qawlihim quloobunaa ghulf; bal taba'al laahu 'alaihaa bikufrihim falaa yu'minoona illaa qaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 649,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 156,
      "text": "Wa-bikufrihim Wa-qawlihim 'alaa Maryama buh-taanan 'azeema"
    },
    {
      "index": 650,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 157,
      "text":
          "Wa qawlihim innaa qatal-nal maseeha 'Eesab na-Maryama Rasoolal laahi Wa-maa qataloohu Wa-maa sala-boohu Wa-laakin shubbiha lahum; Wa-innal lazeenakh talafoo feehee lafee shakkim minh; maa lahum bihee min 'ilmin illat tibaa'az zann; Wa-maa qataloohu yaqeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 651,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 158,
      "text": "Bal rafa'ahul laahu ilayh; Wa-kaanal laahu 'Azeezan Hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 652,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 159,
      "text":
          "Wa-im min Ahlil Kitaabi illaa layu'minanna bihee qabla mawtihee Wa-Yawmal Qiyaamati yakoonu 'alaihim shaheedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 653,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 160,
      "text":
          "Fabizulmim minal lazeena haadoo harramnaa 'alaihim taiyibaatin uhillat lahum Wa-bisadihim 'an sabeelil laahi kaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 654,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 161,
      "text":
          "Wa-akhzihimur ribaa Wa-qad nuhoo 'anhu Wa-aklihim amwaalan naasi bilbaatil; Wa-a'tadnaa lilkaafireena minhum 'azaaban aleema"
    },
    {
      "index": 655,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 162,
      "text":
          "Laakinir raasikhoona fil 'ilmi minhum walmu'minoona yu'minoona bimaaa unzila ilaika Wa-maaa unzila min qablika walmuqeemeenas Salaata walmu-toonaz Zakaata walmu'minoona billaahi wal-yawmil Aakhir; ulaaa'ika sanu'teehim ajran 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 656,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 163,
      "text":
          "Innaaa aw-hainaaa ilaika kamaaa awhainaaa ilaa Noohinw wan-nabiyyeena mim ba'dih; Wa-awhainaaa ilaaa ibraaheema Wa-Ismaaa'eela Wa-Ishaaqa Wa-Ya'qooba wal-Asbaati Wa-'Eesaa Wa-Ayyooba Wa-Yoonusa Wa-haaroona Wa-Sulaimaan; Wa-aatainaa Daawooda Zabooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 657,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 164,
      "text":
          "Wa-Rusulan qad qasas-naahum 'alaika min qablu Wa-Rusulal lam naqsushum 'alaik; Wa-kallamal laahu Moosaa takleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 658,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 165,
      "text":
          "Rusulam mubashshireena Wa-munzireena li'allaa yakoona linnaasi 'alal laahi hujjatum ba'dar Rusul; Wa-kaanal laahu 'Azeezan Hakeema"
    },
    {
      "index": 659,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 166,
      "text":
          "Laakinil laahu yashhadu bimaaa anzala ilaika anzalahoo bi'ilmihee wal-malaaa'ikatu yashhadoon; Wa-kafaa billaahi Shaheeda"
    },
    {
      "index": 660,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 167,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo Wa-saddoo 'an sabeelil laahi qad dalloo dalaalam ba'eedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 661,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 168,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo Wa-zalamoo lam yakunil laahu liyaghfira lahum Wa-laa liyahdiyahum tareeqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 662,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 169,
      "text":
          "Illaa tareeqa jahannamma khaalideena feehaa abadaa; Wa-kaana zaalika 'alal laahi yaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 663,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 170,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhan naasu qad jaaa'akumur Rasoolu bilhaqqi mir Rabbikum fa-ammminoo khairal lakum; Wa-in takfuroo fa-inna lillaahi ma fis samaawaati wal-ard; Wa-kaanal laahu 'Aleemann hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 664,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 171,
      "text":
          "Ya-Ahlal Kitaabi la taghloo fee deenikum Wa-laa taqooloo 'alal laahi illal haqq; innamal Maseehu 'Eesab nu Maryama Rasoolul laahi Wa-Kalimatuhooo alqaahaaa ilaa Maryamma Wa-roohum minhum fa-aaminoo billaahi Wa-Rusulihee Wa-laa taqooloo salaasah; intahoo khairal lakum; innamal laahu Ilaahunw Waahid, Subhaanahooo aien yakoona lahoo walad; lahoo ma fis samaawaati Wa-ma fil ard; Wa-kafaa billaahi Wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 665,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 172,
      "text":
          "Laien yastankifal Maseehu aien yakoona 'abdal lillaahi Wa-lal malaaa'ikatul muqarraboon; Wa-maien yastankif 'an ibaadatihee Wa-yastakbir fasa-yahshuruhum ilaihi jamee'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 666,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 173,
      "text":
          "Fa-ammal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati fa-yuwaffeehim ujoorahum Wa-yazeeduhum min fadlihee Wa-ammal lazeenas tankafoo wastakbaroo fa-yu'azzibuhum 'azaaban aleemanw Wa-laa yajidoona lahum min doonil laahi waliyyanw Wa-laa naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 667,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 174,
      "text":
          "Ya-aiyyuhan naasu qad jaaa'akum burhaanum mir Rabbikum Wa-anzalnaaa ilaikum Nooram Mubeena"
    },
    {
      "index": 668,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 175,
      "text":
          "Fa-ammal lazeena aamanoo billaahi wa'tasamoo bihee fasa-yudkhiluhum fee rahmatim minhu Wa-fadlinw Wa-yahdeehim ilaihi Siraatam Mustaqeema"
    },
    {
      "index": 669,
      "sura": 4,
      "aya": 176,
      "text":
          "Yastaftoonaka qulil laahu yufteekum fil kalaalah; inim ru'un halaka laisa lahoo waladunw Wa-lahoo ukhtun falahaa nisfu maa tarak; Wa-huwa yarisuhaaa il lam yakkul lahaa walad; fa-in kaanatas nataini falahumas sulusaani mimmmaa tarak; Wa-in kaanooo ikhwatar rijaalanw Wa-nisaaa'an faliz-zakari mislu hazzil unsa-ya-iyn; yubaiyinul laahu lakum an tadilloo; wallaahu bikulli shai'in Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 670,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo awfoo bil'uqood; uhillat lakum baheematul an'aami illaa maa yutlaa 'alaikum ghaira muhillis saidi wa-antum hurum; innal laaha yahkumu maa yureed"
    },
    {
      "index": 671,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tuhilloo sha'aaa-'iral laahi wa-lash shahral haraama wa-lal hadya wa-lal qalaaa-ida wa-laa aaam-meenal baital haraama yabtaghoona fadlam mir Rabbihim wa-ridwaanaa; Wa-izaa halaltum fastaadoo; Wa-laa yajriman-nakum shana-aanu qawmin an saddookum 'anil Masjidil haraami an ta'tadoo; wa-ta'aawanoo 'alal birri wattaqwaa; wa-laa ta'aawanoo 'alal ismi wal'udwaan; wattaqul laaha; innal laaha shadeedul 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 672,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Hurrimat 'alaikumul mai-tatu waddamu wa-lahmul khinzeeri wa-maaa uhilla lighairil laahi bihee walmun-khani-qatu wal-mawqoozatu wal-mutarad-diyatu wan-nateehatu wa-maaa akalas sabu'u illaa maa zakkaitum wa-maa zubiha 'alan nusubi wa-an tastaq-simoo bil-azlaam; zaalikum fisq; alyauma ya-isal lazeena kafaroo min deenikum falaa takhshau-hum wakh-shaoun; alyauma akmaltu lakum deenakum wa-atmamtu 'alaikum ni'matee wa-radeetu lakumul Islaama deenaa; famanid turra fee makh-masatin ghaira muta-jaa-nifil li-ismin fa-innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 673,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Yas-aloonaka maazaaa uhilla lahum; qul uhilla lakumut taiyyibaatu wa-maa' allamtum minal jawaarihi mukal-libeena tu'allimoona-hunna mimmaa 'allama-kumul laah fakuloo mimmaaa amsakna 'alaikum wazkurus mal laahi 'alaih; wattaqul laah; innal laaha saree'ul hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 674,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Alyauma uhilla lakumut taiyyibaatu wa-ta'aamul lazeena ootul kitaaba hillul lakum wa-ta'aamukum hillul lahum wal-muhsanaatu minal mu-minaati wal-muhsanaatu minal lazeena ootul kitaaba min qablikum izaaa aatai-tumoohunna ujoorahunna muhsineena ghaira musaa-fiheena wa-laa muttakhizeee akhdaan; wa-main yakfur bil-eemaani faqad habita 'amaluhoo wa-huwa fil aaakhirati minal khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 675,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo izaa qumtum ilas salaati fagh-siloo wujoohakum wa-aidiyakum ilal maraafiqi wam-sahoo biru-oosikum wa-arjulakum ilal ka'bayn; wa-in kuntum junuban fattah-haroo; wa-in kuntum mardaaa aw 'alaa safarin aw jaaa-a ahadum minkum minal ghaaa-iti aw laamastumun nisaaa-a falam tajidoo maaa-an fatayam-mamoo sa'eedan taiyyiban famsahoo biwujoohikum wa-aideekum minh; ma yureedul laahu liyaj'ala 'alaikum min haraj(inw) wa-laakien yureedu liyutah-hirakum wa-liyutimma ni'matahoo 'alaikum la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 676,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wazkuroo ni'matal laahi 'alaikum wa-meesaaqahul lazee waasaqakum biheee iz qultum sami'naa wa-ata'naa wattaqul laah(a); innal laaha 'aleemum bizaatis sudoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 677,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamaanoo koonoo qawwaa-meena lillaahi shuhadaaa-a bilqist, wa-laa yajri-mannakum shana-aanu qawmin 'alaaa allaa ta'diloo; i'diloo; huwa aqrabu littaqwaa wattaqul laah(a); innal laaha khabeerum bimaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 678,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wa'adal laahul lazeena aamanoo wa-'amilus saalihaati lahum maghfiratunw wa-ajrun 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 679,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kafaroo wa-kazzaboo bi-aayaatinaaa ulaaa-ika as-haabul jaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 680,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Yaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanuz kuroo ni'matal laahi 'alaikum iz hamma qawmun aien yabsutooo ilaikum ai-diyahum fakaffa ai-diyahum 'ankum wattaqul laah; wa'alal laahi fal-yatawak-kalil mu-minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 681,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad akhazal laahu meesaaqa banee israaa-eela wa-ba's-naa minhumus nai 'ashara naqeeba(nw) wa-qaalal laahu innee ma'akum la-in aqam-tumus salaata wa-aatai-tumuz zakaata wa-aamantum bi-Rusulee wa'azzar-tumoohum wa-aqrad-tumul laaha qardan hasanal la-ukaffiranna 'ankum saiyyi-aatikum wa-la-udkhilan-nakum jannaatin tajree min tah-tihal anhaar; faman kafara ba'da zaalika minkum faqad dalla sawaaa assabeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 682,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Fabimaa naq-dihim meesaa-qahum la'an-naahum wa-ja'alnaa quloobahum qaasiyah(tan) yuharrifoonal kalima 'amma waadi'ihee wa-nasoo hazzam mimmaa zukkiroo bih; wa-laa tazaalu tattali'u 'alaa khaaa-inatim minhum illaa qaleelam minhum fa'fu 'anhum wasfah; innal laaha yuhibbul muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 683,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-minal lazeena qaalooo innaa nasaaraaa akhaznaa mee-saaqahum fanasoo hazzam mimmaa zukkiroo bihee fa-aghrainaa baina-humul 'adaawata wal-baghdaaa-a ilaa yawmil qiyaamah; wa-sawfa yunabbi-uhumul laahu bimaa kaanoo yasna'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 684,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ahlal kitaabi qad jaaa-akum Rasoolunaa yubaiyyinu lakum kaseeram mimmmaa kuntum tukhfoona minal kitaabi wa-ya'foo 'an kaseer; qad jaaa-akum minal laahi noorunw wa-kitaabum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 685,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Yahdee bihil laahu manit taba'a ridwaanahoo subulas salaam(i) Wa-yukhrijuhum minaz zulumaati ilan noori bi-iznihee Wa-yahdeehim ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 686,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Laqad kafaral lazeena qaalooo innal laaha huwal maseehub nu Maryam(a); qul famaien yamliku minal laahi shai'an in araada aien yuhlikal Maseehab na Maryama Wa-ummahoo Wa-man fil ardi jamee'aa, Wa-lillaahi mulkus samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-maa bainahumaa; yakhluqu maa Yashaaa'; wallaahu 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 687,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalatil Yahoodu wan-Nasaaraa nahnu abnaaa'ul laahi Wa-ahibbaaa'uh; qul falima yu'azzibukum bizunoobikum bal antum basharum mimman khalaq; yaghfiru limaien yashaaa'u Wa-yu'azzibu maien yashaaa'; Wa-lillaahi mulkus samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-maa bainahumaa Wa-ilaihil maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 688,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-Ahlal Kitaabi qad jaaa'akum Rasoolunaa yubaiyinu lakum 'alaa fatratim minar Rusuli an taqooloo maa jaaa'anaa mim basheerinw Wa-laa nazeerin faqad jaaa'akum basheerunw Wa-nazeer; wallaahu 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 689,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaala Moosaa liqawmihee yaa-qawmiz kuroo ni'matal laahi 'alaikum iz ja'ala feekum ambiyaaa'a Wa-ja'alakum mulookanw Wa-aataakum maa lam yu'ti ahadam minal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 690,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Yaa-qawmid khulul Ardal Muqaddasatal latee katabal laahu lakum Wa-laa tartaddoo 'alaaa adbaarikum fatan-qaliboo khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 691,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Moosaaa innaa feehaa qawman jabbaa-reena Wa-innaa lan nad-khulahaa hattaa yakhrujoo minhaa fa-ien yakhrujoo minhaa fa-innaa daa-khiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 692,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Qaala rajulaani minal lazeena yakhaafoona an'amal laahu 'alai-himad khuloo 'alai-himul baab, fa-izaa dakhal-tumoohu fa-innakum ghaaliboon; Wa-'alal laahi fatawakkalooo in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 693,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Moosaaa innaa lan nad-khulahaa aba-dam maa daamoo feehaa fazhab anta Wa-Rabbuka faqaa-tilaaa innaa haa-hunaa qaa'idoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 694,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbi innee laaa amliku illaa nafsee Wa-akhee fafruq bainanaa Wa-bainal qawmil faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 695,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Qaala fa-innahaa muhar-ramatun 'alaihim arba'eena sanah(taien); yateehoona fil ard; falaa ta-sa 'alal qawmil faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 696,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Watlu 'alaihim naba abnai Aadama bilhaqqi iz qarrabaa qurbaanan fatu-qubbila min ahadihimaa Wa-lam yutaqabbal minal aakhari qaala la-aqtu-lannaka qaala inna-maa yataqabbalul laahu minal muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 697,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "La'im basatta ilaiyya yadaka litaq-tulanee maa ana bi-baasitien yadiya ilaika li-aqtulak(a) innee akhaaful laaha Rabbal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 698,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Inee ureedu an tabooo'a bi-ismee Wa-ismika fatakoona min As-haabin Naar; Wa-zaalika jazaaa'uz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 699,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Fatawwa'at lahoo nafsu-hoo qatla akheehi faqatalahoo fa-asbaha minal khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 700,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Faba'asal laahu ghuraabaien yab-hasu fil ardi liyuriyahoo kaifa yuwaaree saw'ata akheeh; qaala yaa-wailata-aa a'ajaztu an akoona misla haazal ghuraabi fa-uwaariya saw-ata akhee fa-asbaha minan naadimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 701,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Min ajli zaalika katabnaa 'alaa Banee Israaa'eela annahoo man qatala nafsam bighairi nafsin aw fasaadin fil ardi faka-annammaa qatalan naasa jamee'a(nw) Wa-man ahyaahaa faka-annamaaa ahyan naasa jamee'aa; Wa-laqad jaaa'at-hum Rusulunaa bil-baiyyinaati summa inna kaseeram minhum ba'da zaalika fil ardi la-musrifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 702,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Innamaa jazaaa'ul lazeena yuhaariboonal laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo Wa-yas'awna fil ardi fasaadan aien yuqattalooo aw yusallabooo aw tuqatta'a aideehim Wa-arjuluhum min khilaafin aw yunfaw minal ard; zaalika lahum khizyun fid dunyaa Wa-lahum fil Aakhirati 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 703,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Illal lazeena taaboo min qabli an taqdiroo 'alaihim fa'lamooo annnal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 704,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanut taqul laaha wabtaghooo ilaihil waseelata Wa-jaahidoo fee sabeelihee la'allakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 705,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo law anna lahum maa fil ardi jamee'anw Wa-mislahoo ma'ahoo liyaftadoo bihee min 'azaabi Yawmil Qiyaamati maa tuqubbila minhum Wa-lahum azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 706,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Yureedoona aien yakhrujoo minan Naari Wa-maa hum bikhaari-jeena minhaa Wa-lahum 'azaabum muqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 707,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wassaariqu wassaariqatu faqta'oo aidi-yahumaa jazaaa'am bimaa kasabaa nakaalam minal laah; wallaahu 'Azeezun hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 708,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Faman taaba mim ba'di zulmihee Wa-aslaha fa-innal laaha yatoobu 'alaih; innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 709,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Alam ta'lam annal laaha lahoo mulkus samaawaati wal-ardi yu'az-zibu maien yashaa'u Wa-yaghfiru li-maien yashaaa'; wallaahu 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 710,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhar Rasoolu laa yahzunkal lazeena yusaa-ri'oona fil kufri minal lazeena qaaloo aamannaa bi-afwaa-hi-him Wa-lam tu'min quloobuhum; Wa-minal lazeena haadoo sammaa'oona lil-kazibi sammaa'oona liqawmin aakhareena lam ya'tooka yuharri-foonal kalima mim ba'di mawaadi'ihee yaqooloona in ooteetum haazaa fakhuzoohu Wa-il lam tu'tawhu fah-zaroo; Wa-maien yuridil laahu fitna-tahoo falan tamlika lahoo minal laahi shai'aa; ulaaa-'ikal lazeena lam yuridil laahu aien yutahhira quloobahum; lahum fid dunyaa khizyunw Wa-lahum fil Aakhirati azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 711,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Sammaa'oona lilkazibi akkaaloona lis-suht; fa-in jaaa'ooka fahkum bainahum aw a'rid anhum Wa-in tu'rid 'anhum falaien yadurrooka shai-a(nw) Wa-in hakamta fahkum bainahum bilqist; innal laaha yuhibbul muqsiteen"
    },
    {
      "index": 712,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-kaifa yuhakki-moonaka Wa-'inda-humut Tawraatu feehaa hukmul laahi summa yatawallawna mim ba'di zaalik; Wa-maaa ulaaa'ika bilmu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 713,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Innaaa anzalnat Tawraata feehaa hudanw Wa-noor(uien); yahkumu bihan Nabiyyoonal lazeena aslamoo lillazeena haadoo war-rabbaaniyyoona wal-ahbaaru bimas tuhfizoo min Kitaabil laahi Wa-kaanoo 'alaihi shuhadaaa'; falaa takhshawun naasa wakhshawni Wa-laa tashtaroo bi-aayaatee samanan qaleelaa; Wa-mal lam yahkum bimaaa anzalal laahu fa-ulaaa'ika humul kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 714,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa-katabnaa 'alaihim feehaaa annan nafsa binnafsi wal'aina bil'aini wal-anfa bilanfi wal-uzuna bil-uzuni wassinna bissinni waljurooha qisaas; faman tasaddaqa bihee fahuwa kaffaaratul lah; Wa-mal lam yahkum bimaaa anzalal laahu fa-ulaaa'ika humuz zalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 715,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaffainaa 'alaaa aasaaarihim bi-'Eesab ni Maryama musaddiqal limaa baina yadaihi minat Tawraati Wa-aatainaahul Injeela feehi hudanw Wa-noorunw Wa-musaddiqal limaa baina yadaihi minat Tawraati Wa-hudanw Wa-maw'izatal lilmuttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 716,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Walyahkum Ahlul Injeeli bimaaa anzalal laahu feeh; Wa-mal lam yahkum bimaaa anzalal laahu fa-ulaaa'ika humul faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 717,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-anzalnaa ilaikal Kitaaba bilhaqqi musaddiqal limaa baina yadaihi minal Kitaabi Wa-muhaiminan 'alaihi fahkum bainahum bimaa anzalal laahu Wa-laa tattabi' ahwaaa'ahum 'ammaa jaaa'aka minal haqq; likullin ja'alnaa minkum shir'atanw Wa-minhaajaa; Wa-law shaaa'al laahu laja'alakum ummatanw waahidatanw Wa-laakil liyabluwakum fee maa aataakum fastabiqul khairaat; ilal laahi marji'ukum jamee'an fa-yunab-bi'ukum bimaa kuntum feehi takhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 718,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Wa-anih kum bainahum bimaaa anzalal laahu Wa-laa tattabi' ahwaaa'ahum wahzarhum aien yaftinooka 'am ba'di maaa anzalal laahu ilaika fa-in tawallaw fa'lam annamaa yureedul laahu aien yuseebahum biba'di zunoobihim; Wa-inna kaseeram minan naasi lafaasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 719,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Afahukmal jaahiliyyati yabghoon; Wa-man ahsanu minal laahi hukmal liqawmien yooqinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 720,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tattakhizul Yahooda wan-nasaaraaa awliyaaa'; ba'duhum awliyaaa'u ba'd; Wa-main yatawallahum minkum fa-innahoo minhum; innal laaha laa yahdil qawmaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 721,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Fataral lazeena fee quloobihim maraduien yusaari'oona feehim yaqooloona nakhshaaa an tuseebanaa daaa'irah; fa'asal laahu aien ya-tiya bilfathi aw amrim min 'indihee fa-yusbihoo 'alaa maaa asarroo feee anfusihim naadimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 722,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaqoolul lazeena aamanooo ahaaa'ulaaa'il lazeena aqsamoo billaahi jahda aimaanihim innahum lama'akum; habitat a'maaluhum fa-asbahoo khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 723,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Yaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo maien yartadda minkum 'an deenihee fasawfa ya'til laahu biqawmien yuhibbuhum Wa-yuhibboonahoo azillatin 'alal mu'mineena a'izzatin 'alal kaafireena yujaahidoona fee sabeelil laahi Wa-laa yakhaafoona lawmata laaa'im; zaalika fadlul laahi yu'teehi maien yashaaa'; wallaahu Waasi'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 724,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Innamaa waliyyukumul laahu Wa-Rasooluhoo wal-lazeena aamanul lazeena yuqeemoonas Salaata Wa-yu'toonaz Zakaata Wa-hum raaki'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 725,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yatawallal laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo wallazeena aamanoo fa-inna hizbal laahi humul ghaaliboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 726,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tattakhizul lazeenat takhazoo deenakum huzuwanw Wa-la'ibam minal lazeena ootul Kitaaba min qablikum walkuffaara awliyaaa'; wattaqul laaha in kuntum muu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 727,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa naadaitum ilas Salaatit takhazoohaa huzu-wan'w Wa-la'ibaa; zaalika biannahum qawmul laa ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 728,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Qul yaaa-Ahlal Kitaabi hal tanqimoona minnaaa illaaa an aamannaa billaahi Wa-maaa unzila ilainaa Wa-maa unzila min qablu Wa-anna aksarakum faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 729,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Qul hal unabbi'ukum bisharrim min zaalika masoobatan 'indal laah(i); mal la'ana-hul laahu Wa-ghadiba 'alaihi Wa-ja'ala min-humul qiradata wal-khanaazeera Wa-'abadat Taaghoot; ulaaa'ika sharrum makaananw Wa-adallu 'an Sawaaa'is Sabeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 730,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa jaaa'ookum qaalooo aamannaa Wa-qad dakhaloo bilkufri Wa-hum qad kharajoo bih; wallaahu a'lamu bimaa kaanoo yaktumoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 731,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Wa-taraa kaseeram minhum yusaari'oona fil ismi wal'udwaani Wa-aklihimus suht; labi'sa maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 732,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Law-laa yanhaahumur rabbaaniyyoona wal-ahbaaru 'an qawlihimul ismaa Wa-aklihimus suht; labi'sa maa kaanoo yasna'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 733,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalatil Yahoodu Yadul laahi maghloolah; ghullat aideehim Wa-lu'inoo bimaa qaaloo; bal yadaahu mabsoo-tataani yunfiqu kaifa yashaaa'; Wa-la-yazeedanna kaseeramm minhum maaa unzila ilaika mir Rabbika tughyaananw Wa-kufraa; Wa-alqainaa bainahumul 'adaawata wal-baghdaaa a'-ilaa Yawmil Qiyaamah; kullamaaa awqadoo naaral lilharbi at-fa-ahal laah; Wa-yas'awna fil ardi fasaadaa(nw); wal-laahu laa yuhibbul mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 734,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Wa-law anna Ahlal Kitaabi aamanoo wattaqaw lakaffarnaa 'anhum saiyiaatihim Wa-la-adkhalnaahum Jannaatin Na'eem"
    },
    {
      "index": 735,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Wa-law annahum aqaamut Tawraata wal-Injeela Wa-maaa unzila ilaihim mir Rabbihim la-akaloo min fawqihim Wa-min tahti arjulihim; minhum ummatum muqta-sida(tunw) Wa-kaseerum minhum saaa'a maa ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 736,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhar Rasoolu balligh maaa unzila ilaika mir Rabbika Wa-il lam taf'al famaaa ballaghta Risaalatah; wallaahu ya'simuka minan naas; innal laaha laa yahdil qawmal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 737,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Qul yaaa-Ahlal Kitaabi lastum 'alaa shai'in hattaa tuqeemut Tawraata wal-Injeela Wa-maaa unzila ilaikum mir Rabbikum; Wa-layazeedanna kaseeram minhum maa unzila ilaika mir Rabbika tugh-yaananw Wa-kufra(n) falaa taasa 'alal qawmil kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 738,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo wallazeena haadoo was-saabi'oona wan-Nasaaraa man aamana billaahi wal-yawmil Aakhiri Wa-'amila saalihan falaa khawfun 'alaihim Wa-laa hum yahzanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 739,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Laqad akhaznaa meesaaqa Banee Israaa'eela Wa-arsalnaaa ilaihim Rusula(n) kullamaa jaaa'ahum Rasoolum bimaa laa tahwaaa anfusuhum fareeqan kazzaboo Wa-fareeqaien yaqtuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 740,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wa-hasibooo allaa takoona fitnatun fa'amoo Wa-sammoo summa taabal laahu 'alaihim summa 'amoo Wa-sammoo kaseerum minhum; wallaahu baseerum bimaa ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 741,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Laqad kafaral lazeena qaalooo innal laaha Huwal maseehub nu Maryama Wa-qaalal Maseehu yaa-Baneee Israaa'eela u'budul laaha Rabbee Wa-Rabbakum innahoo maien yushrik billaahi faqad harramal laahu 'alaihil janna(ta) Wa-ma-waahun Naar(u) Wa-maa lizzaalimeena min ansaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 742,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "laqad kafaral lazeena qaalooo innal laaha saalisu salaasah; Wa-maa min ilaahin illaaa Ilaahunw Waahid; Wa-il lam yantahoo 'ammaa yaqooloona layamas-sannal lazeena kafaroo minhum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 743,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Afalaa yatooboona ilal laahi Wa-yastaghfiroonahu; wallaahu Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 744,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Mal Maseehub nu Maryama illaa Rasoolun qad khalat min qablihir Rusulu Wa-ummuhoo siddeeqatun kaanaa yaa-kulaanit ta'aam; unzur kaifa nubaiyyinu lahumul Aayaati suman zur annaa yu'fakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 745,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Qul ata'budoona min doonil laahi maa laa yamliku lakum darranw Wa-laa naf'aa; wallaahu Huwas Samee'ul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 746,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Qul yaaa-Ahlal Kitaabi laa taghloo fee deenikum ghairal haqq(i) Wa-laa tattabi'ooo ahwaaa'a qawmin qad dalloo min qablu Wa-adalloo kaseeranw Wa-dalloo 'an Sawaaa'is Sabeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 747,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Lu'inal lazeena kafaroo mim Baneee israa'eela 'alaa lisaani Daawooda Wa-'Eesab ni Maryam; zaalika bimaa 'asaw Wa-kaanoo ya'tadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 748,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Kaanoo laa yatanaa-hawna 'am munkarin fa'alooh; labi'sa maa kaanoo yafa'loon"
    },
    {
      "index": 749,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Taraa kaseeram minhum yatawallawnal lazeena kafaroo; labi'sa maa qaddamat lahum anfusuhum an sakhital laahu 'alaihim Wa-fil 'azaabi hum khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 750,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Wa-law kaanoo yu'minoona billaahi wan-nabiyyi Wa-maa unzila ilaihi mat takhazoohum awliyaaa'a Wa-laakinna kaseeram minhum faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 751,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Latajidanna ashad-dan naasi 'adaawatal lillazeena aamanul Yahooda wallazeena ashrakoo Wa-latajidanna aqrabahum mawaddatal lil-lazeena aamanul lazeena qaalooo innaa Nasaaraa; zaalika bi-anna minhum qiseeseena Wa-ruh-baananw Wa-annahum laa yastakbiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 752,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa sami'oo maa unzila ilar Rasooli taraa a'yunahum tafeedu minad dam'i mimmaa 'arafoo minal haqq; yaqooloona Rabbanaa aamannaa faktubnaa ma'ash shaahideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 753,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa lanaa laa nu'minu billaahi Wa-maa jaaa'anaa minal haqqi Wa-natma'u aien yudkhilanaa Rabbunaa ma'al qawmis saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 754,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Fa-asaabahumul laahu bimaa qaaloo Jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaar(u) khaalideena feehaa; Wa-zaalika jazaaa'ul muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 755,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kafaroo Wa-kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa ulaaa'ika As-haabul Jaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 756,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Yaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tuharrimoo taiyyibaati maa ahallal laahu lakum Wa-laa ta'tadooo; innal laaha laa yuhibbul mu'tadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 757,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Wa-kuloo mimmaa raza-qakumul laahu halaalan taiyyibaa; wattaqul laahal lazeee antum bihee mu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 758,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Laa yu'aakhizukumul laahu billaghwi fee aimaanikum Wa-laakien yu'aakhizukum bimaa 'aqqattumul aimaan(a) fakaf-faaratuhoo it'aamu 'asharati masaakeena min awsati maa tut'imoona ahleekum aw kiswatuhum aw tahreeru raqaba(tin) famal lam yajid fa-Siyaamu salaasati aiy-yaam; zaalika kaffaaratu aimaanikum izaa halaftum; wahfazooo aimaanakum; kazaalika yubaiyyinul laahu lakum Aayaatihee la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 759,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanooo innamal khamru walmaisiru wal-ansaabu wal-azlaamu rijsum min 'amalish shaitaani fajtaniboohu la'al-lakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 760,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Innamaa yureedush Shaitaanu aien yooqi'a bainakumul 'adaawata wal-baghdaaa'a fil khamri wal-maisir(i) Wa-yasuddakum 'an zikril laahi Wa-'anis Salaati fahal antum muntahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 761,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Wa-atee'ul laaha Wa-atee'ur Rasoola wahzaroo; fa-in tawal-laitum fa'lamooo annamaa 'alaa Rasoolinal balaaghul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 762,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Laisa 'alal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati junaahun feemaa ta'imooo izaa mat taqaw Wa-aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati summat taqaw Wa-aamanoo summat taqaw Wa-ahsanoo; wallaahu yuhibbul muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 763,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Yaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo la-yablu-wanna-kumul laahu bishai'im minas saidi tanaa-luhooo aideekum Wa-rimaahukum liya'lamal laahu maien yakhaafuhoo bilghaib; famani' tadaa ba'da zaalika falahoo 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 764,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Yaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa taqtulus saida Wa-antum hurum; Wa-man qatalahoo minkum mut'am-midan fajazaaa'um mislu maa qatala minan na'am(i) yahkumu bihee zawaa 'adlim minkum hadyam baalighal Ka'ba(ti) aw kaffaaratun ta'aamu masaakeena aw 'adlu zaalika Siyaamal liyazooqa wabaala amrih; 'afal laahu 'ammaa salaf; Wa-man 'aada fayanta-qimul laahu minh; wallaahu 'azeezun zun tiqaam"
    },
    {
      "index": 765,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Uhilla lakum saidul bahri Wa-ta'aamuhoo mataa'al lakum Wa-lis-saiyyaara(ti) Wa-hurrima 'alaikum saidul barri maa dumtum hurumaa; wattaqul laahal lazeee ilaihi tuh-sharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 766,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Ja'alal laahul Ka'batal Baital Haraama qiyaamal linnaasi wash-Shahral Haraama wal-hadya wal-qalaaa'id; zaalika lita'lamooo annal laaha ya'lamu maa fis samaawaati Wa-maa fil ardi Wa-annal laaha bikulli shai'in 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 767,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "I'lamooo annal laaha shadeedul 'iqaabi Wa-annal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 768,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Maa 'alar Rasooli illal balaaghu; wallaahu ya'lamu maa tubdoona Wa-maa taktumoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 769,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Qul laa yastawil khabeesu wattaiyyibu Wa-law a'jabaka kasratul khabees; fattaqul laaha yaaa-ulil albaabi la'allakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 770,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tas'aloo 'an ashyaaa'a in tubda lakum tasu'kum Wa-in tas'aloo 'anhaa heena yunazzalul Qur'aanu tubda lakum; 'afal laahu 'anhaa; wallaahu Ghafoorun Haleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 771,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 102,
      "text": "Qad sa-alahaa qawmum min qablikum summa asbahoo bihaa kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 772,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Maa ja'alal laahu mim baheeratinw Wa-laa saaa'ibatinw Wa-laa waseelatinw Wa-laa haaminw Wa-laakinnal lazeena kafaroo yaftaroona 'alal laahil kazib; Wa-aksaruhum laa ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 773,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahum ta'aalaw ilaa maaa anzalal laahu Wa-ilar Rasooli qaaloo hasbunaa maa wajadnaa 'alaihi aabaaa'anaa; awa-law kaana aabaaa'uhum laa ya'lamoona shai'anw Wa-laa yahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 774,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo 'alaikum anfusakum laa yadurrukum man dalla izah tadaitum; ilal laahi marji'ukum jamee'an fayunabbi'ukum bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 775,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo shahaadatu bainikum izaa hadara ahadakumul mawtu heenal wasiyyatis naani zawaa 'adlim minkum aw aakharaani min ghairikum in antum darabtum fil ardi fa-asaabatkum museebatul mawt; tahbi-soonahumaa mim ba'dis Salaati fa-yuqsimaani billaahi inir tabtum laa nashtaree bihee samananw Wa-law kaana zaa qurbaa Wa-laa naktumu shahaadatal laahi innaaa izal laminal aasimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 776,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Fa-in 'usira 'alaaa annahumas tahaqqaaa isman fa-aakharaani yaqoomaani maqaama-humaa minal lazeenas tahaqqa 'alaihimul aw-layaani fa-yuqsimaani billaahi lashahaadatunaaa ahaqqu min shahaadati-himaaa Wa-ma' tadainaaa innaaa izal laminaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 777,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Zaalika adnaaa aien ya'too bishshahaadati 'alaa wajhi-haaa aw yakhaafooo an turadda aimaanum ba'da aimaanihim; wattaqul laaha wasma'oo; wallaahu laa yahdil qawmal faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 778,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Yawma yajma'ul laahur Rusula fa-yaqoolu maazaaa ujibtum qaaloo laa 'ilma lanaa innaka Anta 'Allaamul Ghuyoob"
    },
    {
      "index": 779,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Iz qaalal laahu yaa-'Eesab na Maryamaz kur ni'matee 'alaika Wa-'alaa waalidatika; iz aiyyattuka bi-Roohil Qudus(i) tukallimun naasa fil mahdi Wa-kahla(nw) Wa-iz 'allamtukal kitaaba wal-Hikmata Wa-Tawraata wal-Injeel(a) Wa-iz takhluqu minat teeni kahai-'atit tairi bi-iznee fatan-fukhu feeha fatakoonu tairam bi-iznee Wa-tubri'ul akmaha wal-abrasa bi-iznee Wa-iz tukhrijul mawtaa bi-iznee Wa-iz kafaftu Baneee Israaa'eela 'anka iz ji'tahum bil-baiyyinaati fa-qaalal lazeena kafaroo minhum in haazaaa illaa sihrum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 780,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz aw-haitu ilal hawaariy-yeena an aaminoo bee Wa-bi-Rasoolee qaalooo aamannaa wash-had bi-anna-naa muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 781,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "Iz qaalal hawaariy-yoona yaa-'Eesab na Maryama hal yastatee'u Rabbuka aien yunaz-zila alainna maaa'idatam minas samaaa'(i) qaalat taqul laaha in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 782,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo nureedu an na-kula minhaa Wa-tatama-'inna quloo-bunaa Wa-na'lama an qad sadaqtana Wa-nakoona 'alaihaa minash shaahideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 783,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 114,
      "text":
          "Qaala 'Eesab nu Maryamal laahumma Rabbanaaa anzil 'alainaa maaa'idatam minas samaaa'(i) takoonu lanaa 'eedal li-awwalinaa Wa-aakhirinaa Wa-Aayatam minka warzuqnaa Wa-Anta khairur raaziqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 784,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Qaalal laahu innee munaz-ziluhaa 'alaikum famaien yakfur ba'du minkum fa-inneee u'azzibuhoo 'azaabal laaa u'azzibuhooo ahadam minal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 785,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaalal laahu yaa-'Eesab na Maryama 'a-anta qulta linnaasit takhizoonee Wa-ummiya ilaahaini min doonil laahi qaala Subhaanak(a) maa yakkoonu leee an aqoola maa laisa lee bihaqq; in kuntu qultuhoo faqad 'alimtah; ta'lamu maa fee nafsee Wa-laaa a'alamu maa fee nafsika; innaka Anta 'Allaamul Ghuyoob"
    },
    {
      "index": 786,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Maa qultu lahum illaa maaa amartanee bihee ani' budul laaha Rabbeee Wa-Rabbakum; Wa-kuntu 'alaihim shaheedam maa dumtu feehim falammaa tawaffai-tanee kunta Antar Raqeeba 'alaihim; Wa-Anta 'alaa kulli shai'in Shaheed"
    },
    {
      "index": 787,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 118,
      "text":
          "In tu'azzibhum fa-innahum ibaaduka Wa-in taghfir lahum fa-innaka Antal 'Azzezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 788,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 119,
      "text":
          "Qaalal laahu haaza yawmu yanfa'us saadiqeena sidquhum; lahum janaatunn tajree min tah-tihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaaa abadaa; radiyal laahu 'anhum Wa-radoo 'anh; zaalikal fawzul 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 789,
      "sura": 5,
      "aya": 120,
      "text":
          "Lillaahi mulkus samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-maa feehinn; Wa-Huwa 'alaa kulli shai'inn Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 790,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Alhamdu lillaahil lazee khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda Wa-ja'alaz zulumaati wannoor(a); summal lazeena kafaroo bi-Rabbihim ya'diloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 791,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazee khalaqakum min teenin summa qadaaa ajalanw Wa-ajalum musamman 'indah(u) summa antum tamtaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 792,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal laahu fis samaawaati Wa-fil ardi ya'lamu sirrakum Wa-jahrakum Wa-ya'lamu maa taksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 793,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa ta'teehim min Aayatim min Aayaati Rabbihim illaa kaanoo 'anhaa mu'rideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 794,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Faqad kazzaboo bilhaqqi lammaa jaaa'ahum fasawfa ya'teehim ambaaa'u maa kaanoo bihee yas-tahzi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 795,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Alam yarau kam ahlaknaa min qablihim min qarnim makkannaahum fil ardi maa lam numakkil lakum Wa-arsalnas samaaa'a 'alaihim midraara(nw) Wa-ja'alnal anhaara tajree min tah-tihim fa-ahlak-naahum bizunoobihim Wa-ansha'naa mim ba'dihim qarnan aakhareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 796,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-lau nazzalnaa 'alaika Kitaaban fee qirtaasin falama-soohu bi-aideehim laqaalal lazeena kafarooo in haazaaa illaa sihrum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 797,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo lau-laaa unzila alaihi malak(unw) Wa-lau anzalna malakal laqudiyal amru summa laa yunzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 798,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wa-lau ja'alnaahu malakal laja'alnaahu rajulanw Wa-la-labasnaa 'alaihim maa yalbisoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 799,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqadis tuhzi'a bi-Rusulim min qablika fahaaqa billazeena sakhiroo minhum maa kaanoo bihee yastahzi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 800,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Qul seeroo fil ardi summan zuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul mukazzibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 801,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Qul limam maa fis samaawaati wal-ardi qul lillaah; kataba 'alaa nafsihir rahmah; la-yajma-'annakum ilaa Yawmil Qiyaamati laa raiba feeh; allazeena khasirooo an-fusahum fahum laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 802,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-lahoo maa sakana fil lai-li wan-nahaari; Wa-Huwas Samee'ul Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 803,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Qul aghairal laahi attakhizu waliyyan faatiris samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-Huwa yut'imu Wa-laa yut'am; qul inneee umirtu an akoona awwala man aslama Wa-laa takoo-nanna minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 804,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 15,
      "text": "Qul inneee akhaafu in 'asaitu Rabbee 'azaaba Yawmin 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 805,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Maien yusraf 'anhu Yawma'izin faqad rahimahu; Wa-zaalikal fawzul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 806,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Wa-ien yum-saskal laahu bidurrin falaaa kaashifa lahoo illaa Huw(a) Wa-ien yum-saska bikhairin fa-Huwa 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 807,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 18,
      "text": "Wa-Huwal qaahiru fauqa 'ibaadihi; Wa-Huwal Hakeemul Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 808,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Qul ayyu shai'in akbaru shahaada(tan) qulil laahu shaheedum bainee Wa-bainakum; Wa-oohiya ilaiyya haazal Qur'aanu li-unzirakum bihee Wa-mam balagh; a'innakum latash-hadoona anna ma'al laahi aalihatan ukhraa; qul laaa ashhad; qul innamaa Huwa Ilaahunw Waahidunw Wa-innanee bareeee'um mimmaa tushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 809,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Allazeena aatainaa-humul Kitaaba ya'rifoonahoo kamaa ya'rifoona abnaaa'ahum; allazeena khasirooo an-fusahum fahum laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 810,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-man azlamu mim-manif tara 'alal laahi kaziban aw kazzaba bi-Aayaatih; innahoo laa yuflihuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 811,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-yawma nah-shuruhum jamee'an summa naqoolu lil-lazeena ashrakooo aina shura-kaaa'ukumul lazeena kuntum taz'umoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 812,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Summa lam takun fitna-tuhum illaaa an qaaloo wallaahi Rabbinaa maa kunnaa mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 813,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Unzur kaifa kazaboo 'alaaa an-fusihim, Wa-dalla 'anhum maa kaanoo yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 814,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-minhum maien yastami'u ilaik(a) wa-ja'alnaa 'alaa quloobihim akin-natan aien yafqa-hoohu wa-feee aazaa-nihim waqraa; wa-in yarau kulla Aayatil laa yu'minoo bihaa; hattaaa izaa jaaa'ooka yujaadi-loonaka yaqoolul lazeena kafaroo in haazaa illaaa asaateerul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 815,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Wa-hum yan-hauna 'anhu wa-yan-awna 'anh(u) wa-ien yuh-likoona illaa an-fusahum wa-maa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 816,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wa-lau taraaa iz wuqifoo 'alan Naari faqaaloo yaa-laitanaa nuraddu wa-laa nukaz-ziba bi-Aayaati Rabbinaa wa-nakoona minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 817,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Bal badaa lahum maa kaanoo yukhfoona min qabl(u) wa-lau ruddoo la'aadoo limaa nuhoo 'anhu wa-innahum la-kaaziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 818,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalooo in hiya illaa hayaa-tunad dunyaa wa-maa nahnu bimab'ooseen"
    },
    {
      "index": 819,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Wa-lau taraa iz wuqifoo 'alaa Rabbihim; qaala alaisa haazaa bilhaqqi; qaaloo balaa wa-Rabbinaa; qaala fazooqul 'azaaba bimaa kuntum takfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 820,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Qad khasiral lazeena kazzaboo bil-liqaaa'il laah(i) hattaaa izaa jaaa'at-humus Saa'atu bagh-tatan qaaloo yaa-hasratanaa 'alaa maa farratnaa feehaa wa-hum yah-miloona awzaarahum 'alaa zuhoorihim; alaa saaa'a ma yaziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 821,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wa-mal hayaatud dunyaaa illaa la'ibunw Wa-lah-wunw wa-lad-daarul Aakhiratu khairul lillazeena yattaqoon; afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 822,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Qad na'lamu innahoo layah-zunukal lazee yaqooloona fa-innahum laa yukazzi-bunaka wa-laakinnaz zaalimeena bi-Aayaatil laahi yaj-hadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 823,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad kuzzibat Rusulum min qablika fasabaroo 'alaa maa kuzziboo Wa-oozoo hattaaa ataahum nasrunaa; wa-laa mubaddila li-kalimaatil laah; wa-laqad jaaa'aka min naba'il mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 824,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-in kaana kabura 'alaika i'raaduhum fa-inis tata'ta an tabtaghiya nafaqan fil ardi aw sullaman fis samaaa'i fata'tiyahum bi-Aayah; Wa-lau shaaa'al laahu lajama'ahum 'alal hudaa; falaa takoo-nanna minal jaahileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 825,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Innamaa yastajeebul lazeena yasma'oon; wal-mawtaa yab'asu-humul laahu summa ilaihi yurja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 826,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo lau-laa nuzzila 'alaihi Aayatum mir Rabbih; qul innal laaha qaadirun 'alaaa aien yunazzila Aayatanw walaa-kinna aksarahum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 827,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa min daaab-batin fil ardi Wa-laa taaa'irien yateeru bijanaa-haihi illaaa umamun amsaalukum; maa farratnaa fil Kitaabi min shaiyy' summa ilaa Rabbihim yuh-sharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 828,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa summunw wa-bukmun fiz zulumaat(i); maien yasha-il laahu yud-lilhu; wa-maien yashaa yaj'alhu 'alaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 829,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Qul ara'aitakum in ataakum 'azaabul laahi aw atat-kumus Saa'a(tu) a-ghairal laahi tad'oona in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 830,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Bal iyyaahu tad'oona fa-yak-shifu maa tad'oona ilaihi in shaaa'a wa-tansauna maa tushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 831,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad arsalnaaa ilaaa umamim min qablika fa-akhaz-naahum bil-ba'saaa'i wad-darraaa'i la'allahum yata-darra'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 832,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Falau-laaa iz jaaa'ahum ba'sunaa tadarra'oo wa-laakin qasat quloobuhum wa-zaiyyana lahu-mush Shaitaanu maa kaanu ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 833,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Falammaa nasoo maa zukkiroo bihee fatahnaa 'alaihim abwaaba kulli shai(in) hattaaa izaa farihoo bimaaa ootooo akhaz-naahum baghta(tan) fa-izaa hum mublisoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 834,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Faquti'a daa-birul qawmil lazeena zalamoo; walhamdu lillaahi Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 835,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Qul ara'aitum in akhazal laahu sam'akum wa-absaarakum wa-khatama 'alaa quloobikum man ilaahun ghairul laahi ya'teekum bih; unzur kaifa nusarriful Aayaati summa hum yasdifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 836,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Qul ara'aitakum in ataakum 'azaabul laahi baghtatan aw jahra(tan) hal yuhlaku illal qawmuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 837,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa nursilul mursaleena illaa mubash-shireena wa-munzireen(a) faman aamana wa-aslaha falaa khaufun 'alaihim wa-laa hum yahzanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 838,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa yamas-suhumul 'azaabu bimaa kaanu yaf-suqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 839,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Qul laaa aqoolu lakum 'indee khazaaa'inul laahi wa-laaa a'lamul ghaiba wa-laaa aqoolu lakum innee malak(un) in attabi'u illaa maa yuhaaa ilaiy; qul hal yastawil a'maa wal-baseeru; afalaa tata-fakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 840,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Wa-anzir bihil lazeena yakhaa-foona aien yuh-sharooo ilaa Rabbihim laisa lahum min doonihee waliy-yunw wa-laa shafee'ul la'allahum yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 841,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tatrudil lazeena yad'oona Rabbahum bil-ghadaati wal-'ashiyyi yureedoona waj-ha(hu) ma 'alaika min hisaa-bihim min shai(inw) wa-maa min hisaabika 'alaihim min shai(in) fatat-rudahum fatakoona minaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 842,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika fatan-naa ba'dahum biba'dil liya-qulooo ahaaa-ulaaa-e mannal laahu 'alaihim mim bai-ninaa; alaisal laahu bi-a'lama bish-shaakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 843,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa jaaa'akal lazeena yu'minoona bi-Aayaatinaa faqul salaamun 'alaikum kataba Rabbukum 'alaa nafsi-hir rahmata annahu man 'amila minkum sooo'am bijahaalatin summa taaba mim ba'dihee wa-aslaha fa-annahoo Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 844,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika nufassilul Aayaati Wali-tastabeena sabeelul mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 845,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Qul innee nuheetu an a'budal lazeena tad'oona min doonil laah; qul laaa attabi'u ahwaaa'akum qad dalaltu izanw wa-maaa ana minal muhtadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 846,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Qul innee 'alaa baiyyi-natim mir Rabbee wa-kazzabtum bih; maa 'indee maa tasta'jiloona bih; inil hukmu illaa lillaah(i) yaqussul haqqa wa-huwa khairul faasileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 847,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Qul lau anna 'indee maa tasta'jiloona bihee laqudiyal amru bainee wa-bainakum; wallaahu a'lamu biz-zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 848,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Wa-'indahoo mafaa-tihul ghaibi laa ya'lamuhaaa illaa hu; wa-ya'lamu maa fil barri wal-bahr; wa-maa tasqutu minw waraqatin illaa ya'lamuhaa wa-laa habbatin fee zulumaatil ardi wa-laa ratbinw wa-laa yaabisin illaa fee Kitaabim Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 849,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wa-huwal lazee yatawaf-faakum billaili wa-ya'lamu maa jarahtum bin-nahaar(i) summa yab'asukum feehee liyuqdaaa ajalum musamma(n) summa ilaihi marji'ukum summa yunabbi-'ukum bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 850,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-huwal qaahiru fawqa 'ibaadihee wa-yursilu 'alaikum hafaza(tan) hattaaa izaa jaaa'a ahadakumul mawtu tawaffathu rusulunaa wa-hum laa yufarritoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 851,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Summa ruddooo ilal laahi maulaahumul haqq; alaa lahul hukmu wa-huwa asra'ul haasibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 852,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Qul maien yunaj-jeekum min zulumaatil barri walbahri tad'oonahoo tadarru'anw wa-khufyatal la'in anjaanaa min haazihee lanaku-nanna minash shaakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 853,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Qulil laahu yunaj-jeekum minhaa wa-min kulli karbin summa antum tushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 854,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Qul huwal Qaadiru 'alaaa aien yab'asa 'alaikum 'azaabam min fawqikum aw min tahti arjulikum aw yalbisakum shiya'anw wa-yuzeeqa ba'dakum ba'sa ba'd; unzur kaifa nusarriful Aayaati la'allahum yafqahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 855,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Wa-kaz-zaba bihee qaumuka wa-huwal haqq; qul lastu 'alaikum biwakeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 856,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 67,
      "text": "Likulli naba-im mustaqar(runw) wa-saufa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 857,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa ra-aital lazeena yakhoodoona fee Aayaatinaa fa-a'rid 'anhum hattaa yakhudu fee hadeesin ghairih; wa-immaa yunsi-yannakash shaitaanu falaa taq'ud ba'daz zikraa ma'al qawmiz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 858,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa 'alal lazeena yattaqoona min hisaa-bihim min shai'inw wa-laakin zikraa la'allahum yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 859,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Wa-zaril lazeenat takhazoo deenahum la'ibanw wa-lah-wanw Wa-gharrat-humul hayaatud dunyaa; wa-zakkir bihee an tubsala nafsum bimaa kasabat laisa lahaa min doonil laahi waliyyunw wa-laa shafee'(unw) wa-in ta'dil kulla 'adlil laa yu'khaz minhaa; ulaaa-'ikal lazeena ubsiloo bimaa kasaboo lahum sharaabum min hamee-minw wa-'azaabun aleemum bimaa kaanu yakkfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 860,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Qul anad'oo min doonil laahi maa laa yanfa'unaa wa-laa yadur-runaa wa-nuraddu 'alaaa a'qaabina ba'da iz hadaanal laahu kal-lazis tahwat-hush shayaateenu fil ardi hairaana lahooo as-haa-buien yad'oo-nahooo ilal huda' tinaa; qul inna hudal laahi huwal hudaa wa-umirnaa linus-lima li-Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 861,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Wa-an aqeemus salaata wattaqoohu; wa-huwal lazeee ilaihi tuh-sharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 862,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-huwal lazee khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda bilhaqq; Wa-Yawma yaqoolu kun fa-yakoon; Qawluhul haqqu; Wa-lahul mulku Yawma yunfakhu fis Soor; 'Aalimul Ghaibi wash-shahaadati; wa-huwal Hakeemul Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 863,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaala Ibraaheemu li-abeehi Aazara atat-takhizu asnaa-man aaliha(tan) inneee araaka wa-qawmaka fee dalaalim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 864,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika nureee Ibraaheema malakootas samaawaati wal-ardi wa-liyakoona minal mooqineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 865,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Falammaa janna 'alaihil lailu ra-aa kau-kaban qaala haaza Rabbee falammaaa afala qaala laaa uhibbul aafileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 866,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Falammaa ra-al qamara baazighan qaala haazaa Rabbee falammaaa afala qaala la'il lam yahdinee Rabbee la-akunanna minal qawmid daaalleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 867,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Falammaa ra ash-shamsa baazighatan qaala haazaa Rabbee haazaaa akbar(u) falammaaa afalat qaala yaa-qawmi innee bareee'um mimmaa tushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 868,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Innee waj-jahtu wajhiya lillazee fataras samaawaati wal-arda haneefanw wa-maaa ana minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 869,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wa-haaj-jahoo qau-muh(u); qaala a-tuh-haaj-jooon-nee fil laahi wa-qad hadaan(i); wa-laaa akhaafu maa tushri-kuna bihee illaaa aien yashaaa'a Rabbee shai'a(nw) wasi'a Rabbee kulla shai'in 'ilman afalaa tata-zakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 870,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Wa-kaifa akhaafu maa ashraktum wa-laa takhaa-foona annakum ashraktum billaahi maa lam yunazzil bihee 'alaikum sultaanaa; fa-aiyyul fareeqaini ahaqqu bil-amni in kuntum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 871,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Allazeena aamanoo wa-lam yal-bisooo eemaanahum bizulmin ulaaa'ika lahumul amnu wa-hum muhtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 872,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Wa-tilka hujjatunaaa aatai-naahaaa Ibraaheema 'alaa qawmih; narfa'u dara-jaatim man nashaaa'; inna Rabbaka Hakeemun 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 873,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Wa-wahabnaa lahoo Iss-haaqa wa-Ya'qooba; kullan hadainaa; wa-Noohan hadainaa min qablu wa-min zurri-yatihee Daawooda wa-Sulaimaana wa-Ayyooba wa-Yoosufa wa-Moosaa wa-Haaroon; wa-kazaalika najzil muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 874,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Wa-Zakariyyaa wa-Yahyaa wa-'Eesaa wa-Illyaasa kullum minas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 875,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Wa-Ismaa'eela wal-Yasa'a wa-Yunusa wa-Lootan; wa-kullan faddalnaa 'alal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 876,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Wa-min aabaaa'ihim wa-zurri-yaatihim wa-ikhwaa-nihim waj-tabai-naahum wa-hadai-naahum ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 877,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Zaalika hudal laahi yahdee bihee maien yashaaa'u min 'ibaadih; wa-lau ashrakoo la-habita 'anhum maa kaanu ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 878,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena aatai-naahumul Kitaaba wal-hukma wan-Nubuwwah; fa-ien yakfur bihaa haaa'ulaaa'i faqad wak-kalnaa bihaa qawmal laisoo bihaa bikaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 879,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena hadal laahu fabi-hudaa-humuq tadih; qul laaa as'alukum 'alaihi ajran in huwa illaa zikraa lil-'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 880,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa qadarul laaha haqqa qadriheee iz qaaloo maaa anzalal laahu 'alaa basharim min shai'; qul man anzalal Kitaabal lazee jaaa'a bihee Moosaa nooranw Wa-hudal lin-naasi taj'aloo-nahoo qaraa-teesa tubdoonahaa Wa-tukhfoona kaseera(nw) Wa-'ullimtum maa lam ta'lamooo antum Wa-laaa aabaaa'ukum qulil laahu summa zarhum fee khawdihim yal'aboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 881,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Wa-haazaa Kitaabun anzalnaahu Mubaarakum musaddiqul lazee bainaa yadaihi Wa-litunzira ummal Quraa Wa-man hawlahaa; wallazeena yu'minoona bil-Aakhirati yu'minoona bihee Wa-hum 'alaa Salaatihim yuhaafizoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 882,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Wa-man azlamu mimmanif taraa 'alal laahi kaziban aw qaala oohiya ilaiyya Wa-lam yooha ilaihi shai'un Wa-man qaala sa-unzilu misla maaa anzalal laah; Wa-law taraaa iziz zaalimoona fee ghamaraatil mawti walmalaaa'ikatu baasitooo aideehim akhrijooo anfusakum; al-yawma tujzawna 'azaabal hooni bimaa kuntum taqooloona 'alal laahi ghairal haqqi Wa-kuntum 'an aayaatihee tastakbiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 883,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad ji'tumoonaa furaadaa kamaa khalaqnaakum awwala marra(tinw) Wa-taraktum maa khawwal-naakum waraaa'a zuhoorikum Wa-maa naraa ma'akum shufa'aaa'-akumul lazeena za'amtum annahum feekum shurakaaa'; laqat taqatta'a bainakum Wa-dalla 'annkum maa kuntum taz'umoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 884,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha faaliqul habbi wannawaa yukhrijul haiyya minal maiyyiti Wa-mukhrijul maiyyiti minal haiy; zaalikumul laahu fa-annaa tu'fakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 885,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Faaliqul isbaahi Wa-ja'alal laila sakananw wash-shamsa walqamara husbaanaa; zaalika taqdeerul 'Azeezil 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 886,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee ja'ala lakumun nujooma litahtadoo bihaa fee zulumaatil barri walbahr; qad fassalnal Aayaati liqaw-mien ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 887,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Wa-huwal lazeee ansha-akum min nafsinw waahidatin famus-taqarrunw Wa-mustawda'; qad fassalnal Aayaati liqaw mien-yafqahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 888,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazeee anzala minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa-akhrajnaa bihee nabaata kulli shai('in) fa-akhrajnaa minhu khadiran nukhriju minhu habbam mutaraakiba(nw) Wa-minan nakhli min tal'ihaa qin-waanun daaniyatunw Wa-jannaatim min a'naab(inw) wazzaitoona warrummaana mushtabihanw Wa-ghaira mutashaabih; unzurooo ilaa samariheee izaaa asmara Wa-yan'ih; inna fee zaalikum la-Aayaatil liqawmien yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 889,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'aloo lillaahi shurakaaa'al jinna Wa-khalaqa-hum Wa-kharaqoo lahoo baneena Wa-banaatim bighairi 'ilm Subhaanahoo Wa-Ta'aalaa 'amma yasifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 890,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Badee'us samaawaati wal-ardi annnaa yakoonu lahoo waladunw Wa-lam takul lahoo saahiba(tunw) Wa-khalaqa kulla shain'inw Wa-Huwa bikulli shai'in 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 891,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Zaalikumul laahu Rabbukum laaa ilaaha illaa huwa khaaliqu kulli shai'in fa'budooh; Wa-huwa 'alaa kulli shai'inw Wakeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 892,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Laa tudrikuhul absaaru Wa-Huwa yudrikul absaara Wa-huwal Lateeful Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 893,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Qad jaaa'akum basaaa'iru mir Rabbikum faman absara fali-nafsihee Wa-man 'amiya fa'alaihaa; Wa-maaa ana 'alaikum bihafeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 894,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika nusarriful Aayaati Wa-liyaqooloo darasta Wali-nubaiyyi-nahoo liqawmien ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 895,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Ittabi' maaa oohiya ilaika mir Rabbika laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa Wa-a'rid 'anil mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 896,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Wa-law shaaa'al laahu maaa ashrakoo; Wa-maa ja'alnaaka 'alaihim hafeezanw Wa-maaa anta 'alaihim biwakeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 897,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tasubbul lazeena yad'oona min doonil laahi fa-yasubbul laaha 'adwam bighairi 'ilm; kazaalika zaiyannaa likulli ummatin 'amalahum summa ilaa Rabbihim marji'uhum fa-yunabbi'uhum bimaa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 898,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Wa-aqsamoo billaahi jahda aimaanihim la'in jaaa'at-hum Aayatul la-yu'minunna bihaa; qul innamal Aayaatu 'indal laah(i) Wa-maa yush'irukum annahaaa izaa jaaa'at laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 899,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Wa-nuqallibu af'idatahum Wa-absaarahum kamaa lam yu'minoo biheee awwala marratinw Wa-nazaruhum fee tughyaanihim ya'mahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 900,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Wa-law annanaa nazzal-naaa ilaihimul malaaa'ikata Wa-kallamahumul mawtaa Wa-hasharnaa 'alaihim kulla shai'in qubulam maa kaanoo liyu'minooo illaaa aien yashaaa'al laah(u) Wa-laakinna aksarahum yajhaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 901,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika ja'alnaa likulli nabiyyin 'aduwwan Shayaateenal insi waljinni yoohee ba'duhum ilaa ba'din zukhrufal qawli ghurooraa; Wa-law shaaa'a Rabbuka maa fa'aloohu fazarhum Wa-maa yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 902,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "Wa-litasghaaa ilaihi af'idatul lazeena laa yu'minoona bil-Aakhirati Wa-liyardawhu Wa-liyaqtarifoo maa hum muqtarifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 903,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 114,
      "text":
          "Afaghairal laahi abtaghee hakamanw Wa-Huwal lazee anzala ilaikumul Kitaaba mufassalaa; wallazeena ataien-naahumul Kitaaba ya'lamoona annahoo munazzalum mir Rabbika bilhaqqi falaa takoonanna minal mumtareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 904,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Wa-tammat Kalimatu Rabbika sidqanw Wa-'adlaa; laa mubaddila li-Kalimaatih; Wa-Huwas Samee'ul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 905,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Wa-in tuti' aksara man fil ardi yudillooka 'an sabeelil laah; ien yattabi'oona illaz zanna Wa-in hum illaa yakhrusoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 906,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Inna rabbaka Huwa a'lamu maien yadillu 'an sabeelihee Wa-Huwa a'lamu bilmuhtadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 907,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 118,
      "text":
          "Fakuloo mimmmaa zukiras mul laahi 'alaihi in kuntum bi-Aayaatihee mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 908,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 119,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa lakum allaa ta'kuloo mimmaa zukiras mul laahi 'alaihi Wa-qad fassala lakum maa harrama 'alaikum illaa mad turirtum ilaih; Wa-inna kaseeral la-yudilloona bi-ahwaaa'ihim bighairi 'ilm; inna Rabbaka Huwa a'lamu bilmu'tadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 909,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 120,
      "text":
          "Wa-zaroo zaahiral ismi Wa-baatinah; innal lazeena yaksiboonal ismaa sa-yujzawna bimaa kaanoo yaqtarifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 910,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 121,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa ta'kuloo mimmaa lam yuzkaris mul laahi 'alaihi Wa-innahoo lafisq; Wa-innash Shayaateena la-yoohoona ilaaa awliyaaa'ihim liyujaadilookum Wa-in ata'tumoohum innakum lamushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 911,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 122,
      "text":
          "Awa-man kaana maitan fa-ah-yaiynaahu Wa-ja'alnaa lahoo nooraien yamshee bihee fin naasi kamamm masaluhoo fiz zulumaati laisa bikhaarijim minhaa; kazaalika zuyyina lilkaafireena maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 912,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 123,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika ja'alnaa fee kulli qaryatin akaa-bira mujri-meehaa liyamkuroo feehaa Wa-maa yamkuroona illaa bi-anfusihim Wa-maa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 913,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 124,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa jaaa'athum Aayatun qaaloo lan nu'mina hatta nu'taa misla maaa ootiya Rusulul laah; Allahu a'almu haisu yaj'alu Risaalatah; sa-yuseebul lazeena ajramoo saghaarun 'indal laahi Wa-'azaabun shadeedum bimaa kaanoo yamkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 914,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 125,
      "text":
          "Famaien yuridil laahu aien yahdiyahoo yashrah sadrahoo lil-islaami Wa-maien yurid aien yudillahoo yaj'al sadrahoo daiyyiqan harajan ka-annamaa yassa'-adu fis samaaa'; kazaalika yaj'alul laahur rijsa 'alal lazeena laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 915,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 126,
      "text":
          "Wa-haazaa siraatu Rabbika Mustaqeemaa; qad fassalnal Aayaati liqawmien yazzakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 916,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 127,
      "text":
          "Lahum daarus salaami 'inda Rabbihim Wa-huwa waliyyuhum bimaa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 917,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 128,
      "text":
          "Wa-yawma yah-shuruhum jamee'a(ien) yaa-ma'sharal jinni qadis taksartum minal insi Wa-qaala awliyaa'uhum minal insi Rabbanas tamta'a ba'dunaa biba'dinw Wa-balaghnaaa ajalannal lazeee ajjalta lanaa; qaalan naaru maswaakum khaalideena feehaaa illaa maa shaaa 'allaah; inna Rabbaka Hakeemun 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 918,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 129,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika nuwallee ba'daz zaalimeena ba'dam bimaa kaanoo yaksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 919,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 130,
      "text":
          "Yaa-ma'sharal jinni wal-insi alam ya'tikum Rusulum minkum yaqussoona 'alaikum Aayaatee Wa-yunziroonakum liqaaa'a Yawmikum haazaa; qaaloo shahidnaa 'alaaa anfusinaa Wa-gharrat-humul hayaatud dunyaa Wa-shahidooo 'alaa anfusihim annahum kaanoo kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 920,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 131,
      "text":
          "Zaalika al lam yakkur Rabbuka muhlikal quraa bizulminw Wa-ahluhaa ghaafiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 921,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 132,
      "text":
          "Wa-likullin darajaatum mimmaa 'amiloo; Wa-maa Rabbuka bighaafilin 'ammaa ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 922,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 133,
      "text":
          "Wa-Rabbukal ghaniyyu zur rahmah(ti); ien yasha' yuz-hibkum Wa-yastakhlif mim ba'dikum maa yashaaa('u) kamaaa ansha-akum min zurriyyati qawmin aakhareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 923,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 134,
      "text": "Inna maa too'adoona la-aatinw Wa-maaa antum bimu'jizeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 924,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 135,
      "text":
          "Qul yaa-qawmi' maloo 'alaa makaanatikum innee 'aamil(un) fasawfa ta'lamoona man takoonu lahoo 'aaqibatud daar; innahoo laa yuflihuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 925,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 136,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'aloo lillaahi mimmaa zara-a minal harsi walan'aami naseeba(n) faqaaloo haazaa lillaahi biza'mihim Wa-haaza lishurakaa'inaa famaa kaana lishurakaaa'ihim falaa yasilu ilal laah(i) Wa-maa kaana lillaahi fahuwa yasilu ilaa shurakaaa'ihim; saaa'a maa yahkumoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 926,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 137,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika zaiyyana likaseerim minal mushrikeena qatla awlaadihim shurakaaa'uhum liyurdoohum Wa-liyalbisoo 'alaihim deenahum Wa-law shaaa'al laahu maa fa'aloohu fazarhum Wa-maa yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 927,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 138,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo haaziheee an'aamunw Wa-harsun hijrun laa yat'amuhaaa illaa man nashaaa'u biza'mihim Wa-an'aamun hurrimat zuhooruhaa Wa-an'aamul laa yazkuroonas mal laahi 'alaihaf tiraaa'an 'alaiyyh; sa-yajzeehim bimaa kaanoo yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 928,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 139,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo maa fee butooni haazihil an'aami khaalisatul lizukoorinaa Wa-muharramun 'alaaa azwaajinaa Wa-ien yakum maitatan fahum feehi shurakaaa'; sa-yajzeehim wasfahum; innahoo Hakeemun 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 929,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 140,
      "text":
          "Qad khasiral lazeena qatalooo awlaadahum safaham bighairi 'ilminw Wa-harramoo maa razaqahumul laahuf tiraaa'an 'alal laah; qad dalloo Wa-maa kaanoo muhtadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 930,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 141,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee ansha-a jannaatim ma'rooshaatinw Wa-ghaira ma'rooshaa(tinw) wan-nakhla wazzar'a mukhtalifan ukuluhoo wazzaitoona warrum-maana mutashaabiha(nw) Wa-ghaira mutashaabih; kuloo min samariheee izaaa asmara Wa-aatoo haqqahoo yawma hasaadihee Wa-laa tusrifoo; innahoo laa yuhibbul musrifeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 931,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 142,
      "text":
          "Wa-minal an'aami hamoolatanw Wa-farshaa; kuloo mimmaa razaqakumul laahu Wa-laa tattabi'oo khutuwaatish Shaitaan; innahoo lakum 'aduwwum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 932,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 143,
      "text":
          "Samaaniyata azwaaj(im) minad da'nis naini Wa-minal ma'zis nain; qul 'aaaz-zaka-raini harrama amil unsa-yaiyni ammash tamalat 'alaihi arhaamul unsayaiyn(i) nabbi-'oonee bi'ilmin in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 933,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 144,
      "text":
          "Wa-minal ibilis naini Wa-minal baqaris nain; qul 'aaaz-zakaraini harrama amil unsa-yaiyni ammash tamalat 'alaihi arhaamul unsa-yaiyn(i) am kuntum shuhadaaa'a iz wassaa-kumul laahu bihaazaa; faman azlamu mimmanif taraa 'alal laahi kazibal liyuddillan naasa bighairi 'ilm; innal laaha laa yahdil qawmaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 934,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 145,
      "text":
          "Qul laaa ajidu fee maaa oohiya ilaiyya muharraman 'alaa taa'imien yat'amuhooo illaaa aien yakoona maitatan aw damam masfoohan aw lahma khinzeerin fa-innahoo rijsun aw fisqan uhilla lighairil laahi bih; famanid turra ghaira baa-ghinw Wa-laa 'aadin fa-inna Rabbaka Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 935,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 146,
      "text":
          "Wa-'alal lazeena haadoo harramnaa kulla zee zufur(inw) Wa-minal baqari walghanami harramnaa 'alaihim shuhoo-mahumaaa illaa maa hamalat zuhoo-ruhumaaa awil hawaayaaa aw makh talata bi'azm; zaalika jazainaahum bibagh-yihim Wa-innaa la-saadiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 936,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 147,
      "text":
          "Fa-in kazzabooka faqur Rabbukum zoo rahmatinw waasi'a(tinw) Wa-laa yuraddu ba'suhoo 'anil qawmil mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 937,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 148,
      "text":
          "Sayaqoolul lazeena ashrakoo law shaaa'al laahu maaa ashraknaa Wa-laaa aabaaa'unaa Wa-laa harramnaa min shai'; kazaalika kazzabal lazeena min qablihim hattaa zaaqoo ba'sanaa; qul hal 'indakum min 'ilmin fatukh-rijoohu lanaa in tattabi'oona illaz zanna wa-in antum illaa takhhrusoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 938,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 149,
      "text":
          "Qul falillaahil hujjatul baalighatu falaw shaaa'a lahadaakum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 939,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 150,
      "text":
          "Qul halumma shuhadaaa'akumul lazeena yash-hadoona annal laaha harrama haazaa fa-in shahidoo falaa tashhad ma'ahum; Wa-laa tattabi' ahwaaa'al lazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa wallazeena laa yu'minoona bil-Aakhira(ti) Wa-hum bi-Rabbihim ya'diloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 940,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 151,
      "text":
          "Qul ta'aalaw atlu maa harrama Rabbukum 'alaikum allaa tushrikoo bihee shai'anw Wa-bil-waalidaini ihsaana(nw) Wa-laa taqtulooo awlaadakum min imlaaqin nahnu narzuqukum Wa-iyyaahum Wa-laa taqrabul fawaahisha maa zahara minhaa Wa-maa batana Wa-laa taqtulun nafsal latee harramal laahu illaa bilhaqq; zaalikum wassaakum bihee la'allakum ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 941,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 152,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taqraboo maalal yateemi illaa billatee hiyaa ahsanu hattaa yablugha ashudda(hoo) Wa-aoful kaila wal-meezaana bilqisti laa nukallifu nafsan illaa wus'ahaa Wa-izaa qultum fa'diloo Wa-law kaana zaa qurbaa Wa-bi-'ahdil laahi awfoo; zaalikum wassaakum bihee la'allakum tazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 942,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 153,
      "text":
          "Wa-annna haazaa Siraatee mustaqeeman fattabi'oo(hu) Wa-laa tattabi'us subula fata-farraqa bikum 'an sabeelih; zaalikum wassaakum bihee la'allakum tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 943,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 154,
      "text":
          "Summa aatainaa Moosal Kitaaba tammaaman 'alal lazeee ahsana Wa-tafseelal likulli shai'inw Wa-hudanw Wa-rahmatal la'allahum bi-liqaaa'i Rabbihim yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 944,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 155,
      "text":
          "Wa-haazaa Kitaabun anzalnaahu Mubaarakun fattabi'oohu wattaqoo la'al-lakum turhamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 945,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 156,
      "text":
          "An taqooloo inna-maaa unzilal Kitaabu 'alaa taaa'ifataini min qablinaa Wa-in kunnaa 'an diraa-satihim laghaafileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 946,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 157,
      "text":
          "Aw taqooloo law annaaa unzila 'alainal kitaabu lakunnaaa ahdaa minhum; faqad jaaa'akum baiyyinatum mir Rabbikum Wa-hudanw Wa-rahmah; faman azlamu mimman kazzaba bi-Aayaatil laahi Wa-sadafa 'anhaa; sanajzil lazeena yasdifoona 'an Aayaatinaa sooo'al 'azaabi bimaa kaanoo yasdifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 947,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 158,
      "text":
          "Hal yanzuroona illaaa an ta'tiyahumul malaaa'ikatu aw ya'tiya Rabbuka aw ya'tiya ba'du Aayaati Rabbik; yawma ya'tee ba'du Aayaati Rabbika laa yanfa'u nafsan eemaanuhaa lam takun aamanat min qablu aw kasabat feee eemaanihaa khairaa; qulin tazirooo innaa muntaziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 948,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 159,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena farraqoo deenahum Wa-kaanoo shiya'al lasta minhum fee shaiyy'; innamaaa amruhum ilal laahi summa yunabbi'uhum bimaa kaanoo yaf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 949,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 160,
      "text":
          "Man jaaa'a bilhasanati falahoo 'ashru amsaalihaa Wa-man jaaa'a bis-saiyyi'ati falaa yujzaaa illaa mislahaa Wa-hum laa yuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 950,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 161,
      "text":
          "Qul innanee hadaanee Rabbeee ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem(in) deenan qiyamam Millata Ibraaheema haneefa(wn); Wa-maa kaana minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 951,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 162,
      "text":
          "Qul inna Salaatee Wa-nusukee Wa-mah-yaaya Wa-mamaa-tee lillaahi Rabbil aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 952,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 163,
      "text": "Laa shareeka lahoo Wa-bizaalika umirtu Wa-ana awwalul muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 953,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 164,
      "text":
          "Qul aghairal laahi abghee Rabbanw Wa-Huwa Rabbu kulli shaiy(inw); Wa-laa taksibu kullu nafsin illaa 'alaihaa; Wa-laa taziru waaziratunw wizra ukhraa; summa ilaa Rabbikum marji'ukum fa-yunabbi'ukum bimaa kuntum feehi takhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 954,
      "sura": 6,
      "aya": 165,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee ja'alakum khalaaa'ifal ardi Wa-rafa'a ba'dakum fawqa ba'din darajaatil liyabluwakum fee maaa aataakum; inna Rabbaka saree'ul 'iqaabi Wa-innahoo la-Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {"index": 955, "sura": 7, "aya": 1, "text": "Alif-laaam-meem-sad"},
    {
      "index": 956,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Kitaabun unzila ilaika falaa yakun fee sadrika harajum minhu litunzira bihee Wa-zikraa lilmu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 957,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Ittabi'oo maaa unzila 'ilaikum mir Rabbikum Wa-laa tattabi'oo min dooniheee awliyaaa'; qaleelam maa tazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 958,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Wa-kam min qaryatin ahlaknaahaa fajaaa'ahaa ba'sunaa bayaatan aw hum qaaa'iloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 959,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Famaa kaana da'waahum iz jaaa'ahum ba'sunaa illaaa an qaalooo innaa kunnaa zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 960,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Falanas'alannal lazeena ursila ilaihim Wa-lanas'alannal mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 961,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 7,
      "text": "Falanaqus-sanna 'alaihim bi'ilminw Wa-maa kunnaa ghaaa'ibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 962,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Walwaznu Yawma'izinil haqq(u), faman saqulat mawaa-zeenuhoo fa-ulaaa'ika humul muflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 963,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wa-man khaffat mawaazeenuhoo fa-ulaaa'ikal lazeena khasirooo anfusahum bimaa kaanoo bi-Aayaatinaa yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 964,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad makkannaakum fil ardi Wa-ja'alnaa lakum feehaa ma'aayish; qaleelam maa tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 965,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad khalaqnaakum summa sawwar-naakum summa qulnaa lil-malaaa'ikatis judoo li-Aadama fa-sajadooo illaaa Ibleesa lam yakum minas saajideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 966,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Qaala maa mana'aka allaa tasjuda iz amartuk(a) qaala ana khairum minhu khalaqtanee min naarinw Wa-khalaqtahoo min teen"
    },
    {
      "index": 967,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Qaala fahbit minhaa famaa yakoonu laka an ta-ta-kabbara feehaa fakhruj innaka minas saaghireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 968,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 14,
      "text": "Qaala anzirneee ilaa Yawmi yub'asoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 969,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 15,
      "text": "Qaala innaka minal munzareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 970,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Qaala fabimaaa aghwai-tanee la-aq'udanna lahum siraa-takal mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 971,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Summa la-aatiyan-nahum mim baini aideehim Wa-min khalfihim Wa-'an aimaa-nihim Wa-'an shamaaa'ilihim Wa-laa tajidu aksarahum shaakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 972,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Qaala khruj minhaa maz'oomam madhooraa(l); laman tabi'aka minhum la-amla'anna Jahannama minkum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 973,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaaa-Aadamus kun anta Wa-zawjukal Jannata fakulaa min haisu shi'tumaa Wa-laa taqrabaa haazihish shajarata fatakoonaa minaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 974,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Fawaswasa lahumash shaitaanu liyubdiya lahumaa maa wooriya 'anhumaa min saw-aatihimaa Wa-qaala maa nahaakumaa Rabbukumaa 'an haazihish shajarati illaaa an takoonaa malakaini aw takoonaa minal khaalideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 975,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 21,
      "text": "Wa-qaasamahumaaa innee lakumaa laminan naasiheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 976,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Fadal-laahumaa bighuroor; falammaa zaaqash shajarata badat lahumaa saw-aatuhumaa Wa-tafiqaa yakh-sifaani 'alaihimaa minw waraqil jannah(ti) Wa-naadaa-humaa Rabbuhumaaa alam anha-kumaa 'an til-kumash shajarati Wa-aqul lakumaaa innash shaitaana lakumaa 'aduwwum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 977,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Qaalaa Rabbanaa zalamnaaa anfusanaa Wa-il lam taghfir lanaa Wa-tarhamnaa lana-koo-nanna minal khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 978,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Qaalah bitoo ba'dukum liba'din a'duww(unw), Wa-lakum fil ardi mustaqarrunw Wa-mataa'un ilaa heen"
    },
    {
      "index": 979,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Qaala feehaa tah-yawna Wa-feehaa tamoo-toona Wa-minhaa tukhrajoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 980,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Yaa-Baneee Aadama qad anzalnaa 'alaikum libaa-saien yuwaaree saw-aatikum Wa-reesha(nw) Wa-libaasut taqwaa zaalika khair; zaalika min Aayaatil laahi la'allahum yaz-zakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 981,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Yaa-Banee Aadama laa yafti-nanna-kumush shaitaanu kamaaa akhraja aba-waikum minal Jannah(ti) yanzi'u 'anhumaa libaasa-humaa liyuri-yahumaa saw-aati-himaaa; innahoo yaraakum huwa Wa-qabeeluhoo min haisu laa tarawnahum; innaa ja'alnash shayaateena awliyaaa'a lillazeena laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 982,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa fa'aloo faahishatan qaaloo wajadnaa 'alaihaaa aabaaa'ana wallaahu ama-ranaa bihaa; qul innal laaha laa ya'muru bilfah-shaaa(i) a-taqooloona 'alal laahi maa laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 983,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Qul amara Rabbee bil-qisti Wa-aqeemoo wujoohakum 'inda kulli masjid(inw) wad'oohu mukhliseena lahud deen(a); kamaa bada-akum ta'oodoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 984,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Fareeqan hadaa Wa-fareeqan haqqa 'alaihimud dalaalah; innahumut takhazush shayaateena awliyaaa'a min doonil laahi Wa-yah-saboona annahum muhtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 985,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Yaa-Banee Adama khuzoo zeenatakum 'inda kulli masjidinw Wa-kuloo wash-raboo Wa-laa tusrifoo; innahoo laa yuhibbul musrifeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 986,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Qul man harrama zeenatal laahil lateee akhraja li'ibaadihee wat-taiyyi-baati minar rizq; qul hiya lil-lazeena aamanoo fil hayaatid dunyaa khaali-sataien Yawmal Qiyaamah; kazaalika nufassilu(l) Aayaati liqaw-mien ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 987,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Qul innamaa harrama Rabbiyal fawaa-hisha maa zahara minhaa wa-maa batana wal-isma wal-baghya bighairil haqqi Wa-an tushrikoo billaahi maa lam yunazzil bihee sultaananw wa-an taqooloo 'alal laahi maa laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 988,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-likulli ummatin ajal(un), fa-izaa jaaa'a ajaluhum laa yasta'-khiroona saa'atanw wa-laa yastaq-dimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 989,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Yaa-Banee Aadama immaa ya'ti-yannakum Rusulum minkum yaqus-soona 'alaikum Aayaatee famanit taqaa wa-aslaha falaa khawfun 'alaihim wa-laa hum yahzanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 990,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa wastakbaroo 'an-haaa ulaaa'ika As-haabun naari hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 991,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Faman azlamu mimma-nif taraa 'alal laahi kaziban aw kazzaba bi-Aayaatih; ulaaa'ika yanaa-luhum nasee-buhum minal Kitaab; hattaaa izaa jaaa'at-hum rusulunaa yatawaf-fawnahum qaalooo ai-na maa kuntum tad'oonaa min doonil laah(i); qaaloo dalloo 'annaa wa-shahidoo 'alaaa an-fusihim annahum kaanoo kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 992,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Qaalad khuloo feee uma-min qad khalat min qab-likum minal jinni wal-insi fin naar(i); kullamaa dakhalat ummatul la'anat ukhtaha; hattaaa izad daa-rakoo feehaa jamee'an qaalat ukh-raahum li-oolaa-hum Rabbanaa haaa-u'laaa'i adal-loonaa fa-aatihim 'azaaban di'fam minan naar(i); qaala likul-lin di'funw wa-laakil laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 993,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalat oolaahum li-ukh-raahum famaa kaana lakum 'alainaa min fadlin fazoo-qul azaaba bimaa kuntum taksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 994,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa wastak-baroo 'anhaa laa tufat-tahu lahum abwaabus samaaa(i) wa-laa yad-khuloonal jannata hattaa yalijal jamalu fee sammil khiyaat; wa-kazaalika najzil mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 995,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Lahum min jahannama mihaa-dunw wa-min faw-qihim ghawaash(i); wa-kazaalika najziz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 996,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wal-lazeena aamanoo wa-'amilus saalihaati la nukallifu nafsan illaa wus'ahaaa ulaaa'ika As-haabul jannati, hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 997,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-naza'naa maa fee sudoo-rihim min ghillin tajree min tah-ti-himul anhaar(u), wa-qaalul hamdu lil-laahil lazee hadaa-naa lihaaza wa-maa kunna linah-tadiya lau-laaa ann hadaanal laah(u), laqad jaaa'at Rusulu Rabbinaa bilhaqq; Wa-noodoo an til-kumul jannatu ooris-tumoohaa bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 998,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Wa-naadaa As-haabul jannati as-haaban naari an qad wajadnaa maa wa'ada-naa Rabbunaa haqqan fahal wajad-tum maa wa'ada Rabbukum haqqa(n); qaaloo na'am, fa-azzana mu'azzinum bainahum al la'natul laahi 'alaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 999,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yasud-doona 'an sabeelil laahi wa-yabghoo-nahaa 'iwaja(nw), Wa-hum bil-aakhirati kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1000,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-baina-humaa hijaab(unw), Wa-'alal A'raafi rijaa-luien ya'rifoona kullam bi-seemaahum; Wa-naadaw as-haabal jannati an salaamun 'alaikum; lam yad-khuloohaa wa-hum yatma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1001,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa surifat absaaruhum tilqaaa'a as-haabin naari qaaloo Rabbanaa laa taj'alnaa ma'al qawmiz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1002,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-naadaaa as-haabul a'raafi rijaa-laien ya'rifoonahum bi-seemaahum qaaloo maaa aghnaa 'ankum jam'ukum wa-maa kuntum tastak-biroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1003,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "A-haaa'ulaaa'il lazeena aqsamtum laa yanaa-luhumul laahu bi-rahmah(tin); ud-khulul Jannata laa khawfun 'alaikum wa-laaa antum tah-zanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1004,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa-naadaaa as-haabun naari as-haabal Jannati an afeedoo 'alainaa minal maaa'i aw mimma raza-qakumul laah(u); qaaloo innal laaha harrama-humaa 'alal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1005,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Allazeenat takhazoo deenahum lahwanw Wa-la'i-banw Wa-gharrat-humul hayaatud dunyaa; fal-Yawma nannsaahum kamaa nasoo liqaaa'a Yawmihim haazaa Wa-maa kaanoo bi-aayaatinaa yajhadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1006,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad ji'naahum bi-Kitaabin fassalnaahu 'alaa 'ilmin hudanw Wa-rahmatal liqaw-mien yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1007,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Hal yanzuroona illaa ta'weelah(u); yawma ya'tee ta'wee-luhoo yaqoolul lazeena nasoohu min qablu qad jaaa'at Rusulu Rabbinaa bilhaqq; fahal lanaa min shufa'aaa'a fa-yashfa'oo lanaaa aw nuraddu fana'mala ghairal lazee kunnaa na'mal; qad khasirooo an-fusahum Wa-dalla 'anhum maa kaanoo yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1008,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Inna Rabbakumul laahul lazee khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda fee sittati ayyaamin summas tawaa 'alal 'arshi yughshil lailan nahaara yatlu-buhoo haseesanw wash-shamsa wal-qamara wan-nujooma musakh-khaa-raatim bi-amrih(i); alaa lahul khalqu wal-amr(u); tabaarakal laahu Rabbul 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1009,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Ud'oo Rabbakum tadarru'anw Wa-khufyah(tan); innahoo laa yuhibbul mu'tadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1010,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tufsidoo fil ardi ba'da islaahihaa wad'oohu khawfanw Wa-tama'aa; inna rahmatal laahi qareebum minal muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1011,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee yursilur riyaaha bushram baina yadai rahmatihee hattaaa izaaa aqallat sahaaban siqaalan suqnaahu libaladim maiyitin fa-annzalnaa bihil maaa'a fa-akhrajnaa bihee minn kullis samaraat; kazaalika nukhrijul mawtaa la'allakum tazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1012,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Walbaladut taiyibu yakhruju nabaatuhoo bi-izni Rabbihee wallazee khabusa laa yakhruju illaa nakidaa; kazaalika nusarriful Aayaati liqawminy yashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1013,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Laqad arsalnaa noohan ilaa qawmihee faqaala yaa-qawmi' budul laaha maa lakum min ilaahin ghairuhoo inneee akhaafu 'alaikum 'azaaba Yawmin 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1014,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 60,
      "text": "Qaalal mala-u min qaw-miheee innaa lanaraaka fee dalaalim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1015,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa-qawmi laisa bee dalaalatunw Wa-laakinnee Rasoolum mir Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1016,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Uballighukum Risaalaati Rabbee Wa-ansahu lakum Wa-a'lamu minal laahi maa laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1017,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Awa'ajibtum an jaaa'akum zikrum mir Rabbikum 'alaa rajulim minkum liyunzirakum Wa-litattaqoo Wa-la'allakum turhamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1018,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Fakazzaboohu fa-anjai-naahu wallazeena ma'ahoo fil fulki Wa-aghraqnal lazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa; innahum kaanoo qawman 'ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1019,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Wa-ilaa 'aadin akhaahum Hoodaa; qaala yaa-qawmi' budul laaha maa lakum min ilaahin ghairuh; afalaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1020,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Qaalal mala-ul lazeena kafaroo min qawmiheee innaa lanaraaka fee safaahatinw Wa-innaa la-nazunnuka minal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1021,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa-qawmi laisa bee safaahatunw Wa-laakinnee Rasoolum mir Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1022,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 68,
      "text": "Uballighukum Risaalaati Rabbee Wa-ana lakum naasihun ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1023,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Awa'ajibtum an jaaa'akum zikrum mir Rabbikum 'alaa rajulim minkum liyunzirakum; wazkurooo iz ja'alakum khulafaaa'a mim ba'di qawmi noohinw Wa-zaadakum fil khalqi bastatan fazkurooo aalaaa'al laahi la'allakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1024,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Qaalooo aji'tanaa lina'budal laaha wahdahoo Wa-nazara maa kaana ya'budu aabaaa'unaa fa'tinaa bimaa ta'idunaaa in kunta minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1025,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Qaala qad waqa'a alaikum mir Rabbikum rijsunw Wa-ghadab, atujaadiloonanee feee asmaaa'in sammaitumoohaaa antum Wa-aabaaa'ukum maa nazzalal laahu bihaa min sultaan; fantazirooo innee ma'akum minal muntazireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1026,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Fa-anjainaahu wallazeena ma'ahoo birahmatim minnaa Wa-qata'naa daabiral lazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa Wa-maa kaanoo mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1027,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-ilaa Samooda akhaahum Saalihaa; qaala yaa-qawmi' budul laaha maa lakum min ilaahin ghairuhoo qad jaaa'atkum baiyinatum mir Rabbikum haazihee naaqatul laahi lakum Aayatan fazaroohaa ta'kul feee ardil laahi Wa-laa tamassoohaa bisooo'in fa-ya'khuzakum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1028,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wazkuroo iz ja'alakum khulafaaa'a mim ba'di 'Aadinw Wa-bawwa-akum fil ardi tattakhizoona min suhoolihaa qusooranw Wa-tanhitoonal jibaala buyootan fazkurooo aalaaa'al laahi Wa-laa ta'saw fil ardi mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1029,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Qaalal mala-ul lazeenas takbaroo min qawmihee lillazeenas tud'ifoo liman aamana minhum ata'lamoona anna Saaliham mursalum mir Rabbih; qaalooo innaa bimaaa ursila bihee mu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1030,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Qaalal lazeenas takbarooo innaa billazeee aamanntum bihee kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1031,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Fa'aqarun naaqata wa'ataw 'an amri Rabbihim Wa-qaaloo yaa-Saalihu' tinaa bimaa ta'idunaaa in kunta minal mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1032,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 78,
      "text": "Fa-akhazat-humur rajfatu fa-asbahoo fee daarihim jaasimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1033,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Fa-tawalla 'anhum Wa-qaala yaa-qawmi laqad ablaghtukum Risaalata Rabbee Wa-nasahtu lakum Wa-laakil laa tuhibboonan naasiheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1034,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wa-Lootan iz qaala liqawmiheee ata'toonal faahishata maa sabaqakum bihaa min ahadim minal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1035,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Innakum lata'toonar rijaala shahwatam min doonin nisaaa'; bal antum qawmum musrifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1036,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana jawaaba qawmihee illaa an qaalooo akhrijoohum min qaryatikum innahum unaasuny yatatahharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1037,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Fa-anjainaahu Wa-ahlahooo illam ra-atahoo kaanat minal ghaabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1038,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Wa-'amtarnaa 'alaihim mataran fanzur kaifa kaana aaqibatul mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1039,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Wa-ilaa Madyana akhaahum Shu'aybaa; qaala yaa-qawmi' budul laaha maa lakum min ilaahin ghairuhoo qad jaaa'atkum baiyinatum mir Rabbikum fa-awful kaila walmeezaana Wa-laa tabkhasun naasa ashyaa'ahum Wa-laa tufsidoo fil ardi ba'da islaahihaa; zaalikum khairul lakum in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1040,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taq'udoo bikulli siraatin too'idoona Wa-tasuddoona 'an sabeelil laahi man aamana bihee Wa-tabghoonahaa 'iwajaa; waz-kurooo iz kuntum qaleelan fakassarakum wanzuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1041,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Wa-In kaana taaa'ifatum minkum aamanoo billazeee ursiltu bihee Wa-taaa'ifatul lam yu'minoo fasbiroo hattaa yahkumal laahu bainanaa; Wa-Huwa khairul haakimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1042,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Qaalal mala-ul lazeenas takbaroo min qawmihee lanukhrijannaka yaa-Shu'aibu wallazeena aamanoo ma'aka min qaryatinaaa aw lata'oo-dunna fee millatinaa; qaala awa-law kunnaa kaariheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1043,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Qadif tarainaa 'alal laahi kaziban in 'udnaa fee millatikum ba'da iz najjaanal laahu minhaa; Wa-maa yakoonu lanaaa an na'ooda feehaaa illaaa ai yashaaa'al laahu Rabbunaa; wasi'a Rabbunaa kulla shai'in 'ilmaa; 'alal laahi tawakkalnaa; Rabbanaf tah bainanaa Wa-baina qawminaa bilhaqqi Wa-Anta khairul faatiheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1044,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal mala-ul lazeena kafaroo min qawmihee la'init taba'tum Shu'aiban innakum izal lakhaasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1045,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 91,
      "text": "Fa-akhazat-humur rajfatu fa-asbahoo fee daarihim jaasimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1046,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Allazeena kazzaboo Shu'aiban ka-al lam yaghnaw feehaa; allazeena kazzaboo Shu'aiban kaanoo humul khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1047,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Fatawalla 'anhum Wa-qaala yaa-qawmi laqad ablaghtukum Risaalaati Rabbee Wa-nasahtu lakum fakaifa aasaa 'alaa qawmin kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1048,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaa fee qaryatim min Nabiyyin illaaa akhaznaaa ahlahaa bil-ba'saaa'i waddarraaa'i la'allahum yaddarra'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1049,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Summa baddalnaa makaa-nas saiyi'atil hasanata hattaa 'afaw Wa-qaaloo qad massa aabaa'anad darraaa'u wassarraaa'u fa-akhaznaahum baghtatanw Wa-hum laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1050,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Wa-law anna ahlal quraaa aamanoo wattaqaw lafatahnaa 'alaihim barakaatim minas samaaa'i wal-ardi Wa-laakin kazzaboo fa-akhaznaahum bimaa kaanoo yaksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1051,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Afa-amina ahlul quraaa ai ya'tiyahum ba'sunaa bayaatanw Wa-hum naaa'imoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1052,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Awa-amina ahlul quraaa ai ya'tiyahum ba'sunaa duhanw Wa-hum yal'aboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1053,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Afa-aminoo makral laah; falaa ya'manu makral laahi illal qawmul khaasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1054,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Awa-lam yahdi lillazeena yarisoonal arda mim ba'di ahlihaaa al law nashaaa'u asabnaahum bizunoobihim; Wa-natba'u 'alaa quloobihim fahum laa yasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1055,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Tilkal quraa naqussu 'alaika min ambaaa'ihaa; Wa-laqad jaaa'at-hum Rusuluhum bilbaiyinaati famaa kaanoo liyu'minoo bimaa kazzaboo min qabl; kazaalika yatba'ul laahu 'alaa quloobil kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1056,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa wajadnaa li-aksarihim min 'ahd; Wa-inw wajadnaaa aksarahum lafaasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1057,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Summa ba'asnaa mim ba'dihim Moosaa bi-Aayaatinaaa ilaa Fir'awana Wa-mala'ihee fazalamoo bihaa fanzur kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1058,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala Moosaa yaa-Fir'awnu inneee Rasoolum mir Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1059,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Haqeequn 'alaaa al laaa aqoola 'alal laahi illal haqq; qad ji'tukum bibaiyinatim mir Rabbikum fa-arsil ma'iya Baneee Israaa'eel"
    },
    {
      "index": 1060,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Qaala in kunnta ji'ta bi-Aayatin fa'ti bihaa in kunnta minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1061,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 107,
      "text": "Fa-alqaa 'asaahu fa-izaa hiya su'baanum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1062,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 108,
      "text": "Wa-naza'a yadahoo fa-izaa hiya baidaaa'u linnaazireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1063,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 109,
      "text": "Qaalal mala-u min qawmi Fir'awna inna haazaa lasaahirun 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1064,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 110,
      "text": "Yureedu ai yukhrijakum min ardikum famaazaa ta'muroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1065,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 111,
      "text": "Qaalooo arjih Wa-akhaahu Wa-arsil fil madaaa'ini haashireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1066,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 112,
      "text": "Ya'tooka bikulli saahirin 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1067,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaaa'as saharatu Fir'awna qaaloo inna lanaa la-ajjran in kunnaa nahnul ghaalibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1068,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 114,
      "text": "Qaala na'am Wa-innakum laminal muqarrabeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1069,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Moosaaa immaaa an tulqiya Wa-immaaa an nakoona nahnul mulqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1070,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Qaala alqoo falam-maaa alqaw saharooo a'yunan naasi wastarhaboohum Wa-jaaa'oo bisihrin 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1071,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Wa-awhainaaa ilaa Moosaaa an alqi 'asaaka fa-izaa hiya talqafu maa ya'fikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1072,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 118,
      "text": "Fawaqa'al haqqu Wa-batala maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1073,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 119,
      "text": "Faghuliboo hunaalika wanqalaboo saaghireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1074,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 120,
      "text": "Wa-ulqiyas saharatu saajideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1075,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 121,
      "text": "Qaaloo aamannaa bi-Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {"index": 1076, "sura": 7, "aya": 122, "text": "Rabbi Moosaa Wa-Haaroon"},
    {
      "index": 1077,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 123,
      "text":
          "Qaala Fir'awnu aamantum bihee qabla an aazana lakum; inna haaza lamakrum makartumoohu fil madeenati litukhrijoo minhaaa ahlahaa fasawfa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1078,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 124,
      "text":
          "La-uqatti'anna aidiyakum Wa-arjulakum min khilaafin summa la-usallibannakum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1079,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 125,
      "text": "Qaaloo innaaa ilaa Rabbinaa munqaliboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1080,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 126,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa tanqimu minnaaa illaaa an aamannaa bi-Aayaati Rabbinaa lammaa jaaa'atnaa; Rabbanaaa afrigh 'alainaa sabranw Wa-tawaffanaa muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1081,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 127,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal mala-u min qawmi Fir'awna atazaru Moosaa Wa-qawmahoo liyufsidoo fil ardi Wa-yazaraka Wa-aalihatak; qaala sanuqattilu abnaaa'ahum Wa-nastahyee nisaaa'ahum Wa-innaa fawqahum qaahiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1082,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 128,
      "text":
          "Qaala Moosaa liqawmihis ta'eenoo billaahi wasbiroo innal arda lillaahi yoorisuhaa mai yashaaa'u min 'ibaadihee wal-'aaqibatu lilmuttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1083,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 129,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo oozeenaa min qabli an ta'tiyanaa Wa-mim ba'di maa ji'tanaa; qaala 'asaa Rabbukum ai yuhlika 'aduwwakum Wa-yastakhli-fakum fil ardi fayanzura kaifa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1084,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 130,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad akhaznaaa Aala Fir'awna bis-sineena Wa-naqsim minas samaraati la'allahum yazzakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1085,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 131,
      "text":
          "Fa-izaa jaaa'at-humul hasanatu qaaloo lanaa haazihee Wa-in tusibhum saiyi'atuny yattaiyaroo bi-Moosaa Wa-mam ma'ah; alaaa innamaa taaa'iruhum 'indal laahi Wa-laakinna aksarahum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1086,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 132,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo mahmaa taatinaa bihee min Aayatil litas'haranaa bihaa famaa nahnu laka bimu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1087,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 133,
      "text":
          "Fa-arsalnaa 'alaihimut toofaana waljaraada walqum-mala waddafaadi'a waddama Aayaatim mufassalaatin fastakbaroo Wa-kaanoo qawmam mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1088,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 134,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa waqa'a 'alaihimur rijzu qaaloo ya-Moosad-u lanaa rabbaka bimaa 'ahida 'indaka la'in kashafta 'annar rijza lanu 'minanna laka Wa-lanursilanna ma'aka Banee Israaa'eel"
    },
    {
      "index": 1089,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 135,
      "text":
          "Falammaa kashafnaa 'anhumur rijza ilaaa ajalin hum baalighoohu izaa hum yankusoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1090,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 136,
      "text":
          "Fantaqamnaa minhum fa'aghraqnaahum Fil' yammi bi-Annahum kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa Wa-kaanoo 'anhaa ghaafileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1091,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 137,
      "text":
          "Wa-awrasnal qawmal lazeena kaanoo yustad'afoona mashaariqal ardi Wa-maghaari-bahal latee baaraknaa feehaa Wa-tammat kalimatu Rabbikal husnaa 'alaa Baneee Israaa'eela bimaa sabaroo Wa-dammarnaa maa kaana yasna'u Fir'awnu Wa-qawmuhoo Wa-maa kaanoo ya'rishoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1092,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 138,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaawaznaa bi-Banneee Israaa'eelal bahra fa-ataw 'alaa qawminy ya'kufoona 'alaaa asnaamil lahum; qaaloo yaa-Moosaj 'al lanaa ilaahan kamaa lahum aalihah; qaala innakum qawmun tajhaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1093,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 139,
      "text":
          "Innaa haaa'ulaaa'i mutabbarum maa hum feehi Wa-baatilum maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1094,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 140,
      "text":
          "Qaala a-ghairal laahi abgheekum ilaahanw Wa-Huwa faddalakum 'alal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1095,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 141,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz anjainaakum min Aali Fir'awna yasoomoo-nakum sooo'al 'azaab, yuqattiloona abnaaa'akum Wa-yastahyoona nisaaa'akum; Wa-fee zaalikum balaaa'um mir Rabbikum 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1096,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 142,
      "text":
          "Wa-waa'adnaa Moosaa salaaseena lailatanw Wa-at-mamnaahaa bi'ashrim fatamma meeqaatu Rabbihee arba'eena lailah; Wa-qaala Moosaa liakheehi Haaroonakh lufnee fee qawmee Wa-aslih Wa-laa tattabi' sabeelal mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1097,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 143,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa jaaa'a Moosa limeeqaatinaa Wa-kallamahoo Rabbuhoo qaala Rabbi arineee anzur ilaik; qaala lan taraanee Wa-laakinin zur ilal jabali fa-inis taqarra makaanahoo fasawfa taraanee; falammaa tajallaa Rabbuhoo liljabali ja'alahoo dakkanw Wa-kharra Moosaa sa'iqaa; falammaaa afaaqa qaala Subhaanaka tubtu ilaika Wa-ana awwalul mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1098,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 144,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa-Moosaaa innis tafaituka 'alan naasi bi-Risaalaatee Wa-bi-kalaamee fakhuz maaa aataituka Wa-kum minash shaakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1099,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 145,
      "text":
          "Wa-katabnaa lahoo fil alwaahi min kulli shai'im maw'izaanw Wa-tafseelal likulli shai'in fakhuzhaa biquwwatinw wa'mur qawmaka ya'khuzoo bi-ahsanihaa; sa'ooreekum daaral faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1100,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 146,
      "text":
          "Sa-asrifu 'an Aayaatiyal lazeena yatakabbaroona fil ardi bighairil haqq; Wa-iny yaraw kulla Aayatil laa yu'minoo bihaa Wa-iny yaraw sabeelar rushdi laa yattakhizoohu sabeelanw Wa-iny yaraw sabeelal ghaiyi yattakhizoohu sabeelaa; zaalika bi-annahum kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa Wa-kaanoo 'anhaa ghaafileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1101,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 147,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa Wa-liqaaa'il Aakhirati habitat 'amaaluhum; hal yujzawna illaa maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1102,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 148,
      "text":
          "Wattakhaza qawmu Moosaa mim ba'dihee min huliyyihim 'ijlan jasadal lahoo khuwaar; alam yaraw annahoo laa yukallimuhum Wa-laa yahdeehim sabeelaa; ittakhazoohu Wa-kaanoo zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1103,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 149,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa suqita feee aideehim Wa-ra aw-annahum qad dalloo qaaloo la'il lam yarhamnaa Rabbunaa Wa-yaghfir lanaa lanakoonanna minal khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1104,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 150,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa raja'a Moosaaa ilaa qawmihee ghadbaana asifan qaala bi'samaa khalaftumoonee min ba'dee 'a-'ajiltum amra Rabbikum Wa-alqal alwaaha Wa-akhaza bira'si akheehi yajurruhoo ilaiyh; qaalab na umma innal qawmas tad'afoonee Wa-kadoo yaqtu-loonanee; falaa tushmit biyal a'daaa'a Wa-laa taj'alnee ma'al qawmiz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1105,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 151,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbigh fir lee Wa-li-akhee Wa-adkhilnaa fee rahmatika Wa-Anta arhamur raahimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1106,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 152,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeenat takhazul 'ijla-sa yanaaluhum ghadabum mir Rabbihim Wa-zillatun fil hayaatid dunyaa; Wa-kazaalika najzil muftareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1107,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 153,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena 'amilus saiyiaati summa taaboo min ba'dihaa Wa-aamanooo inna Rabbaka min ba'dihaa la-Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1108,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 154,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa sakata 'an Moosal ghadabu akhazal alwaaha Wa-fee nuskhatihaa hudanw Wa-rahmatul lil-lazeena hum li-Rabbihim yarhaboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1109,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 155,
      "text":
          "Wakhtaara Moosaa qawmahoo sab'eena rajulal li-meeqaatinaa falammaa akhazat-humur rajfatu qaala Rabbi law shi'ta ahlaktahum min qablu Wa-iyyaay; 'a-tuhlikuna bimaa fa'alas sufahaaa'u minaa in hiya illaa fitnatuka tudillu bihaa man tashaaa'u Wa-tahdee man tashaaa; Anta waliyyunaa faghfir lanaa warhamnaa Wa-Anta khairul ghaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1110,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 156,
      "text":
          "Waktub lanaa fee haazi-hid dunyaa hasanatanw Wa-fil Aakhirati innaa hudnaaa ilaik; qaala 'azaabee useebu bihee man ashaaa'u Wa-rahmatee wasi'at kulla shai'; fasa-aktubuhaa lil-lazeena yattaqoona Wa-yu'toonaz Zakaata wal-lazeena hum bi-Aayaatinaa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1111,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 157,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yattabi'oonar Rasoolan Nabiyyal ummiyyal lazee yajidoonahoo maktooban 'indahum fit Tawraati wal-Injeeli ya'muruhum bilma'roofi Wa-yanhaahum 'anil munkari Wa-yuhillu lahumul taiyibaati Wa-yuharrimu 'alaihimul khabaaa'isa Wa-yada'u 'anhum israhum wal-aghlaalal latee kaanat 'alaihim; fallazeena aamanoo bihee Wa-'azzaroohu Wa-nasaroohu wattaba'un nooral lazeee unzila ma'ahooo ulaaa'ika humul muflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1112,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 158,
      "text":
          "Qul yaaa-aiyuhan naasu innee Rasoolul laahi ilaikum jamee'anil lazee lahoo mulkus samaawaati wal-ardi laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa yuhyee Wa-yumeetu fa-aaminoo billaahi Wa-Rasoolihin Nabiyyil ummiy-yil lazee yu'minu billaahi Wa-Kalimaatihee wattabi'oohu la'allakum tahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1113,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 159,
      "text":
          "Wa-min qawmi Moosaaa ummatuny yahdoona bilhaqqi Wa-bihee ya'diloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1114,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 160,
      "text":
          "Wa-qatta'naahumus natai 'ashrata asbaatan umamaa; Wa-awhainaa ilaa Moosaaa izis tasqaahu qawmuhooo anid rib bi'asaakal hajara fambajasat minhus nata 'ashrata 'ainan qad 'alima kullu unaasim mashrabahum; Wa-zallalnaa 'alaihimul ghamaama Wa-anzalnaa 'alaihimul manna was-Salwaa kuloo min taiyibaati maa razaqnaakum; Wa-maa zalamoonaa Wa-laakin kaanooo anfusahum yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1115,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 161,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qeela lahumus kunoo haazihil qaryata Wa-kuloo minhaa haisu shi'tum Wa-qooloo hittatunw wadkhulul baaba sujjadan naghfir lakum khateee'aatikum; sanazeedul muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1116,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 162,
      "text":
          "Fabaddalal lazeena zalamoo minhum qawlan ghairal lazee qeela lahum fa-arsalnaa 'alaihim rijzan minas samaaa'i bimaa kaanoo yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1117,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 163,
      "text":
          "Was'alhum 'anil qaryatil latee kaanat haadiratal bahri iz ya'doona fis Sabti iz ta'teehim heetaanuhum yawma Sabtihim shurra'anw Wa-yawma laa yasbitoona laa ta'teehim; kazaalika nabloohum bimaa kaanoo yafsuqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1118,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 164,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaalat ummatum minhum lima ta'izoona qaw-manil laahu muhlikuhum aw mu'azzibuhum 'azaaban shadeedan qaaloo ma'ziratan ilaa Rabbikum Wa-la'allahum yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1119,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 165,
      "text":
          "Falammaa nasoo maa zukkiroo bihee anjainal lazeena yanhawna 'anis sooo'i Wa-akhaznal lazeena zalamoo bi'azaabim ba'eesim bimaa kaanoo yafsuqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1120,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 166,
      "text":
          "Falammaa 'ataw 'am maa nuhoo 'anhu qulna lahum koonoo qiradatan khaasi'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1121,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 167,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz ta-azzana Rabbuka la-yab'asannna 'alaihim ilaa Yawmil Qiyaamati mai yasoomuhum sooo'al 'azaab; inna Rabbaka lasaree'ul 'iqaabi Wa-innahoo la-Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1122,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 168,
      "text":
          "Wa-qatta'naahum fil ardi umaman min-humus saalihoona Wa-min-hum doona zaalika Wa-balawnaahum bil-hasanaati was-saiyi'aati la'allahum yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1123,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 169,
      "text":
          "Fakhalafa min ba'dihim khalfunw warisul Kitaaba ya'khuzoona 'arada haazal adnaa Wa-yaqooloona sayughfaru lanaa Wa-iny ya'tihim 'aradun misluhoo ya'khuzooh; alam yu'khaz 'alaihim meesaaqul Kitaabi an laa yaqooloo 'alal laahi illal haqqa Wa-darasoo maa feeh; wad-Daarul Aakhirtu khairul lil-lazeena yattaqoon; afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1124,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 170,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yumas-sikoona bil-Kitaabi Wa-aqaamus Salaata innaa laa nudeeu 'ajral musliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1125,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 171,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz nataqnal jabala fawqahum ka-annahoo zullatunw Wa-zannooo annahoo waaqi'un bihim khuzoo maaa aatainaakum biquwwatinw wazkuroo maa feehi la'allakum tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1126,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 172,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz akhaza Rabbuka min Baneee Aadama min zuhoorihim zurriyyatahum Wa-ashhadahum 'alaa anfusihim alastu bi-Rabbikum qaaloo balaa shahidnaaa; an taqooloo Yawmal Qiyaamati innaa kunnaa 'an haazaa ghaafileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1127,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 173,
      "text":
          "Aw taqoolooo innamaaa ashraka aabaaa'unaa min qablu Wa-kunnaa zurriyyatan min ba'dihim 'a-fa-tuhlikunaa bi-maa fa'alal mubtiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1128,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 174,
      "text": "Wa-kazaalika nufassilul Aayaati Wa-la'allahum yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1129,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 175,
      "text":
          "Watlu 'alaihim naba allazeee aatainaahu Aayaatinaa fansalakha minhaa fa-atba'a hush-Shaytaanoo fakaana minal ghaaween"
    },
    {
      "index": 1130,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 176,
      "text":
          "Wa-law shi'naa larafa'naahu bihaa Wa-laakin-nahooo akhlada ilal ardi wattaba'a hawaah; famasaluhoo kamasalil kalbi in tahmil 'alaihi yalhas aw tatruk-hu yalhas; zaalika masalul qawmil lazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa; faqsusil qasasa la'allahum yatafakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1131,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 177,
      "text":
          "Saaa'a masalanil qawmul lazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa Wa-anfusahum kaanoo yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1132,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 178,
      "text":
          "Mai yahdil laahu fa-huwal muhtadee Wa-mai yudlil fa-ulaaa'ika humul khaasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1133,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 179,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad zara'naa li-jahannama kaseeran minal jinni wal-insi lahum quloobul laa yafqahoona bihaa Wa-lahum a'yunul laa yubisiroona bihaa Wa-lahum aazaanul laa yasma'oona bihaa; ulaaa'ika kal-an'aami bal hum adall; ulaaa'ika humul ghaafiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1134,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 180,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahil Asmaaa-'ul Husnaa fad'oohu bihaa Wa-zarul lazeena yulhidoona feee Asmaaa'ih; sa-yujzawna maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1135,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 181,
      "text":
          "Wa-mimman khalaqnaaa ummatuny yahdoona bilhaqqi Wa-bihee ya'diloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1136,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 182,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa sanastadrijuhum min haisu laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1137,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 183,
      "text": "Wa-umlee lahum; inna kaidee mateen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1138,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 184,
      "text":
          "Awalam yatafakkaroo maa bisaahibihim min jinnah; in huwa illaa nazeerun mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1139,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 185,
      "text":
          "Awalam yanzuroo fee malakootis samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-maa khalaqal laahu min shai'inw Wa-an 'asaaa ai yakoona qadiq taraba ajaluhum fa-bi-ayyi hadeesin ba'dahoo yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1140,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 186,
      "text":
          "Mai yudlil lillaahu falaa haadiya lah; Wa-yazaruhum fee tughyaanihim ya'mahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1141,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 187,
      "text":
          "Yas'aloonaka 'anis Saa'ati aiyaana mursaahaa qul innamaa 'ilmuhaa 'inda Rabbee laa yujalleehaa liwaqtihaaa illaa Hoo; saqulat fis samaawaati wal-ard; laa ta'teekum illaa baghtah; yas'aloonaka ka-annaka hafiyyun 'anhaa qul innamaa 'ilmuhaa 'indal laahi Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1142,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 188,
      "text":
          "Qul laaa amliku linafsee naf'anw Wa-laa darran illaa maa shaaa'al laah; Wa-law kuntu a'lamul ghaiba lastaksartu minal khairi Wa-maa massaniyas soo'; in ana illaa nazeerunw Wa-basheerul liqawminy yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1143,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 189,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazee khalaqakum min nafsinw waahidatinw Wa-ja'ala minhaa zawjahaa liyas-kuna ilaihaa falammaa taghash-shaahaa hamalat hamlan khafeefan famarrat bihee falammaaa asqalad da'a-wal laaha Rabbahumaa la'in aataitana saalihal lanakoonanna minash shaakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1144,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 190,
      "text":
          "Falammaaa aataahumaa saalihan ja'alaa lahoo shurakaaa'a feemaaa aataahumaa; fata'aalal laahu 'ammaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1145,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 191,
      "text": "A-yushrikoona maa laa yakhluqu shai'anw Wa-hum yukhlaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1146,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 192,
      "text": "Wa-laa yastatee'oona lahum nasranw Wa-laaa anfusahum yansuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1147,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 193,
      "text":
          "Wa-in tad'oohum ilal hudaa laa yattabi'ookum; sawaaa'un 'alaikum a-da'awtumoohum 'am antum saamitoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1148,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 194,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena tad'oona min doonil laahi 'ibaadun amsaalukum fad'oohum fal-yastajeeboo lakum in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1149,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 195,
      "text":
          "A-lahum arjuluny yamshoona bihaa 'am lahum 'aidiny yabtishoona bihaaa 'am lahum a'yunuy yubsiroona bihaaa 'am lahum aazaanuny yasma'oona bihaa; qulid 'oo shurakaaa'akum thumma keedooni falaa tunziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1150,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 196,
      "text":
          "Inna waliyyial laahul lazee nazzalal Kitaaba Wa-Huwa yatawallas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1151,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 197,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena tad'oona min doonihee laa yastatee'oona nasrakum Wa-laaa anfusahum yansuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1152,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 198,
      "text":
          "Wa-in tad'oohum ilal hudaa laa yasma'oo Wa-taraahum yanzuroona ilaika Wa-hum laa yubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1153,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 199,
      "text": "Khuzil 'afwa Wa-mur bil'urfi Wa-A'rid 'anil jaahileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1154,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 200,
      "text":
          "Wa-immaa yanzaghannaka minash Shaitaani nazghun fasta'iz billaah; innahoo Samee'un Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1155,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 201,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeenat taqaw izaa massahum taaa'ifun minash Shaitaani tazakkaroo fa-izaa hum mubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1156,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 202,
      "text": "Wa-ikhwaanuhum yamuddoonahum fil ghayyi thumma laa yuqsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1157,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 203,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa lam ta'tihim bi-aayatin qaaloo law-laj tabai-tahaa; qul innamaaa attabi'u maa yoohaaa ilaiya mir Rabbee; haazaa basaaa'iru mir Rabbikum Wa-hudanw Wa-rahmatul liqawminy yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1158,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 204,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa quri'al Quraanu fastami'oo lahoo Wa-ansitoo la-'allakum turhamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1159,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 205,
      "text":
          "Wazkur Rabbaka fee nafsika tadarru'anw Wa-kheefatanw Wa-doonal jahri minal qawli bilghuduwwi wal-aasali Wa-laa takum minal ghaafileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1160,
      "sura": 7,
      "aya": 206,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena 'inda Rabbika laa yastakbiroona 'an 'ibaadatihee Wa-yusabbihoonahoo Wa-lahoo yasjudoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1161,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Yas'aloonaka 'anil anfaali qulil anfaalu lillaahi war-Rasooli fattaqul laaha Wa-aslihoo zaata bainikum Wa-atee'ul laaha Wa-Rasoolahooo in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1162,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Innamal mu'minoonal lazeena izaa zukiral laahu wajilat quloobuhum Wa-izaa tuliyat 'alaihim Aayaatuhoo zaadat-hum eemaananw Wa-'alaa Rabbihim yatawakkaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1163,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "Allazeena yuqeemoonas Salaata Wa-mimmaa razaqnaahum yunfiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1164,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika humul mu'minoona haqqaa; lahum darajaatun 'inda Rabbihim Wa-magh-firatunw Wa-rizqun kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1165,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Kaamaaa akhrajaka Rabbuka mim baitika bilhaqq; Wa-inna fareeqam minal mu'mineena lakaarihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1166,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Yujaadiloonaka fil haqqi ba'da maa tabaiyana kaannamaa yasaaqoona ilal mawti Wa-hum yanzuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1167,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz ya'idukumul laahu ihdat taaa'ifataini annahaa lakum Wa-tawaddoona anna ghaira zaatish shawkati takoonu lakum Wa-yureedul laahu ai yuhiqqal haqqa bikalimaatihee Wa-yaqta'a daabiral kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1168,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 8,
      "text": "Liyuhiqqal haqqa Wa-tubtilal baatila Wa-law karihal mujrimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1169,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Iz tastagheesoona Rabbakum fastajaaba lakum annee mumiddukum bi-alfim minal malaaa'ikati murdifeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1170,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa ja'alahul laahu illaa bushraa Wa-litatma'inna bihee quloobukum; Wa-man nasru illaa min 'indil laah; innal laaha Azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1171,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Iz yughashsheekumun nu'assa amanatam minhu Wa-yunazzilu 'alaikum minas samaaa'i maaa'al liyutah-hirakum bihee Wa-yuzhiba 'ankum rijzash Shaitaani Wa-liyarbita 'ala quloobikum Wa-yusabbita bihil aqdaam"
    },
    {
      "index": 1172,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Iz yoohee Rabbuka ilal malaaa'ikati annee ma'akum fasabbitul lazeena aamanoo; sa-ulqee fee quloobil lazeena kafarur ru'ba fadriboo fawqal a'naaqi wadriboo minhum kulla banaan"
    },
    {
      "index": 1173,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bi-annahum shaaaqqul laaha Wa-Rasoolah; Wa-mai yushaqiqil laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo fa-innal laaha shadeedul 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1174,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 14,
      "text": "Zaalikum fazooqoohu Wa-anna lilkaafireena 'azaaban Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1175,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanoo izaa laqeetumul lazeena kafaroo zahfan falaa tuwalloohumul adbaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1176,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wa-mai yuwallihim yawma'izin duburahooo illaa mutaharrifal liqitaalin aw mutahaiyizan ilaa fi'atin faqad baaa'a bighadabim minal laahi Wa-ma'waahu Jahannamu Wa-bi'sal maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1177,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Falam taqtuloohum Wa-laakinnal laaha qatalahum; Wa-maa ramaita iz ramaita Wa-laakinnal laaha ramaa; Wa-liyubliyal mu'mineena minhu balaaa'an hasanaa; innal laaha Samee'un Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1178,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 18,
      "text": "Zaalikum Wa-annal laaha moohinu kaidil kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1179,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "In tastaftihoo faqad jaaa'akumul fathu Wa-in tantahoo fahuwa khairul lakum Wa-in ta'oodoo na'ud Wa-lan tughniya 'ankum fi'atukum shai'anw Wa-law kasurat Wa-annal laaha ma'al mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1180,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanoo atee'ul laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo Wa-laa tawallaw 'anhu Wa-antum tasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1181,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 21,
      "text": "Wa-laa takoonoo kallazeena qaaloo sami'naa Wa-hum laa yasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1182,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Inna sharrad dawaaabbi 'indal laahis summul bukmul lazeena laa ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1183,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa-law 'alimal laahu feehim khairal la-asma'ahum; Wa-law asma'ahum latawallaw Wa-hum mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1184,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanus tajeeboo lillaahi Wa-lir-Rasooli izaa da'aakum limaa yuhyeekum wa'lamooo annal laaha yahoolu bainal mar'i Wa-qalbihee Wa-anahooo ilaihi tuhsharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1185,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wattaqoo fitnatal laa tuseebannal lazeena zalamoo minkum khaaaassatanw wa'lamooo annal laaha shadeedul 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1186,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Wazkurooo iz antum qaleelum mustad-'afoona fil ardi takhaafoona ai yatakhat-tafakumun naasu fa-aawaakum Wa-aiyadakum binasrihee Wa-razaqakum minat taiyibaati la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1187,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa takhoonal laaha war-Rasoola Wa-takhoonooo amaanaatikum Wa-antum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1188,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wa'lamooo annamaaa amwaalukum Wa-awlaadukum fitnatunw Wa-annal laaha 'indahooo ajrun azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1189,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanooo in tattaqul laaha yaj'al lakum furqaananw Wa-yukaffir 'ankum saiyi-aatikum Wa-yaghfir lakum; wallaahu zul fadlil 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1190,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz yamkuru bikal lazeena kafaroo liyusbitooka aw yaqtulooka aw yukhrijook; Wa-yamkuroona Wa-yamkurul laahu wallaahu khairul maakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1191,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa tutlaa 'alaihim Aayaatunaa qaaloo qad sami'naa law nashaaa'u laqulnaa misla haazaaa in haazaaa illaaa asaateerul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1192,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaalul laahumma in kaana haazaa huwal haqqa min 'indika fa-amtir 'alainaa hijaaratam minas samaaa'i awi 'tinaa bi-'azaabin aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1193,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaanal laahu liyu'az-zibahum Wa-anta feehim; Wa-maa kaanal laahu mu'az-zibahum Wa-hum yastaghfiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1194,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa lahum allaa yu'az-zibahumul laahu Wa-hum yasuddoona 'anil Masjidil Haraami Wa-maa kaanooo awliyaaa'ah; in awliyaaa'-uhooo illal muttaqoona Wa-laakinna aksarahum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1195,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana Salaatuhum 'indal Baiti illa mukaaa-anw wa-tasdiyah; fazooqul 'azaaba bimaa kuntum takfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1196,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo yunfiqoona amwaalahum liyasuddoo 'an sabeelil laah; fasayunfiqoonahaa summa takoonu 'alaihim hasratan summa yughlaboon; wal-lazeena kafarooo ilaa Jahannnama yuhsharoona"
    },
    {
      "index": 1197,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Liyameezal laahul khabeesa minat taiyibi Wa-yaj'alal khabeesa ba'dahoo 'ala ba'din fayarkumahoo jamee'an fayaj'alahoo fee Jahannnam; ulaaa'ika humul khaasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1198,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Qul lillazeena kafarooo iny yantahoo yughfar lahum maa qad salafa Wa-iny ya'oodoo faqad madat sunnatul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1199,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaatiloohum hattaa laa takoona fitnatunw Wa-yakoonad deenu kulluhoo lillaah; fainin tahaw fa-innal laaha bimaa ya'maloona Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1200,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Wa-in tawallaw fa'lamooo annal laaha mawlaakum; ni'mal mawlaa Wa-ni'man naseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1201,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Wa'lamooo annamaa ghanimtum min sha'in fa-anna lillaahi khumusahoo Wa-lir-Rasooli Wa-lizil qurba walyataamaa walmasaakeeni wabnis sabeeli in kuntum aamantum billaahi Wa-maaa anzalnaa 'ala 'abdinaa yawmal Furqaani yawmal taqal jam'aan; wal-laahu 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1202,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Iz antum bil'udwatid dunyaa Wa-hum bil'udwatil quswaa warrakbu asfala minkum; Wa-law tawaa'attum lakhtalaftum fil mee'aadi Wa-laakil liyaqdiyal laahu amran kaana maf'oolal liyahlika man halaka 'am baiyinatinw Wa-yahyaa man haiya 'am baiyinah; Wa-innal laaha la-Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1203,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Iz yureekahumul laahu fee manaamika qaleela; Wa-law araakahum kaseeral lafashiltum Wa-latanaaza'tum fil amri Wa-laakinnal laaha sallam; innahoo 'aleemum bizaatis sudoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 1204,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz yureekumoohum izil taqaitum feee a'yunikum qaleelanw Wa-yuqallilukum feee a'yunihim liyaqdiyal laahu amran kaana maf'oolaa; Wa-ilal laahi turja'ul umoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 1205,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhal lazeena aamanooo izaa laqeetum fi'atan fasbutoo wazkurul laaha kaseeral la'allakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1206,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-atee'ul laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo Wa-laa tanaaza'oo fatafshaloo Wa-tazhaba reehukum wasbiroo; innal laaha ma'as saabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1207,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa takoonoo kallazeena kharajoo min diyaarihim bataranw Wa-ri'aaa'an naasi Wa-yasuddoona 'an sabeelil laah; wallaahu bimaa ya'maloona muheet"
    },
    {
      "index": 1208,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz zaiyana lahumush shaitaanu a'ma-alahum Wa-qaala laa ghaaliba lakumul yawma minan naasi Wa-innee jaarul lakum falammaa taraaa'atil fi'ataani nakasa 'alaa aqibaihi Wa-qaala innee bareee'um minkum innee araa maa laa tarawna inneee akhaaful laah; wallaahu shadeedul 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1209,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Iz yaqoolul munaafiqoona wallazeena fee quloobihim maradun gharra haaa'ulaaa'i deenuhum; Wa-mai yatawakkal 'alal laahi fa-innal laaha 'azee-zun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1210,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa-law taraaa iz yatawaf-fal lazeena kafarul malaaa'ikatu yadriboona wujoohahum Wa-adbaarahum Wa-zooqoo 'azaabal hareeq"
    },
    {
      "index": 1211,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bimaa qaddamat aideekum Wa-anal laaha laisa bizallaamil lil-'abeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1212,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Kadaabi Aali Fir'awna wal-lazeena min qablihim; kafaroo bi-Aayaatil laahi fa-akhazahu-mul laahu bizunoobihim; innal laaha qawiyyun shadeedul 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1213,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bi-annal laaha lam yakumu ghaiyiran ni'matan an'amahaa 'alaa qawmin hattaa yughaiyiroo maa bianfusihim Wa-annal laaha samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1214,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Kadaabi Aali Fir'awna wallazeena min qablihim; kazzaboo bi-Aayaati Rabbihim faahlaknaahum bizunoobihim Wa-aghraqnaa Aala Fir'awn; Wa-kullun kaanoo zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1215,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Inna sharrad dawaaabbi 'indal laahil lazeena kafaroo fahum laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1216,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Allazeena 'aahatta min-hum summa yanqudoona 'ahdahum fee kulli marratinw Wa-hum laa yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1217,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Fa-immaa tasqafannahum fil harbi fasharrid bihim man khalfahum la'allahum yazzakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1218,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-immaa takhaafana min qawmin khiyaanatan fambiz ilaihim 'alaa sawaaa'; innal laaha laa yuhibbul khaaa'ineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1219,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yahsabannal lazeena kafaroo sabaqooo; innahum laa yu'jizoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1220,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wa-a'iddoo lahum mas tata'tum min quwwatinw Wa-mir ribaatil khaili turhiboona bihee 'aduwwal laahi Wa-'aduwwakum Wa-aakhareena min doonihim laa ta'lamoo-nahum Allaahu ya'lamuhum; Wa-maa tunfiqoo min shai'in fee sabeelil laahi yuwaffa ilaikum Wa-antum laa tuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1221,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-in janahoo lissalmi fajnah lahaa Wa-tawakkal 'alal laah; innahoo Huwas Samee'ul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1222,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Wa-iny yureedooo any yakhda'ooka fainna hasbakal laah; Huwal lazeee aiyadaka binasrihee Wa-bilmu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1223,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Wa-allafa baina quloobihim; law anfaqta maa fil ardi jamee'am maaa allafta baina quloobihim Wa-laakinnal laaha allafa bainahum; innaahoo 'Azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1224,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhan Nabiyyu hasbukal laahu Wa-manit taba'aka minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1225,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhan Nabiyyu harridil mu'mineena 'alal qitaal; iny yakum minkum 'ishroona saabiroona yaghliboo mi'atayn; Wa-iny yakum minkum min'atuny yaghlibooo alfam minal lazeena kafaroo bi-anahum qawmul laa yafqahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1226,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Al'aana khaffafal laahu 'ankum Wa-'alima anna feekum da'faa; fa-iny yakum minkum mi'atun saabiratuny yaghliboo mi'atayn; Wa-iny yakum minkum alfuny yaghlibooo alfaini bi-iznil laah; wallaahu ma'as saabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1227,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Maa kaana li-Nabiyyin ai yakoona lahooo asraa hatta yuskhina fil ard; tureedoona aradad dunyaa wallaahu yureedul Aakhirah; wallaahu 'Azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1228,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Law-laa Kitaabum minal laahi sabaqa lamassakum fee-maaa akhaztum 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1229,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Fakuloo mimaa ghanimtum halaalan taiyibaa; watta qullaah; innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1230,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhan Nabiyyu qul liman feee aideekum minal asraaa iny ya'lamil laahu fee quloobikum khairany yu'tikum khayram mimmaaa ukhiza minkum Wa-yaghfir lakum; wallaahu Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1231,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wa-iny yureedoo khiyaa-nataka faqad khaanul laaha min qablu fa-amkana minhum; wallaahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1232,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo Wa-haajaroo Wa-jaahadoo bi-amwaalihim Wa-anfusihim fee sabeelil laahi wallazeena aawaw Wa-nasarooo ulaaa'ika ba'duhum awliyaaa'u ba'd; wallazeena aamanoo Wa-lam yuhaajiroo maa lakum minw walaayatihim min shai'in hatta yuhaajiroo; Wa-inis tansarookum fid deeni fa'alaiku munnasru illaa 'alaa qawmin bainakum Wa-bainahum meesaaq; wallaahu bimaa ta'maloona Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1233,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kafaroo ba'duhum awliyaaa'u ba'd; illaa taf'aloohu takun fitnatun fil ardi Wa-fasaadun kabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1234,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aamanoo Wa-haajaroo Wa-jaahadoo fee sabeelil laahi wallazeena aawaw Wa-nasarooo ulaaa'ika humul mu'minoona haqqaa; lahum maghfiratunw Wa-rizqun kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1235,
      "sura": 8,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aamanoo min ba'du Wa-haajaroo Wa-jaahadoo ma'akum fa-Ulaaa'ika minkum; Wa-ulul arhaami baduhum awlaa biba'din fee Kitaabil laah; innal laaha bikulli shai'in 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1236,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Baraaa'atum minal laahi Wa-Rasooliheee ilal lazeena 'aahattum minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1237,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Faseehoo fil ardi arba'ata ashhurinw wa'lamooo annakum ghairu mu'jizil laahi Wa-annal laaha mukhzil kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1238,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Wa azaanum minal laahi Wa-Rasooliheee ilan naasi yawmal Hajjil Akbari annal laaha bareee'um minal mushrikeena Wa-Rasooluh; fa-in tubtum fahuwa khairullakum Wa-in tawallaitum fa'lamooo annakum ghairu mu'jizil laah; Wa-bashiril lazeena kafaroo biazaabin aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1239,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Illal lazeena 'aahattum minal mushrikeena summa lam yanqusookum shai'anw-wa lam yuzaahiroo 'alaikum ahadan fa-atimmooo ilaihim 'ahdahum ilaa muddatihim; innal laaha yuhibbul muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1240,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Fa izansalakhal Ashhurul Hurumu faqtulul mushrikeena haisu wajattumoohum Wa-khuzoohum wahsuroohum waq'udoo lahum kulla marsad; fa-in taaboo Wa-aqaamus Salaata Wa-aatawuz Zakaata fakhalloo sabeelahum; innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1241,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-in ahadum minal mushrikeenas tajaaraka fa-ajirhu hattaa yasma'a Kalaamal laahi summa ablighhu ma-manah; zaalika bi-annahum qawmul laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1242,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Kaifa yakoonu lilmush-rikeena 'ahdun 'indal laahi Wa-'inda Rasoolihee illal lazeena 'aahattum 'indal Masjidil Haraami famas taqaamoo lakum fastaqeemoo lahum; innal laaha yuhibbul muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1243,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Kaifa Wa-iny-yazharoo 'alaikum laa yarquboo feekum illanw Wa-laa zimmah; yurdoo nakum biafwaahihim Wa-ta'baa quloobuhum Wa-aksaruhum faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1244,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Ishtaraw bi-Aayaatil laahi samanan qaleelan fasaddoo 'an sabeelih; innahum saaa'a maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1245,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Laa yarquboona fee mu'minin illanw Wa-laa zimmah Wa-ulaaa'ika humul mu'tadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1246,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Fa-in taaboo Wa-aqaamus Salaata Wa-aatawuz Zakaata fa-ikhwaanukum fid deen; Wa-nufassilul Aayaati liqawminy ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1247,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-in nakasooo aimaanahum mim ba'di 'ahdihim Wa-ta'anoo fee deenikum faqaatilooo a'immatal kufri innahum laaa aimaana lahum la'allahum yantahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1248,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Alaa tuqaatiloona qawman nakasooo aimaanahum Wa-hammoo bi-ikhraajir Rasooli Wa-hum bada'ookum awwala marrah; atakhshawnahum; fallaahu ahaqqu an takhshawhu in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1249,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Qaatiloohum yu'az-zibhumul laahu bi-aideekum Wa-yukhzihim Wa-yansurkum 'alaihim Wa-yashfi sudoora qawmim mu-'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1250,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wa yuzhib ghaiza quloobihim; Wa-yatoobullaahu 'alaa mai yashaaa'; wallaahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1251,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Am hasibtum an tutrakoo Wa-lammaa ya'lamil laahul lazeena jaahadoo minkum Wa-lam yattakhizoo min doonil laahi Wa-laa Rasoolihee Wa-lal mu'mineena waleejah; wallaahu khabeerum bimaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1252,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "maa kaana lilmushrikeena ai ya'muroo masaajidal laahi shaahideena 'alaaa anfusihim bilkufr; ulaaa'ika habitat a'maaluhum Wa-fin naari hum khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1253,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Innamaa ya'muru masaa-jidal laahi man aamana billaahi wal-Yawmil Aakhiri Wa-aqaamas Salaata Wa-aataz Zakaata Wa-lam yakhshaa illal laaha fa'asaaa ulaaa'ika aien yakoonoo minal muhtadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1254,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Aja'altum siqaayatal haaajji Wa-'imaaratal masjidil haraami kamman aamana billaahi wal-Yawmil Aakhiri Wa-jaahada fee sabeelil laah; laa yastawoona 'indal laah; wallaahu laa yahdil qawmaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1255,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Allazeena aamanoo Wa-haajaroo Wa-jaahadoo fee sabeelil laahi bi-amwaalihim Wa-anfusihim a'zamu darajatan 'indal laah; Wa-ulaaa'ika humul faaa'izoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1256,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Yubashshiruhum Rabbuhum birahmatim minhu Wa-ridwaaninw Wa-Jannaatil lahum feehaa na'eemum muqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1257,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 22,
      "text": "Khaalideena feehaaa abadaa; innal laaha 'indahooo ajrun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1258,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tattakhizooo aabaaa-'akum Wa-ikhwaanakum awliyaaa'a inis tahabbul kufra 'alal eemaan; Wa-maien yatawal-lahum minkum fa-ulaaa'ika humuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1259,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Qul in kaana aabaaa'ukum Wa-abnaaa'ukum Wa-ikhwaanukum Wa-azwaajukum Wa-'asheeratukum Wa-amwaaluniq taraftumoohaa Wa-tijaaratun takhshawna kasaadahaa Wa-masaakinu tardawnahaaa ahabba ilaikum minal laahi Wa-Rasoolihee Wa-Jihaadin fee Sabeelihee fatarabbasoo hattaa ya'tiyallahu bi amrih; wallaahu laa yahdil qawmal faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1260,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Laqad nasarakumul laahu fee mawaatina kaseeratinw Wa-yawma Hunainin iz a'jabatkum kasratukum falam tughni 'ankum shai'anw Wa-daaqat 'alaikumul ardu bimaa rahubat summa wallaitum mudbireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1261,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Summa anzalal laahu sakeenatahoo 'alaa Rasoolihee Wa-'alalmu 'mineena Wa-anzala junoodal lam tarawhaa Wa-azzabal lazeena kafaroo; Wa-zaalika jazaaa'ul kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1262,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Summa yatoobul laahu mim ba'di zaalika 'alaa mai yashaaa'; wallaahu Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1263,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanooo innamal mushrikoona najasun falaa yaqrabul Masjidal Haraama ba'da 'aamihim haaza; Wa-in khiftum 'ailatan fasawfa yughnee kumul laahu min fadliheee in shaaa'; innallaaha 'Aleemun hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1264,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Qaatilul lazeena laa yu'minoona billaahi Wa-laa bil-yawmil Aakhiri Wa-laa yuharrimoona maa harramal laahu Wa-Rasooluhoo Wa-laa yadeenoona deenal haqqi minal lazeena ootul Kitaaba hattaa yu'tul jizyata aien yadinw Wa-hum saaghiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1265,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalatil yahoodu 'Uzairunib nul laahi Wa-qaalatin Nasaaral Maseehub nul laahi zaalika qawluhum bi-afwaahihim yudaahi'oona qawlal lazeena kafaroo min qabl; qatalahumul laah; annaa yu'fakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1266,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "ittakhazooo ahbaarahum Wa-ruhbaanahum arbaabam min doonil laahi wal-Maseehab na Maryama Wa-maaa umirooo illaa liya'budooo Ilaahanw Waa-hidan laaa ilaaha illaa Hoo; Subhaanahoo 'ammaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1267,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Yureedoona aien yutfi'oo nooral laahi bi'afwaahihim Wa-ya'bal laahu illaaa aien yutimma noorahoo Wa-law karihal kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1268,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "huwal lazeee ar-sala Rasoolahoo bilhudaa Wa-deenil haqqi liyuzhirahoo 'alad deeni kullihee Wa-law karihal mushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1269,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanooo inna kaseeram minal ahbaari warruhbaani la-ya'kuloona amwaalan naasi bil-baatili Wa-yasuddoona 'an sabeelil laah; wallazeena yaknizoonaz zahaba wal-fiddata Wa-laa yunfiqoonahaa fee sabeelil laahi fabashshirhum bi'azaabin aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1270,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Yawma yuhmaa 'alaihaa fee naari jahannama fatukwaa bihaa jibaahuhum Wa-junoobuhum Wa-zuhooruhum haazaa maa kanaztum li-anfusikum fazooqoo maa kuntum taknizoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1271,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Inna 'iddatash shuhoori 'indal laahis naa 'ashara shahran fee Kitaabil laahi yawma khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda minhaaa arba'atun hurum; zaalikad deenul qaiyyim; falaa tazlimoo feehinna anfusakum; Wa-qaatilul mushrikeena kaaaffatan kamaa yuqaati-loonakum kaaaffah; wa'lamooo annal laaha ma'al muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1272,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Inna-man naseee'u ziyaadatun fil kufri yudallu bihil lazeena kafaroo yuhil-loonahoo 'aamanw Wa-yuhar-rimoonahoo 'aamal liyuwaati'oo 'iddata maa harramal laahu fayuhilloo maa harramal laah; zuyyina lahum sooo'u a'maalihim; wallaahu laa yahdil qawmal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1273,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo maa lakum izaa qeela lakumun firoo fee sabeelil laahis saaqaltum ilal ard; aradeetum bilhayaatid dunyaa minal Aakhirah; famaa mataa'ul hayaatid dunyaa fil Aakhirati illaa qaleel"
    },
    {
      "index": 1274,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Illaa tanfiroo yu'az-zibkum 'azaaban aleemanw Wa-yastabdil qawman ghairakum Wa-laa tadurroohu shai'aa; wal-laahu 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1275,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Illaa tansuroohu faqad nasarahul laahu iz akhrajahul lazeena kafaroo saaniyas naini iz humaa fil ghaari iz yaqoolu lisaahibihee laa tahzan innnal laaha ma'anaa; fa-anzalal laahu sakeenatahoo 'alaihi Wa-aiyyadahoo bijunoodil lam tarawhaa Wa-ja'ala kalimatal lazeena kafarus suflaa; Wa-Kalimatul laahi hiyal 'ulyaa; wallaahu 'Azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1276,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Infiroo khifaafanw Wa-siqaalanw Wa-jaahidoo bi-amwaalikum Wa-anfusikum fee sabeelil laah; zaalikum khairul lakum in kuntum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1277,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Law kaana 'aradan qareebanw Wa-safaran qaasidal lattaba'ooka Wa-laakim ba'udat 'alaihimush shuqqah; Wa-sayahlifoona billaahi lawis tata'naa lakharajnaa ma'akum; yuhlikoona anfusahum wal-laahu ya'lamu innahum lakaa-ziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1278,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Afal laahu 'anka lima azinta lahum hattaa yatabaiy-yana lakal lazeena sadaqoo Wa-ta'lamal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1279,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Laa yastaazinukal lazeena yu'minoona billaahi wal-Yawmil Aakhiri aien yujaa-hidoo bi-amwaalihim Wa-anfusihim; wallaahu 'aleemum bilmut-taqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1280,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Innamaa yastaazinukal lazeena laa yu'minoona billaahi wal-Yawmil Aakhiri wartaabat quloobuhum fahum fee raibihim yataraddadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1281,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-law araadul khurooja la-'addoo lahoo 'uddatanw Wa-laakin karihal laahum bi'aasahum fasabbatahum Wa-qeelaq 'udoo ma'al qaa'ideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1282,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Law kharajoo feekum maa zaadookum ilaa Khabaalanw Wa-la-awda'oo khilaalakum yabghoona-kumul fitnata Wa-feekum sammaa'oona lahum; wallaahu 'aleemum biz-zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1283,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Laqadib taghawul fitnata min qablu Wa-qallaboo lakal umoora hattaa jaaa'al haqqu Wa-zahara amrul laahi Wa-hum kaarihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1284,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Wa-minhum maien yaqoolu' zal lee Wa-laa taftinneee; alaa fil fitnati saqatoo; Wa-inna Jahannama lamuheetatum bil-kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1285,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "In tusibka hasanatun tasu'hum; Wa-in tusibka museebatuny yaqooloo qad akhaznaaa amranaa min qablu Wa-yatawallaw Wa-hum farihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1286,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Qul laien yuseebanaaa illaa maa katabal laahu lanaa Huwa mawlaanaa; Wa-'alal laahi fal-yatawakka-lil mu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1287,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Qul hal tarabbasoona binaaa illaaa ihdal husnayayni Wa-nahnu natrabbasu bikum aien yus-eebakumul laahu bi'azaa-bim min 'indiheee aw biaidee-naa fatarabbasooo innaa ma'akum mutarabbisoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1288,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Qul anfiqoo taw'an aw karhal laien yutaqabbala min-kum innakum kuntum qawman faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1289,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa mana'ahum 'an tuqbala minhum nafaqaatuhum illaaa annahum kafaroo billaahi Wa-bi-Rasoolihee Wa-laa ya'toonas Salaata illaa Wa-hum kusaalaa Wa-laa yunfiqoona illaa Wa-hum kaarihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1290,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Falaa tu'jibka amwaaluhum Wa-laaa awlaaduhum; innamaa yureedul laahu liyu'az-zibahum bihaa fil hayaatid dunyaa Wa-tazhaqa anfusuhum Wa-hum kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1291,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Wa-yahlifoona billaahi innnahum laminkum Wa-maa hum minkum Wa-laakinnahum qawmuien yafraqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1292,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Law yajidoona malja'an aw maghaaraatin aw mudda-khalal lawallaw ilaihi Wa-hum yajmahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1293,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa minhum maien yalmizuka fis sadaqaati fa-in u'too minhaa radoo Wa-illam yu'taw minhaaa izaa hum yaskhatoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1294,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Wa-law annahum radoo maaa aataahumul laahu Wa-Rasooluhoo Wa-qaaloo hasbunal laahu sayu'teenal laahu min fadlihee Wa-Rasooluhooo innaaa ilal laahi raaghiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1295,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Innamas sadaqaatu lilfuqaraaa'i walmasaakeeni wal-'aamileena 'alaihaa wal-mu'al-lafati quloobuhum Wa-fir riqaabi walghaarimeena Wa-fee sabeelil laahi wabnis sabeeli fareedatam minal laah; wal-laahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1296,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-minhumul lazeena yu'zoonan nabiyya Wa-yaqooloona huwa uzun; qul uzunu khairil lakum yu'minu billaahi Wa-yu'minu lil-mu'mineena Wa-rahmatul lil-lazeena aamanoo minkum; wallazeena yu'zoona Rasoolal laahi lahum 'azaabun 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1297,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "yahlifoona billaahi lakum liyurdookum wallaahu Wa-Rasooluhoo ahaqqu ai yurdoohu in kaanoo mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1298,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Alam ya'lamooo annahoo maien yuhaadidil laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo faanna lahoo Naara jahannama khaalidan feehaa; zaalikal khizyul 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1299,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Yahzarul munaafiqoona an tunaz zala 'alaihim Sooratun tunabbi 'uhum bimaa feequloobihim; qulistahzi'oo innal laaha mukhrijum maa tahzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1300,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Wala'in sa-altahum layaqoolunna innamaa kunnaa nakhoodu Wa-nal'ab; qul abillaahi Wa-'Aayaatihee Wa-Rasoolihee kuntum tastahzi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1301,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Laa ta'taziroo qad kafartum ba'da eemaanikum; in na'fu 'an taaa'ifatin minkum nu'az-zib taaa'ifatan bi-annahum kaanoo mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1302,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Almunaafiqoona wal-munaafiqaatu ba'duhum mim ba'd; yaamuroona bilmunkari Wa-yanhawna 'anil ma'roofi Wa-yaqbidoona aidiyahum; nasul laaha fanasiyahum; innal munaafiqeena humul faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1303,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Wa'adal laahul munafiqeena wal-munaafiqaati wal-kuffaara naara jahannnamma khaalideena feehaa; hiya hasbuhum; Wa-la'annahumul laahu Wa-lahum 'azaabum muqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1304,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Kallazeena min qablikum kaanoo ashadda minkum quwwatanw Wa-aksara amwaalanw Wa-awlaadan fastamta'oo bikhalaaqihim fastamta'tum bikhalaaqikum kamas tamta'al lazeena min qablikum bikhalaa-qihim Wa-khudtum kallazee khaadooo; ulaaa'ika habitat a'maaluhum fid dunyaa wal-Aakhirati Wa-ulaaa'ika humul khaasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1305,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Alam ya'tihim naba ul-lazeena min qablihim qawmi Noohinw Wa-'Aadinw Wa-Samooda Wa-qawmi Ibraaheema Wa-as-haabi Madyana wal-mu'tafikaat; atathum Rusuluhum bilbaiy-yinaati famaa kaanal laahu liyazlimahum Wa-laakin kaanooo anfusahum yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1306,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wal-mu'minoona wal-mu'minaatu ba'duhum awliyaaa'u ba'd; ya'muroona bilma'roofi Wa-yanhawna 'anil munkari Wa-yuqeemoonas Salaata Wa-yu'toonaz Zakaata Wa-yutee'oonal laaha Wa-Rasoolah; ulaaa'ika sayarhamu-humul laah; innal laaha 'Azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1307,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Wa'adal laahul mu'-mineena walmu'minaati Jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaa Wa-masaakina taiyyibatan fee Jannnaati 'adn; Wa-ridwaanum minal laahi akbar; zaalika huwal fawzul 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1308,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "yaaa-aiyyuhan Nabiyyu jaahidil kuffaara walmunaafiqeena waghluz 'alaihim; Wa-maawaahum jahannnamu Wa-bi'sal maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1309,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Yahlifoona billaahi Wa-qaaloo Wa-laqad qaaloo kalimatal kufri Wa-kafaroo ba'da Islaamihim Wa-hammoo bimaa lam yanaaloo; Wa-maa naqamooo illaaa an aghnaa humullaahu Wa-Rasooluhoo min fadlih; fainy yatooboo yaku khairal lahum Wa-iny yatawal law yu'az zibhumullaahu 'azaaban aleeman fiddunyaa wal Aakhirah; wamaa lahum fil ardi minw waliyyinw Wa-laa naseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1310,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Wa-minhum man 'aaha-dal laaha la'in aataanaa min fadlihee lanas-saddaqanna Wa-lanakoonanna minas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1311,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Falammaaa aataahum min fadlihee bakhiloo bihee Wa-tawallaw Wa-hum mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1312,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Fa-a'qabahum nifaaqan fee quloobihim ilaa Yawmi yalqaw-nahoo bimaaa akhlaful laaha maa wa'adoohu Wa-bimaa kaanoo yakhziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1313,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Alam ya'lamooo annal laaha ya'lamu sirrahum Wa-najwaahum Wa-annal laaha 'Allaamul Ghuyoob"
    },
    {
      "index": 1314,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yalmizoonal mut tawwi'eena minalmu'mineena fis sadaqaati wallazeena laa yajidoona illaa juhdahum fayaskharoona minhum sakhiral laahu minhum Wa-lahum azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1315,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Istaghfir lahum aw laa tastaghfir lahum in tastaghfir lahum sab'eena marratan falaien yaghfiral laahu lahum; zaalika bi-annahum kafaroo billaahi Wa-Rasoolih; wallaahu laa yahdil qawmal faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1316,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Farihal mukhallafoona bimaq'adihim khilaafa Rasoolil laahi Wa-karihooo aien yujaahidoo bi-amwaalihim Wa-anfusihim fee sabeelil laahi Wa-qaaloo laa tanfiroo fil harr; qul Naaru jahannama ashaddu harraa; law kaanoo yafqahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1317,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Falyadhakoo qaleelanw walyabkoo kaseeran jazaaa'an bimaa kaanoo yaksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1318,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Fa-ir raja'akal laahu ilaa taaa'ifatim minhum fastaaa-zanooka lilkhurooji faqul lan takhrujoo ma'iya abadanw Wa-lan tuqaatiloo ma'iya 'aduwwan innakum radeetum bilqu'oodi awwala marratin faq'udoo ma'al khaalifeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1319,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tusalli 'alaaa ahadim minhum maata abadanw Wa-laa taqum 'alaa qabriheee innahum kafaroo billaahi Wa-Rasoolihee Wa-maatoo Wa-hum faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1320,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tu'jibka amwaaluhum Wa-awlaaduhum; innamaa yureedul laahu aien yu'azzibahum bihaa fid dunyaa Wa-tazhaqa anfusuhum Wa-hum kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1321,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaaa unzilat Sooratun an aaminoo billaahi Wa-jaahidoo ma'a Rasoolihis taazanaka ulut tawli minhum Wa-qaaloo zarnaa nakum ma'al qaa'ideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1322,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Radoo bi-aie yakoonoo ma'al khawaalifi Wa-tubi'a 'alaa quloobihim fahum laa yafqahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1323,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Laakinir Rasoolu wal-lazeena aamanoo ma'ahoo jaahadoo bi-amwaalihim Wa-anfusihim; Wa-ulaaa'ika lahumul khairaatu Wa-ulaaa'ika humul muflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1324,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "A'addal laahu lahum Jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaa; zaalikal fawzul 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1325,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaaa'al mu'az-ziroona minal A'raabi liyu'zana lahum Wa-qa'adal lazeena kazabul laaha Wa-Rasoolah; sayuseebul lazeena kafaroo minhum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1326,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Laisa 'alad du'aaa'fai Wa-laa 'alal mardaa Wa-laa 'alal lazeena laa yajidoona maa yunfiqoona harajun izaa nasahoo lillaahi Wa-Rasoolih; maa 'alal muhsineena min sabeel; wallaahu Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1327,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa 'alal lazeena izaa maaa atawka litahmilahum qulta laaa ajidu maaa ahmilukum 'alaihi tawallaw Wa-a'yunuhum tafeedu minad dam'i hazanan allaa yajidoo maa yunfiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1328,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Innamas sabeelu 'alal lazeena yasta'zinoonaka Wa-hum aghniyaaa'; radoo bi-aien yakoonoo ma'al khawaalifi Wa-taba'al laahu 'alaa quloobihim fahum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1329,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Ya'taziroona ilaikum izaa raja'tum ilaihim; qul laa ta'taziroo lan nu'mina lakum qad nabba-annal laahu min akhbaarikum; Wa-sa-yaral laahu 'amalakum Wa-Rasooluhoo thumma turaddoona ilaa 'Aalimil Ghaibi washshahaadati fa-yunabbi'ukum bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1330,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Sa yahlifoona billaahi lakum izanqalabtum ilaihim litu'ridoo 'anhum fa-a'ridoo 'anhum innahum rijsunw Wa-ma'waahum jahannamu jazaaa'an bi maakaanoo yaksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1331,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Yahlifoona lakum litardaw 'anhum fa-in tardaw 'anhum fa-innal laaha laa yardaa 'anil qawmil faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1332,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Al-A'raabu ashaddu kufranw Wa-nifaaqanw Wa-ajdaru allaa ya'lamoo hudooda maaa anzalal laahu 'alaa Rasoolih; wallaahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1333,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Wa-minal A'raabi mai yattakhizu maa yunfiqu maghramanw Wa-yatarabbasu bikumud dawaaa'ir; alaihim daaa'iratus saw'; wallaahu Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1334,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Wa-minal A'raabi maien yu'minu billaahi wal-yawmil aakhiri Wa-yattakhizu maa yunfiqu qurubaatin 'indal laahi Wa-salawaatir Rasool; 'alaaa innahaa qurbatul lahum; sayudkhilu-humul laahu fee rahmatih; innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1335,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Was-saabiqoonal awwaloona minal Muhaajireena wal-Ansaari wallazeenat taba'oo-hum bi-ihsaanir radiyal laahu 'anhum Wa-radoo 'anhu Wa-a'adda lahum jannaatin tajree tahtahal anhaaru khaalideena feehaaa abadaa; zaalikal fawzul 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1336,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Wa-mimmann hawlakum minal A'raabi munaafiqoona Wa-min ahlil Madeenati maradoo 'alan nifaaq, laa ta'lamuhum nahnu na'lamuhum; sanu'azzibuhum marrataini summa yuraddoona ilaa 'azaabin 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1337,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Wa-aakharoo na'tarafoo bizunoobihim khalatoo 'amalan saalihanw Wa-aakhara saiyyi'an 'asal laahu 'aien yatooba 'alaihim; innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1338,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Khuz min amwaalihim sadaqtan tutahhiruhum Wa-tuzakkeehim bihaa Wa-salli 'alaihim inna salaataka sakanul lahum; wallaahu Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1339,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Alam ya'lamooo annal laaha huwa yaqbalut tawbata 'an ibaadihee Wa-ya'khuzus sadaqaati Wa-annal laaha huwat Tawwaabur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1340,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Wa-qul i'maloo fasayaral laahu 'amalakum Wa-Rasooluhoo wal-mu'minoon; Wa-saturaddoona ilaa 'Aalimil Ghaibi washshahaadati fa-yunabbi'ukum bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1341,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Wa-aakharoona murjawna li-amril laahi immaa yu'azzibuhum Wa-immaa yatoobu 'alaihim; wallaahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1342,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Wallazeenat takhazoo masjidan diraaranw Wa-kufranw Wa-tafreeqan bainal mu'mineena Wa-irsaadal liman haarabal laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo min qabl; Wa-la-yahlifunna in aradnaaa illal husnaa wallaahu yash-hadu innahum lakaaziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1343,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Laa taqum feehi abadaa; lamasjidun ussisa 'alat taqwaa min awwali yawmin ahaqqu 'an taqooma feeh; feehi rijaaluien yuhibbona 'aien yata-tah-haroo; wallaahu yuhibbul muttah-hireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1344,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Afaman assasa bunyaanahoo 'alaa taqwaa minal laahi Wa-ridwaanin khairun am man assasa bunyaanahoo 'alaa shafaa jurufin haarin fanhaara bihee fee Naari Jahannam; wallaahu laa yahdil qawmaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1345,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Laa yazaalu bunyaanu-humul lazee banaw reebatan fee quloobihim illaaa an taqatta'a quloobuhum; wal-laahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1346,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Innal laahash taraa minal mu'mineena anfusahum Wa-amwaalahum bi-anna lahumul jannah; yuqaatiloona fee sabeelil laahi fa-yaqtuloona Wa-yuqtaloona wa'dan 'alaihi haqqan fit Tawraati wal-Injeeli wal-Qur'aaan; Wa-man awfaa bi'ahdihee minal laah; fastabshiroo bi-bay'ikumul lazee baaya'tum bih; Wa-zaalika huwal fawzul 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1347,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "At-taaa'iboonal 'aabidoonal haamidoonas saaa'ihoonar raaki'oonas saajidoonal aamiroona bilma'roofi wannaahoona 'anil munkari walhaafizoona lihudoodil laah; Wa-bashshiril mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1348,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "Maa kaana lin-nabiyyi wallazeena aamanooo 'aien yastaghfiroo lil-mushrikeena Wa-law kaanoo ulee qurbaa min ba'di maa tabiyyana lahum annahum As-haabul jaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1349,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 114,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaanas tighfaaru ibraaheema li-abeehi illaa 'an maw'idatinw Wa-'adahaaa iyyaahu falammaa tabaiyyana lahooo annahoo 'aduwwul lillaahi tabarra-a minh; inna Ibraaheema la-awwaahun haleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1350,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaanal laahu liyudilla qawman ba'da iz hadaahum hatta yubaiyyina lahum maa yattaqoon; innal laaha bikulli shai'in 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1351,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha lahoo mulkus samaawaati wal-ardi yuhyee Wa-yumeet; Wa-maa lakum min doonil laahi minw waliyyinw Wa-laa naseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1352,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Laqat taabal laahu 'alan nabiyyi wal-Muhaajireena wal-Ansaaril lazeenat taba'oohu fee saa'atil 'usrati min ba'di maa kaada yazeeghu quloobu fariqin minhum thumma taaba 'alaihim; innahoo bihim Ra'oofur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1353,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 118,
      "text":
          "Wa-'alas salaasatil lazeena khullifoo hattaaa izaa daaqat 'alaihimul ardu bimaa rahubat Wa-daaqat 'alaihim anfusuhum Wa-zannnooo al laa malja-a minal laahi illaaa ilaihi summa taaba 'alaihim liyatooboo; innal laaha Huwat Tawwaabur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1354,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 119,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanut taqul laaha Wa-koonoo ma'as saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1355,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 120,
      "text":
          "Maa kaana li-ahlil Madeenati Wa-man hawlahum minal A'raabi aien yatakhallafoo 'ar Rasoolil laahi Wa-laa yarghaboo bi-anfusihim 'an nafsih; zaalika bi-annahum laa yuseebuhum zama-unw Wa-laa nasabunw Wa-laa makhmasatun fee sabeelil laahi Wa-laa yata'oona mawti'ai yagheezul kuffaara Wa-laa yanaaloona min 'aduwwin nailan illaa kutiba lahum bihee 'amalun saalih; innal laaha laa yudee'u ajral muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1356,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 121,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yunfiqoona nafa-qatan sagheeratanw Wa-laa kabeeratanw Wa-laa yaqta'oona waadiyan illaa kutiba lahum liyajziyahumul laahu ahsana maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1357,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 122,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaanal mu'minoona liyanfiroo kaaaffah; falaw-laa nafara min kulli firqatim minhum taaa'ifatul liyatafaqqahoo fid deeni Wa-liyunziroo qawmahum izaa raja'ooo ilaihim la'allahum yahzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1358,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 123,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo qaatilul lazeena yaloonakum minal kuffaari walyajidoo feekum ghilzah; wa'lamooo annal laaha ma'al muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1359,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 124,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa maaa unzilat Sooratun faminhum maien yaqoolu aiyyukum zaadat hu-haazihee eemaanaa; fa-ammal lazeena aamanoo fazaadat-hum eemaananw Wa-hum yastabshiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1360,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 125,
      "text":
          "Wa-ammal lazeena fee quloobihim maradun fazaadat-hum rijsan ilaa rijsihim Wa-maatoo Wa-hum kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1361,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 126,
      "text":
          "A-Wa-laa yarawna annahum yuftanoona fee kulli 'aamin marratan 'aw marrataini thumma laa yatooboona Wa-laa hum yazzakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1362,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 127,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa maaa unzilat Sooratun nazara ba'duhum ilaa ba'din hal yaraakum min ahadin thumman sarafoo; sarafal laahu quloobahum bi-annahum qawmul laa yafqahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1363,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 128,
      "text":
          "Laqad jaaa'akum Rasoolum min anfusikum 'azeezun 'alaihi maa 'anittum hareesun 'alaikum bilmu'mineena ra'oofur raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1364,
      "sura": 9,
      "aya": 129,
      "text":
          "Fa-in tawallaw faqul hasbiyal laahu laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa 'alaihi tawakkkaltu Wa-Huwa Rabbul 'Arshil 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1365,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 1,
      "text": "Alif-Laaam-Raa; tilka Aayaatul Kitaabil Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1366,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "A-kaana linnaasi 'ajaaban 'an 'awhainaaa 'ilaa rajulin minhum 'an anzirin naasa Wa-bashshiril lazeena 'aamanoo 'anna lahum qadama sidqin 'inda Rabbihim; qaalal kaafiroona 'inna haazaa la-saahirun mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1367,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Inna Rabbakumul laahul lazee khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda fee sittati aiy-yaamin thummas tawaa 'alal 'Arshi yudabbirul amra maa min shafee'in illaa min ba'di iznih; zalikumul laahu Rabbukum fa'budooh; afalaa tazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1368,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Ilaihi marji'ukum jamee-'anw wa'dal laahi haqqaa; innahoo yabda'ul khalqa thumma yu'eeduhoo liyajziyal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati bilqist; wallazeena kafaroo lahum sharaabun min hamee-minw Wa-'azaabun 'aleemun bimaa kaanoo yakfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1369,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazee ja'alash shamsa diyaaa'anw walqamara nooranw Wa-qaddarahoo manaazila li-ta'lamoo 'adadas sineena walhisaab; maa khalaqal laahu zaalika illa bilhaqq; yufassilul aayaati li-qawminy ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1370,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Inna fikh tilaafil laili wannahaari Wa-maa khalaqal laahu fis samaawaati wal-ardi la-aayaatin liqawmien yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1371,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena laa yarjoona liqaaa'anaa Wa-radoo bilhayaatid dunyaa watma'-annoo bihaa wallazeena hum 'an Aayaatinaa ghaafiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1372,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 8,
      "text": "Ulaaa'ika ma'waahumun Naaru bimaa kaanoo yaksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1373,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati yahdeehim Rabbuhum bi-eemaanihim tajree min tahtihimul anhaaru fee jannaatin Na'eem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1374,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Da'waahum feehaa Subhaanakal laahumma Wa-tahiyyatuhum feehaa salaam; Wa-aakhiru da'waahum anil hamdu lillaahi Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1375,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Wa-law yu'ajjilul laahu linnaasish sharra sti'-jaalahum bil-khairi laqudiya ilaihim 'ajaluhum fa-nazarul lazeena laa yarjoona liqaaa'anaa fee tughyaanihim ya'mahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1376,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa massal insaanad durru da'aanaa li-jambiheee aw qaa'idan aw qaaa'iman falammaa kashafnaa 'anhu durrahoo marra ka-an lam yad'unaaa ilaa durrin massah; kazaalika zuyyina lilmusrifeena maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1377,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad ahlaknal quroona min qablikum lammaa zalamoo Wa-jaaa'at-hum Rusuluhum bil-baiy-yinaati Wa-maa kaanoo liyu'minoo; kazaalika najzil qawmal mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1378,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Thumma ja'alnaakum khalaaa'ifa fil ardi min ba'dihim li-nanzura kaifa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1379,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa tutlaa 'alaihim aayaatunaa baiy-yinaatin qaalal lazeena laa yarjoona liqaaa'a na'ti bi-Qur'aanin ghairi haazaaa aw baddilh; qul maa yakoonu leee 'an 'ubaddilahoo min tilqaaa'i nafsee in attabi'u illaa maa yoohaaa ilaiy-ya inneee akhaafu in 'asaytu Rabbee 'azaaba Yawmin 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1380,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Qul law shaaa'al laahu maa talawtuhoo 'alaikum Wa-laaa adraakum bihee faqad labistu feekum 'umuran min qablih; afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1381,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Faman azlamu mimmanif taraa 'alal laahi kaziban aw kazzaba bi-Aayaatih; innahoo laa yuflihul mujrimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1382,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-ya'budoona min doonil laahi maa laa yadurruhum Wa-laa yanfa'uhum Wa-yaqooloona haaa'ulaaa'i shufa'aaa-'unaa 'indal laah; qul 'a-tunabbi-'oonal laaha bi-maa laa ya'lamu fis samaawaati Wa-laa fil ard; subhaanahoo Wa-Ta'aalaa 'ammaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1383,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaanan naasu illaaa ummatanw waahidatan fa-khtalafoo; Wa-law-laa kalimatun sabaqat mir Rabbika laqudiya bainahum fee-maa feehi yakhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1384,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaqooloona law-laaa unzila 'alaihi aayatun mir Rabbihee faqul innamal ghaibu lillaahi fantaziroo innee ma'akum minal muntazireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1385,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaaa azaqnan naasa rahmatan min ba'di darraaa'a massat-hum izaa lahum makrun feee aayaatinaa; qulil laahu asra'u makraa; inna rusulanaa yaktuboona maa tamkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1386,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazee yusayyirukum fil barri walbahri hattaaa izaa kuntum fil fulki Wa-jaraina bihim bi-reehin tayyibatinw Wa-farihoo bihaa jaaa'at-haa reehun 'aasifunw Wa-jaaa'ahumul mawju min kulli makaaninw Wa-zannooo 'annahum 'uheeta bihim da'a wullaaha mukhliseena lahud deena la'in anjaitanaa min haazihee la-nakoonanna minash shaakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1387,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Falammaaa anjaahum izaa hum yabghoona fil ardi bighairil haqq; yaaa-aiy-yuhan naasu innamaa bagh-yukum 'alaaa anfusikum mataa'al hayaatid dunyaa thumma ilainaa marji'ukum fanunabbi-'ukum bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1388,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Innamaa masalul hayaatid dunyaa ka-maaa'in anzalnaahu minas samaaa'i fakhtalata bihee nabaatul ardi mimmaa ya'kulun naasu wal-an'aam; hattaaa izaaa akhazatil ardu zukhrufahaa wazzayyanat Wa-zanna ahluhaaa annahum qaadiroona 'alaihaaa ataahaaa amrunaa lailan aw nahaaran faja'alnaahaa haseedan ka-'an lam taghna bil-ams; kazaalika nufassilul aayaati liqawmien yatafakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1389,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu yad'ooo ilaa daaris salaami Wa-yahdee many yashaaa'u ilaa Siraatin Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1390,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Lil-lazeena ahsanul husnaa Wa-ziyaadatunw Wa-laa yarhaqu wujoohahum qatarunw Wa-laa zillah; ulaaa'ika as-haabul jannati hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1391,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kasabus saiyi-aati jazaaa'u saiyi'atin bimislihaa Wa-tarhaquhum zillah; maa lahum minal laahi min 'aasimin ka-annamaaa ughshiyat wujoohuhum qita'an minal laili muzlimaa; ulaaa'ika As-haabun Naari hum feeha khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1392,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wa-yawma nahshuruhum jamee'an thumma naqoolu lil-lazeena ashrakoo makaanakum antum Wa-shurakaaa'ukum; fazaiy-yalnaa bainahum Wa-qaala shurakaaa'uhum maa kuntum iyyaanaa ta'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1393,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Fakafaa billaahi shaheedan bainanaa Wa-bainakum in kunnaa 'an 'ibaadatikum laghaafileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1394,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Hunaalika tabloo kullu nafsin maaa 'aslafat; Wa-ruddoo ilal laahi mawlaahumul haqqi Wa-dalla 'anhum maa kaanoo yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1395,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Qul maien yarzuqukum minas samaaa'i wal-ardi ammanien yamlikus sam'a wal-absaara Wa-maien yukhrijul haiyya minal maiyyiti Wa-yukhrijul maiyyita minal haiyyi Wa-maien yudabbirul amr; fasa-yaqooloonal laah; faqul afalaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1396,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Fazaalikumul laahu Rabbukumul haqq; famaazaa ba'dal haqqi illad dalaalu fa-anna tusrafoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1397,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Kazaalika haqqat Kalimatu Rabbika 'alal lazeena fasaqooo annahum laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1398,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Qul hal min shurakaaa-'ikum maien yabda'ul khalqa thumma yu'eeduh; qulil laahu yabda'ul khalqa thumma yu'eeduhoo fa-annaa tu'fakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1399,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Qul hal min shurakaaa-'ikum maien yahdeee ilal haqq; qulil laahu yahdee lilhaqq; afamaien yahdeee ilal haqqi ahaqqu aien yuttaba'a ammal laa yahiddeee illaaa aien yuhdaa famaa lakum kaifa tahkumoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1400,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa yattabi'u aksaruhum illaa zannaa; innaz zanna laa yughnee minal haqqi shai'aa; innal laaha 'Aleemun bimaa yaf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1401,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana haazal Qur'aanu ai yuftaraa min doonil laahi Wa-laakin tasdeeqal lazee baina yadaihi Wa-tafseelal Kitaabi laa raiba fee mir Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1402,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Am yaqooloonaf taraahu qul fa'too bi-sooratin mislihee wad'oo manis tata'tum min doonil laahi in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1403,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Bal kazzaboo bimaa lam yuheetoo bi'ilmihee Wa-lammaa ya'tihim ta'weeluh; kazaalika kazzabal lazeena min qablihim fanzur kaifa kaana 'aaqibatuz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1404,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Wa-minhum maien yu-'minu bihee Wa-minhum mal laa yu'minu bih; Wa-Rabbuka a'lamu bilmufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1405,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Wa-in kazzabooka faqul lee 'amalee Wa-lakum 'amalukum antum bareee'oona mimmaaa a'malu Wa-ana bareee'um mimmaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1406,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-minhum maien yastami'oona iliak; afa-anta tusmi'us summa Wa-law kaanoo laa ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1407,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-minhum maien yanzuru ilaik; afa-anta tahdil 'umya Wa-law kaanoo laa yubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1408,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha laa yazlimun naasa shai'anw Wa-laakin nannaasa anfusahum yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1409,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma yahshuruhum ka-'an lam yalbasooo illaa saa'atan minan nahaari yata'aarafoona bainahum; qad khasiral lazeena kazzaboo bi-liqaaa'il laahi Wa-maa kaanoo muhtadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1410,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-imma nuriyannaka ba'dal lazee na'iduhum aw natawaffayannaka fa-ilainaa marji'uhum thummal laahu shaheedun 'alaa maa yaf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1411,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-likulli ummatir Rasoolun fa-izaa jaaa'a Rasooluhum qudiya bainahum bilqisti Wa-hum laa yuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1412,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 48,
      "text": "Wa-yaqooloona mataa haazal wa'du in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1413,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Qul laaa amliku linafsee darranw Wa-laa naf'an illaa maa shaaa'al laah; likulli ummatin ajalun izaa jaaa'a ajaluhumfa laaa yasta'khiroona saa'atanw Wa-laa yastaqdimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1414,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Qul 'a-ra'aytum in ataakum 'azaabuhoo bayaatan aw nahaaran maazaa yasta'jilu minhul mujrimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1415,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "A-thumma izaa maa waqa'a aamantum bih; aaal-'aana Wa-qad kuntum bihee tasta'jiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1416,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Thumma qeela lil-lazeena zalamoo zooqoo 'azaabal khuldi hal tujzawna illaa bimaa kuntum taksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1417,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-yastanbi'oonaka 'a-haqqun huwa qul ee Wa-Rabbeee innahoo lahaqq; Wa-maaa antum bimu'jizeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1418,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wa-law anna likulli nafsin zalamat maa fil ardi laftadat bih; Wa-asarrun nadaamata lammaa ra-awul 'azaab, Wa-qudiya bainahum bilqist; Wa-hum laa yuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1419,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Alaaa inna lillaahi maa fis samaawaati wal-ard; alaaa inna wa'dal laahi haqqunw Wa-laakinna aksarahum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1420,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 56,
      "text": "Huwa yuhyee Wa-yumeetu Wa-ilaihi turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1421,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhan naasu qad jaaa'atkum maw'izatun mir Rabbikum Wa-shifaaa'ul limaa fis sudoori Wa-hudanw Wa-rahmatul lil-mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1422,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Qul bi-fadlil laahi Wa-bi-rahmatihee fa-bi-zaalika fal-yafrahoo huwa khairun mimmaa yajma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1423,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Qul ara'aitum maaa anzalal laahu lakum mir rizqin faja'altum minhu haraamanw Wa-halaalan qul aaallaahu azina lakum; am 'alal laahi taftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1424,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa zannul lazeena yaftaroona 'alal laahil kaziba Yawmal Qiyaamah; innal laaha lazoo fadlin 'alan naasi Wa-laakinna aksarahum laa yashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1425,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa takoonu fee sha'ninw Wa-maa tatloo minhu min qur'aaninw Wa-laa ta'maloona min 'amalin illaa kunnaa 'alaikum shuhoodan iz tufeedoona feeh; Wa-maa ya'zubu 'ar Rabbika min misqaali zarratin fil ardi Wa-laa fis samaaa'i Wa-laaa asghara min zaalika Wa-laaa akbara illaa fee Kitaabin Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1426,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Alaa innaa awliyaaa'al laahi laa khawfun 'alaihim Wa-laa hum yahzanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1427,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 63,
      "text": "Allazeena aamanoo Wa-kaanoo yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1428,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Lahumul bushraa fil hayaatid dunyaa Wa-fil Aakhirah; laa tabdeela li-kalimaatil laah; zaalika huwal fawzul 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1429,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yahzunka qawluhum; innal 'izzata lillaahi jamee'aa; Huwas Samee'ul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1430,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Alaaa inna lillaahi man fis samaawaati Wa-man fil ard; Wa-maa yattabi'ul lazeena yad'oona min doonil laahi shurakaaa'; iny yattabi'oona illaz zanna Wa-in hum illaa yakhrusoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1431,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazee ja'ala lakumul laila litaskunoo feehi wannahaara mubsiraa; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil li-qawmien yasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1432,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Qaalut takhazal laahu waladan Subhaanahoo Huwal Ghaniyyu lahoo maa fis samaawaati Wa-maa fil ard; in 'indakum min sultaanin bihaazaaa; a'-taqooloona 'al allaahi maa laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1433,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 69,
      "text": "Qul innal lazeena yaftaroona 'al allaahil kaziba laa yuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1434,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Mataa'un fid dunyaa thumma ilainaa marji'uhum thumma nuzeequhumul 'azaabash shadeeda bimaa kaanoo yakfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1435,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Watlu 'alaihim naba-a-Noohin iz qaala liqawmihee yaa qawmi in kaana kabura 'alaikum maqaamee Wa-tazkeeree bi-Aayaatil laahi fa'alal laahi tawakkaltu fa-ajmi'ooo amrakum Wa-shurakaaa'akum thumma laa yakun amrukum 'alaikum ghummatan thummaq dooo ilaiyya Wa-laa tunziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1436,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Fa-in tawallaitum famaa sa-altukum min ajrin; in ajriya illaa 'alal laahi Wa-umirtu an akoona minal muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1437,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Fa-kazzaboohu fa-najjainaahu Wa-man ma'ahoo fil fulki Wa-ja'alnaahum khalaaa'ifa Wa-aghraqnal lazeena kazzaboo bi-aayaatinaa fanzur kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul munzareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1438,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Thumma ba'asnaa min ba'dihee Rusulan ilaa qawmihim fajaaa'oohum bil-baiyyinaati famaa kaanoo liyu'minoo bimaa kazzaboo bihee min qabl; kazaalika natba'u 'alaa quloobil mu'tadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1439,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Thumma ba'asnaa min ba'dihim Moosaa Wa-Haaroona ilaa Fir'awna Wa-mala'ihee bi-aayaatinaa fastakbaroo Wa-kaanoo qawman mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1440,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'ahumul haqqu min 'indinaa qaalooo inna haazaa la-sihrun mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1441,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Qaalaa Moosaaa 'a-taqooloona lil-haqqi lammmaa jaaa'a-kum 'a-sihrun haazaa Wa-laa yuflihus saahiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1442,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo aji'tanaa litalfitanaa 'ammaa wajadnaa 'alaihi aabaaa'anaa Wa-takoona lakumal kibriyaaa'u fil ardi Wa-maa nahnu lakumaa bi-mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1443,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 79,
      "text": "Wa-qaala Fir'awnu' toonee bikulli saahirin 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1444,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'assa haratu qaala lahum Moosaaa alqoo maaa antum mulqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1445,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Falammaaa alqaw qaala Moosaa maa ji'tum bihis sihr; innal laaha sa-yubtiluhoo; innal laaha laa yuslihu 'amalal mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1446,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Wa-yuhiqqul laahul haqqa bi-Kalimaatihee Wa-law karihal mujrimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1447,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Famaaa aamana li-Moosaaa illaa zurriyyatun min qawmihee 'alaa khawfin min Fir'awna Wa-mala'ihim 'any yaftinahum; Wa-inna Fir'awna la'aalin fil ardi Wa-innahoo laminal musrifeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1448,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala Moosaa yaa-qawmi in kuntum aamantum billaahi fa'alaihi tawakkalooo in kuntum muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1449,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Faqaaloo 'alal laahi tawakkalnaa Rabbanaa laa taj'alnaa fitnatal lilqawmiz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1450,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 86,
      "text": "Wa-najjinaa birahmatika minal qawmil kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1451,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Wa-awhainaaa ilaa Moosaa Wa-akheehi an tabaw Wa-aali-qawmikuma bi-Misra buyootanw waj'aloo buyootakum qiblatanw Wa-aqeemus Salaah; Wa-bashshiril mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1452,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala Moosaa Rabbanaaa innaka aataita Fir'awna Wa-mala ahoo zeenatanw Wa-amwaalan fil hayaatid dunyaa Rabbanaa liyudillo 'ansabeelika Rabbanat mis 'alaaa amwaalihim washdud 'alaa quloobihim falaa yu'minoo hatta yarawul 'azaabal aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1453,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Qaala qad ujeebad da'watukumaa fastaqeemaa Wa-laa tattabi'aaanni sabeelal lazeena laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1454,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaawaznaa bi-Baneee Israaa'eelal bahra fa-atba'ahum Fir'awnu Wa-junooduhoo baghyanw Wa-'adwaa; hattaaa izaaa adrakahul gharaqu qaala aamantu annahoo laaa ilaaha illal lazeee aamanat bihee Banooo Israaa'eela Wa-ana minal muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1455,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 91,
      "text": "Aaal-'aana Wa-qad 'asaita qablu Wa-kunta minal mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1456,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Falyawma nunajjeeka bibadanika litakoona liman khalfaka Aayah; Wa-inna kaseeran minan naasi 'an aayaatinaa laghaafiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1457,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad bawwa'naa Baneee Israaa'eela mubawwa 'a sidqinw Wa-razaqnaahum minat taiyibaati fa-makhtalafoo hattaa jaaa'ahmul 'ilm; inna Rabbaka yaqdee bainahum Yawmal Qiyaamati feemaa kaanoo feehi yakhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1458,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Fa-in kunta fee shakkin mimmaaa anzalnaaa ilaika fas'alil lazeena yaqra'oonal Kitaaba min qablik; laqad jaaa'akal haqqu mir Rabbika fa-laa takoonanna minal mumtareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1459,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa takoonanna minal lazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatil laahi fatakoona minal khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1460,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 96,
      "text": "Innal lazeena haqqat 'alaihim Kalimatu Rabbika laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1461,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 97,
      "text": "Wa-law jaaa'at-hum kullu Aayatin hattaa yarawul 'azaabal aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1462,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Falaw-laa kaanat qaryatun aamanat fa-nafa'ahaaa eemaanuhaaa illaa qawma Yoonusa lammaaa aamanoo kashafnaa 'anhum 'azaabal khizyi fil hayaatid dunyaa Wa-matta'naahum ilaa heen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1463,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Wa-law shaaa'a Rabbuka la-aamana man fil ardi kulluhum jamee'aa; afa-anta tukrihun naasa hattaa yakoonoo mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1464,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana linafsin an tu'mina illaa bi-iznil laah; Wa-yaj'alur rijsa 'alal lazeena laa ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1465,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Qulin zuroo maazaa fissamaawaati wal ard; Wa-maa tughnil Aayaatu wannuzuru 'an qawmil laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1466,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Fahal yantaziroona illaa misla ayyaamil lazeena khalaw min qablihim; qul fantazirooo innee ma'akum minal muntazireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1467,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Thumma nunajjee Rusulana wallazeena aamanoo; kazaalika haqqan 'alainaa nunjil mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1468,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Qul yaaa-ayyuhan naasu in kuntum fee shakk-in min deenee fa-laa a'budul lazeena ta'budoona min doonil laahi Wa-laakin a'budul laahal lazee yatawaffaakum Wa-umirtu an akoona minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1469,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Wa-an aqim wajhaka liddeeni Haneefanw Wa-laa takoonanna minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1470,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tad'u min doonil laahi maa laa yanfa'uka Wa-laa yadurruk; fa-in fa'alta fa-innaka izam minaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1471,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Wa-ien yamsaskal laahu bidurrin falaa kaashifa lahoo illaa hoo;wa iny yuridka bikhairin falaa raaadda lifadlih; yuseebu bihee many yashaaa'u min 'ibaadih; Wa-huwal Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1472,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Qul yaaa-ayyuhan naasu qad jaaa'akumul haqqu mir Rabbikum; famanih tadaa fa-innamaa yahtadee li-nafsih; Wa-man dalla fa-innamaa yadillu 'alaihaa; Wa-maaa ana 'alaikum bi-wakeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 1473,
      "sura": 10,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Wattabi' maa yoohaaa ilaika wasbir hattaa yahkumal laah; Wa-Huwa khairul haakimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1474,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Alif-Laaam-Raa; Kitaabun uhkimat Aayaatuhoo summa fussilat mil ladun Hakeemin Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1475,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Allaa ta'budooo illal laah; innanee lakum minhu nazeerunw Wa-basheer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1476,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Wa-anis taghfiroo Rabbakum summa toobooo ilaihi yumatti'kum mataa'an hasanan ilaaa ajalim musammanw Wa-yu'ti kulla zee fadlin fadlahoo Wa-in tawallaw fa-inneee akhaafu 'alaikum 'azaaba Yawmin Kabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1477,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 4,
      "text": "Ilal laahi marji'ukum Wa-Huwa 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1478,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Alaa innahum yasnoona sudoorahum liyastakhfoo minh; alaa heena yastaghshoona siyaabahum ya'lamu maa yusirroona Wa-maa yu'linoon; innahoo 'aleemun bizaatis sudoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 1479,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa min daaabbatin fil ardi illaa 'alal laahi rizquhaa Wa-ya'lamu mustaqarrahaa Wa-mustawda'ahaa; kullun fee Kitaabim Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1480,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda fee sittati aiyaaminw Wa-kaana 'Arshuhoo alal maaa'i liyabluwakum aiyyukum ahsanu 'amalaa; Wa-la'in qulta innakum mab'oosoona min ba'dil mawti la-yaqoolannal lazeena kafaroo in haazaaa illaa sihrum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1481,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Wala'in akharnaa 'anhumul 'azaaba ilaaa ummatim ma'doodatil la-yaqoolunna maa yahbisuh; alaa yawma ya'teehim laisa masroofan 'anhum Wa-haaqa bihim maa kaanoo bihee yastahzi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1482,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wa-la'in azaqnal insaana minnaa rahmatan summa naza'naahaa minhu, innahoo laya'oosun kafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 1483,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wala'in azaqnaahu na'maaa'a ba'da darraaa'a massat-hu la-yaqoolanna zahabas saiyiaatu 'anneee; innahoo lafarihun fakhoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 1484,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Illal lazeena sabaroo Wa-'amilus saalihaati ulaaa'ika lahum maghfiratunw Wa-ajrun kabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1485,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Fala'allaka taarikum ba'da maa yoohaaa ilaika Wa-daaa'iqum bihee sadruka aien yaqooloo law-laaa unzila 'alaihi kanzun aw jaaa'a ma'ahoo malak; innamaa anta nazeer; wallaahu 'alaa kulli shai'inw wakeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 1486,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Am yaqooloonaf taraahu qul faatoo bi'ashri Suwarim mislihee muftarayaatinw wad'oo manis tata'tum min doonil laahi in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1487,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Fa-il-lam yastajeeboo lakum fa'lamooo annamaaa unzilla bi'ilmil laahi Wa-al laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa fahal antum muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1488,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Man kaana yureedul hayaatad dunyaa zeenatahaa nuwaffi ilaihim a'maa-lahum feehaa Wa-hum feehaa laa yubkhasoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1489,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena laisa lahum fil Aakhirati illan Naaru Wa-habita maa sana'oo feehaa Wa-baatilum maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1490,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Afaman kaana 'ala baiyyinatim mir Rabbihee Wa-yatloohu shaahidum minhu Wa-min qablihee Kitaabu Moosaaa imaamanw Wa-rahmah; ulaaa-'ika yu'minoona bih; Wa-main yakfur bihee minal Ahzaabi fan-naaru maw'iduh; falaa taku fee miryatim minh; innahul haqqu mir Rabbika Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1491,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-man azlamu mimmanif taraa 'alal laahi kazibaa; ulaaa'ika yu'radoona 'alaa Rabbihim Wa-yaqoolul ashhaa duhaaa'ulaaa'il lazeena kazaboo 'alaa Rabbihim; alaa la'natul laahi alaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1492,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yasuddoona 'an sabeelil laahi Wa-yabghoonahaa 'iwajanw Wa-hum bil Aakhiratihum kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1493,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika lam yakoonoo mu'jizeena fil ardi Wa-maa kaana lahum min doonil laahi min awliyaaa'; yudaa'afu lahumul 'azaab; maa kaanoo yastatee'oonas sam'a Wa-maa kaanoo yubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1494,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena khasirooo anfusahum Wa-dalla 'anhum maa kaanoo yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1495,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 22,
      "text": "Laa jarama annahum fil Aakhirati humul akhsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1496,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati Wa-akhbatooo ilaa Rabbihim ulaaa'ika Ashaabul Jannati hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1497,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Masalul fareeqaini kal-a'maa wal-asammi walbaseeri wassamee'; hal yastawiyaani masalaa; afalaa tazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1498,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad arsalnaa Noohan ilaa qawmihee innee lakum nazeerum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1499,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Al laa ta'budooo illal laaha inneee akhaafu 'alaikum 'azaaba Yawmin aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1500,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Faqaalal mala-ul lazeena kafaroo min qawmihee ma naraaka illaa basharam mislanaa Wa-maa naraakat taba'aka illal lazeena hum araazilunaa baadiyar raayi Wa-maa naraa lakum 'alainaa min fadlim bal nazunnukum kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1501,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa-qawmi ara'aitum in kuntu 'alaa baiyyinatim mir Rabbee Wa-aataanee rahmatam min 'indihee fa'um-miyat 'alaikum anulzimuku-moohaa Wa-antum lahaa kaarihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1502,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaa-qawmi laaa as'alukum 'alaihi maalan in ajriya illaa 'alal laah; Wa-maaa ana bitaaridil lazeena aamanoo; innahum mulaaqoo Rabbihim Wa-laakinneee araakum qawman tajhaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1503,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaa-qawmi main yansurunee minal laahi in tarattuhum; afalaa tazak-karoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1504,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa aqoolu lakum 'indee khazaa'inul laahi Wa-laaa a'lamul ghaiba Wa-laa aqoolu inee malakunw Wa-laaa aqoolu lillazeena tazdareee a'yunukum lai yu'tiyahumul laahu khairan Allaahu a'lamu bimaa feee anfusihim innee izal laminaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1505,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Noohu qad jaadaltanaa fa-aksarta jidaalanaa faatinaa bimaa ta'idunaaa in kunta minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1506,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Qaala innamaa yaateekum bihil laahu in shaaa'a Wa-maaa antum bimu'jizeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1507,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yanfa'ukum nusheee in arattu an ansaha lakum in kaanal laahu yureedu aien yughwi-yakum; Huwa Rabbukum Wa-ilaihi turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1508,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Am yaqooloonaf taraahu qul inif taraituhoo fa'alaiya ijraamee Wa-ana bareee'um mimmaa tujrimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1509,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa oohiya ilaa Noohin annahoo lany-yu'mina min qawmika illaa man qad aamana falaa tabta'is bimaa kaanoo yaf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1510,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wasna'il fulka bi-a'yuninaa Wa-wahyinaa Wa-laa tukhaa-tibnee fil lazeena zalamoo; innahum mughraqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1511,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wa-yasna'ul fulka Wa-kullamaa marra 'alaihi mala'um min qawmihee sakhiroo minh; qaala in taskharoo minnaa fa-innaa naskharu minkum kamaa taskharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1512,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Fasawfa ta'lamoona mai ya'teehi 'azaabuny yukhzeehi Wa-yahillu 'alaihi 'azaabun muqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1513,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Hattaaa izaa jaaa'a amrunaa Wa-faarat tannooru qulnah mil feehaa min kullin zawjainis naini Wa-ahlaka illaa man sabaqa 'alaihil qawlu Wa-man aaman; Wa-maaa aamana ma'ahooo illaa qaleel"
    },
    {
      "index": 1514,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalar kaboo feehaa bismil laahi majraihaa Wa-mursaahaa; inna Rabbee la-Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1515,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-hiya tajree bihim fee mawjin kaljibaali Wa-naadaa Noohunib nahoo Wa-kaana fee ma'zilien yaa-bunai yarkam ma'anaa Wa-laa takum ma'al kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1516,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Qaala sa-aaweee ilaa jabalien ya'simunee minal maaa'; qaala laa 'aasimal yawma min amril laahi illaa mar rahim; Wa-haala bainahumal mawju fakaana minal mughraqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1517,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Wa-qeela yaaa ardubla'ee maaa'aki Wa-yaa-samaaa'u aqli'ee Wa-gheedal maaa'u Wa-qudiyal amru wastawat 'alal joodiyyi Wa-qeela bu'dal lilqawmiz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1518,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa naadaa noohur Rabbahoo faqaala Rabbi innabnee min ahlee Wa-inna wa'dakal haqqu Wa-Anta ahkamul haakimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1519,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa-Noohu innahoo laisa min ahlika innahoo 'amalun ghairu saalihin falaa tas'alni maa laisa laka bihee 'ilmun inneee a'izuka an takoona minal jaahileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1520,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Qaala rabbi inneee a'oozu bika an as'alaka maa laisa lee bihee 'ilmunw Wa-illaa taghfir lee Wa-tarhamneee akum minal khaasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1521,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Qeela yaa-Noohuh bit bisalaamim minnaa Wa-barakaatin 'alaika Wa-'alaaa umamim mimmam ma'ak; Wa-umamun sanumatti'uhum summa yamassuhum minaa 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1522,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Tilka min ambaaa'il ghaibi nooheehaaa ilaika maa kunta ta'lamuhaaaa anta Wa-laa qawmuka min qabli haazaa fasbir innal 'aaqibata lilmuttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1523,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa-ilaa 'aadin akhaahum Hoodaa; qaala yaa-qawmi' budul laaha maa lakum min ilaahin ghairuhooo in antum illaa muftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1524,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Yaa-qawmi laaa as'alukum 'alaihi ajran in ajriya illaa 'alal lazee fataranee; afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1525,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaa-qawmis taghfiroo Rabbakum summa toobooo ilaihi yursilis samaaa'a 'alaikum midraaranw Wa-yazidkum quwwatan ilaa quwwatikum Wa-laa tatawallaw mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1526,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Hoodu maa ji'tanaa bibaiyinatinw Wa-maa nahnu bitaarikeee aalihatinaa 'an qawlika Wa-maa nahnu laka bimu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1527,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "In naqoolu illa' taraaka ba'du aalihatinaa bisooo'; qaala inneee ushhidul laaha wash-hadooo annee bareee'um mimmaa tushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1528,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 55,
      "text": "Min doonihee fakeedoonee jamee'an summa laa tunziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1529,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Innee tawakkaltu 'alal laahi Rabbee Wa-Rabbikum; maa min daaabbatin illaa Huwa aakhizum binaasiyatihaa; inna Rabbee 'alaa Siraatim mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1530,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Fa-in tawallaw faqad ablaghtukum maaa ursiltu biheee ilaikum; Wa-yastakhlifu Rabbee qawman ghairakum Wa-laa tadur-roonahoo shai'aa; inna Rabbee 'alaa kulli shai'in Hafeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 1531,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa jaaa'a amrunaa naj-jainaa Hoodanw wallazeena aamanoo ma'ahoo birahmatim minnaa Wa-naj-jainaahum min 'azaabin ghaleez"
    },
    {
      "index": 1532,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Wa-tilka 'aad, jahadoo bi-Aayaati Rabbihim Wa-'asaw Rusulahoo wattaba'ooo amra kulli jabbaarin 'aneed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1533,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wa-utbi'oo fee haazihid dunyaa la'natanw Wa-Yawmal Qiyaamah; alaaa inna 'Aadan kafaroo Rabbahum; alaa bu'dal li-'Aadin qawmin Hood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1534,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-ilaa Samooda akhaahum Saalihaa; qaala yaa-qawmi' budul laaha maa lakum min ilaahim ghairuhoo Huwa ansha-akum minal ardi wasta'-marakum feehaa fastaghfiroohu summa toobooo ilaih; inna Rabbee Qareebum Mujeeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1535,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Saalihu qad kunta feenaa marjuwwan qabla haazaaa atanhaanaaa an na'bu-da maa ya'budu aabaaa'unaa Wa-innanaa lafee shakkim mimmaa tad'oonaaa ilaihi mureeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1536,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa-qawmi ara'aytum in kuntu 'alaa baiyinatim mir Rabbee Wa-aataanee minhu rahmatan famai yansurunee minal laahi in 'asaituhoo famaa tazeedoonanee ghaira takhseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1537,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaa-qawmi haazihee naaqatul laahi lakum aayatan fazaroohaa taakul feee ardil laahi Wa-laa tamassoohaa bisooo'in fa-yaakhuzakum azaabun qareeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1538,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Fa-'aqaroohaa faqaala tamatta'oo fee daarikum salaasata aiy-yaamin zaalika wa'dun ghairu makzoob"
    },
    {
      "index": 1539,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'a amrunaa najjainaa Saalihanw wal-lazeena aamanoo ma'ahoo birahmatim minnaa Wa-min khizyi Yawmi'iz inna Rabbaka Huwal Qawiyyul 'Azeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 1540,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Wa-akhazal lazeena zalamus saihatu fa-asbahoo fee diyaarihim jaasimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1541,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Ka-al lam yaghnaw feehaaa; alaaa inna Samooda kafaroo Rabbahum; alaa bu'dal li-Samood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1542,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad jaaa'at Rusulunaaa Ibraaheema bilbushraa qaaloo salaaman qaala salaamun famaa labisa an jaaa'a bi'ij-lin haneez"
    },
    {
      "index": 1543,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Falammaa ra-aaa aidiyahum laa tasilu ilaihi nakirahum Wa-awjasa minhum kheefah; qaaloo laa takhaf innaaa ursilnaaa ilaa qawmi Loot"
    },
    {
      "index": 1544,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wamra-atuhoo qaaa'imatun fadahikat fabashsharnaahaa bi-Iss-haaqa Wa-minw waraaa'i Iss-haaqa Ya'qoob"
    },
    {
      "index": 1545,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Qaalat yaa-wailataaa 'aalidu Wa-ana 'ajoozunw Wa-haaza ba'lee shaikhan inna haazaa lashai'un 'ajeeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1546,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Qaalooo ata'jabeena min amril laahi rahmatul laahi Wa-barakaatuhoo 'alaikum Ahlal Bayt; innahoo Hameedun Majeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1547,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Falammaa zahaba an Ibraaheemar raw'u Wa-jaaa'at hul-bushraaa yujaadilunaa fee qawmi Loot"
    },
    {
      "index": 1548,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 75,
      "text": "Inna Ibraaheema la-haleemun awwaahun muneeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1549,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-Ibraaheemu a'rid 'an haazaaa innahoo qad jaaa'a amru Rabbika Wa-innahum aateehim 'azaabun ghairun mardood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1550,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa jaaa'at Rusulunaa Lootan seee'a bihim Wa-daaqa bihim zar'anw Wa-qaala haazaa yawmun 'aseeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1551,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaaa'ahoo qawmuhoo yuhra'oona ilaihi Wa-min qablu kaanoo ya'maloonas saiyyiaat; qaala yaa-qawmi haaa'ulaaa'i banaatee hunna atharu lakum fattaqul laaha Wa-laa tukhzooni fee daifee alaisa minkum rajulur rasheed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1552,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo laqad 'alimta maa lanaa fee banaatika min haqq, Wa-innaka lata'lamu maa nureed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1553,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 80,
      "text": "Qaala law anna lee bikum quwwatan aw aaweee ilaa ruknin shadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1554,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Lootu innaa Rusulu Rabbika lain yasiloo ilaika fa-asri bi-ahlika biqit-'im minal laili Wa-laa yaltafit minkum ahadun illam ra-ataka innahoo museebuhaa maaa asaabahum; inna maw'i-dahumus subh; alaisas subhu biqareeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1555,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'a amrunaa ja'alnaa 'aaliyahaa saafilahaa Wa-amtamaa 'alaihaa hijaaratam min sijjeelim mandood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1556,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 83,
      "text": "Musawwamatan 'inda Rabbik; Wa-maa hiya minaz zaalimena biba'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1557,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Wa-ilaa Madyana akhaahum Shu'aibaa; qaala yaa-qawmi' budul laaha maa lakum min ilaahin ghairuhoo Wa-laa tanqusul mikyaala walmeezaan; inneee araakum bikhairinw Wa-innee akhaafu 'alaikum 'azaaba Yawmim muheet"
    },
    {
      "index": 1558,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaa-qawmi awful mikyaala walmeezaana bilqisti Wa-laa tabkhasun naasa ashyaaa'ahum Wa-laa ta'saw fil ardi mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1559,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Baqiyyatul laahi khairul lakum in kuntum mu'mineen; Wa-maa ana 'alaikum bihafeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 1560,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Shu'aybu 'a-salaatuka ta'muruka an natruka maa ya'budu aabaaa'unaaa aw an naf'ala feee amwaalinaa maa nashaaa'oo innaka la-antal haleemur rasheed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1561,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa qawmi ara'aitum in kuntu 'alaa baiyinatim mir Rabbee Wa-razaqanee minhu rizqan hasanaa; Wa-maaa ureedu an ukhaalifakum ilaa maaa anhaakum 'anh; in ureedu illal islaaha mastata't; Wa-maa tawfeeqeee illaa billaah; 'alaihi tawakkaltu Wa-ilaihi uneeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1562,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaa-qawmi laa yajri-mannakum shiqaaqeee aien yuseebakum mislu maaa asaaba qawma Noohin aw qawma Hoodin aw qawma Saalih; Wa-maa qawmu Lootim minkum biba'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1563,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Wastaghfiroo Rabbakum summa toobooo ilaih; inna Rabbee Raheemunw Wadood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1564,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Shu'aibu maa nafqahu kaseeram mimmaa taqoolu Wa-innaa lanaraaka feenaa da'eefanw Wa-law-laa rahtuka larajamnaaka Wa-maaa anta 'alainaa bi'azeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 1565,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa-qawmi arahteee a'azzu 'alaikum minal laahi wattakhaztumoohu waraaa'akum zihriyyan inna Rabbee bimaa ta'maloona muheet"
    },
    {
      "index": 1566,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaa-qawmi' maloo 'alaa makaanatikum innee 'aamilun sawfa ta'lamoona many ya'teehi 'azaabuny yukhzeehi Wa-man huwa kaazib; wartaqibooo innnee ma'akum raqeeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1567,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa jaaa'a amrunaa najjainaa shu'aibanw wal-lazeena aamanoo ma'ahoo birahmatim minnaa Wa-akhazatil lazeena zalamus saihatu fa-asbahoo fee diyaarihim jaasimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1568,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Ka-al lam yaghnaw feehaaa; alaa bu'dal li-Madyana Kamaa ba'idat Samood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1569,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 96,
      "text": "Wa-laqad arsalnaa Moosaa bi-Aayaatinaa Wa-sultaanim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1570,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Ilaa Fir'awna Wa-mala'ihee fattaba'ooo amra Fir'awna Wa-maaa amru Fir'awna birasheed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1571,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Yaqdumu qawmahoo Yawmal Qiyaamati fa-awrada-humun Naara Wa-bi'sal wirdul mawrood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1572,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Wa-utbi'oo fee haazihee la'natanw Wa-Yawmal Qiyaamah; bi'sar rifdul marfood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1573,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Zaalika min ambaaa'il quraa naqussuhoo 'alaika minhaa qaaa'imunw Wa-haseed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1574,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa zalamnaahum Wa-laakin zalamooo anfusahum famaaa aghnat 'anhum aalihatuhumul latee yad'oona min doonil laahi min shai'il lammaa jaaa'a amru Rabbika Wa-maa zaadoohum ghaira tatbeeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1575,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika akhzu Rabbika izaaa akhazal quraa Wa-hiya zaalimah; inna akhzahooo aleemun shadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1576,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Inna fee zaalika la-aayatal liman khaafa 'azaabal Aakhirah; zaalika Yawmum majmoo'ul lahun naasu Wa-zaalika Yawmum mashhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1577,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 104,
      "text": "Wa-maa nu'akhkhiruhooo illaa li-ajalim ma'dood"
    },
    {
      "index": 1578,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Yawma yaati laa takallamu nafsun illaa bi-iznih; faminhum shaqiyyunw Wa-sa'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1579,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Fa-ammal lazeena shaqoo fafin Naari lahum feehaa zafeerunw Wa-shaheeq"
    },
    {
      "index": 1580,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Khaalideena feehaa maa daamatis samaawaatu wal-ardu illaa maa shaaa'a Rabbuk; inna Rabbaka fa'-'aalul limaa yureed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1581,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Wa-ammal lazeena su'idoo fafil Jannati khaalideena feehaa maa daamatis samaawaatu wal-ardu illaa maa shaaa'a Rabbuk; ataaa'an ghaira majzooz"
    },
    {
      "index": 1582,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Falaa taku fee miryatim mimmmaa ya'budu haaa'ulaaa'; maa ya'budoona illaa kamaa ya'budu aabaaa'uhum min qabl; Wa-innaa lamuwaf-foohum naseebahum ghaira manqoos"
    },
    {
      "index": 1583,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Moosal Kitaaba fakhtulifa feeh; Wa-law-laa Kalimatun sabaqat mir Rabbika laqudiya bainahum; Wa-innahum lafee shakkim minhu mureeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1584,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Wa-inna kullal lammaa la-yuwaffiyannahum Rabbuka a'maalahum; innahoo bimaa ya'maloona Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1585,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "Fastaqim kamaaa umirta Wa-man taaba ma'aka Wa-laa tatghaw; innahoo bimaa ta'maloona Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1586,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tarkanooo ilal lazeena zalamoo fatamassa-kumun Naaru Wa-maa lakum min doonil laahi min awliyaaa'a summa laa tunsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1587,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 114,
      "text":
          "Wa-aqimis Salaata tarafayin nahaari Wa-zulafam minal layl; innal hasanaati yuzhibnas saiyi-aat; zaalika zikraa liz-zaakireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1588,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 115,
      "text": "Wasbir fa-innal laaha laa yudee'u ajral muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1589,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Falaw-laa kaana minal qurooni min qablikum ooloo baqiyyatiny yanhawna 'anil fasaadi fil ardi illaa qaleelam mimman anjainaa minhum; wattaba'al lazeena zalamoo maaa utrifoo feehi Wa-kaanoo mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1590,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana Rabbuka liyuhlikal quraa bizulminw Wa-ahluhaa muslihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1591,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 118,
      "text":
          "Wa-law shaaa'a Rabbuka laja'al annnaasa ummatanw waa-hidatanw Wa-laa yazaaloona mukhtalifeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1592,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 119,
      "text":
          "Illaa mar rahima Rabbuk; Wa-lizaalika khalaqahum; Wa-tammat Kalimatu Rabbika la-amla'ana Jahannama minal jinnati wannnaasi ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1593,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 120,
      "text":
          "Wa-kullan naqussu 'alaika min ambaaa'ir Rusuli maa nusabbitu bihee fu'aadak; Wa-jaaa'aka fee haazihil haqqu Wa-maw'izatunw Wa-zikraa lilmu'-mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1594,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 121,
      "text":
          "Wa-qul lillazeena laa yu'minoo na'maloo 'alaa makaanatikum innaa 'aamiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1595,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 122,
      "text": "Wantaziroo innaa mun-taziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1596,
      "sura": 11,
      "aya": 123,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahi ghaibus samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-ilaihi yurja'ul amru kulluhoo fa'bud-hu Wa-tawakkal 'alaih; Wa-maa Rabbuka bighaafilin 'ammaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1597,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 1,
      "text": "Alif-Laaam-Raa; tilka Aayaatul Kitaabil Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1598,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Innaaa anzalnaahu quraanan 'Arabiyyal la-'allakum ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1599,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Nahnu naqussu 'alaika ahsanal qasasi bimaaa awhainaaa ilaika haazal quraana Wa-in kunta min qablihee laminal ghaafileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1600,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Iz qaala Yoosufu li-abeehi yaaa-abati innee ra-aytu ahada 'ashara kawkabanw wash-shamsa walqamara ra-aytuhum lee saajideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1601,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa-bunaiya laa taqsus ru'yaaka 'alaaa ikhwatika fayakeedoo laka kaidaa; innash Shaitaana lil-insaani 'aduwwum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1602,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika yajtabeeka rabbuka Wa-yu'allimuka min ta'weelil ahaadeesi Wa-yutimmu ni'matahoo 'alaika Wa-'alaaa Aali Ya'qooba kamaaa atammahaa 'alaaa abawaika min qablu Ibraaheema Wa-Ishaaq; inna Rabbaka 'Aleemun hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1603,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 7,
      "text": "Laqad kaana fee Yoosufa Wa-ikhwatiheee Aayaatul lissaaa'ileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1604,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Iz qaaloo la-Yoosufu Wa-akhoohu ahabbu ilaaa Abeenaa minnaa Wa-nahnu 'usbatun; inna abaanaa lafee dalaalim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1605,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Uqtuloo Yoosufa awitra hoohu ardany yakhlu lakum wajhu abeekum Wa-takoonoo mim ba'dihee qawman saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1606,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Qaalaa qaaa'ilum minhum laa taqtuloo Yoosufa Wa-alqoohu fee ghayaabatil jubbi yaltaqithu badus sai-yaarati in kuntum faa-'ileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1607,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaaa-abaanaa maa laka laa ta'mannaa 'alaa Yoosufa Wa-innaa lahoo lanaa-sihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1608,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Arsillhu ma'anaa ghadany yarta'wa yal'ab Wa-innaa lahoo lahaafizoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1609,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Qaala innee la-yahzununeee an tazhaboo bihee Wa-akhaafu any ya'kulahuz zi'bu Wa-antum 'anhu ghaafiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1610,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo la-in akalahuz zi'bu Wa-nahnu 'usbatun innaaa izal lakhaasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1611,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Falammaa zahaboo bihee Wa-ajma'ooo aien yaj'aloohu fee ghayaabatil jubb; Wa-awhainaaa ilaihi latunabbi-'annahum bi-amrihim haaza Wa-hum laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1612,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 16,
      "text": "Wa-jaaa'ooo abaahum 'ishaaa-'aien yabkoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1613,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaaa-abaanaaa innaa zahabnaa nastabiqu Wa-taraknaa Yoosufa 'inda mataa'inaa fa-akhalahuz zi'b, Wa-maaa anta bimu'minil lanaa Wa-law kunnaa saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1614,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaaa'oo 'alaa qameesi-hee bidamin kazib qaala bal sawwalat lakum anfusukum amraa; fasabrun jameel; wallaahul musta'aanu 'alaa maa tasifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1615,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaaa'at saiyyaaratun fa-arsaloo waaridahum fa-adlaa dalwah; qaala yaa-bushraa haaza ghulaam; Wa-asarroohu bi-daa'ah; wallaahu 'aleemum bimaa ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1616,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-sharawhu bisamanim bakhsin daraahima ma'doo-datinw Wa-kaanoo feehi minaz zaahideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1617,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazish taraahu mim Misra limra atiheee akrimee maswaahu 'asaaa any-yanfa'anaaa aw nattakhizahoo waladaa; Wa-kazaalika mak-kannaa li-Yoosufa fil ardi Wa-linu'allimahoo min ta'weelil ahaadees; wallaahu ghaalibun 'alaaa amrihee Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1618,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa balagha ashuddahooo aatainaahu hukmanw Wa-'ilmaa; Wa-kazaa-lika najzil muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1619,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa-raawadat-hul latee huwa fee baitihaa 'an nafsihee Wa-ghallaqatil abwaaba Wa-qaalat haita lak; qaala ma'aazal laahi innahoo rabbeee ahsana maswaay; innahoo laa yuflihuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1620,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad hammat bihee Wa-hamma bihaa law-laaa ar ra-aa burhaana rabbih; kazaalika linasrifa 'anhu sooo'a walfa-hshaaa'; innahoo min 'ibaadi-nal mukhlaseen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1621,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wastabaqal baaba Wa-qaddat qameesahoo min duburinw Wa-alfayaa saiyidahaa ladal baab; qaalat maa jazaaa'u man araada bi ahlika sooo'an illaaa any-yusjana aw azaabun 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1622,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Qaala hiya raawadatnee 'an nafsee Wa-shahida shaahidum min ahlihaa in kaana qameesuhoo qudda min qubulin fasadaqat Wa-huwa minal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1623,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wa-in kaana qameesuhoo qudda min duburin fakazabat Wa-huwa minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1624,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Falammaa ra-aa qamee-sahoo qudda min duburin qaala innahoo min kaidikunna inna kaidakunna 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1625,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Yoosufu a'rid 'an haaza wastaghfiree li-zanbiki innaki kunti minal khaati'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1626,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala niswatun fil madeenatim ra-atul 'Azeezi turaawidu fataahaa 'an nafsihee qad shaghafahaa hubbaa; innaa lana-raahaa fee dalaalim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1627,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Falammaa sami'at bimak-rihinna arsalat ilaihinna Wa-a'tadat lahunna muttaka-anw Wa-aatat kulla waahidatim min-hunna sikkeenanw Wa-qaala-tikh ruj 'alaihinna falammaa ra-aynahooo akbarnahoo Wa-qatta'na aydiyahunna Wa-qulna haasha lillaahi maa haaza basharaa; in haazaaa illaa malakun kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1628,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Qaalat fazaalikunnal lazee lumtunnanee feeh; Wa-laqad raawattuhoo 'an nafsihee fasta'sam; Wa-la'il lam yaf'al maaa aamuruhoo la-yusjananna Wa-la-yakoonam minas saaghireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1629,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Qaala rabbis sijnu ahabbu ilaiyya mimma yad'oo-naneee 'ilaihi Wa-illaa tasrif 'annee kaidahunna asbu ilaihinna Wa-akum minal jaahileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1630,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Fastajaaba lahoo rabbuhoo fasarafa 'anhu kaidahunn; innahoo huwas Samee'ul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1631,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Summa badaa lahum min ba'di maa ra-awul Aayaati layasjununnahoo hatta heen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1632,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-dakhala ma'a hussijna fata-yaan; qaala ahaduhumaaa inneee araaneee a'siru khamranw Wa-qaalal aakharu inneee araaneee ahmilu fawqa ra'see khubzan ta'kulut tairu minhu; nabbi'naa bi-ta'weelih; innaa naraaka minal muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1633,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Qaala laa ya'teekumaa ta'aamun turzaqaaniheee illaa nabba'tukumaa bi-ta'weelihee; qabla aien ya'ti-yakumaa; zaalikumaa mimmaa 'allamanee rabbee; innee taraktu millata qawmil laa yu'minoona billaahi wahum bil-aakhirati hum kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1634,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wattaba'tu millata aabaaa'eee Ibraaheema Wa-Iss-haaqa Wa-Ya'qoob; maa kaana lanaaa an nushrika billaahi min shai'; zaalika min fadlil laahi 'alainaa Wa-'alan naasi Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa yashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1635,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Yaa-saahibayis sijni 'a-arbaabum mutafarriqoona khayrun amil laahul waahidul qahhaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1636,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Maa ta'budoona min doonihee illaaa asmaaa'an sam maitumoohaaa antum Wa-aabaaa'ukum maaa anzalal laahu bihaa min sultan; inilhukmu illaa lillaah; amara allaa ta'budooo illaaa iyyaah; zaalikad deenul qaiyimu Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1637,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Yaa-saahibayis sijni ammaaa ahadukumaa fa-yasqee rabbahoo khamranw Wa-ammal aakharu fa-yuslabu fata'kulut tairu mir ra'sih; qudiyal amrul lazee feehi tastaftiyaan"
    },
    {
      "index": 1638,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala lillazee zanna annahoo najim minhumaz kurnee 'inda rabbika fa-ansaahush Shaitaanu zikra Rabbihee falabisa fis sijni bid'a sineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1639,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal maliku inneee araa sab'a baqaraatin simaanien ya'kuluhunna sab'un 'ijaafunw Wa-sab'a sumbulaatin khudrinw Wa-ukhara yaabisaat; yaaa-ayyuhal mala-u aftoonee fee ru'yaaya in kuntum lirru'yaa ta'buroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1640,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Qaalooo adghaasu ahlaa-minw Wa-maa nahnu bi-ta'weelil ahlaami bi'aalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1641,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazee najaa minhumaa waddakara ba'da ummatin ana unabbi'ukum bi-ta'weelihee fa-arsiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1642,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Yoosufu ayyuhas siddeequ aftinaa fee sab'i baqaraatin simaaniny ya'kuluhunna sab'un 'ijaafunw Wa-sabi'i sumbulaatin khudrinw Wa-ukhara yaabisaatil la'alleee arji'u ilan naasi la'allahum ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1643,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Qaala tazra'oona sab'a sineena da-aban famaa hasattum fazaroohu fee sumbu-liheee illaa qaleelam mimmaa ta'kuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1644,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Thumma ya'tee mim ba'di zaalika sab'un shidaaduny ya'kulna maa qaddamtum lahunna illaa qaleelam mimma tuhsinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1645,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Thumma ya'tee mim ba'di zalika 'aamun feehi yughaa-sun naasu Wa-feehi ya'siroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1646,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal maliku 'toonee bihee falammaa jaaa'ahur rasoolu qaalar ji ilaa rabbika fas'alhu maa baalun niswatil laatee qatta'na aydiyahunn; inna Rabbee bikaidihinna 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1647,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Qaala maa khatbukunna iz raawattunna Yoosufa 'an nafsih; qulna haasha lillaahi maa 'alimnaa 'alaihi min sooo'; qaalatim ra-atul 'Azeezil 'aana hashasal haqq, ana raawat-tuhoo 'an nafsihee Wa-innahoo laminas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1648,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Zaalika liya'lama annee lam akhunhu bilghaibi Wa-annal laaha laa yahdee kaidal khaaa'ineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1649,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa ubarri'u nafsee; innan nafsa la-ammaaratum bissooo'i illaa maa rahima Rabbee; inna Rabbee Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1650,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal maliku' toonee biheee astakhlishu linafsee falammaa kallamahoo qaala innakal yawma ladainaa makeenun ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1651,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 55,
      "text": "Qaalaj 'alnee 'alaa khazaaa'inil ardi innee hafeezun 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1652,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika makkannaa li-Yoosufa fil ardi yatabawwa'u minhaa haisu yashaaaa'; nuseebu birahmatinaa man nashaaa'u Wa-laa nudee'u ajral muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1653,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Wa-la-ajrul Aakhirati khairul lillazeena aamanoo Wa-kaanoo yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1654,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaaa'a ikhwatu Yoosufa fadakhaloo 'alaihi fa'arafahum Wa-hum lahoo munkiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1655,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa jahhazahum bijahaazihim qaala' toonee bi-akhil lakum min abeekum; alaa tarawna anneee oofil kaila Wa-ana khairul munzileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1656,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Fa-il lam taatoonee bihee falaa kaila lakum 'indee Wa-laa taqraboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1657,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 61,
      "text": "Qaaloo sanuraawidu 'anhu abaahu Wa-innaa lafaa'iloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1658,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala lifityaanihij 'aloo bidaa'atahum fee rihaalihim la'allahum ya'rifoonahaaa izan qalabooo ilaaa ahlihim la'allahum yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1659,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Falammaa raja'ooo ilaaa abeehim qaaloo yaaa-abaanaa muni'a minnal kailu fa-arsil ma'anaaa akhaanaa naktal Wa-innaa lahoo lahaafizoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1660,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Qaala hal aamanukum 'alaihi illaa kamaa amintukum 'alaaa akheehi min qabl; fal-laahu khairun haafizanw Wa-Huwa arhamur Raahimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1661,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa fatahoo mataa-'ahum wajadoo bidaa'atahum ruddat ilaihim qaaloo yaaa-abaanaa maa nabghee; haazihee bida-'atunaa ruddat ilainaa Wa-nameeru ahlanaa Wa-nahfazu akhaanaa Wa-nazdaadu kaila ba'eer; zaalika kailuien yaseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1662,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Qaala lan ursilahoo ma'akum hattaa tu'tooni mawsiqam minal laahis lataa-tunnanee biheee illaaa aien yuhaata bikum falammaaa aatawhu mawsiqahum qaalal laahu 'alaa maa naqoolu Wakeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 1663,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala yaa-baniyya laa tadkhuloo mim baabinw waa-hidinw wadkhuloo min abwaabim mutafarriqah; Wa-maaa ughnee 'ankum minal laahi min shai'in; inil hukmu illaa lillaahi 'alaihi tawakkaltu Wa-'alaihi fal-yatawakkalil Mutawakkiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1664,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa dakhaloo min haisu amarahum aboohum maa kaana yughnee 'anhum minal laahi min shai'in illaa haajatan fee nafsi Ya'qooba qadaahaa; Wa-innahoo lazoo 'ilmil limaa 'allamnaahu Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1665,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa dakhaloo 'alaa Yoosufa aawaaa ilaihi akhaahu qaala inneee ana akhooka falaa tabta'is bimaa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1666,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jahhazahum bijahaazihim ja'alas siqaayata fee rahli akheehi summa azzana mu'azzinun ayyatuhal 'eeru innakum lasaariqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1667,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 71,
      "text": "Qaaloo Wa-aqbaloo 'alaihim maazaa tafqidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1668,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo nafqidu suwaa'al maliki Wa-liman jaaa'a bihee himlu ba'eerinw Wa-ana bihee za'eem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1669,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo tallaahi laqad 'alimtum maa ji'na linufsida fil ardi Wa-maa kunnaa saariqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1670,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 74,
      "text": "Qaaloo famaa jazaaa'u-hooo in kuntum kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1671,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo jazaaa'uhoo manw wujida fee rahlihee fahuwa jazaaa'uh; kazaalika najziz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1672,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Fabada-a bi-aw'iyatihim qabla wi'aaa'i akheehi summas takhrajahaa minw wi-'aaa'i akheeh; kazaalika kidnaa li-Yoosuf; maa kaana liyaakhuza akhaahu fee deenil maliki illaaa aien yashaaa'al laah; narfa'u darajaatim man nashaaa'; Wa-fawqa kulli zee 'ilmin 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1673,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo ien yasriq faqad saraqa akhul lahoo min qabl; fa-asarrahaa Yoosufu fee nafsihee Wa-lam yubdihaa lahum; qaala antum sharrum makaananw wallaahu a'lamu bimaa tasifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1674,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaaa-ayyuhal 'Azeezu inna lahooo aban shaikhan kabeeran fakhuz ahadanaa makaanahoo innaa naraaka minal muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1675,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Qaala ma'aazal laahi an naakhuza illaa manw wajadnaa mataa'anaa 'indahoo innaaa izal lazaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1676,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Falammas tay'asoo minhu khalasoo najiyyan qaala kabeeruhum alam ta'lamoon anna abaakum qad akhaza 'alaikum mawsiqam minal laahi Wa-min qablu maa farrattum fee Yoosufa falan abrahal arda hattaa yaazana leee abeee aw yahkumal laahu lee Wa-huwa khairul haakimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1677,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Irji'ooo ilaaa abeekum faqooloo yaaa-abaanaaa innab naka saraq; Wa-maa shahidnaaa illaa bimaa 'alimnaa Wa-maa kunnaa lilghaibi haafizeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1678,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Was'alil qaryatal latee kunnaa feehaa wal'eeral lateee aqbalnaa feehaa Wa-innaa lasaadiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1679,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Qaala bal sawwalat lakum anfusukum amran fasabrun jameelun 'asal laahu aien yaa-tiyanee bihim jamee'aa; innahoo Huwal 'Aleemul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1680,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Wa-tawallaa 'anhum Wa-qaala yaaa-asafaa 'alaa Yoosufa wabyaddat 'aynaahu minal huzni fahuwa kazeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1681,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo tallaahi tafta'u tazkuru Yoosufa hattaa takoona haradan aw takoona minal haalikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1682,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Qaala innamaaa ashkoo bassee Wa-huzneee ilal laahi Wa-a'lamu minal laahi maa laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1683,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Yaa-baniyyaz haboo fatahassasoo mien Yoosufa Wa-akheehi Wa-laa tai'asoo mir rawhil laahi innahoo laa yai'asu mir rawhil laahi illal qawmul kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1684,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Falammaa dakhaloo 'alaihi qaaloo yaaa-ayyuhal 'Azeezu massanaa Wa-ahlanad durru Wa-ji'naa bibidaa 'timmuzjaatin fa-awfi lanal kaila Wa-tasaddaq 'alainaa innal laaha yajzil mutasaddiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1685,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Qaala hal 'alimtum maa fa'altum bi-Yoosufa Wa-akheehi iz antum jaahiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1686,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo 'a-innaka la-anta Yoosufu qaala ana Yoosufu Wa-haazaaa akhee qad mannal laahu 'alainaa innahoo mai yattaqi Wa-yasbir fa-innal laaha laa yudee'u ajral muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1687,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo tallaahi laqad aasarakal laahu 'alainaa Wa-in kunnaa lakhaati'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1688,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Qaala laa tasreeba 'alaikumul yawma yaghfirul laahu lakum Wa-Huwa arhamur raahimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1689,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Izhaboo biqameesee haazaa fa-alqoohu 'alaa wajhi abee yaati baseeranw waatoonee bi-ahlikum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1690,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa fasalatil 'eeru qaala aboohum innee la-ajidu reeha Yoosufa law-laaa an tufannidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1691,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 95,
      "text": "Qaaloo tallaahi innaka lafee dalaalikal qadeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1692,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Falammaaa an jaaa' albasheeru alqaahu 'alaa wajhihee fartadda baseeran qaala alam aqul lakum inneee a'lamu minal laahi maa laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1693,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaaa-abaanas taghfir lanaa zunoo-banaaa innaa kunnaa khaati'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1694,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Qaala sawfa astaghfiru lakum Rabbeee innahoo Huwal Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1695,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Falammaa dakhaloo 'alaa Yoosufa aawaaa ilaihi abayaihi Wa-qaalad khuloo Misra in shaaa' al-laahu aamineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1696,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Wa-raf'a abawaihi 'alal 'arshi Wa-kharroo lahoo sujjadaa; Wa-qaala yaaa-abati haaza taaweelu ru'yaaya min qablu qad ja'alahaa Rabbee haqqaa; Wa-qad ahsana beee iz akhrajanee minas sijni Wa-jaaa'a bikum minal badwi mim ba'di an nazaghash Shaitaanu bainee Wa-baina ikhwatee; inna Rabbee lateeful limaa yashaaa'; innahoo Huwal 'Aleemul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1697,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Rabbi qad aataitanee minal mulki Wa-'allamtanee min taaweelil ahaadees; faati-ras samaawaati wal-ardi Anta waliyyee fid dunyaa wal-Aakhirati tawaffanee muslimanw Wa-alhiqnee bissaaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1698,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Zaalika min ambaaa'il ghaibi nooheehi ilaika Wa-maa kunta ladaihim iz ajma'ooo amrahum Wa-hum yamkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1699,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 103,
      "text": "Wa-maa aksarun naasi Wa-law harasta bimu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1700,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa tas'aluhum 'alaihi min ajr; in huwa illaa zikrul lil'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1701,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Wa-ka-ayyim min Aayatin fis samaawaati wal-ardi yamurroona 'alaihaa Wa-hum 'anhaa mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1702,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 106,
      "text": "Wa-maa yu'minu aksaru-hum billaahi illaa Wa-hum mushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1703,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Afa-aminooo an taatiya-hum ghaashiyatum min 'azaabil laahi aw taatiyahumus Saa'atu baghtatanw Wa-hum laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1704,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Qul haazihee sabeeleee ad'ooo ilal laah; 'alaa baseera-tin ana Wa-manit taba'anee Wa-Subhaanal laahi Wa-maaa ana minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1705,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaa min qablika illaa rijaalan nooheee ilaihim min ahlil quraa; afalam yaseeroo fil ardi fa-yanzuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul lazeena min qablihim; Wa-la-Daarul Aakhirati Khairul lillazeenat taqaw; afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1706,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Hattaaa izas tai'asar Rusulu Wa-zannooo annahum qad kuziboo jaaa'ahum nas-runaa fanujjiya man nashaaa'u Wa-laa yuraddu baasunna 'anil qawmil mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1707,
      "sura": 12,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Laqad kaana fee qasasihim 'ibratul li-ulil albaab; maa kaana hadeesany yuftaraa Wa-laakin tasdeeqal lazee baina yadihi Wa-tafseela kulli shai'inw Wa-hudanw Wa-rahmatal liqawmien yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1708,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Alif-Laaam-Meeem-Raa; tilka Aayaatul Kitaab; wallazee unzila ilaika mir Rabbikal haqqu Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1709,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Allaahul lazee raf'as samaawaati bighairi 'amadin tarawnahaa summas tawaa 'alal 'Arshi Wa-sakhkharash shamsa walqamara kulluny yajree li-ajalim musammaa; yudabbirul amra yufassilil Aayaati la'allakum biliqaaa'i Rabbikum tooqinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1710,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee maddal arda Wa-ja'ala feehaa rawaasiya Wa-anhaaraa; Wa-min kullis samaraati ja'ala feehaa zawjainis naini Yughshil lailan nahaar; inna fee zaalika la-aayaatil liqawmien yatafakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1711,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Wa-fil ardi qita'um muta-jaawiraatunw Wa-jannaatum min a'naabinw Wa-zar'unw Wa-nakheelun sinwaanunw Wa-ghairu sinwaanien yusqaa bimaaa'inw waahid; Wa-nufaddilu ba'dahaa 'alaa ba'din fil ukul; inna fee zaalika la-aayaatil liqawmien ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1712,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Wa-in ta'jab fa'ajabun qawluhum 'a-izaa kunna turaaban 'a-inna lafee khalqin jadeed; ulaaa-'ikal lazeena kafaroo bi-Rabbihim Wa-ulaaa'ikal aghlaalu feee a'naaqihim Wa-ulaaa'ika As-haabun Naari hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1713,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-yasta'jiloonaka bis-saiyi'ati qablal hasanati Wa-qad khalat min qablihimul masulaat; Wa-inna Rabbaka lazoo maghfiratil linnaasi 'alaa zulmihim Wa-inna Rabbaka lashadeedul 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1714,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaqoolul lazeena kafaroo law-laaa unzila 'alaihi Aayatum mir Rabbih; innamaaa anta munzirunw Wa-likulli qawmin haad"
    },
    {
      "index": 1715,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Allaahu ya'lamu maa tahmilu kullu unsaa Wa-maa tagheedul arhaamu Wa-maa tazdaad, Wa-kullu shai'in 'indahoo bimiqdaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1716,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 9,
      "text": "Aalimul Ghaibi wash-shahaadatil Kaabeerul Muta'aal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1717,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Sawaaa'um minkum man asarral qawla Wa-man jahara bihee Wa-man huwa mustakhfim billaili Wa-saaribum binnahaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1718,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Lahoo mu'aqqibaatum mim baini yadaihi Wa-min khalfihee yahfazoonahoo min amril laah; innal laaha laa yughaiyyiru maa biqawmin hattaa yughaiyiroo maa bianfusihim; Wa-izaaa araadal laahu biqawmin sooo'an falaa maradda lah; Wa-maa lahum min doonihee minw waal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1719,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazee yureekumul barqa khawfanw Wa-tama'anw Wa-yunshi'us sahaabas siqaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1720,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-yusabbihur ra'du bihamdihee walmalaaa'ikatu min kheefatihee Wa-yursilus sawaa'iqa fa-yuseebu bihaa mai yashaaa'u Wa-hum yujaadiloona fil laahi Wa-Huwa shadeedul mihaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1721,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Lahoo da'watul haqq; wallazeena yad'oona min doonihee laa yastajeeboona lahum bishai'in illaa kabaasiti kaffaihi ilal maaa'i liyablugha faahu Wa-maa huwa bibaalighih; Wa-maa du'aaa'ul kaafireena illaa fee dalaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1722,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahi yasjudu man fis samaawaati wal-ardi taw-'anw Wa-karhanw Wa-zilaaluhum bilghuduwwi wal-aasaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1723,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Qul mar Rabbus samaawaati wal-ard; qulil laah; qul afattakhaztum min dooniheee awliyaaa'a laa yamlikoona li-anfusihim naf'anw Wa-laa darraa; qul hal yastawil a'maa wal-baseeru am hal tastawiz zulumaatu wannoor; am ja'aloo lillaahi shurakaaa'a khalaqoo kakhalqihee fatashaa-bahal khalqu 'alaihim; qulil laahu Khaaliqu kulli shai'inw Wa-Huwal Waahidul Qahhar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1724,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Anzala minas samaaa'i maaa'an fasaalat awdiyatum biqadarihaa fahtamalas sailu zabadar raabiyaa; Wa-mimmmaa yooqidoona 'alaihi fin naarib tighaaa'a bilyatin aw mataa'in zabadum misluh; kazaalika yadribul laahul haqqa wal-baatil; fa-ammaz zabadu fa-yazhabu jufaaa'aa; Wa-ammaa maa yanfa'un naasa fa-yamkusu fil ard; kazaalika yadribul laahul amsaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1725,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Lillazeenas tajaaboo lirabbihimul husnaa; wallazeena lam yastajeeboo lahoo law anna lahum maa fil ardi jamee'anw Wa-mislahoo ma'ahoo laftadaw bih; ulaaa'ika lahum sooo'ul hisaab; Wa-ma'waahum Jahannamu Wa-bi'sal mihaad"
    },
    {
      "index": 1726,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Afamai ya'lamu annamaaa unzila ilaika mir Rabbikal haqqu kaman huwa a'maa; innamaa yatazakkaru ulul albaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1727,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 20,
      "text": "Allazeena yoofoona bi'ahdil laahi Wa-laa yanqu-doonal meesaaq"
    },
    {
      "index": 1728,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yasiloona maaa amaral laahu bihee an yoosala Wa-yakhshawna Rabbahum Wa-yakhaafoona sooo'al hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1729,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena sabarub tighaaa'a Wajhi Rabbihim Wa-aqaamus Salaata Wa-anfaqoo mimmaa razaqnaahum sirranw Wa-'alaaniyatanw Wa-yadra'oona bilhasanatis saiyi'ata ulaaa'ika lahum 'uqbad daar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1730,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Jannaatu 'adnien yadkhu-loonahaa Wa-man salaha min aabaaa'ihim Wa-azwaajihim Wa-zurriyyaatihim walmalaaa'i-katu yadkhuloona 'alaihim min kulli baab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1731,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 24,
      "text": "Salaamun 'alaikum bimaa sabartum; fani'ma 'uqbad daar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1732,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yanqudoona 'Ahdal laahi mim ba'di meesaaqihee Wa-yaqta'oona maaa amaral laahu biheee ai yoosala Wa-yufsidoona fil ardi ulaaa'ika lahumul la'natu Wa-lahum sooo'ud daar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1733,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Allaahu yabsutur rizqa limai yashaaa'u Wa-yaqdir; Wa-farihoo bilhayaatid dunyaa Wa-mal hayaatud dunya fil Aakhirati illaa mataa'"
    },
    {
      "index": 1734,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaqoolul lazeena kafaroo law-laaa unzila 'alaihi Aayatum mir Rabbih; qul innal laaha yudillu maien yashaa'u Wa-yahdeee ilaihi man anaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1735,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Allazeena aamanoo Wa-tatma'innu quloobuhum bizikril laah; alaa bizikril laahi tatma'innul quloob"
    },
    {
      "index": 1736,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Allazeena aamanoo Wa-a'amilus saalihaati toobaa lahum Wa-husnu ma-aab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1737,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Kazaalika arsalnaaka feee ummatin qad khalat min qablihaaa umamul litatluwa 'alaihimul lazeee awhainaaa ilaika Wa-hum yakfuroona bir-Rahmaaan; qul Huwa Rabbee laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa 'alaihi tawakkaltu Wa-ilaihi mataab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1738,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-law anna Quraanan suyyirat bihil jibaalu aw qutti'at bihil ardu aw kullima bihil mawtaa; bal lillaahil amru jamee'aa; afalam yai'asil lazeena aamanooo al law yashaaa 'ullaahu lahadan naasa jamee'aa; Wa-laa yazaalul lazeena kafaroo tuseebuhum bimaa sana'oo qaari'atun aw tahullu qareebam min daarihim hatta ya'tiya wa'dul laah; innal laaha laa yukhliful mee'aad"
    },
    {
      "index": 1739,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqadis tuhzi'a bi-Rusulim min qablika fa-amlaitu lillazeena kafaroo summa akhaztuhum fakaifa kaana 'iqaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1740,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Afaman Huwa qaaa'imun 'alaa kulli nafsim bimaa kasabat; Wa-ja'aloo illlaahi shurakaaa'a qul samoohum; am tunabbi'oona-hoo bimaa laa ya'lamu fil ardi; am bizaahirim minal qawl; bal zuyyina lillazeena kafaroo makruhum Wa-suddoo 'anis sabeel; Wa-mai yudlilil laaahu famaa lahoo min haad;"
    },
    {
      "index": 1741,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Lahum 'azaabun fil hayaatid dunyaa Wa-la'azaabul Aakhirati ashaaq, Wa-maa lahum minal laahi min waaq"
    },
    {
      "index": 1742,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Masalul Jannatil latee wu'idal muttaqoona tajree min tahtihal anhaaru ukuluhaa daaa'imunw Wa-zilluhaa; tilka uqbal lazeenat taqaw Wa-'uqbal kafireenan Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1743,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aatainaa-humul Kitaaba yafrahoona bimaa unzila ilaika Wa-minal Ahzaabi mai yunkiru ba'dah; qul innamaa umirtu an a'budal laaha Wa-laaa ushrika bih; ilaihi ad'oo Wa-ilaihi maab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1744,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika anzalnaahu hukman 'Arabiyyaa; Wa-la'init taba'ta ahwaaa-'ahum ba'da-maa jaaa'aka minal 'ilmi maa laka minal laahi minw waliyinw Wa-laa waaq"
    },
    {
      "index": 1745,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad arsalnaa Rusulam min qablika Wa-ja'alnaa lahum azwaajanw Wa-zurriyyah; Wa-maa kaana lirasoolin aien ya'tiya bi-aayatin illaa bi-iznil laah; likulli ajalin kitaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1746,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 39,
      "text": "Yamhul laahu maa yashaaa'u Wa-yusbitu Wa-'indahooo ummul Kitaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1747,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Wa-im maa nurriyannaka ba'dal lazee na'iduhum aw nata-waffayannaka fa-innamaa 'alaikal balaaghu Wa-'alainal hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1748,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaraw annaa na'til arda nanqusuhaa min atraafihaa; wallaahu yahkumu laa mu'aqqiba lihukmih; Wa-Huwa saree'ul hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1749,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-qad makaral lazeena min qablihim falillaahil makru jamee'aa; ya'lamu maa taksibu kullu nafs; Wa-sa-ya'lamul kuffaaru liman 'uqbad daar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1750,
      "sura": 13,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaqoolul lazeena kafaroo lasta mursalaa; qul kafaa billaahi shaheedam bainee Wa-bainakum Wa-man 'indahoo 'ilmul Kitaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1751,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Alif-Laaam-Raa; Kitaabun anzalnaahu ilaika litukhrijan naasa minaz zulumaati ilan noori bi-izni Rabbihim ilaa siraatil 'Azeezil Hameed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1752,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Allaahil lazee lahoo maa fis samaawaati Wa-maa fill ard; Wa-wailul lilkaafireena min 'azaabin shadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1753,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yastahibboo-nal hayaatad dunyaa 'alal aakhirati Wa-yasuddoona 'ansabeelil laahi Wa-yabghoonahaa 'iwajaa; ulaaa 'ika fee dalaalin ba'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1754,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaa mir Rasoolin illaa bilisaani qawmihee liyubaiyina lahum fa-yudillul laahu mai yashaaa'u Wa-yahdee mai yashaaa'; Wa-Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1755,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad arsalnaa Moosaa bi-Aayaatinaa an akhrij qawmaka minaz zulumaati ilan noori Wa-zak-kirhum bi-ayyaamil laah; inna fee zaalika la-aayaatil likulli sabbaarin shakoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 1756,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaala Moosaa liqawmihiz kuroo ni'matal laahi 'alaikum iz anjaakum min Aali Fir'awna yasoomoo-nakum sooo'al 'azaabi Wa-yuzabbihoona abnaaa'akum Wa-yastahyoona nisaaa'akum; Wa-fee zaalikum balaaa'un mir Rabbikum 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1757,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz ta-azzana Rabbukum la'in shakartum la-azeedannakum Wa-la'in kafartum inna 'azaabee lashadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1758,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala Moosaaa in takfurooo antum Wa-man fil ardi jamee'an fa-innal laaha la-Ghaniyyun Hameed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1759,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Alam ya'tikum naba'ul lazeena min qablikum qawmi Noohinw Wa-'Aadinw Wa-Samood, wallazeena mim ba'dihim; laa ya'lamuhum illallaah; jaaa'at hum Rusuluhum bilbaiyinaati faraddooo aydiyahum feee afwaahihim Wa-qaalooo innaa kafarnaa bimaaa ursiltum bihee Wa-innaa lafee shakkim mimmaa tad'oonanaaa ilaihi mureeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 1760,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Qaalat Rusuluhum afil laahi shakkun faatiris samaawaati wal-ardi yad'ookum liyaghfira lakum min zunoobikum Wa-yu'akhirakum ilaaa ajalin musammaa; qaaloo in antum illaa basharum mislunaa tureedoona an tasuddoonaa 'ammaa kaana ya'budu aabaaa'unaa fa'toonaa bi-sultaanin mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1761,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Qaalat lahum Rusuluhum in nahnu illaa basharum mislukum Wa-laakinnal laaha yamunnu 'alaa maien yashaaa'u min 'ibaadihee Wa-maa kaana lanaaa an na'tiyakum bisul-taanin illaa bi-iznil laah; Wa-'alal laahi falyatawakkalil mu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1762,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa lanaa allaa natawakkala 'alal laahi Wa-qad hadaanaa subulanaa; Wa-lanasbiranna 'alaa maaa aazaitumoonaa; Wa-'alal laahi falyatawakkalil mutawakkiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1763,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena kafaroo li-Rusulihim lanukhrijanna-kum min aardinaaa aw la-ta'oodunna fee millatinaa fa-awhaaa ilaihim Rabbuhum lanuhlikannaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1764,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-lanuskinan-nakumul arda min ba'dihim; zaalika liman khaafa maqaamee Wa-khaafa wa'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1765,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 15,
      "text": "Wastaftahoo Wa-khaaba kullu jabbaarin 'aneed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1766,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 16,
      "text": "Minw waraaa'ihee jahannamu Wa-yusqaa min maaa'in sadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1767,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Yatajarra'uhoo Wa-laa yakaadu yuseeghuhoo Wa-ya'teehil mawtu min kulli makaaninw Wa-maa huwa bimaiyitinw Wa-minw waraaa'ihee 'azaabun ghaleez"
    },
    {
      "index": 1768,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Masalul lazeena kafaroo bi-Rabbihim; a'maaluhum karamaadinish taddat bihir reehu fee yawmin 'aasifin; laa yaqdiroona mimmaa kasaboo 'alaa shai'; zaalika huwad dalaalul ba'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1769,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annal laaha khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda bilhaqq; iny yasha yuzhibkum Wa-ya'ti bikhalqin jadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 1770,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 20,
      "text": "Wa-maa zaalika 'alal laahi bi-'azeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 1771,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-barazoo lillaahi jamee'an faqaalad du'afaaa'u lil-lazeenas takbarooo innaa kunnaa lakum taba'an fahal antum mughnoona 'annaa min 'azaabil laahi min shai'; qaaloo law hadaanal laahu la-hadaynaakum sawaaa'un 'alainaaa ajazi'naa am sabarnaa maa lanaa min mahees"
    },
    {
      "index": 1772,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalash Shaitaanu lammaa qudiyal amru innal laaha wa'adakum wa'dal haqqi Wa-wa'attukum fa-akhlaftukum Wa-maa kaana liya 'alaikum min sultaanin illaaa an da'awtukum fastajabtum lee falaa taloomoonee Wa-loomooo anfusakum maaa ana bimusrikhikum Wa-maaa antum bimusrikhiyya innee kafartu bimaaa ashraktumooni min qabl; innaz zaalimeena lahum azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1773,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa-udkhilal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati Jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaa bi-izni Rabbihim tahiyyatuhum feeha salaam"
    },
    {
      "index": 1774,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Alam tara kaifa darabal laahu masalan kalimatan taiyibatan kashajaratin taiyibatin asluhaa saabitunw Wa-far'uhaa fis samaaa'"
    },
    {
      "index": 1775,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Tu'teee ukulahaa kulla heenim bi-izni Rabbihaa; Wa-yadribul laahul amsaala linnaasi la'allahum yatazak-karoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1776,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Wa-masalu kalimatin khabeesatin kashajaratin khabee-satinij tussat min fawqil ardi maa lahaa min qaraar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1777,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Yusabbitul laahul lazeena aamanoo bilqawlis saabiti fil hayaatid dunyaa Wa-fil Aakhirati Wa-yudillul laahuz zaalimeen; Wa-yaf'alul laahu maa yashaaa'"
    },
    {
      "index": 1778,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilal lazeena baddaloo ni'matal laahi kufranw Wa-ahalloo qawmahum daaral bawaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1779,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 29,
      "text": "Jahannama yaslawnahaa Wa-bi'sal qaraar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1780,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'aloo lillaahi andaadal liyudilloo 'an sabeelih; qul tamatta'oo fa-innaa maseerakum ilan Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1781,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Qul li'ibaadiyal lazeena aamanoo yuqeemus Salaata Wa-yunfiqoo mimmaa razaqnaahum sirranw Wa-'alaaniyatam min qabli any yaatiya Yawmul laa bai'un feehi Wa-laa khilaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1782,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Allaahul lazee khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda Wa-anzala minas samaaa'i maaa'an faakhraja bihee minas samaraati rizqal lakum Wa-sakhkhara lakumul fulka litajriya fil bahri bi-amrihee Wa-sakhkhara lakumul anhaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1783,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-sakhkhara lakumush shamsa walqamara daaa'ibaini Wa-sakhkhara lakumul laila wannahaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1784,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-aataakum min kulli maa sa-altumooh; Wa-in ta'uddoo ni'matal laahi laa tuhsoohaa; innal insaana lazaloo-mun kaffaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1785,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaala Ibraaheemu Rabbij 'al haazal balada aaminanw wajnubnee Wa-baniyya an na'budal asnaam"
    },
    {
      "index": 1786,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Rabbi innahunna adlalna kaseeram minan naasi faman tabi'anee fa-innahoo minnee Wa-man 'asaanee fa-innaka Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1787,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaaa inneee askantu min zurriyyatee biwaadin ghairi zee zar'in 'inda Baitikal Muharrami Rabbanaa liyuqeemus Salaata faj'al af'idatam minan naasi tahweee ilaihim warzuqhum minas samaraati la'allahum yashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1788,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaaa innaka ta'lamu maa nukhfee Wa-maa nu'lin; Wa-maa yakhfaa 'alal laahi min shai'in fil ardi Wa-laa fis samaaa'"
    },
    {
      "index": 1789,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Alhamdu lillaahil lazee wahaba lee 'alal kibari Ismaa'eela Wa-Ishaaq; inna Rabbee lasamee'ud du'aaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 1790,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Rabbij 'alnee muqeemas Salaati Wa-min zurriyyatee Rabbanaa Wa-taqabbal du'aaa'"
    },
    {
      "index": 1791,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Rabbanagh fir lee Wa-liwaalidaiya Wa-lilmu'mineena Yawma yaqoomul hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1792,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tahsabannal laaha ghaafilan 'ammaa ya'maluz zaalimoon; innamaa yu'akh-khiruhum li-Yawmin tashkhasu feehil absaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1793,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Muhti'eena muqni'ee ru'oosihim laa yartaddu ilaihim tarfuhum Wa-af'idatuhum hawaaa'"
    },
    {
      "index": 1794,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Wa-anzirin naasa Yawma yaateehimul 'azaabu fa-yaqoolul lazeena zalamoo Rabbanaaa akhkhirnaaa ilaaa ajalin qareebin nujib da'wataka Wa-nattabi-'ir Rusul; awalam takoonooo aqsamtum min qablu maa lakum min zawaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1795,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa-sakantum fee masaakinil lazeena zalamooo anfusahum Wa-tabaiyana lakum kaifa fa'alnaa bihim Wa-darabnaa lakumul amsaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1796,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-qad makaroo makrahum Wa-'indal laahi makruhum Wa-in kaana makruhum litazoola minhul jibaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 1797,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Falaa tahsabannal laaha mukhlifa wa'dihee Rusulah; innal laaha 'azeezun zun tiqaam"
    },
    {
      "index": 1798,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Yawma tubaddalul ardu ghairal ardi wassamaawaatu Wa-barazoo lillaahil Waahidil Qahhaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1799,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 49,
      "text": "Wa-taral mujrimeena Yawma'izim muqarraneena filas faad"
    },
    {
      "index": 1800,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 50,
      "text": "Saraabeeluhum min qatiraaninw Wa-taghshaa wujoohahumun Naar"
    },
    {
      "index": 1801,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Liyajziyal laahu kulla nafsim maa kasabat; innal laaha saree'ul hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1802,
      "sura": 14,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Haaza balaaghul linnaasi Wa-liyunzaroo bihee Wa-liya'lamooo annamaa Huwa Illaahunw Waahidunw Wa-liyaz-zakkara ulul albaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 1803,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 1,
      "text": "Alif-Laaam-Raa; tilka Aayaatul Kitaabi Wa-Qur-aa-nim Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1804,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Rubamaa yawaddul lazeena kafaroo law kaanoo muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1805,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Zarhum yaakuloo Wa-yatamatta'oo Wa-yulhihimul amalu fasawfa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1806,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 4,
      "text": "Wa-maaa ahlaknaa min qaryatin illaa Wa-lahaa kitaabum ma'loom"
    },
    {
      "index": 1807,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 5,
      "text": "Maa tasbiqu min ummatin ajalahaa Wa-maa yastaakhiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1808,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo yaaa-aiyuhal lazee nuzzila 'alaihiz Zikru innaka lamajnoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1809,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 7,
      "text": "Law maa taateenaa bil-malaaa'ikati in kunta minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1810,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Maa nunazzilul malaaa'i-kata illaa bilhaqqi Wa-maa kaanooo izam munzareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1811,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 9,
      "text": "Innaa Nahnu nazalnaz Zikra Wa-Innaa lahoo lahaa-fizoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1812,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 10,
      "text": "Wa-laqad arsalnaa min qablika fee shiya'il awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1813,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 11,
      "text": "Wa-maa yaateehim mir Rasoolin illaa kaanoo bihee yastahzi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1814,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 12,
      "text": "kazaalika naslukuhoo fee quloobil mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1815,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 13,
      "text": "Laa yu'minoona bihee Wa-qad khalat sunnatul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1816,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-law fatahnaa 'alaihim baabam minas samaaa'i fazaloo feehi ya'rujoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1817,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 15,
      "text": "Laqaaloo innamaa sukkirat absaarunaa bal nahnu qawmum mashooroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1818,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad ja'alnaa fis samaaa'i buroojanw Wa-zaiyannaahaa linnaazireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1819,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 17,
      "text": "Wa-hafiznaahaa min kulli Shaitaanir rajeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1820,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 18,
      "text": "Illaa manis taraqas sam'a fa-atba'ahoo shihaabum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1821,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Wal-arda madadnaahaa Wa-alqainaa feehaa rawaasiya Wa-ambatnaa feehaa min kulli shai'im mawzoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1822,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnaa lakum feehaa ma'aayisha Wa-mal lastum lahoo biraaziqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1823,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-im min shai'in illaa 'indanaa khazaaa-'inuhoo Wa-maa nunazziluhooo illaa biqadarim ma'loom"
    },
    {
      "index": 1824,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-arsalnar riyaaha la-waaqiha fa-anzalnaa minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa-asqai-naakumoohu Wa-maaa antum lahoo bikhaazineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1825,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 23,
      "text": "Wa-innnaa la-nahnu nuhyee Wa-numeetu Wa-nahnul waarisoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1826,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Wa-la-qad 'alimnal mustaqdimeena minkum Wa-laqad 'alimnal mustaakhireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1827,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 25,
      "text": "Wa-inna Rabbaka Huwa yahshuruhum; innahoo Hakeemun 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1828,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 26,
      "text": "Wa-laqad khalaqnal insaana min salsaalim min hama-im masnoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1829,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 27,
      "text": "Waljaaanna khalaqnaahu min qablu min naaris samoom"
    },
    {
      "index": 1830,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaala Rabbuka lilmalaaa'-ikati innee khaaliqum basharam min salsaalim min hama-im masnoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1831,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Fa-izaa sawwaituhoo Wa-nafakhtu feehi mir roohee faqa'oo lahoo saajideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1832,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 30,
      "text": "Fasajadal malaaa'ikatu kulluhum ajma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1833,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 31,
      "text": "Illaaa ibleesa abaaa ai yakoona ma'as saajideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1834,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 32,
      "text": "Qaala yaaa-Ibleesu maa laka allaa takoona ma'as saajideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1835,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Qaala lam akul li-asjuda libasharin khalaqtahoo min salsaalim min hama-im masnoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1836,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 34,
      "text": "Qaala fakhruj minhaa fa-innaka rajeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1837,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 35,
      "text": "Wa-inna 'alaikal la'nata ilaa Yawmid Deen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1838,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 36,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbi fa-anzirneee ilaa Yawmi yub'asoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1839,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 37,
      "text": "Qaala fa-innaka minal munzareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1840,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 38,
      "text": "Ilaa Yawmil waqtil ma'loom"
    },
    {
      "index": 1841,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbi bimaaa aghwaitanee la-uzayyin-anna lahum fil ardi Wa-la-ughwiyan-nahum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1842,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 40,
      "text": "Illaa 'ibaadaka minhumul mukhlaseen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1843,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 41,
      "text": "Qaala haaza Siraatun 'alaiya Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1844,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Inna 'ibaadee laisa laka 'alaihim sultaanun illaa manit taba'aka minal ghaaween"
    },
    {
      "index": 1845,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 43,
      "text": "Wa-inna jahannama lamaw'iduhum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1846,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 44,
      "text": "Lahaa sab'atu abwaab; likulli baabim minhum juz'um maqsoom"
    },
    {
      "index": 1847,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 45,
      "text": "Innal muttaqeena fee Jannaatinw Wa-'uyoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1848,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 46,
      "text": "Udkhuloohaa bisalaamin aamineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1849,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-naza'naa ma fee sudoorihim min ghillin ikhwaanan 'alaa sururim mutaqaabileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1850,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 48,
      "text": "Laa yamas-suhum feehaa nasabunw Wa-maa hum minhaa bimukhrajeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1851,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 49,
      "text": "Nabbi' 'ibaadeee annneee an al-Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1852,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 50,
      "text": "Wa-anna 'azaabee huwal 'azaabul aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1853,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 51,
      "text": "Wa-nabbi'hum 'an daifi Ibraaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1854,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Iz dakhaloo 'alaihi faqaaloo salaaman qaala innaa minkum wajiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1855,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 53,
      "text": "Qaaloo la tawjal innaa nubashshiruka bighulaamin 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1856,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Qaala abashshartumoonee 'alaaa am massaniyal kibaru fabima tubashshiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1857,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 55,
      "text": "Qaaloo bashsharnaaka bilhaqqi falaa takum minal qaaniteen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1858,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 56,
      "text": "Qaala Wa-mai yaqnatu mir rahmati Rabbiheee illad daaaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1859,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 57,
      "text": "Qaala famaa khatbukum aiyuhal mursaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1860,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 58,
      "text": "Qaaloo innaaa ursilnaaa ilaa qawmim mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1861,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 59,
      "text": "Illaaa Aala Loot; innaa lamunajjoohum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1862,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 60,
      "text": "Illam ra-atahoo qaddarnaaa innahaa laminal ghaabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1863,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 61,
      "text": "Falamma jaaa'a Aala Lootinil mursaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1864,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 62,
      "text": "Qaala innakum qawmum munkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1865,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 63,
      "text": "Qaaloo bal ji'naaka bimaa kaanoo feehi yamtaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1866,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 64,
      "text": "Wa-atainaaka bilhaqqi Wa-innaa lasaadiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1867,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Fa-asri bi-ahlika biqit'im minal laili wattabi' adbaarahum Wa-laa yaltafit minkum ahadunw wamdoo haisu tu'maroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1868,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Wa-qadainaaa ilaihi zaalikal amra anna daabira haaa'ulaaa'i maqtoo'um musbiheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1869,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 67,
      "text": "Wa-jaaa'a ahlul madeenati yastabshiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1870,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 68,
      "text": "Qaala inna haaa'ulaaa'i daifee falaa tafdahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1871,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 69,
      "text": "Wattaqul laaha Wa-laa tukhzoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1872,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 70,
      "text": "Qaalooo awalam nanhaka 'anil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1873,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 71,
      "text": "Qaala haaa'ulaaa'i banaateee in kuntum faa'ileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1874,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 72,
      "text": "La'amruka innahum lafee sakratihim ya'mahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1875,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 73,
      "text": "Fa-akhazat-humus saihatu mushriqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1876,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Faja'alnaa 'aaliyahaa saafilahaa Wa-amtamaa 'alaihim hijaaratam min sijjeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 1877,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 75,
      "text": "Inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil lilmutawassimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1878,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 76,
      "text": "Wa-innahaa labi-sabeelim muqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1879,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 77,
      "text": "Inna fee zaalika la-Aayatal lilmu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1880,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 78,
      "text": "Wa-in kaana Ashaabul Aikati lazaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1881,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 79,
      "text": "Fantaqamnaa minhum Wa-innahumaa labi-imaamim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1882,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 80,
      "text": "Wa-laqad kazzaba ashaabul Hijril mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1883,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 81,
      "text": "Wa-aatainaahum Aayaatinaa fakaanoo 'anhaa mu'rideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1884,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 82,
      "text": "Wa-kaanoo yanhitoona minal jibaali buyootan aamineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1885,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 83,
      "text": "Fa-akhazat-humus saihatu musbiheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1886,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 84,
      "text": "Famaaa aghnaa 'anhum maa kaanoo yaksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1887,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa khalaqnas samaawaati wal-arda Wa-maa bainahumaaa illaa bilhaqq; Wa-innas Saa'ata la-aatiyatun fasfahis safhal jameel"
    },
    {
      "index": 1888,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 86,
      "text": "Inna Rabbaka Huwal khallaaqul 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1889,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 87,
      "text": "Wa-laqad aatainaaka sab'am minal masaanee wal-Qur-aanal 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1890,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Laa tamuddanna 'ainaika ilaa maa matta-'naa biheee azwaajam minhum Wa-laa tahzan 'alaihim wakhfid janaahaka lilmu-'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1891,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 89,
      "text": "Wa-qul inneee anan nazeerul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1892,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 90,
      "text": "Kamaaa anzalnaa 'alal muqtasimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1893,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 91,
      "text": "Allazeena ja'alul Quraana 'i-deen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1894,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 92,
      "text": "Fawa-Rabbika lanas'a-lannahum ajma'een"
    },
    {"index": 1895, "sura": 15, "aya": 93, "text": "Ammaa kaanoo ya'maloon"},
    {
      "index": 1896,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 94,
      "text": "Fasda' bimaa tu'maru Wa-a'rid anil mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1897,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 95,
      "text": "Innaa kafainaakal mustahzi'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1898,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yaj'aloona ma'al laahi ilaahan aakhar; fasawfa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1899,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 97,
      "text": "Wa-laqad na'lamu annaka yadeequ sadruka bimaa yaqooloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1900,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 98,
      "text": "Fasbbih bihamdi Rabbika Wa-kum minas saajideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1901,
      "sura": 15,
      "aya": 99,
      "text": "Wa'bud Rabbaka hattaa yaatiyakal yaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1902,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Ataaa amrul laahi falaa tasta'jilooh; Subhaanahoo Wa-Ta'aalaa 'ammaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1903,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Yunazzilul malaaa-'ikata birroohi min amrihee 'alaa mai yashaaa'u min 'ibaadiheee an anzirooo annahoo laaa ilaaha illaaa ana fattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1904,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "Khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda bilhaqq; Ta'aalaa 'ammaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1905,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 4,
      "text": "Khalaqal insaana min nutfatin fa-izaa huwa khaseemum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1906,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Wal-an-'amaa khalaqahaa; lakum feehaa dif'unw Wa-manaafi'u Wa-minhaa taakuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1907,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 6,
      "text": "Wa-lakum feehaa jamaalun heena tureehoona Wa-heena tasrahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1908,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-tahmilu asqaalakum ilaa baladil lam takoonoo baaligheehi illaa bishiqqil anfus; inna Rabbakum la-Ra'oofur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1909,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Walkhaila wal-bighaala wal-hameera litarkaboohaa Wa-zeenah; Wa-yakhluqu maa laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1910,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wa-'alal laahi qasdus sabeeli Wa-minhaa jaaa'ir; Wa-law shaaa'a lahadaakum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 1911,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazeee anzala minas samaaa'i maaa'al lakum minhu sharaabunw Wa-minhu shajarun feehi tuseemoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1912,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Yumbitu lakum bihiz zar'a wazzaitoona wanna-kheela wal-a'naaba Wa-min kullis samaraat, inna fee zaalika la-Aayatal liqawminy yatafakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1913,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-sakkhkhara lakumul laila wannahaara wash-shamsa walqamara wannujoomu musakhkharaatum bi-amrih; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil liqawminy ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1914,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa zara-a lakum fil ardi mukhtalifan alwaanuh; inna fee zaalika la-Aayatal liqawminy yazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1915,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee sakhkharal bahra litaakuloo minhu lahman tariyyanw Wa-tastakhrijoo minhu hilyatan talbasoonahaa Wa-taral fulka mawaakhira feehi Wa-litabtaghoo min fadlihee Wa-la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1916,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wa-alqaa fil ardi rawaasiya an tameeda bikum Wa-anhaaranw Wa-sublulal la-'allakum tahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1917,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 16,
      "text": "Wa-'alaamaat; Wa-bin-najmi hum yahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1918,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 17,
      "text": "Afamany yakhluqu kamal laa yakhluq; afalaa tazak-karoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1919,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-in ta'uddoo ni'matal laahi laa tuhsoohaa; innal laaha la-Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1920,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 19,
      "text": "Wallaahu ya'lamu maa tusirroona Wa-maa tu'linoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1921,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yad'oona min doonil laahi laa yakhluqoona shai'anw Wa-hum yukhlaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1922,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 21,
      "text": "Amwaatun ghairu ahyaaa'inw Wa-maa yash'uroona aiyaana yub'asoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1923,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Illahukum Ilaahunw Waahid; fallazeena laa yu'minoona bil-Aakhirati quloobuhum munkiratunw Wa-hum mustakbiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1924,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Laa jarama annal laaha ya'lamu maa yusirrona Wa-ma yu'linoon; innahoo laa yuhibbul mustakbireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1925,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahum maazaaa anzala Rabbukum qaaloo asaateerul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1926,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Liyahmilooo awzaarahum kaamilatany Yawmal Qiyaamati Wa-min awzaaril lazeena yudilloonahum bighairi 'ilm; alaa saaa'a maa yaziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1927,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Qad makaral lazeena min qablihim fa-atal laahu bunyaa-nahum minal qawaa'idi fakharra 'alaihimus saqfu min fawqihim Wa-ataahumul 'azaabu min haisu laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1928,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Summa Yawmal Qiyaamati yukhzeehim Wa-yaqoolu aina shurakaaa'iyal lazeena kuntum tushaaaqqoona feehim; qaalal lazeena ootul 'ilma innal khizyal Yawma wassooo'a 'alal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1929,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Allazeena tatawaf-faahu-mul malaaa'ikatu zaalimeee anfusihim fa-alqawus salama maa kunnaa na'malu min sooo'; balaaa innal laaha 'aleemum bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1930,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Fadkhulooo abwaaba jahannama khaalideena feeha falabi'sa maswal mutakab-bireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1931,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Wa-qeela lillazeenat taqaw maazaaa anzala Rabbukum; qaaloo khairaa; lillazeena ahsanoo fee haazihid dunyaa hasanah; Wa-la-Daarul Aakhirati khair; Wa-lani'ma daarul muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1932,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Jannaatu 'Adniny yadkhuloonahaa tajree min tahtihal anhaaru lahum feehaa maa yashaaa'oon; kazaalika yajzil laahul muttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1933,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Allazeena tatawaf-faahumul malaaa'ikatu taiyibeena yaqooloona salaamun 'alai-kumud khulul Jannata bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1934,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Hal yanzuroona illaaa an taatiyahumul malaaa'ikatu aw yaatiya amru Rabbik; kazaalika fa'alal lazeena min qablihim; Wa-maa zalamahumul laahu Wa-laakin kaanoo anfusahum yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1935,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Fa-asaabahum saiyi-aatu maa 'amiloo Wa-haaqa bihim maa kaano bihee yastahzi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1936,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena ashrakoo law shaaa'al laahu ma 'abadnaa min doonihee min shai'in nahnu Wa-laaa aabaaa'unaa Wa-laa harramnaa min doonihee min shai'; kazaalika fa'alal lazeena min qablihim fahal 'alar Rusuli illal balaaghul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1937,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad ba'asnaa fee kulli ummatir Rasoolan ani' budul laaha wajtanibut Taaghoota faminhum man hadal laahu Wa-minhum man haqqat 'alaihid dalaalah; faseeroo fil ardi fanzuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul mukazzibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1938,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "In tahris 'alaa hudaahum fa-innal laaha laa yahdee mai yudillu Wa-maa lahum min naasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1939,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wa-aqsamoo billaahi jahda aimaanihim laa yab'asul laahu mai yamoot; balaa wa'dan 'alaihi haqqanw Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1940,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Liyubaiyina lahumul lazee yakhtalifoona feehi Wa-liya'lamal lazeena kafarooo annahum kaanoo kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1941,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Innamaa qawlunaa lishay'in izaa aradnaahu an naqoola lahoo kun fa-yakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1942,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena haajaroo fil laahi mim ba'di maa zulimoo lanubawwi'-annahum fid dunyaa hasanatanw Wa-la-ajrul Aakhirati akbar; law kaanoo ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1943,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 42,
      "text": "Allazeena sabaroo Wa-'alaa Rabbihim yatawak-kaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1944,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaa min qablika illaa rijaalan nooheee ilaihim; fas'alooo ahlaz zikri in kuntum laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1945,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Bilbaiyinaati waz-Zubur; Wa-anzalnaaa ilaikaz Zikra litubaiyina linnaasi maa nuzzila ilaihim Wa-la'allahum yatafakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1946,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Afa-aminal lazeena makarus saiyi-aati ai yakhsifal laahu bihimul arda aw yaaa-tiyahumul 'azaabu min haisu laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1947,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 46,
      "text": "Aw yaakhuzahum fee taqallubihim famaa hum bi-mu'jizeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1948,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Aw yaakhuzahum 'alaa takhawwuf; fa-inna Rabbakum la-Ra'oofur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1949,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Awa-lam yaraw ilaa maa khalaqal laahu min shai'iny yatafaiya'u zilaaluhoo 'anil yameeni washshamaaa'-ili sujjadal lillaahi Wa-hum daakhiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1950,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahi yasjudu maa fis samaawaati Wa-maa fil ardi min daaabbatinw walma-laaa'ikatu Wa-hum laa yastakbiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1951,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 50,
      "text": "yakhaafoona Rabbahum min fawqihim Wa-yaf'aloona maa yu'maroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1952,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal laahu laa tatta-khizooo ilaahainis naini innamaa Huwa Ilaahunw Waahid; fa-iyyaaya farhaboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1953,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-lahoo maa fis samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-lahud deenu waasibaa; afaghairal laahi tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1954,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa bikum min ni'matin faminal laahi summa izaa massakumud durru fa-ilaihi taj'aroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1955,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Summaa izaa kashafad durra 'ankum izaa fareequm minkum bi-Rabbihim yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1956,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 55,
      "text": "Liyakfuroo bimaa aatainaahum; fatamatta'oo, faswfa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1957,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaj'aloona limaa laa ya'lamoona naseebam mimmaa razaqnnaahum; tallaahi latus'alunaa 'ammaa kuntum taftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1958,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaj'aloona lillaahil banaati Subhaanahoo Wa-lahum maa yashtahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1959,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa bushshira ahaduhum bil-unsaa zalla wajhuhoo muswaddanw Wa-huwa kazeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1960,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "yatawaaraa minal qawmi min sooo'i maa bushshira bih; a-yumsikuhoo 'alaa hoonin am yadussuhoo fit turaab; alaa saaa'a maa yahkumoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1961,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Lillazeena laa yu'minoona bil-Aakhirati masalus saw'i Wa-lillaahil masalul a'laa; Wa-Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1962,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-law yu'aakhizul laahun naasa bizulminhim maa taraka 'alaihaa min daaabbatinw Wa-laakiny yu'akhkhiruhum ilaaa ajalim musamman fa-izaa jaaa'a ajaluhum laa yastaakhiroona saa'atanw Wa-laa yastaqdimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1963,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaj'aloona lillaahi maa yakrahoona Wa-tasifu alsinatuhumul kaziba anna lahumul husnaa laa jarama anna lahumun Naara Wa-annahum mufratoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1964,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Tallaahi laqad arsalnaaa ilaaa umamim min qablika fazayyana lahumush Shaitaanu a'maalahum fahuwa waliyyuhumul yawma Wa-lahum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1965,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa anzalnaa 'alaikal Kitaaba illaa litubaiyina lahumul lazikh talafoo feehi Wa-hudanw Wa-rahmatal liqawminy yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1966,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu anzala minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa-ahyaa bihil arda ba'da mawtihaa; inna fee zaalika la-aayatal liqaw-miny yasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1967,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Wa-inna lakum fil an'aami la'ibrah; nusqeekum mimmmaa fee butoonihee mim baini farsinw Wa-damil labanann khaalisan saaa'ighallish shaaribeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1968,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Wa-min samaraatin nakheeli wal-a'nnaabi tattakhizoona minhu sakaranw Wa-rizqann hasanaa; inna fee zaalika la-Aayatal liqawmien ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1969,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Wa-awhaa Rabbuka ilan nahli anit takhizee minal jabaali buyootanw Wa-minash shajari Wa-mimmaa ya'rishoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1970,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Summma kulee min kullis samaraati faslukee subula Rabbiki zululaa; yakhruju mim butoonihaa sharaabum mukh-talifun alwaanuhoo feehi shifaaa'ul linnaas, innna fee zaalika la-Aayatal liqawmien yatafakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1971,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu khalaqakum suma tatawaffaakum; Wa-minkum maien yuradu ilaaa arzalil 'umuri likai laa ya'lama ba'da 'ilmin shai'aa; innal laaha 'Aleemun Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1972,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu faddala ba'dakum 'alaa ba'din fir rizq; famal lazeena fuddiloo biraaaddee rizqihim 'alaa maa malakat aimaanuhum fahum feehi sawaaa'; afabini'matil laahi yajhadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1973,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu ja'ala lakum min anfusikum azwaajanw Wa-ja'ala lakum min azwaajikum baneena Wa-hafadatanw Wa-razaqakum minat taiyyibaat; afabil-baatili yu'minoona Wa-bini'matil laahi hum yakkfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1974,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-ya'budoona min doonil laahi maa laa yamliku lahum rizqam minas samaawaati wal-ardi shai'anw Wa-laa yastatee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1975,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Falaa tadriboo lillaahil amsaal; innal laaha ya'lamu Wa-antum laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1976,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Darabal laahu masalan 'abdam mammlookal laa yaqdiru 'alaa shai'inw Wa-mar razaqnaahu mminnaa rizqan hasanan fahuwa yunfiqu minhu sirranw Wa-jahra; hal yasta-woon; alhamdu lillaah; bal aksaruhum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1977,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Wa-darabal laahu masalar rajulaini ahaduhumaaa abkamu laa yaqdiru 'alaa shai'inw Wa-huwa kallun 'alaa mawlaahu ainamaa yuwajjihhu laa yaati bikhairin hal yastawee huwa Wa-maien yaamuru bil'adli Wa-huwa 'alaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1978,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Wa-lillaahi ghaibus samaawaati wal-ard; Wa-maaa amrus Saa'ati illaa kalamhil basari aw huwa aqrab; innal laaha 'alaaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 1979,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu akhrajakum mim butooni ummahaatikum laa ta'lamoona shai'anw Wa-ja'ala lakumus sam'a wal-absaara wal-af'idata la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1980,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Alam yaraw ilat tairi musakhkharaatin fee jawwis samaaa'i maa yumsikuhunna illal laah; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil liqawminy yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1981,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu ja'ala lakum mim buyootikum sakananw Wa-ja'ala lakum min juloodil an'aami buyootan tastakhif-foonahaa yawma za'nikum Wa-yawma iqaamatikum Wa-min aswaafihaa Wa-awbaarihaa Wa-ash'aarihaaa asaasanw Wa-mataa'an ilaa heen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1982,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu ja'ala lakum mimmaa khalaqa zilaalanw Wa-ja'ala lakum minal jibaali aknaananw Wa-ja'ala lakum saraabeela taqeekumul harra Wa-saraabeela taqeekum baasakum; kazaalika yutimmu ni'matahoo alaikum la'allakum tuslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1983,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 82,
      "text": "Fa-in tawallaw fa-innamaa 'alaikal balaaghul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1984,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Ya'rifoona ni'matal laahi summa yunkiroonahaa Wa-aksaruhumul kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1985,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Wa-yawma nab'asu min kulli ummatin shaheedan summa laa yu'zanu lillazeena kafaroo Wa-laa hum yusta'taboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1986,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa ra al-lazeena zalamul 'azaaba falaa yukhaf-fafu 'anhum Wa-laa hum yunzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1987,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa ra al-lazeena ashrakoo shurakaaa'ahum qaaloo Rabbana haaa'ulaaa'i shurakaaa'unal lazeena kunnaa nad'oo min doonika fa-alqaw ilaihimul qawla innakum lakaaziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1988,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Wa-alqaw ilal laahi yawma'izinis salama Wa-dalla 'anhum maa kaanoo yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1989,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Allazeena kafaroo Wa-saddoo 'an sabeelil laahi zidnaahum 'azaaban fawqal 'azaabi bimaa kaanoo yufsidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1990,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Wa-yawma nab'asu fee kulli ummmatin shaheedan 'alaihim min anfusihim Wa-ji'naa bika shaheedan 'alaa haaa'ulaaa'; Wa-nazzalnaa 'alaikal Kitaaba tibyaanal likulli shai'inw Wa-hudanw Wa-rahmatanw Wa-bushraa lilmuslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 1991,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha ya'muru bil-'adli wal-ihsaani Wa-eetaaa'i zil qurbaa Wa-yanhaa 'anil fahshaaa'i wal-munkari walbagh-i' ya'izukum la'allakum tazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1992,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Wa-awfoo bi-Ahdil laahi izaa 'aahattum Wa-laa tanqudul aimaana ba'da tawkeedihaa Wa-qad ja'altumul laaha 'alaikum kafeelaa; innal laaha ya'lamu maa taf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1993,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa takoonoo kallatee naqadat ghazlahaa mim ba'di quwwatin ankaasaa; tattakhizoona aimaanakum dakhlalam bainakum an takoona ummatun hiya arbaa min ummah; innnamaa yablookumul laahu bih; Wa-la-yubaiyyinanna lakum yawmal Qiyaamati maa kuntum feehi takhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1994,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Wa-law shaaa'al laahu laja'alakum ummmatanw waahidatanw Wa-laakien yudillu maien yashaaa'u Wa-yahdee maien yashaaa'; Wa-latus'alunna 'ammaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1995,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tattakhizooo aimaanakum dakhalam bainakum fatazilla qadamum ba'da subootihaa Wa-tazooqus sooo'a bimmaa sadattum 'an sabeelil laahi Wa-lakum 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 1996,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tashtaroo bi-'ahdil laahi samanan qaleelaa; innamaa 'indal laahi huwa khairul lakum in kuntum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1997,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "maa 'indakum yanfadu Wa-maa 'indal laahi baaq; Wa-lanajziyannal lazeena sabarooo ajjrahum bi-ahsani maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1998,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Man 'amila saaliham min zakarin aw unsaa Wa-huwa mu'minun falanuhyiyannahoo hayaatan taiiyibatanw Wa-lanajzi-yannnahum ajrahum bi-ahsani maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 1999,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Fa-izaa qara-tal Quraana fasta'iz billaahi minashh Shai-taanir rajeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2000,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Innahoo laisa lahoo sultaanun 'alal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'alaa Rabbihim yatawakkaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2001,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Innnamaa sultaanuhoo 'alal lazeena yatawallawnahoo wallazeena hum bihee mushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2002,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa baddalnaaa Aayatam makaana Aayatinw wal-laahu a'lamu bimaa yunazzilu qaalooo innamaa anta muftar; bal aksaruhum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2003,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Qul nazzalahoo Roohul Qudusi mir Rabbika bilhaqqi liyusabbital lazeena aamanoo Wa-hudanw Wa-bushraa lilmuslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2004,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad na'lamu annahum yaqooloona innamaa yu'allimuhoo bashar; lisaanul lazee yulhidoona ilaihi a'ja-miyyunw Wa-haaza lisaanun 'Arabiyyum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2005,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena laa yu'minoona bi-Aayaatil laahi laa yahdehimul laahu Wa-lahum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2006,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Innamaa yaftaril kazibal lazeena laa yu'minoona bi-Aayaatil laahi Wa-ulaaa'ika humul kaaziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2007,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Man kafara billaahi mim ba'di eemaanihee illaa man ukriha Wa-qalbuhoo mutmma'innum bil-eemaani Wa-laakim man sharaha bilkufri sadran fa'alaihim ghadabum minal laahi Wa-lahum 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2008,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bi-annahumus tahabbul hayaatad dunyaa 'alal Aakhirati Wa-annal laaha laa yahdil qawmal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2009,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena taba'al laahu 'alaa quloobihim Wa-sam'ihim Wa-absaarihim Wa-ulaaa'ika humul ghaafiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2010,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 109,
      "text": "Laa jarama annnahum fil Aakhirati humul khassiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2011,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Summa inna Rabbaka lillazeena haajaroo mim ba'dimaa futinoo summma jaahadoo Wa-sabaroo inna Rabbaka mim ba'dihaa la Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2012,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Yawma taatee kullu nafsin tujaadilu 'an nafsihaa Wa-tuwaffaa kullu nafsim maa 'amilat Wa-hum laa yuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2013,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "Wa-darabal laahu masalan qaryatan kaanat aaminatam mutma'innataien yaaateehaa rizquhaa raghadam min kulli makaanin fakafarat bi-an'umil laahi fa-azaaqahal laahu libaasal joo'i walkhawfi bimaa kaanoo yasna'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2014,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad jaaa'ahum Rasoolum minhum fakazzaboohu fa-akhazahumul 'azaabu Wa-hum zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2015,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 114,
      "text":
          "Fakuloo mimmaa razaqa-kumul laahu halaalan taiyyibanw washkuroo ni'matal laahi in kuntum iyyaahu ta'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2016,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Innamaa harama 'alai-kumul maitata waddama Wa-lahmal khinzeeri Wa-maaa uhilla lighairil laahi bihee famanid turra ghaira baaghinw Wa-laa 'aadin fa-innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2017,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taqooloo limaa tasifu alsinatukumul kaziba haaza halaalunw Wa-haazaa haraamul litaftaroo 'alal laahil kazib; innal lazeena yaftaroona 'alal laahil kaziba laa yuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2018,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 117,
      "text": "Mata'un qaleelunw Wa-lahum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2019,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 118,
      "text":
          "Wa-'alal lazeena haadoo harramnaa ma qasasnaa 'alaika min qablu Wa-maa zalamanaahum Wa-laakin kaanoo anfusahum yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2020,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 119,
      "text":
          "Summma inna Rabbaka lillazeena 'amilus sooo'a bijahaalatin summa taaboo mim ba'di zaaalika Wa-aslahoo inna Rabbaka mim ba'dihaa la-Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2021,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 120,
      "text":
          "Inna Ibraaheema kaana ummatan qaanital lillaahi Haneefanw Wa-lam yaku minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2022,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 121,
      "text":
          "Shaakiral li-an'umih; ijtabaahu Wa-hadaahu ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2023,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 122,
      "text":
          "Wa-aatainaahu fid dunyaa hasanah; Wa-innahoo fil Aakhirati laminas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2024,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 123,
      "text":
          "Summma awhainaa ilaika anit tabi' Millata Ibraaheema haneefaa; Wa-maa kaana minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2025,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 124,
      "text":
          "Innnamaa ju'ilas Sabtu 'alal lazeenakhtalafoo feeh; Wa-inna Rabbaka la yahkumu bainahum Yawmal Qiyaamati feemaa kaanoo feehi yakhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2026,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 125,
      "text":
          "Ud'u ilaa sabeeli Rabbika bilhikmati walmaw-'izatil hasanati Wa-jaadilhum billatee hiya ahsan; inna Rabbaka huwa a'almu biman dalla 'an sabeelihee Wa-Huwa a'lamu bilmuhtadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2027,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 126,
      "text":
          "Wa-in 'aaqabtum fa'aaqiboo bimisli maa 'ooqibtum bihee Wa-la'in sabartum lahuwa khairul lissaabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2028,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 127,
      "text":
          "Wasbir Wa-maa sabruka illaa billaah; Wa-laa tahzan 'alaihim Wa-laa taku fee daiqim mimmaa yamkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2029,
      "sura": 16,
      "aya": 128,
      "text": "Innal laaha ma'al lazeenat taqaw wal-lazeena hum muhsinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2030,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Subhaanal lazeee asraa bi'abdihee lailam minal Masjidil Haraami ilal Masjidil Aqsal lazee baaraknaa haw-lahoo linuriyahoo min aayaatinaa; innahoo Huwas Samee'ul Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2031,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Wa-aatainaa Moosal Kitaaba Wa-ja'alnaahu hudal liBaneee Israaa'eel; allaa tat-takhizoo min doonee wakeelaa."
    },
    {
      "index": 2032,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "Zurriyyata man hamalnaa ma'a Nooh innahoo kaana 'abdan shakooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2033,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Wa qadainaaa ilaa Baneee Israaa'eela fil Kitaabi latufsidunna fil ardi marratain; Wa-lata'lunna'uluwwan kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2034,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Fa-izaa jaaa'a wa'du oolaahumaa ba'asnaaa 'alykum 'ibaadal lanaaa ulee baasin shadeedin fajaasoo khilaalad diyaar; Wa-kaana wa'dam maf'oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2035,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Summa radadnaa lakumul karrata 'alaihim Wa-amdad-naakum-bi amwaalinuw Wa-baneen; Wa-ja'alnaakum aksara nafeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2036,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "In ahsantum ahsantum li-anfusikum Wa-in asaatum falahaa; fa-izaa jaaa'a wa'dul aakhirati liyasooo'oo wujoo-hakum Wa-liyadkhulul masjida kamaa dakhaloohu awwala marratinw Wa-liyutabbiroo maa a'law tatbeera"
    },
    {
      "index": 2037,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Asaa rabbukum aien yarhamakum; Wa-in 'uttum 'udnaa; Wa-ja'alnaa jahannama lilkaafireena haseera"
    },
    {
      "index": 2038,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Inna haazal Quraana yahdee lillatee hiya aqwamu Wa-yubashshirul mu'mineenal lazeena ya'maloonas saalihaati anna lahum ajran kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2039,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-annal lazeena laa yu'minoona bil-aakhirati a'tadnaa lahum 'azaaban aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2040,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Wa-yad'ul insaanu bishsharri du'aaa-'ahoo bilkhayr; Wa-kaanal insaanu 'ajoola"
    },
    {
      "index": 2041,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnal laila wannahaara Aayatayni famahawnaaa Aayatal laili Wa-ja'alnaaa Aayatan nahaari mubsiratal litabtaghoo fadlam mir Rabbikum Wa-lita'lamoo 'adadas sineena walhisaab; Wa-kulla shai'in fassalnaahu tafseelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2042,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-kulla insaanin alzamnaahu taaa'irahoo fee 'unuqihee Wa-nukhriji lahoo Yawmal Qiyaamati kitaabany yalqaahu manshooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2043,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 14,
      "text": "Iqra kitaabaka kafaa bi-nafsikal Yawma 'alaika haseebaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2044,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Manih tadaa fa-innamaa yahtadee linafsihee Wa-man dalla fa-innamaa yadillu 'alaihaa; Wa-laa taziru waaziratunw wizra ukhraa; Wa-maa kunnaa mu'azzibeena hatta nab'asa Rasoola"
    },
    {
      "index": 2045,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaaa aradnaaa an nuhlika qaryatan amarnaa mutrafeehaa fafasaqoo feehaa fahaqqa 'alaihal qawlu fadammarnaahaa tadmeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2046,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Wa-kam ahlaknaa minal qurooni min ba'di Nooh; Wa-kafaa bi-Rabbika bizunoobi 'ibaadihee Khabeeram Baseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2047,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Man kaana yureedul 'aajilata 'ajjalnaa lahoo feehaa maa nashaaa'u liman nureedu summa ja'alnaa lahoo Jahannama yaslaahaa mazmoomammad hooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2048,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Wa-man araadal Aakhirata Wa-sa'aa lahaa sa'yahaa Wa-huwa mu'minun fa-ulaaa'ika kaana sa'yuhum mashkooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2049,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Kullan numiddu haaa-'ulaaa'i Wa-haaa'ulaaa'i min 'ataaa'i rabbik; Wa-maa kaana 'ataaa'u rabbika mahzooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2050,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Unzur kaifa faddalnaa ba'dahum 'alaa ba'd; Wa-lal-Aakhiratu akbaru darajaatinw Wa-akbaru tafdeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2051,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Laa taj'al ma'al laahi ilaahan aakhara fataq'uda mazoomam makhzoolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2052,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa qadaa Rabbuka allaa ta'budooo illaaa iyyaahu Wa-bilwaalidaini ihsaanaa; immaa yablughanna 'indakal kibara ahaduhumaaa aw kilaahumaa falaa taqul lahumaaa uffinw Wa-laa tanharhumaa Wa-qullahumaa qawlan kareemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2053,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Wakhfid lahumaa janaahaz zulli minar rahmati Wa-qur Rabbir hamhumaa kamaa rabbayaanee sagheera"
    },
    {
      "index": 2054,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Rabbukum a'lamu bimaa fee nufoosikum; in takoonoo saaliheena fa-innahoo kaana lil-awwaabeena Ghafoooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2055,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Wa-aati zal qurbaa haqqahoo walmiskeena wabnas sabeeli Wa-laa tubazzir tabzeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2056,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Innal mubazzireena kaanoo ikhwaanash shayaateeni Wa-kaanash shaytaanu li-Rabbihee kafooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2057,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wa-immaa tu'ridanna 'anhum ubtighaaa'a rahmatim mir rabbika tarjoohaa faqul lahum qawlam maisooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2058,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taj'al yadaka maghloolatan ilaa 'unuqika Wa-laa tabsut-haa kullal basti fataq'uda maloomam mahsooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2059,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Inna Rabbaka yabsutur rizqa limaien yashaaa'u Wa-yaqdir; innahoo kaana bi'ibaadihee Khabeeran Baseera"
    },
    {
      "index": 2060,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taqtulooo awlaadakum khashyata imlaaqin nahnu narzuquhum Wa-iyyaakum; inna qatlahum kaana khit-'an kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2061,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taqrabuz zinaaa innahoo kaana faahishatanw Wa-saaa'a sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2062,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taqtulun nafsal latee harramal laahu illaa bilhaqq; Wa-man qutila mazlooman faqad ja'alnaa liwaliyyihee sultaanan falaa yusrif fil qatli innahoo kaana mansooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2063,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taqraboo maalal yateemi illaa billatee hiya ahsanu hattaa yablugha ashuddah; Wa-awfoo bil'ahd, innal 'ahda kaana mas'oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2064,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-awful kaila izaa kiltum Wa-zinoo bilqistaasil mustaqeem; zaalika khairunw Wa-ahsanu ta'weelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2065,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taqfu maa laisa laka bihee 'ilm; innas sam'a walbasara walfu'aada kullu ulaaa'ika kaana 'anhu mas'oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2066,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tamshi fil ardi marahan innaka lan takhriqal arda Wa-lan tablughal jibaala toola"
    },
    {
      "index": 2067,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 38,
      "text": "Kullu zaalika kaana sayyi'uhoo inda Rabbika makroohaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2068,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Zaalika mimmaaa awhaaa ilaika Rabbuka minal hikmah; Wa-laa taj'al ma'al laahi ilaahan aakhara fatulqaa fee Jahannama maloomammad hooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2069,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Afa-asfaakum rabbukum bilbaneena wattakhaza minal malaaa'ikati inaasaa; innakum lataqooloona qawlan 'azeema"
    },
    {
      "index": 2070,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad sarrafnaa fee haazal Quraani liyazzakkaroo Wa-maa yazeeduhum illaa nufooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2071,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Qul law kaana ma'ahooo aalihatun kamaa yaqooloona izal labtaghaw ilaa zil 'Arshi Sabeela"
    },
    {
      "index": 2072,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 43,
      "text": "Subhaanahoo Wa-Ta'aalaa 'ammaa yaqooloona 'uluwwan kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2073,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Tusabbihu lahus samaawaatus sab'u wal-ardu Wa-man feehinn; Wa-im min shai'in illaa yusabbihu bihamdihee Wa-laakil laa tafqahoona tasbeehahum; innahoo kaana Haleeman Ghafooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2074,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qara'-tal Quraana ja'alnaa bainaka Wa-bainal lazeena laa yu'minoona bil-aakhirati hijaabam mastooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2075,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnaa 'alaa quloo-bihim akinnatan any yafqahoohu Wa-feee aazaanihim waqraa; Wa-izaa zakarta Rabbaka fil Quraani wahdahoo wallaw 'alaaa adbaarihim nufooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2076,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Nahnu a'lamu bimaa yastami'oona biheee iz yastami'oona ilaika Wa-iz hum najwaaa iz yaqooluz zaalimoona in tattabi'oona illaa rajulam mas-hooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2077,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Unzur kaifa daraboo lakal amsaala fadalloo falaa yastatee'oona sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2078,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalooo 'a-izaa kunnaa 'izaamanw Wa-rufaatan 'a-innaa lamab'oosoona khalqan jadeedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2079,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 50,
      "text": "Qul koonoo hijaaratan aw hadeedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2080,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Aw khalqam mimmaa yakburu fee sudoorikum; fasa-yaqooloona maien yu'eedunaa qulil lazee fatarakum awwala marrah; fasa yunghidoona ilaika ru'oosahum Wa-yaqooloona mataahoo; qul 'asaaa any yakoona qareeba"
    },
    {
      "index": 2081,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Yawma yad'ookum fatastajeeboona bihamdihee Wa-tazunnoona il labistum illaa qaleela"
    },
    {
      "index": 2082,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-qul li'ibaadee yaqoolul latee hiya ahsan; innash shaitaana yanzaghu bainahum; innash shaitaana kaana lil-insaani 'aduwwam mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2083,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Rabbukum a'lamu bikum iny yasha' yarhamkum aw iny yasha' yu'azzibkum; Wa-maaa arsalnaaka 'alaihim wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2084,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Wa-Rabbuka a'lamu biman fis samaawaati wal-ard; Wa-laqad faddalnaa ba'dan Nabiyyeena 'alaa ba'dinw Wa-aatainaaa Daawooda Zabooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2085,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Qulid 'ul lazeena za'amtum min doonihee falaa yamlikoona kashfad durri 'ankum Wa-laa tahweelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2086,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena yad'oona yabtaghoona ilaa Rabbihimul waseelata ayyuhum aqrabu Wa-yarjoona rahmatahoo Wa-yakhaafoona 'azaabah; inna 'azaaba rabbika kaana mahzooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2087,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-in min qaryatin illaa Nahnu muhlikoohaa qabla Yawmil Qiyaamati aw mu'az-ziboohaa 'azaaban shadeedaa; kaana zaalika fil Kitaabi mastooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2088,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa mana'anaaa an nursila bil-aayaati illaaa an kazzaba bihal awwaloon; Wa-aatainaa Samoodan naaqata mubsiratan fazalamoo bihaa; Wa-maa nursilu bil-aayaati illaa takhweefaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2089,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qulnaa laka inna rabbaka ahaata binnaas; Wa-maa ja'alnar ru'yal lateee arainaaka illaa fitnatal linnaasi washshajaratal mal'oonata fil quraan; Wa-nukhaw-wifuhum famaa yazeeduhum illa tughyaanan kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2090,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qulnaa lilma-laaa'ikatis judoo li-Aadama fasajadooo illaaa Ibleesa qaala 'a-asjudu liman khalaqta teena"
    },
    {
      "index": 2091,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Qaala ara'aytaka haazal lazee karramta 'alaiya la'in akhartani ilaa Yawmil Qiyaamati la-ahtanikanna zurriyyatahooo illaa qaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2092,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Qaalaz hab faman tabi'aka minhum fa-inna Jahannama jazaaa'ukum jazaaa'am mawfooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2093,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Wastafziz manis tata'ta minhum bisawtika Wa-ajlib 'alaihim bikhailika Wa-rajilika Wa-shaarik-hum fil amwaali wal-awlaadi Wa-'idhum; Wa-maa ya'iduhumush Shaitaanu illaa ghurooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2094,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Inna 'ibaadee laisa laka 'alaihim sultaan; Wa-kafaa bi-Rabbika Wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2095,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Rabbukumul lazee yuzjee lakumul fulka fil bahri litabtaghoo min fadlih; innahoo kaana bikum Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2096,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa massakumud durru fil bahri dalla man tad'oona illaaa iyyaahu falammaa najjaakum ilal barri a'radtum; Wa-kaanal insaanu kafooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2097,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Afa-amintum aien yakhsifa bikum jaanibal barri aw yursila 'alaikum haasiban summa laa tajidoo lakum wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2098,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Am amintum aien yu'eedakum feehi taaratan ukhraa fa-yursila 'alaikum qaasifam minar reehi fa-yugh-riqakum bimaa kafartum summa laa tajidoo lakum 'alainaa bihee tabee'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2099,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad karramnaa Baneee aadama Wa-hamalnaahum fil barri walbahri Wa-razaqnaahum minat taiyibaati Wa-faddalnaahum 'alaa kaseerim mimman khalaqnaa tafdeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2100,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Yawma nad'oo kulla unaasim bi-imaamihim faman ootiya kitaabahoo bi-yameenihee fa-ulaaa'ika yaqra'oona kitaabahum Wa-laa yuzlamoona fateelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2101,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Wa-man kaana fee haaziheee a'maa fahuwa fil aakhirati a'maa Wa-adallu sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2102,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-in kaadoo la-yaftinoonaka 'anil lazeee awhainaaa ilaika litaftariya 'alainaaa ghairahoo Wa-izallat takhazooka khaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2103,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wa-law-laaa an sabbatnaaka laqad kitta tarkanu ilaihim shai'an qaleela"
    },
    {
      "index": 2104,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Izal la-azaqnaaka di'fal hayaati Wa-di'fal mamaati summa laa tajidu laka 'alainaa naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2105,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Wa-in kaadoo la-yastafizzoonaka minal ardi liyukhri-jooka minhaa Wa-izal laa yalbasoona khilaafaka illaa qaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2106,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Sunnata man qad arsalnaa qablaka mir Rusulinaa Wa-laa tajidu lisunnatinaa tahweelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2107,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Aqimis Salaata liduloo-kish shamsi ilaa ghasaqil laili Wa-quraanal Fajri inna quraa-nal Fajri kaana mashhoodaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2108,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Wa-minal laili fatahajjad bihee naafilatal laka 'asaaa any yab'asaka Rabbuka Maqaamam Mahmoodaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2109,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wa-qur Rabbi adkhilnee mudkhala sidqinw Wa-akhrijnee mukhraja sidqinw waj'al lee mil ladunka sultaanan naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2110,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Wa-qul jaaa'al haqqu Wa-zahaqal baatil; innal baatila kaana zahooqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2111,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Wa-nunazzilu minal quraani maa huwa shifaaa'unw Wa-rahmatullil mu'mineena Wa-laa yazeeduz zaalimeena illaa khasaaraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2112,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaaa an'amnaa 'alal insaani a'rada Wa-na-aa bijaani-bihee Wa-izaa massahush sharru kaana ya'oosaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2113,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Qul kulluny ya'malu 'alaa shaakilatihee fa-rabbukum a'lamu biman huwa ahdaa sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2114,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Wa-yas'aloonaka 'anir rooh; qulir roohu min amri rabbee Wa-maaa ooteetum minal 'ilmi illaa qaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2115,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Wa-la'in shi'naa lanaz-habanna billazeee awhainaaa ilaika summa laa tajidu laka bihee 'alainaa wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2116,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 87,
      "text": "Illaa rahmatam mir Rabbik; inna fadlahoo kaana 'alaika kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2117,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Qul la'inij tama'atil insu waljinnu 'alaaa aien ya'too bimisli haazal quraani laa ya'toona bimislihee Wa-law kaana ba'duhum liba-'din zaheeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2118,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad sarrafnaa linnaasi fee haazal quraani min kulli masalin fa-abaaa aksarun naasi illaa kufooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2119,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo lan nu'mina laka hattaa tafjura lanaa minal ardi yamboo'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2120,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Aw takoona laka jannatum min nakheelinw Wa-'inabin fatufajjiral anhaara khilaalahaa tafjeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2121,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Aw tusqitas samaaa'a kamaa za'amta 'alainaa kisafan aw ta'tiya billaahi wal-malaaa'ikati qabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2122,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Aw yakoona laka baitum min zukhrufin aw tarqaa fis samaaa'i Wa-lan nu'mina liruqiyyika hatta tunazzila 'alainaa kitaaban naqra'uh; qul Subhaana Rabbee hal kuntu illaa basharar Rasoolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2123,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa mana'an naasa any yu'minooo iz jaaa'ahumul hudaaa illaaa an qaalooo aba'asal laahu basharar Rasoolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2124,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Qul law kaana fil ardi malaaa-'ikatuien yamshoona mutma'in-neena lanazzalnaa 'alaihim minas samaaa'i malakar Rasoolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2125,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Qul kafaa billaahi shaheedam bainee Wa-bainakum; innahoo kaana bi'ibaadihee Khabeeram Baseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2126,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yahdil laahu fahuwal muhtad; Wa-mai yudlil falan tajida lahum awliyaaa'a min doonih; Wa-nahshuruhum Yawmal Qiyaamati 'alaa wujoohihim umyanw Wa-bukmanw Wa-summaa; ma'waahum Jahannamu kullamaa khabat zidnaahum sa'eeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2127,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Zaalika jazaa'uhum bi-annahum kafaroo bi-aayaatinaa Wa-qaalooo 'a-izaa kunnaa 'izaamanw Wa-rufaatan 'a-innaa la-mab'oosoona khalqan jadeedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2128,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaraw annal laahal lazee khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda qaadirun 'alaaa aien yakhluqa mislahum Wa-ja'ala lahum ajalal laa raiba fee; fa-abaz zaalimoona illaa kufooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2129,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "Qul law antum tamlikoona khazaaa'ina rahmati Rabbeee izal la-amsaktum khash-yatal infaaq; Wa-kaanal insaanu qatooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2130,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Moosaa tis'a Aayaatim baiyyinaatin fas'al Baneee Israaa'eela iz jaaa'ahum faqaala lahoo Fir'awnu inee la-azunnuka yaa-Moosaa mas-hooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2131,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Qaala laqad 'alimta maaa anzala haaa'ulaaa'i illaa Rabbus samaawaati wal-ardi basaaa'ira Wa-innee la-azun-nuka yaa-Fir'awnu masbooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2132,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Fa-araada aien yastafizzahum minal ardi fa-aghraqnaahu Wa-mam ma'ahoo jamee'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2133,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Wa-qulnaa min ba'dihee li-Baneee Israaa'eelas kunul arda fa-izaa jaaa'a wa'dul aakhirati ji'naa bikum lafeefaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2134,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Wa-bilhaqqi anzalnaahu Wa-bilhaqqi nazal; Wa-maaa arsalnaaka illaa mubash-shiranw Wa-nazeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2135,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Wa-quraanan faraqnaahu litaqra-ahoo 'alan naasi 'alaa muksinw Wa-nazzalnaahu tanzeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2136,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Qul aaminoo biheee aw laa tu'minoo; innal lazeena ootul 'ilma min qabliheee izaa yutlaa 'alaihim yakhirroona lil-azqaani sujjadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2137,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaqooloona Subhaana Rabbinaaa in kaana wa'du Rabbinaa lamaf'oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2138,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 109,
      "text": "Wa-yakhirroona lil-azqaani yabkoona Wa-yazeeduhum khushoo'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2139,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Qulid 'ul laaha awid 'ur Rahmaana ayyam maa tad'oo falahul asmaaa'ul Husnaa; Wa-laa tajhar bi-Salaatika Wa-laa tukhaafit bihaa wabtaghi baina zaalika sabeela"
    },
    {
      "index": 2140,
      "sura": 17,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Wa-qulil hamdu lillaahil lazee lam yattakhiz waladanw Wa-lam yakul lahoo shareekun fil mulki Wa-lam yakul lahoo waliyyum minaz zulli Wa-kabbirhu takbeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2141,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Alhamdu lillaahil lazeee anzala 'alaa 'abdihil kitaaba Wa-lam yaj'al lahoo 'iwajaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2142,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Qaiyimal liyunzira ba'asan shadeedam mil ladunhu Wa-yubashshiral mu'mineenal lazeena ya'maloonas saalihaati anna lahum ajran hasanaa"
    },
    {"index": 2143, "sura": 18, "aya": 3, "text": "Maakiseena feehi abadaa"},
    {
      "index": 2144,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 4,
      "text": "Wa-yunziral lazeena qaalut takhazal laahu waladaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2145,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Maa lahum bihee min 'ilminw Wa-laa li-aabaaa'ihim; kaburat kalimatan takhruju min afwaahihim; iny yaqooloona illaa kazibaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2146,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Fala'allaka baakhi'un nafsaka 'alaaa aasaarihim il lam yu'minoo bihaazal hadeesi asafaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2147,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Innaa ja'alnaa ma 'alal ardi zeenatal lahaa linabluwahum ayyuhum ahsanu 'amalaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2148,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 8,
      "text": "Wa-innaa la-jaa'iloona maa 'alaihaa sa'eedan juruzaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2149,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Am hasibta anna Ashaabal Kahfi war-Raqeemi kaanoo min Aayaatinaa 'ajabaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2150,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Iz awal fityatu ilal Kahfi faqaaloo Rabbanaaa aatinaa mil ladunka rahmatanw Wa-haiyi' lanaa min amrinaa rashadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2151,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 11,
      "text": "Fadarabnaa 'alaaa aazaanihim fil Kahfi seneena 'adadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2152,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Summa ba'asnaahum lina'lama ayyul hizbaini ahsaa limaa labisooo amadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2153,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Nahnu naqussu 'alaika naba-ahum bilhaqq; innahum fityatun aamanoo bi-Rabbihim Wa-zidnaahum hudaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2154,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-rabatnaa 'alaa quloo-bihim iz qaamoo faqaaloo Rabbunaa Rabbus samaawaati wal-ardi lan nad'uwa min dooniheee ilaahal laqad qulnaaa izan shatataa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2155,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Haaa'ulaaa'i qawmunat takhazoo min dooniheee aalihatal law laa yaatoona 'alaihim bisultaanim baiyin; faman azlamu mimmaniftaraa 'alal laahi kazibaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2156,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wa-izi'tazal tumoohum Wa-maa ya'budoona illal laaha faawooo ilal kahfi yanshur lakum Rabbukum mir rahmatihee Wa-yuhaiyi' lakum min amrikum mirfaqa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2157,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Wa-tarash shamsa izaa tala'at tazaawaru 'an kahfihim zaatal yameeni Wa-izaa gharabat taqriduhum zaatash shimaali Wa-hum fee fajwatim minh; zaalika min Aayaatil laah; maien yahdil laahu fahuwal muhtad, Wa-maien yudlil falan tajida lahoo waliyyam murshidaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2158,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-tahsabuhum ayqaazanw Wa-hum ruqood; Wa-nuqallibuhum zaatal yameeni Wa-zaatash shimaali Wa-kalbuhum baasitun ziraa'ayhi bilwaseed; lawit tala'ta 'alaihim la-wallaita minhum firaaranw Wa-lamuli'ta minhum rubaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2159,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika ba'asnaahum liyatasaaa'aloo bainahum; qaala qaaa'ilum minhum kam labistum qaaloo labisnaa yawman aw ba'da yawm; qaaloo Rabbukum a'lamu bimaa labistum fab'asooo ahadakum biwariqikum haazihee ilal madeenati falyanzur ayyuhaaa azkaa ta'aaman falyaatikum birizqim minhu walyatalattaf Wa-laa yush'iranna bikum ahadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2160,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Innahum ien yazharoo 'alaikum yarjumookum aw yu'eedookum fee millatihim Wa-lan tuflihooo izan abadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2161,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika a'sarnaa 'alaihim liya'lamooo anna wa'dal laahi haqqunw Wa-annas Saa'ata laa raiba feehaa iz yatanaaza'oona bainahum amrahum faqaalub noo 'alaihim bunyaanaa; Rabbuhum a'lamu bihim; qaalal lazeena ghalaboo 'alaaa amrihim lanat-takhizanna 'alaihim masjidaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2162,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Sa-yaqooloona salaasatur raabi'uhum kalbuhum Wa-yaqooloona khamsatun saadisuhum kalbuhum rajmam bilghaib; Wa-yaqooloona sab'atunw Wa-saaminuhum kalbuhum; qur Rabbeee a'lamu bi'iddatihim maa ya'lamuhum illaa qaleel; falaa tumaari feehim illaa miraaa'an zaahiranw Wa-laa tastafti feehim minhum ahadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2163,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 23,
      "text": "Wa-laa taqoolanna lishai'in innee faa'ilun zaalika ghadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2164,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Illaaa aien yashaaa'al laah; wazkur Rabbaka izaa naseeta Wa-qul 'asaaa any yahdiyani Rabbee li-aqraba min haazaa rashadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2165,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 25,
      "text": "Wa-labisoo fee kahfihim salaasa mi'atin sineena wazdaadoo tis'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2166,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Qulil laahu a'lamu bimaa labisoo lahoo ghaibus samaawaati wal-ardi absir bihee Wa-asmi'; maa lahum min doonihee minw waliyyinw Wa-laa yushriku fee hukmihee ahadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2167,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Watlu maaa oohiya ilaika min Kitaabi Rabbika laa mubaddila li-Kalimaatihee Wa-lan tajida min doonihee multahadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2168,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wasbir nafsaka ma'al lazeena yad'oona Rabbahum bilghadaati wal'ashiyyi yureedoona Wajhahoo Wa-laa ta'du 'aynaaka 'anhum tureedu zeenatal hayaatid dunyaa Wa-laa tuti' man aghfalnaa qalbahoo 'an zikrinaa wattaba'a hawaahu Wa-kaana amruhoo furutaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2169,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Wa-qulil haqqu mir Rabbikum faman shaaa'a falyu'minw Wa-man shaaa'a falyakfur; innaaa a'tadnaa lizzaalimeena Naaran ahaata bihim suraadiquhaa; Wa-ien yastagheesoo yughaasoo bimaaa'in kalmuhli yashwil wujooh' bi'sash sharaab; Wa-saaa'at murtafaqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2170,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati innaa laa nudee'u ajra man ahsana 'amalaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2171,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika lahum Jannaatu 'Adnin tajree min tahtihimul anhaaru yuhallawna feehaa min asaawira min zahabinw Wa-yalbasoona siyaaban khudram min sundusinw Wa-istabraqim muttaki'eena feehaa 'alal araaa'ik; ni'mas sawaab; Wa-hasunat murtafaqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2172,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wadrib lahum masalar rajulaini ja'alnaa li-ahadihimaa jannataini min a'naabinw Wa-hafafnaahumaa binakhilinw Wa-ja'alnaa bainahumaa zar'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2173,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Kiltal jannataini aatat ukulahaa Wa-lam tazlim minhu shai'anw Wa-fajjarnaa khi-laalahumaa naharaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2174,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-kaana lahoo samarun faqaala lisaahibihee Wa-huwa yuhaawiruhoo ana aksaru minka maalanw Wa-a'azzu nafaraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2175,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-dakhala jannatahoo Wa-huwa zaalimul linafsihee qaala maaa azunnu an tabeeda haaziheee abadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2176,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa azunnus Saa'ata qaaa'imatanw Wa-la'ir rudittu ilaa Rabbee la-ajidanna khairam minhaa munqalabaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2177,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Qaala lahoo saahibuhoo Wa-huwa yuhaawiruhooo akafarta billazee khalaqaka min turaabin summa min nutfatin summa sawwaaka rajulaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2178,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 38,
      "text": "Laakinaa Huwal laahu Rabbee Wa-laa ushriku bi-Rabbeee ahadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2179,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wa-law-laaa iz dakhalta jannataka qulta maa shaaa'al laahu laa quwwata illaa billaah; in tarani ana aqalla minka maalanw Wa-waladaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2180,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Fa'asaa Rabeee aien yu'tiyani khairam min jannatika Wa-yursila 'alaihaa husbaanam minas samaaa'i fatusbiha sa'eedan zalaqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2181,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 41,
      "text": "Aw yusbiha maaa'uhaaa ghawran falan tastatee'a lahoo talabaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2182,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-uheeta bisamarihee faasbaha yuqallibu kaffaihi 'alaa maaa anfaqa feehaa Wa-hiya khaawiyatun 'alaa 'urooshihaa Wa-yaqoolu yaalaitanee lam ushrik bi-Rabbeee ahadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2183,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-lam takul lahoo fi'atuien yansuroonahoo min doonil laahi Wa-maa kaana muntasiraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2184,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Hunaalikal walaayatu lillaahil haqq; huwa khairun sawaabanw Wa-khairun 'uqbaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2185,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wadrib lahum masalal hayaatid dunyaa kamaaa'in anzalnaahu minas samaaa'i fakhtalata bihee nabaatul ardi fa-asbaha hasheeman tazroo-hur riyaah; Wa-kaanal laahu 'alaa kulli shai'im muqtadiraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2186,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Almaalu walbanoona zeenatul hayaatid dunya wal-baaqiyaatus saalihaatu khairun 'inda Rabbika sawaabanw Wa-khairun amalaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2187,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-yawma nusaiyirul jibaala Wa-taral arda baariza-tanw Wa-hasharnaahum falam nughaadir minhum ahadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2188,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa 'uridoo 'alaa Rabbika saffaa, laqad ji'tumoonaa kamaa khalaqnaakum awala marrah; bal za'amtum allannaj'ala lakum maw'idaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2189,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Wa-wudi'al kitaabu fataral mujrimeena mushfiqeena mimmaa feehi Wa-yaqooloona yaa-wailatanaa maa lihaazal kitaabi laa yughaadiru saghee-ratanw Wa-laa kabeeratan illaaa ahsaahaa; Wa-wajadoo maa 'amiloo haadiraa; Wa-laa yazlimu Rabbuka ahadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2190,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qulnaa lilma-laaa'ikatis judoo li-Aadama fasajadooo illaaa Ibleesa kaana minal jinni fafasaqa 'an amri Rabbih; afatattakhizoonahoo Wa-zurriyatahooo awliyaaa'a min doonee Wa-hum lakum 'aduww; bi'sa lizzaalimeena badalaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2191,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Maaa ash-hattuhum khalqas samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-laa khalqa anfusihim Wa-maa kuntu muttakhizal mudilleena 'adudaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2192,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma yaqoolu naadoo shurakaaa'i yal-lazeena za'amtum fada'awhum falam yastajeeboo lahum Wa-ja'alnaa bainahum maw-biqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2193,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-ra al-mujrimoonan Naara fazannooo annahum muwaaqi'oohaa Wa-lam yajidoo 'anhaa masrifaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2194,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad sarrafnaa fee haazal quraani linnaasi min kulli masal; Wa-kaanal insaanu aksara shai'in jadalaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2195,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa mana'an naasa any yu'minooo iz jaaa'ahumul hudaa Wa-yastaghfiroo Rabbahum illaaa an taatiyahum sunnatul awwaleena aw yaatiyahumul 'azaabu qubulaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2196,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa nursilul mursaleena illaa mubashshireena Wa-munzireen; Wa-yujaadilul lazeena kafaroo bilbaatili liyudhidoo bihil haqqa wattakhazooo Aayaatee Wa-maaa unziroo huzuwaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2197,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Wa-man azlamu mimman zukkira bi-ayaati Rabbihee fa-a'rada 'anhaa Wa-nasiya maa qaddamat yadaah; innaa ja'alnaa 'alaa quloobihim akinnatan any yafqahoohu Wa-feee aazaanihim waqraa; Wa-in tad'uhum ilal hudaa falany yahtadooo izan abadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2198,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-Rabbukal Ghafooru zur rahmati law yu'aakhi-zuhum bimaa kasaboo la'ajala lahumul 'azaab; bal lahum maw'idul laien yajidoo min doonihee maw'ilaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2199,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Wa-tilkal quraaa ahlak-nahum lammaa zulamoo Wa-ja'alnaa limahlikihim maw'idaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2200,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaalaa Moosaa lifataahu laaa abrahu hattaaa ablugha majma'al bahrayni aw amdiya huqubaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2201,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Falammaa balaghaa majma'a bainihimaa nasiyaa hootahumaa fattakhaza sabeelahoo fil bahri sarabaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2202,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaawazaa qaala lifataahu aatinaa ghadaaa'anaa laqad laqeena min safarinaa haazaa nasabaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2203,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Qaala ara'ayta iz awainaaa ilas sakhrati fa-innee naseetul hoota Wa-maaa ansaaneehu illash Shaitaanu an azkurah; wattakhaza sabeelahoo fil bahri 'ajabaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2204,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Qaala zaalika maa kunnaa nabghi; fartaddaa 'alaa aasaari-him-maa qasasaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2205,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Fa-wajadaa 'abdam min 'ibaadinaaa aatainaahu Rahmatam min 'indinaa Wa-'allamnaahu mil ladunnaa 'ilmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2206,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Qaala lahoo Moosaa hal attabi'uka 'alaaa an tu'allimani mimmaa 'ullimta rushdaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2207,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 67,
      "text": "Qaalaa innaka lan tastatee'a ma'iya sabraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2208,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 68,
      "text": "Wa-kaifa tasbiru 'alaa maa lam tuhit bihee khubraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2209,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Qaala satajiduneee in shaa 'al-laahu saabiranw Wa-laaa a'see laka amraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2210,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Qaala fa-init taba'tanee falaa tas'alnee 'an shai'in hattaaa uhdisa laka minhu zikraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2211,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Fantalaqaa hattaaa izaa rakibaa fis safeenati kharaqahaa qaala akharaqtahaa litughriqa ahlahaa laqad ji'ta shai'an imraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2212,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 72,
      "text": "Qaala alam aqul innaka lan tastatee'a ma'iya sabraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2213,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Qaala laa tu'aakhiznee bimaa naseetu Wa-laa turhiqnee min amree 'usraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2214,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Fantalaqaa hattaa izaa laqiyaa ghulaaman faqatalahoo qaala aqatalta nafsan zakiy-yatam bighairi nafs; laqad ji'ta shai'an nukraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2215,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 75,
      "text": "Qaala alam aqul laka innaka lan tastatee'a ma'iya sabraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2216,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Qaala in sa-altuka 'an shai'im ba'dahaa falaa tusaahibnee qad balaghta mil ladunnee 'uzraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2217,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Fantalaqaa hattaaa izaaa atayaaa ahla qaryatinis tat'amaaa ahlahaa fa-abaw any yudaiyifoohumaa fawajadaa feehaa jidaarany yureedu any yanqadda fa-aqaamah; qaala law shi'ta lattakhazta 'alaihi ajraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2218,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Qaala haazaa firaaqu bainee Wa-bainik; sa-unabi-'uka bitaaweeli maa lam tastati' 'alaihi sabraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2219,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Ammas safeenatu fakaanat limasaakeena ya'maloona fil bahri fa-arattu an a'eebahaa Wa-kaana waraaa'-ahum malikuien yaakhuzu kulla safeenatin ghasbaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2220,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wa-aammal ghulaamu fakaana abawaahu mu'minaini fakhasheenaaa aien yurhiqa-humaa tughyaananw Wa-kufraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2221,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Faradnaa aien yubdila-humaa Rabbuhumaa khairam minhu zakaatanw Wa-aqraba ruhmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2222,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Wa-ammal jidaaru fakaana lighulaamaini yateemaini fil madeenati Wa-kaana tahtahoo kanzul lahumaa Wa-kaana aboohumaa saalihan fa-araada Rabbuka any yablughaaa ashuddahumaa Wa-yastakhrijaa kanzahumaa rahmatam mir Rabbik; Wa-maa fa'altuhoo 'an amree; zaalika taaweelu maa lam tasti' 'alaihi sabra"
    },
    {
      "index": 2223,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Wa-yas'aloonaka 'an Zil Qarnaini qul sa-atloo 'alaikum minhu zikraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2224,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Innaa makkannaa lahoo fil ardi Wa-aatainaahu min kulli shai'in sababaa"
    },
    {"index": 2225, "sura": 18, "aya": 85, "text": "Fa-atba'a sababaa"},
    {
      "index": 2226,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Hattaaa izaa balagha maghribash shamsi wajadahaaa taghrubu fee 'aynin hami'a-tinw Wa-wajada 'indahaa qawmaa; qulnaa yaa-Zal Qarnaini immaaa an tu'az-ziba Wa-immaaa an tattakhiza feehim husnaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2227,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Qaala amma man zalama fasawfa nu'azzibuhoo summa yuraddu ilaa Rabbihee fa-yu-'azzibuhoo azaaban nukraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2228,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Wa-ammaa man aamana Wa-'amila saalihan falahoo jazaaa'anil husnaa Wa-sanaqoolu lahoo min amrinaa yusraa"
    },
    {"index": 2229, "sura": 18, "aya": 89, "text": "Summa atba'a sababaa"},
    {
      "index": 2230,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Hattaaa izaa balagha matli'ash shamsi wajdahaa tatlu'u alaa qawmil lam naj'al lahum min doonihaa sitraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2231,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 91,
      "text": "Kazaalika Wa-qad ahatnaa bimaa ladaihi khubraa"
    },
    {"index": 2232, "sura": 18, "aya": 92, "text": "Summa atba'a sababaa"},
    {
      "index": 2233,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Hattaaa izaa balagha bainas saddaini wajada min doonihimaa qawmal laa yakaa-doona yafqahoona qawlaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2234,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Zal qarnaini inna Yaajooja Wa-Maajooja mufsidoona fil ardi fahal naj'alu laka kharjan 'alaaa an taj'ala bainanaa Wa-bainahum saddaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2235,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 95,
      "text":
          "Qaala maa makkannee feehi Rabbee khairun fa-a'eenoonee biquwwatin aj'al bainakum Wa-bainahum radmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2236,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Aatoonee zubaral hadeed, hattaaa izaa saawaa bainas sadafaini qaalan fukhoo hattaaa izaa ja'alahoo naaran qaala aatooneee ufrigh 'alaihi qitraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2237,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 97,
      "text": "Famas taa'ooo aien yazharoohu Wa-mas tataa'oo lahoo naqbaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2238,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Qaala haaza rahmatum mir Rabbee fa-izaa jaaa'a wa'du Rabbee ja'alahoo dakkaaa'a; Wa-kaana; Wa-du Rabbee haqqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2239,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Wa-taraknaa ba'dahum Yawma'izien yamooju fee ba'dinw Wa-nufikha fis Soori fajama'naahum jam'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2240,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 100,
      "text": "Wa-'aradnaa jahannama Yawma'izil lilkaafireena 'ardaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2241,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Allazeena kaanat a'yunuhum fee ghitaaa'in 'an zikree Wa-kaanoo la yastatee'oona sam'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2242,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Afahasibal lazeena kafarooo aien yattakhizoo 'ibaadee min dooneee awliyaaa'; innaaa a'tadnaa jahannama lil-kaafireena nuzulaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2243,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 103,
      "text": "Qul hal nunabbi'ukum bilakhsareena a'maalaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2244,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Allazeena dalla sa'yuhum fil hayaatid dunyaa Wa-hum yahsaboona annahum yuhsinoona sun'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2245,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena kafaroo bi-aayaati Rabbihim Wa-liqaaa'ihee fahabitat a'maaluhum falaa nuqeemu lahum Yawmal Qiyaamati waznaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2246,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Zaalika jazaaa'uhum jahannamu bimaa kafaroo wattakhazooo Aayaatee Wa-Rusulee huzuwaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2247,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 107,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati kaanat lahum Jannaatul Firdawsi nuzulaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2248,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 108,
      "text": "Khaalideena feeha la yabghoona 'anhaa hiwalaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2249,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Qul law kaanal bahru midaadal li-kalimaati Rabbee lanafidal bahru qabla an tanfada Kalimaatu Rabbee Wa-law ji'naa bimislihee madadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2250,
      "sura": 18,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Qul innamaaa ana basharum mislukum yoohaaa ilaiya annamaa ilaahukum Ilaahunw Waahid; faman kaana yarjoo liqaaa'a Rabbihee falya'mal 'amalan saalihanw Wa-laa yushrik bi'ibaadati Rabbiheee ahadaa"
    },
    {"index": 2251, "sura": 19, "aya": 1, "text": "Kaaaf-Haa-Yaa-'Ayyyn-Saaad"},
    {
      "index": 2252,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Zikru rahmati Rabbika 'abdahoo Zakariyya"
    },
    {
      "index": 2253,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "Iz naadaa Rabbahoo nidaaa'an khafiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2254,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbi innee wahanal 'azmu minnee washta-'alar ra'su shaibanw Wa-lam akun bidu'aaa'ika Rabbi shaqiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2255,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Wa-innee khiftul mawaaliya minw waraaa'ee Wa-kaanat imra atee 'aqiran fa-hablee mil ladunka waliyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2256,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 6,
      "text": "Yarisunee Wa-yarisu min aali Ya'qoob, waj'alhu Rabbi radiyya"
    },
    {
      "index": 2257,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Yaa-Zakariyyaaa innaa nubashshiruka bi-ghulaamin ismuhoo Yahyaa lam naj'al lahoo min qablu samiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2258,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbi annaa yakoonu lee ghulaamunw Wa-kaanat imra-atee 'aaqiranw Wa-qad balaghtu minal kibari 'itiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2259,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Qaala kazaalika qaala Rabbuka huwa 'alaiya haiyinunw Wa-qad khalaqtuka min qablu Wa-lam taku shai'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2260,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbij 'al leee Aayah; qaala Aayatuka allaa tukalliman naasa salaasa layaalin sawiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2261,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Fakharaja 'alaa qawmihee minal mihraabi fa-awhaaa ilaihim an sabbihoo bukratanw Wa-'ashiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2262,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Yaa-Yahyaa khuzil Kitaaba biquwwatinw Wa-aatainaahul hukma sabiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2263,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 13,
      "text": "Wa-hanaanam mil ladunnaa Wa-zakaatanw Wa-kaana taqiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2264,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 14,
      "text": "Wa-barram biwaalidayhi Wa-lam yakum jabbaaran 'asiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2265,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wa-salaamun 'alaihi yawma wulida Wa-yawma yamootu Wa-yawma yub'asu haiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2266,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wazkur fil Kitaabi Maryma; izin tabazat min ahlihaa makaanan sharqiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2267,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Fattakhazat min doonihim hijaaban fa-arsalnaaa ilaihaa roohanaa fatamassala lahaa basharan sawiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2268,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 18,
      "text": "Qaalat inneee a'oozu bir-Rahmaani minka in kunta taqiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2269,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Qaala innamaa ana rasoolu Rabbiki li-ahaba laki ghulaaman zakiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2270,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Qaalat anna yakoonu lee ghulaamunw Wa-lam yamsasnee bashrunw Wa-lam aku baghiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2271,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Qaala kazaaliki qaala Rabbuki huwa 'alaiya haiyyimunw Wa-linaj-'alahooo Aayatal linnaasi Wa-rahmatam minnaa; Wa-kaana amram maqdiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2272,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 22,
      "text": "Fahamalat-hu fantabazat bihee makaanan qasiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2273,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Fa-ajaaa-'ahal makhaadu ilaa jiz'in nakhlati qaalat yaa-laitanee mittu qabla haazaa Wa-kuntu nasyam mansiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2274,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Fanaadaahaa min tahtihaaa allaa tahzanee qad ja'ala Rabbuki tahtaki sariyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2275,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-huzzeee ilaiki bijiz-'in nakhlati tusaaqit 'alaiki rutaban janiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2276,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Fakulee washrabee Wa-qarree 'ainaa; fa-immaa tarayinnna minal bashari ahadan faqooleee innee nazartu lir-Rahmaani sawman falan ukallimal yawma insiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2277,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Fa-atat bihee qawmahaa tahmiluhoo qaaloo yaa-Maryamoo laqad ji'ti shai'an fariyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2278,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ukhta Haaroona maa kaana abooki mra'a saw'inw Wa-maa kaanat ummuki baghiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2279,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Fa-ashaarat ilaih; qaaloo kaifa nukallimu man kaana fil mahdi sabiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2280,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Qaala innee 'abdul laahi aataaniyal Kitaaba Wa-ja'alanee Nabiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2281,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alanee mubaarakan aina maa kuntu Wa-awsaanee bis-Salaati waz-Zakaati maa dumtu haiyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2282,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 32,
      "text": "Wa-barram biwaalidatee Wa-lam yaj'alnee jabbaaran shaqiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2283,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wassalaamu 'alaiya yawma wulidtu Wa-yawma amootu Wa-yawma ub'asu haiyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2284,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 34,
      "text": "Zaalika 'Eesab nu Maryama; qawlal haqqil lazee feehi yamtaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2285,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Maa kaana lillaahi aien yattakhiza minw waladin Subhaanah; izaa qadaaa amran fa-innamaa yaqoolu lahoo kun fa-yakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2286,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-innal laaha Rabbee Wa-Rabbukum fa'budooh; haazaa Siraatum Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2287,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Fakhtalafal ahzaabu min bainihim fawailul lillazeena kafaroo min mashhadi Yawmin 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2288,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Asmi' bihim Wa-absir Yawma ya'toonanaa laakiniz zaalimoonal yawma fee dalaalin mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2289,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wa-anzirhum Yawmal hasrati iz qudiyal amr; Wa-hum fee ghaflatinw Wa-hum laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2290,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 40,
      "text": "Innaa nahnu narisul arda Wa-man 'alaihaa Wa-ilainaa yurja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2291,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 41,
      "text": "Wazkur fil Kitaabi Ibraaheem; innahoo kaana siddeeqan Nabiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2292,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Iz qaala li-abeehi yaaa-abati lima ta'budu maa laa yasma'u Wa-laa yubsiru Wa-laa yughnee 'anka shai'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2293,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-abati innee qad jaaa'anee minal 'ilmi maa lam ya'tika fattabi'neee ahdika siraatan Sawiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2294,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-abati laa ta'budish Shaitaan; innash Shaitaana kaana lir-Rahmaani 'asiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2295,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-abati innee akhaafu aien yamassaka 'azaabum minar Rahmaani fatakoona lish-Shaitaani waliyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2296,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Qaala araaghibun anta 'an aalihatee yaaa-Ibraaheemu la-'il lam tantahi la-arjumannaka wahjurnee maliyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2297,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Qaala salaamun 'alaika sa-astaghfiru laka Rabbeee innahoo kaana bee hafiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2298,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-a'tazilukum Wa-maa tad'oona min doonil laahi Wa-ad'oo Rabbee 'asaaa allaaa akoona bidu'aaa'i Rabbee shaqiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2299,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Fa-lam ma'tazalahum Wa-maa ya'budoona min doonil laahi wahabnaa lahoo is-haaqa Wa-ya'qoob; Wa-kullan ja'alnaa Nabiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2300,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa wahabnaa lahum mirrahmatinaa Wa-ja'alnaa lahum lisaana sidqin 'aliyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2301,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Wazkur fil Kitaabi Moosaaa; innahoo kaana mukhlasanw Wa-kaana Rasoolan Nabiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2302,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-naadainaahu min jaanibit Tooril aimani Wa-qarrabnaahu najiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2303,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 53,
      "text": "Wa-wahabnaa lahoo mir rahmatinaaa akhaahu Haaroona Nabiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2304,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wazkur fil Kitaabi ismaa'eel; innahoo kaana saadiqal wa'di Wa-kaana Rasoolan Nabiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2305,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Wa-kaana ya'muru ahlahoo bis-Salaati waz-zakaati Wa-kaana 'inda Rabbihee mardiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2306,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 56,
      "text": "Wazkur fil Kitaabi Idrees; innahoo kaana siddeeqan Nabiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2307,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 57,
      "text": "Wa-rafa'naahu makaanan 'aliyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2308,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena an'amal laahu 'alaihim minan Nabiyyeena min zurriyyati Aadama Wa-mimman hamalnaa ma'a Noohinw Wa-min zurriyyati Ibraaheema Wa-Israaa'eela Wa-mimman hadainaa wajta-bainaaa; izaa tutlaa 'alaihim Aayaatur Rahmaani kharroo sujjadanw Wa-bukiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2309,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Fakhalafa min ba'dihim khalfun adaa'us Salaata wattaba'ush shahawaati fasawfa yalqawna ghaiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2310,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Illaa man taaba Wa-aamana Wa-'amila saalihan fa-ulaaa'ika yadkhuloonal jannata Wa-laa yuzlamoona shai'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2311,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Jannaati 'adninil latee wa'adar Rahmaanu ibaadahoo bilghaib; innahoo kaana wa'duhoo ma'tiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2312,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Laa yasma'oona feehaa laghwan illaa salaamaa; Wa-lahum rizquhum feehaa bukratanw Wa-'ashiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2313,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 63,
      "text": "Tilkal jannatul latee noorisu min 'ibaadinaa man kaana taqiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2314,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa natanazzalu illaa bi-amri Rabbika lahoo maa baina aideenaa Wa-maa khalfanaa Wa-maa baina zaalik; Wa-maa kaana Rabbuka nasiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2315,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Rabbus samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-maa bainahumaa fa'bud-hu wastabir li'ibaadatih; hal ta'lamu lahoo samiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2316,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 66,
      "text": "Wa-yaqoolul insaanu 'a-izaa maa mittu lasawfa ukhraju haiyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2317,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "A-Wa-laa yazkurul insaanu annaa khalaqnaahu min qablu Wa-lam yaku shai'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2318,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Fawa-Rabbika lanahshu-rannahum wash-shayaateena summa lanuhdirannahum hawla jahannama jisiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2319,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Summa lanan-zi'anna min kulli shee'atin aiyuhum ashaddu 'alar Rahmaani 'itiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2320,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 70,
      "text": "Summa lanahnu a'lamu billazeena hum awlaa bihaa siliyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2321,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wa-in minkum illaa waariduhaa; kaana 'alaa Rabbika hatmam maqdiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2322,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Summa nunajjil lazeenat taqaw Wa-nazaruz zaalimeena feehaa jisiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2323,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa tutlaa 'alaihim Aayaatunaa baiyinaatin qaalal lazeena kafaroo lillazeena aamanooo aiyul fareeqaini khairum maqaamanw Wa-ahsanu nadiyyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2324,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wa-kam ahlaknaa qablahum min qarnin hum ahsanu asaasanw Wa-ri'yaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2325,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Qul man kaana fid da-laalati falyamdud lahur Rahmaanu maddaa; hattaaa izaa ra-aw maa yoo'adoona immal 'azaaba Wa-immas Saa'ata fasa-ya'lamoona man huwa sharrum makaananw Wa-ad'afu jundaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2326,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Wa-yazeedul laahul lazeenah tadaw hudaa; wal-baaqiyaatus saalihaatu khairun 'inda Rabbika sawaabanw Wa-khairum maraddaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2327,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Afara'aytal lazee kafara bi-Aayaatinaa Wa-qaala la-oota-yanna maalanw Wa-waladaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2328,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 78,
      "text": "At-tala'al ghaiba 'amit takhaza 'indar Rahmaani 'ahdaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2329,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Kallaa; sanaktubu maa yaqoolu Wa-namuddu lahoo minal 'azaabi maddaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2330,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 80,
      "text": "Wa-narisuhoo maa yaqoolu Wa-ya'teenaa fardaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2331,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 81,
      "text": "Wattakhazoo min doonil laahi aalihatal liyakoonoo lahum 'izzaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2332,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Kallaa; sa-yakfuroona bi'ibaadatihim Wa-yakoonoona 'alaihim diddaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2333,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annaaa arsalnash Shayaateena 'alal kaafireena ta'uzzuhum azzaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2334,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 84,
      "text": "Falaa ta'jal alaihim innamaa na-'uddu lahum 'addaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2335,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 85,
      "text": "Yawma nahshurul muttaqeena ilar Rahmaani wafdaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2336,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 86,
      "text": "Wa-nasooqul mujrimeena ilaa Jahannama wirdaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2337,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Laa yamlikoonash shafaa'ata illaa manit takhaza 'indar Rahmaani 'ahdaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2338,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 88,
      "text": "Wa-qaalut takhazar Rahmaanu waladaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2339,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 89,
      "text": "Laqad ji'tum shai'an iddaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2340,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Takaadus samaawaatu yatafattarna minhu Wa-tanshaq qul-ardu Wa-takhirrul jibaalu haddaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2341,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 91,
      "text": "An da'aw lir-Rahmaani waladaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2342,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 92,
      "text": "Wa-maa yambaghee li-Rahmaani aien yattakhiza waladaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2343,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "In kullu man fis samaawaati wal-ardi illaaa aatir Rahmaani 'abdaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2344,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 94,
      "text": "Laqad ahsaahum Wa-addahum 'addaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2345,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 95,
      "text": "Wa-kulluhum aateehi Yawmal Qiyaamati fardaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2346,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati sa-yaj'alu lahumur Rahmaanu wuddaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2347,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Fa-innamaa yassarnaahu bilisaanika litubashshira bihil muttaqeena Wa-tunzira bihee qawmal luddaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2348,
      "sura": 19,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Wa-kam ahlaknaa qabla-hum min qarnin hal tuhissu minhum min ahadin aw tasma'u lahum rikzaa"
    },
    {"index": 2349, "sura": 20, "aya": 1, "text": "Taa-Haa"},
    {
      "index": 2350,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Maaa anzalnaa 'alaikal Qur-aana litashqaaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2351,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "Illaa tazkiratal limany yakhshaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2352,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 4,
      "text": "Tanzeelan mimman khalaqal arda was-samaawaatil 'ulaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2353,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 5,
      "text": "Ar-Rahmaanu 'alal 'Arshis tawaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2354,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Lahoo maa fis samaawaati Wa-maa fil ardi Wa-maa bainahumaa Wa-maa tahtas saraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2355,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 7,
      "text": "Wa-in tajhar bilqawli fainnahoo ya'lamus sirra Wa-akhfaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2356,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 8,
      "text": "Allaahu laaa ilaaha illaa huwa lahul asmaa'ul husnaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2357,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 9,
      "text": "Wa-hal ataaka hadeesu Moosa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2358,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Iz ra-aa naaran faqaala li-ahlihim kusooo inneee aanastu naaral la'alleee aateekum minhaa biqabasin aw ajidu 'alan naari hudaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2359,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 11,
      "text": "Falammaaa ataahaa noodiya yaa-Moosaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2360,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Inneee Ana Rabbuka fakhla' na'laika innaka bilwaadil muqaddasi Tuwaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2361,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 13,
      "text": "Wa anakhtartuka fastami' limaa yoohaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2362,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Innaneee Anal laahu laaa ilaaha illaa Ana fa'budnee Wa-aqimis salaata lizikree"
    },
    {
      "index": 2363,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Innas Saa'ata aatiyatun akaadu ukhfeehaa litujzaa kullu nafsin bimaa tas'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2364,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Falaa yasuddannaka 'anhaa mal laa yu'minu bihaa wattaba'a hawaahu fatardaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2365,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 17,
      "text": "Wa-maa tilka bi-yamee-nika yaa-Moosaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2366,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Qaala hiya 'asaaya atawakka'u alaihaa Wa-ahushshu bihaa 'alaa ghanamee Wa-liya feehaa ma-aaribu ukhraa"
    },
    {"index": 2367, "sura": 20, "aya": 19, "text": "Qaala alqihaa yaa-Moosaa"},
    {
      "index": 2368,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 20,
      "text": "Fa-alqaahaa fa-izaa hiya haiyatun tas'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2369,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 21,
      "text": "Qaala khuzhaa Wa-laa ta-khaf sanu'eeduhaa seeratahal oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2370,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wadmum yadaka ilaa janaahika takhruj baidaaa'a min ghairi sooo'in Aayatan ukhraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2371,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 23,
      "text": "Linuriyaka min Aayaatinal Kubra"
    },
    {
      "index": 2372,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 24,
      "text": "Izhab ilaa Fir'awna innahoo taghaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2373,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 25,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbish rah lee sadree"
    },
    {"index": 2374, "sura": 20, "aya": 26, "text": "Wa-yassir leee amree"},
    {
      "index": 2375,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 27,
      "text": "Wahlul 'uqdatan milli saanee"
    },
    {"index": 2376, "sura": 20, "aya": 28, "text": "Yafqahoo qawlee"},
    {
      "index": 2377,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 29,
      "text": "Waj'al lee wazeeran min ahlee"
    },
    {"index": 2378, "sura": 20, "aya": 30, "text": "Haaroona akhee"},
    {"index": 2379, "sura": 20, "aya": 31, "text": "Ushdud biheee azree"},
    {"index": 2380, "sura": 20, "aya": 32, "text": "Wa-ashrik-hu feee amree"},
    {"index": 2381, "sura": 20, "aya": 33, "text": "Kai nusabbihaka kaseeraa"},
    {"index": 2382, "sura": 20, "aya": 34, "text": "Wa-nazkuraka kaseeraa"},
    {
      "index": 2383,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 35,
      "text": "Innaka kunta binaa baseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2384,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 36,
      "text": "Qaala qad ooteeta su'laka yaa-Moosaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2385,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 37,
      "text": "Wa-laqad manannaa 'alaika marratan ukhraaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2386,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 38,
      "text": "Iz awhainaaa ilaaa ummika maa yoohaaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2387,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Ani qzifeehi fit Taabooti fa-qzifeehi fil yammi fal-yul-qihil yammu bis-saahili ya'khuzhu 'aduwwul lee Wa-'aduwwul lah; Wa-alqaitu 'alaika mahabbatan minnee Wa-litusna'a 'alaa 'ainee"
    },
    {
      "index": 2388,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Iz tamsheee ukhtuka fataqoolu hal adullukum 'alaa maien yakfuluhoo faraja-'naaka ilaaa ummika kai taqarra 'ainuhaa Wa-laa tahzan; Wa-qatalta nafsan fanajjainaaka minal ghammi Wa-fatannaaka futoonaa; falabista sineena feee ahli Madyana summa ji'ta 'alaa qadarien yaa-Moosa"
    },
    {"index": 2389, "sura": 20, "aya": 41, "text": "Wastana'-tuka linafsee"},
    {
      "index": 2390,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 42,
      "text": "Izhab anta Wa-akhooka bi-Aayaatee Wa-laa taniyaa fee zikree"
    },
    {
      "index": 2391,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 43,
      "text": "Izhabaaa ilaa Fir'awna innahoo taghaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2392,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Faqoolaa lahoo qawlal laiyinal la-allahoo yatazakkkaru 'aw yakhshaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2393,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Qaalaa Rabbanaaa innanaa nakhaafu aien yafruta 'alainaaa aw ai yatghaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2394,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 46,
      "text": "Qaala laa takhaafaaa innanee ma'akumaa asma'u Wa-araa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2395,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Faatiyaahu faqoolaaa innaa Rasoolaa Rabbika fa-arsil ma'anaa Banee Israaa'eela Wa-laa tu'azzibhum qad ji'naaka bi-Aayatim mir Rabbika wassa-laamu 'alaa manit taba'al hudaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2396,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Innaa qad oohiya ilainaaa annnal 'azaaba 'alaa man kaz-zaba Wa-tawalla"
    },
    {
      "index": 2397,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 49,
      "text": "Qaala famar Rabbu-kumaa yaa-Moosa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2398,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 50,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbunal lazeee a'taa kulla shai'in khalqahoo summa hadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2399,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 51,
      "text": "Qaala famaa baalul quroonil oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2400,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Qaala 'ilmuhaa 'inda Rabee fee kitaab, laa yadillu Rabbee Wa-laa yansaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2401,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Allazee ja'ala lakumul arda mahdanw Wa-salaka lakum feehaa subulanw Wa-anzala minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa-akhrajnaa biheee azwaajam min nabaatin shatta"
    },
    {
      "index": 2402,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Kuloo war'aw an'aamakum; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil li-ulin nuhaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2403,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Minhaa khalaqnaakum Wa-feehaa nu'eedukum Wa-minhaa nukhrijukum taaratan ukhraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2404,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 56,
      "text": "Wa-laqad arainaahu Aayaatinaa kullahaa fakaz-zaba Wa-abaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2405,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 57,
      "text": "Qaala aji'tanaa litukhri-janaa min ardinaa bisihrika yaa-Moosa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2406,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Falanaatiyannaka bisihrim mislihee faj'al bainanaa Wa-bainaka maw'idal laa nukhlifuhoo nahnu Wa-laaa anta makaanan suwaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2407,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 59,
      "text": "Qaala maw'idukum yawmuz zeenati Wa-ai yuhsharan naasu duhaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2408,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 60,
      "text": "Fatawallaa Fir'awnu fajjama'a kaidahoo summa ataa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2409,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Qaala lahum Moosaa wailakum laa taftaroo 'alal laahi kaziban fa-yus-hitakum bi-'azaab, Wa-qad khaaba manif taraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2410,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 62,
      "text": "Fatanaaza'ooo amrahum bainahum Wa-asarrun najwaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2411,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Qaalooo in haaazaani lasaahiraani yureedaani aien yukhrijaakum min ardikum bisihrihimaa Wa-yazhabaa bitareeqatikumul muslaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2412,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Fa-ajmi'oo kaidakum summa' too saffaa; Wa-qad aflahal yawma manis ta'laa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2413,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-Moosaaa immaaa an tulqiya Wa-immaaa an nakoona awala man alqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2414,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Qaala bal alqoo fa-izaa hibaaluhum Wa-'isiyyuhum yukhaiyalu ilaihi min sihrihim annahaa tas'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2415,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 67,
      "text": "Fa-awjasa fee nafsihee kheefatam Moosa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2416,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 68,
      "text": "Qulnaa laa takhaf innaka antal a'laa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2417,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Wa-alqi maa fee yamee-nika talqaf maa sana'oo; innamaa sana'oo kaidu saahir; Wa-laa yuflihus saahiru haisu ataa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2418,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Fa-ulqiyas saharatu sujjadan qaalooo aamannaa bi-Rabbi Haaroona Wa-Moosa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2419,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Qaala aamantum lahoo qabla an aazana lakum; innahoo lakabeerukumul lazee 'allama-kumus sihra fala-uqatti'anna aidiyakum Wa-arjulakum min khilaafinw Wa-la-usallibannakum fee juzoo'in nakhli Wa-lata'lamunna aiyunaaa ashaddu 'azaabanw Wa-abqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2420,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo lan nu'siraka 'alaa maa jaaa'anaa minal baiyinaati wallazee fataranaa faqdi maaa anta qaad; innamaa taqdee haazihil hayaatad dunyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2421,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Innaaa aamannaa bi-Rabbinaa liyaghfira lanaa khataayaanaa Wa-maaa akrahtanaa 'alaihi minas sihr; wallaahu khairunw Wa-abqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2422,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Innahoo mai ya'ti Rabbahoo mujriman fa-inna lahoo Jahannama laa yamootu feehaa Wa-laa yahyaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2423,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Wa-main ya'tihee mu'minan qad 'amilas saalihaati fa-ulaaa'ika lahumud darajaatul 'ulaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2424,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Jannaatu 'Adnin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaa; Wa-zaalika jazaaa'u man tazakka"
    },
    {
      "index": 2425,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad awhainaaa ilaa Moosaaa an asri bi'ibaadee fadrib lahum tareeqan fil bahri yabasal laa takhaafu darakanw Wa-laa takhshaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2426,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Fa-atba'ahum Fir'awnu bijunoodihee faghashiyahum minal yammmi maa ghashi-yahum"
    },
    {
      "index": 2427,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 79,
      "text": "wa-adalla fir'awnu qawmahoo Wa-maa hadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2428,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Yaa-Baneee Israaa'eela qad anjainaakum min 'aduw-wikum Wa-wa'adnaakum jaanibat Tooril aimana Wa-nazzalnaa 'alaikumul Manna was-Salwaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2429,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Kuloo min taiyibaati maa razaqnaakum Wa-laa tatghaw feehi fa-yahilla 'alaikum ghadabee Wa-mai yahlil 'alaihi ghadabee faqad hawaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2430,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Wa-innee la-Ghaffaarul liman taaba Wa-aamana Wa-'amila saalihan summah tadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2431,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 83,
      "text": "Wa-maaa a'jalaka 'an qawmika yaa-Moosa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2432,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 84,
      "text": "Qaala hum ulaaa'i 'alaaa asaree Wa-'ajiltu ilaika Rabbi litardaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2433,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Qaala fa-innaa qad fatannaa qawmaka mim ba'dika Wa-adallahumus Saamiriyy"
    },
    {
      "index": 2434,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Faraja'a Moosaaa ilaa qawmihee ghadbaana asifaa; qaala yaa-qawmi alam ya'idkum Rabbukum wa'dan hasanaa; afataala 'alaikumul 'ahdu am arattum ai yahilla 'alaikum ghadabum mir Rabbikum fa-akhlaftum maw'idee"
    },
    {
      "index": 2435,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo maaa akhlafnaa maw'idaka bimalkinna Wa-laakinna hummilnaaa awzaaram min zeenatil qawmi faqazafnaahaa fakazaalika alqas Saamiriyy"
    },
    {
      "index": 2436,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Fa-akhraja lahum 'ijlan jasadal lahoo khuwaarun faqaaloo haazaaa ilaahukum Wa-ilaahu Moosaa fanasee"
    },
    {
      "index": 2437,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Afalaa yarawna allaa yarji'u ilaihim qawlanw Wa-laa yamliku lahum darranw Wa-laa naf'aa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2438,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad qaala lahum Haaroonu min qablu yaa-qawmi innamaa futintum bihee Wa-inna Rabbakumur Rahmaanu fattabi'oonee Wa-atee'ooo amree"
    },
    {
      "index": 2439,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo lan nabraha 'alaihi 'aakifeena hattaa yarji'a ilainaa Moosaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2440,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 92,
      "text": "Qaala Yaa-Haaroonu maa mana-'aka iz ra-aitahum dallooo"
    },
    {
      "index": 2441,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 93,
      "text": "Allaa tattabi'ani afa'asaita amree"
    },
    {
      "index": 2442,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Qaala yabna'umma laa ta'khuz bi-lihyatee Wa-laa bi-ra'see innee khasheetu an taqoola farraqta baina Baneee Israaa'eela Wa-lam tarqub qawlee"
    },
    {
      "index": 2443,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 95,
      "text": "Qaala famaa khatbuka yaa-Saamiriyy"
    },
    {
      "index": 2444,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Qaala basurtu bimaa lam yabsuroo bihee faqabadtu qabdatam min asarir Rasooli fanabaztuhaa Wa-kazaalika sawwalat lee nafsee"
    },
    {
      "index": 2445,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Qaala fazhab fa-inna laka fil hayaati an taqoola laa misaasa Wa-inna laka maw'idal lan tukhlafahoo wanzur ilaaa ilaahikal lazee zalta 'alaihi 'aakifaa; la-nuharriqannahoo thumma la-nansifannahoo fil yammi nasfaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2446,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Innamaaa ilaahu-kumul laahul lazee laa ilaaha illaa Hoo; wasi'a kulla shai'in ilmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2447,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Kazaalika naqussu 'alaika min anbaaa'i maa qad sabaq; Wa-qad aatainaaka mil ladunnaa Zikraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2448,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 100,
      "text": "Man a'rada 'anhu, fa-innahoo yahmilu Yawmal Qiyaamati wizraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2449,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 101,
      "text": "Khaalideena feehi Wa-saaa'a lahum Yawmal Qiyaamati himlaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2450,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Yawma yunfakhu fissoori Wa-nahshurul mujrimeena Yawma 'izin zurqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2451,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 103,
      "text": "Yatakhaafatoona bainahum il labistum illaa 'ashraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2452,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "nahnu a'lamu bimaa yaqooloona iz yaqoolu amsaluhum tareeqatan il labistum illaa yawmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2453,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 105,
      "text": "Wa-yas'aloonaka 'anil jibaali faqul yansifuhaa Rabbee nasfaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2454,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 106,
      "text": "Fa-yazaruhaa qaa'an safsafaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2455,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 107,
      "text": "Laa taraa feehaa 'iwajanw Wa-laaa amtaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2456,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Yawma-izien yattabi'oonad daa'iya laa 'iwaja lahoo Wa-khasha'atil aswaatu lir-Rahmaani falaa tasma'u illaa hamsaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2457,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Yawma-'izil laa tanfa'ush shafaa'atu illaa man azina lahur Rahmaanu Wa-radiya lahoo qawlaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2458,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Ya'lamu maa bainaa aideehim Wa-maa khalfahum Wa-laa yuheetoona bihee 'ilmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2459,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 111,
      "text":
          "Wa-'anatil wujoohu lil-Haiiyil Qaiyoomi Wa-qad khaaba man hamala zulmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2460,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "Wa-main ya'mal minas saalihaati Wa-huwa mu'minun falaa yakhaafu zulmanw Wa-laa hadmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2461,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 113,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika anzalnaahu Qur-aanan 'Arabiyyanw Wa-sarrafnaa fee-hi minal wa'eedi la'allahum yattaqoona aw yuhdisu lahum zikraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2462,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 114,
      "text":
          "Fata'aalal laahul Malikul Haqq; Wa-laa ta'jal bil-Quraani min qabli aien yuqdaaa ilaika wahyuhoo Wa-qur Rabbi zidnee 'ilmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2463,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad 'ahidnaaa ilaaa Aadama min qablu fanasiya Wa-lam najid lahoo 'azmaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2464,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qulnaa lilma-laaa'ikatis judoo li-Aadama fasajadooo illaaa Ibleesa; abaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2465,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Faqulnaa yaaa-Aadamu inna haazaa 'aduwwul laka Wa-lizawjika falaa yukhrijan-nakumaa minal Jannati fatashqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2466,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 118,
      "text": "Innaa laka allaa tajoo'a feeha Wa-laa ta'raa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2467,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 119,
      "text": "Wa-annaka laa tazma'u feehaa Wa-laa tadhaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2468,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 120,
      "text":
          "Fa-waswasa ilaihish Shaitaanu qaala yaaa-Aadamu hal adulluka 'alaa shajaratil khuldi Wa-mulkil laa yablaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2469,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 121,
      "text":
          "Fa-akalaa minhaa fabadat lahumaa saw-aatuhumaa Wa-tafiqaa yakhsifaani 'alaihimaa minw waraqil jannah; Wa-'asaaa Aadamu Rabbahoo faghawaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2470,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 122,
      "text": "Summaj tabbahu Rabbuhoo fataaba 'alaihi Wa-hadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2471,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 123,
      "text":
          "Qaalah bita minhaa jamee'am ba'dukum liba'din 'aduww; fa-immaa ya'tiyannakum minnee hudan famanit taba'a hudaaya falaa yadillu Wa-laa yashqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2472,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 124,
      "text":
          "Wa-man a'rada 'an Zikree fa-inna lahoo ma'eeshatan dankanw Wa-nahshuruhoo Yawmal Qiyaamati a'maa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2473,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 125,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbi lima hashar-tanee a'maa Wa-qad kuntu baseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2474,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 126,
      "text":
          "Qaala kazaalika atatka Aayaatunaa fanaseetahaa Wa-kazaalikal Yawma tunsaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2475,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 127,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika najzee man asrafa Wa-lam yu'min bi-Aayaati Rabbih; Wa-la'azaabul Aakhirati ashaddu Wa-abqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2476,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 128,
      "text":
          "Afalam yahdi lahum kam ahlaknaa qablahum minal qurooni yamshoona fee masaakinihim; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil li-ulin nuhaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2477,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 129,
      "text":
          "Wa-law-laa Kalimatun sabaqat mir Rabbika lakaana lizaamanw Wa-'ajalun musammaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2478,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 130,
      "text":
          "Fasbir 'alaa maa yaqooloona Wa-sabbih bihamdi Rabbika qabla tuloo'ish shamsi Wa-qabla ghuroobihaa Wa-min aanaaa'il laili fasabbih Wa-atraafan nahaari la-'allaka tardaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2479,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 131,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tamuddanna 'ainaika ilaa ma matta'na biheee azwajam minhum zahratal hayaatid dunya linaftinahum feeh; Wa-rizqu Rabbika khairunw Wa-abqaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2480,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 132,
      "text":
          "Wa'mur ahlaka bis-Salaati wastabir 'alaihaa laa nas'aluka rizqaa; nahnu narzuquk; wal-'aaqibatu littaqwaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2481,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 133,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo law-laa ya'teenaa bi-aayatin mir Rabbih; awa-lam ta'tihim baiyyinatu maa fis suhufil oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2482,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 134,
      "text":
          "Wa-law annaaa ahlaknaahum bi-'azaabin min qablihee laqaaloo Rabbanaa law-laaa arsalta ilainaa Rasoolan fanattabi'a Aayaatika min qabli an nazilla Wa-nakhzaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2483,
      "sura": 20,
      "aya": 135,
      "text":
          "Qul kullum mutarabbisun fa-tarabbasoo fa-sa-ta'lamoona man Ashaabus Siraatis Sawiyyi Wa-manih tadaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2484,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 1,
      "text": "Iqtaraba linnaasi hisaabuhum Wa-hum fee ghaflatim mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2485,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Maa ya'teehim min zikrim mir Rabbihim muhdasin illas tama'oohu Wa-hum yal'aboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2486,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Laahiyatan quloobuhum; Wa-asarrun najwal lazeena zalamoo hal haazaaa illaa basharum mislukum 'afa-ta'toonas sihra Wa-antum tubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2487,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbee ya'lamul qawla fis samaaa'i wal-ardi Wa-Huwas Samee'ul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2488,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Bal qaalooo adghaasu ahlaamin bal iftaraahu bal huwa shaa'irun fal-ya'tinaa bi-Aayatin kamaa ursilal awwaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2489,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Maaa aaamanat qablahum min qaryatin ahlaknaahaa a-fahum yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2490,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaa qablaka illaa rijaalan nooheee ilaihim fas'aloo ahlaz zikri in kuntum laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2491,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa ja'alnaahum jasadal laa ya'kuloonat ta'aama Wa-maa kaanoo khaalideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2492,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Summa sadaqnaa-humul wa'da fa-anjainaahum Wa-man nashaaa'u Wa-ahlaknal musrifeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2493,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 10,
      "text": "Laqad anzalnaaa ilaikum Kitaaban feehi zikrukum afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2494,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Wa-kam qasamnaa min qaryatin kaanat zaalimatanw Wa-ansha'-naa ba'dahaa qawman aakhareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2495,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 12,
      "text": "Falammaaa ahassoo ba'sanaaa izaa hum minhaa yarkudoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2496,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Laa tarkudoo warji'ooo ilaa maaa utriftum feehi Wa-masaakinikum la'allakum tus'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2497,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 14,
      "text": "Qaaloo yaa-wailanaaa innaa kunnaa zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2498,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Famaa zaalat tilka da'waahum hattaa ja'alnaahum haseedan khaamideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2499,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 16,
      "text": "Wa-maa khalaqnas samaaa'a wal-arda Wa-maa bainahumaa laa'ibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2500,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Law aradnaaa an nattakhiza lahwal lat-takhaznaahu mil ladunnaaa in kunnaa faa'ileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2501,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Bal naqzifu bilhaqqi 'alal baatili fa-yadmaghuhoo fa-izaa huwa zaahiq; Wa-lakumul wailu mimmaa tasifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2502,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Wa-lahoo man fis samaawaati wal-ard; Wa-man 'indahoo laa yastakbiroona 'an 'ibaada-tihee Wa-laa yastahsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2503,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 20,
      "text": "Yusabbihoona laila wannahaara laa yafturoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2504,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 21,
      "text": "Amit takhazooo aalihatam minal ardi hum yunshiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2505,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Law kaana feehimaaa aalihatun illal laahu lafasadataa; fa-Subhaanal laahi Rabbil 'Arshi 'ammaa yasifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2506,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 23,
      "text": "Laa yus'alu 'ammaa yaf'alu Wa-hum yus'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2507,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Amit takhazoo min doonihee aalihatan qul haatoo burhaanakum haaza zikru mam ma'iya Wa-zikru man qablee; bal aksaruhum laa ya'lamoonal haqqa fahum mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2508,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaa min qablika mir Rasoolin illaa nooheee ilaihi annahoo laaa ilaaha illaaa Ana fa'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2509,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalut takhazar Rahmaanu waladaa; Subhaanahu bal 'ibaadum mukramoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2510,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 27,
      "text": "Laa yasbiqoonahoo bil-qawli Wa-hum bi-amrihee ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2511,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Ya'lamu maa baina aideehim Wa-maa khalfahum Wa-laa yashfa'oona illaa limanir tadaa Wa-hum min khash-yatihee mushfiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2512,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Wa-main yaqul minhum inneee ilaahum min doonihee fazaalika najzeehi Jahannam; kazaalika najziz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2513,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaral lazeena kafarooo annas samaawaati wal-arda kaanataa ratqan fafataqnaa-humaa Wa-ja'alnaa minal maaa'i kulla shai'in haiyin afalaa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2514,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnaa fil ardi rawaasiya an tameeda bihim Wa-ja'alnaa feehaa fijaajan subulal la'allahum yahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2515,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnas samaaa'a saqfam mahfoozanw Wa-hum 'an Aayaatihaa mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2516,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee khalaqal laila wannahaara washshamsa wal-qamara kullun fee falakiny yasbahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2517,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa ja'alnaa libasharim min qablikal khuld; afa immitta fahumul khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2518,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Kullu nafsin zaaa'iqatul mawt; Wa-nablookum bi-sharri walkhairi fitnatanw Wa-ilainaa turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2519,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa ra-aakal lazeena kafarooo ien yattakhizoonaka illa huzuwan; ahaazal lazee yazkuru aalihatakum Wa-hum bi-zikrir Rahmaani hum kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2520,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Khuliqal insaanu min 'ajal; sa-ureekum Aayaatee falaa tasta'jiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2521,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 38,
      "text": "Wa-yaqooloona mataa haazal wa'du in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2522,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Law ya'lamul lazeena kafaroo heena laa yakuffoona 'anw wujoohihimun Naara Wa-laa 'an zuhoorihim Wa-laa hum yunsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2523,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Bal ta'teehim baghtatan fatabhatuhum falaa yastatee'oona raddahaa Wa-laa hum yunzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2524,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqadis tuhzi'a bi-Rusulim min qablika fahaaqa billazeena sakhiroo minhum maa kaanoo bihee yastahzi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2525,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Qul main yakla-'ukum billaili wannahaari minar Rahmaan; bal hum 'an zikri Rabbihim mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2526,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Am lahum aalihatun tamna'uhum min dooninaa; laa yastatee'oona nasra anfusihim Wa-laa hum minna yus-haboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2527,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Bal matta'naa haaa'ulaaa'i Wa-aabaaa'ahum hattaa taala 'alaihimul 'umur; afalaa yarawna anna na'til arda nanqusuhaa min atraafihaa; afahumul ghaaliboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2528,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Qul innamaaa unzirukum bilwahyi; Wa-laa yasma'us summud du'aaa-'a izaa maa yunzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2529,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-la'in massat-hum nafhatun min 'azaabi Rabbika la-yaqoolunna yaawailanaaa innnaa kunnaa zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2530,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-nada'ul mawaazeenal qista li-Yawmil Qiyaamati falaa tuzlamu nafsun shai'aa; Wa-in kaana misqaala habbatim min khardalin atainaa bihaa; Wa-kafaa binaa haasibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2531,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Moosa Wa-haaroonal Furqaana Wa-diyaa'anw Wa-zikral lilmuttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2532,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yakhshawna Rabbahum bilghaibi Wa-hum minas Saa'ati mushfiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2533,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 50,
      "text": "Wa-haazaa Zikrum Mubaarakun anzalnaah; afa-antum lahoo munkiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2534,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaaa Ibraaheema rushdahoo min qablu Wa-kunnaa bihee 'aalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2535,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Iz qaala li-abeehi Wa-qawmihee maa haazihit tamaaseelul lateee antum lahaa 'aakifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2536,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 53,
      "text": "Qaaloo wajadnaaa aabaaa'anaa lahaa 'aabideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2537,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 54,
      "text": "Qaala laqad kuntum antum Wa-aabaaa'ukum fee dalaalin mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2538,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 55,
      "text": "Qaalooo aji'tanaa bil-haqqi am anta minal laa'ibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2539,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Qaala bar Rabbukum Rabbus samaawaati wal-ardil lazee fatarahunna Wa-ana 'alaa zaalikum minash shaahideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2540,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 57,
      "text": "Wa-tallaahi la-akeedanna asnaamakum ba'da an tuwalloo mudbireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2541,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Faja'alahum juzaazan illaa kabeeral lahum la'allahum ilaihi yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2542,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo man fa'ala haazaa bi-aalihatinaaa innahoo laminaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2543,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 60,
      "text": "Qaaloo sami'naa fatany yazkuruhum yuqaalu lahooo ibraaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2544,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 61,
      "text": "Qaaloo fa'too bihee 'alaaa a'yunin naasi la'allahum yash-hadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2545,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 62,
      "text": "Qaalooo 'a-anta fa'alta haazaa bi-aalihatinaa yaaa-ibraaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2546,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Qaala bal fa'alahoo kabeeruhum haazaa fas'aloohum in kaanoo yantiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2547,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 64,
      "text": "Faraja'ooo ilaaa anfusihim faqaalooo innakum antumuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2548,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Summa nukisoo 'alaa ru'oosihim laqad 'alimta maa haaa'ulaaa'i yantiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2549,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Qaala afata'budoona min doonil laahi maa laa yanfa'ukum shai'anw Wa-laa yadurrukum"
    },
    {
      "index": 2550,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Uffil lakum Wa-limaa ta'budoona min doonil laah; afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2551,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 68,
      "text": "Qaaloo harriqoohu wansurooo aalihatakum in kuntum faa'ileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2552,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 69,
      "text": "Qulnaa yaa-naaru koonee bardanw Wa-salaaman 'alaaa Ibraaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2553,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 70,
      "text": "Wa-araadoo bihee kaidan faja'alnaahumul akhsareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2554,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wa-najjainaahu Wa-Lootan ilal ardil latee baaraknaa feehaa lil-'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2555,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Wa-wahabnaa lahooo Ishaaqa; Wa-Ya'qooba naafilah; Wa-kullan ja'alnaa saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2556,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnaahum a'immataien yahdoona bi-amrinaa Wa-awhainaaa ilaihim fi'lal khairaati Wa-iqaamas Salaati Wa-eetaaa'az Zakaati Wa-kaanoo lanaa 'aabideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2557,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wa-Lootan aatainaahu hukmanw Wa-'ilmanw Wa-najjainaahu minal qaryatil latee kaanat ta'malul khabaaa'is; innahum kaanoo qawma saw'in faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2558,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 75,
      "text": "Wa-adkhalnaahu fee rahmatinaa innahoo minas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2559,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Wa-noohan iz naadaa min qablu fastajabnaa lahoo fanajjainaahu Wa-ahlahoo minal karbil 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2560,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Wa-nasarnaahu minal qawmil lazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa; innahum kaanoo qawma saw'in fa-aghraq-naahum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 2561,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Wa-Daawooda Wa-Sulaimaana iz yahkumaani fil harsi iz nafashat feehi ghanamul qawmi Wa-kunnaa lihukmihim shaahideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2562,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Fafahhamnaahaa sulaimaan; Wa-kullan aatainaa hukmanw wa'ilmanw Wa-sakh-kharnaa ma'a Daawoodal jibaala yusabbihna wattayr; Wa-kunnaa faa'ileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2563,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wa-'allamanaahu san'ata laboosil lakum lituhsinakum min ba'sikum fahal antum shaakiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2564,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Wa-li-Sulaimaanar reeha 'aasifatan tajree bi-amriheee ilal ardil latee baaraknaa feehaa; Wa-kunnaa bikulli shai'in 'aalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2565,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Wa-minash Shayaateeni maien yaghoosoona lahoo Wa-ya'maloona 'amalan doona zaalika Wa-kunna lahum haafizeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2566,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Wa-Ayyooba iz naadaa Rabbahooo annee massaniyad durru Wa-Anta arhamur raahimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2567,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Fastajabnaa lahoo fakashaf-naa maa bihee min durrinw Wa-aatainaahu ahlahoo Wa-mislahum ma'ahum rahmatan min 'indinaa Wa-zikraa lil'aabideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2568,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 85,
      "text": "Wa-Ismaa'eela Wa-Idreesa Wa-Zal Kifli kullum minas saabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2569,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 86,
      "text": "Wa-adkhalnaahum fee rahmatinaa innahum minas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2570,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Wa-Zan Nooni iz zahaba mughaadiban fa-zannaa al lan naqdira 'alaihi fanaadaa fiz zulumaati al laaa ilaaha illaaa Anta Subhaanaka innee kuntu minaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2571,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Fastajabnaa lahoo Wa-najjainaahu minal ghamm; Wa-kazaalika nunjil mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2572,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Wa-Zakariyyaaa iz naadaa Rabbahoo Rabbi laa tazarnee fardanw Wa-Anta khairul waariseen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2573,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Fastajabnaa lahoo Wa-wahabnaa lahoo Yahyaa Wa-aslahnaa lahoo zawjah; innahum kaanoo yusaari'oona fil khairaati Wa-yad'oonanaa raghabanw Wa-rahabaa; Wa-kaanoo lanaa khaashi'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 2574,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Wallateee ahsanat farjahaa fanafakhnaa feehaa min roohinaa Wa-ja'alnaahaa wabnahaaa Aayatan lil'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2575,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Inna haaziheee ummatukum ummatanw waahidatanw Wa-Ana Rabbukum fa'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2576,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 93,
      "text": "Wa-taqatta'ooo amrahum bainahum kullun ilainaaa raaji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2577,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 94,
      "text":
          "Famaien ya'mal minas saalihaati Wa-huwa mu'minun falaa kufraana lisa'yihee Wa-innaa lahoo kaatiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2578,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 95,
      "text": "Wa-haraamun 'alaa qaryatin ahlaknaahaaa annahum laa yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2579,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 96,
      "text":
          "Hattaaa izaa futihat Ya'jooju Wa-Ma'jooju Wa-hum min kulli hadabien yansiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2580,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 97,
      "text":
          "Waqtarabal wa'dul haqqu fa-izaa hiya shaakhisatun absaarul lazeena kafaroo yaawailanaa qad kunna fee ghaflatin min haaza bal kunnaa zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2581,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 98,
      "text":
          "Innakum Wa-maa ta'budoona min doonil laahi hasabu Jahannama antum lahaa waaridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2582,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 99,
      "text":
          "Law kaana haaa'ulaaa'i aalihatan maa waradoohaa Wa-kullun feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2583,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 100,
      "text": "Lahum feehaa zafeerunw Wa-hum feehaa laa yasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2584,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena sabaqat lahum minnal husnaaa ulaaa'ika 'anhaa mub'adoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2585,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 102,
      "text":
          "Laa yasma'oona hasee-sahaa Wa-hum fee mash tahat anfusuhum khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2586,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Laa yahzunuhumul faza'ul akbaru Wa-tatalaq-qaahumul malaaa'ikatu haazaa Yawmukumul lazee kuntum too'adoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2587,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 104,
      "text":
          "Yawma natwis samaaa'a kataiyis sijilli lilkutub; kamaa bada'naa awwala khalqin nu'eeduh; wa'dan 'alainaa; innaa kunna faa'ileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2588,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 105,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad katabnaa fiz Zaboori min ba'diz zikri annal arda yarisuhaa 'ibaadi-yas saalihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2589,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 106,
      "text": "Inna fee haaza labalaa-ghal liqawmin 'aabideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2590,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 107,
      "text": "Wa-maaa arsalnaaka illaa rahmatal lil'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2591,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 108,
      "text":
          "Qul innamaa yoohaa ilaiya annamaaa ilaahukum illaahunw Waahid, fahal antum muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2592,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Fa-in tawallaw faqul aazantukum 'alaa sawaaa'; Wa-in adreee aqareebun am ba'eedun maa too'adoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2593,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 110,
      "text": "Innahoo ya'lamul jahra minal qawli Wa-ya'lamu maa taktumoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2594,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 111,
      "text": "Wa-in adree la'allahoo fitnatul lakum Wa-mataa'un ilaa heen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2595,
      "sura": 21,
      "aya": 112,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbih kum bil-haqq; Wa-Rabbunar Rahmaa-nul musta'aanu 'alaa maa tasifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2596,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Yaaa ayyuhan naasuttaqoo Rabbakum; inna zalzalatas Saa'ati shai'un 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2597,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Yawma tarawnahaa tazhalu kullu murdi'atin 'ammaaa arda'at Wa-tada'u kullu zaati hamlin hamlahaa Wa-tarannaasa sukaaraa Wa- maa hum bisukaaraa Wa-lakinaa 'azaabal laahi shadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2598,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Wa-minan naasi maien yujaadilu fil laahi bighairi 'ilminw Wa-yattabi'u kullaa shaitaanim mareed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2599,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Kutiba 'alaihi annahoo man tawallaahu fa-annahoo yudilluhoo Wa-yahdeehi ilaa 'azaabis sa'eer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2600,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhan naasu in kuntum fee raibin minal ba'thi fa-innaa khalaqnaakum min turaabin thumma min nutfatin thumma min 'alaqatin thumma min mudghatin mukhallaqatinw Wa-ghairi mukhallaqatin linubaiyina lakum; Wa-nuqirru fil arhaami maa nashaaa'u ilaaa ajalin musamman thumma nukhrijukum tiflan thumma litablughooo ashuddakum Wa-minkum mai yutawaffa Wa-minkum mai yuraddu ilaaa arzalil 'umuri likailaa ya'lama min ba'di 'ilmin shai'aa; Wa-taral arda haamidatan fa-izaaa anzalnaa 'alaihal maaa'ah tazzat Wa-rabat Wa-ambatat min kulli zawjin baheej"
    },
    {
      "index": 2601,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bi annal laaha Huwal haqqu Wa-annahoo yuhyil mawtaa Wa-annahoo 'alaakulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2602,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-annas Saa'ata aatiya tul laa raiba feeha Wa-annal laaha yab'asuman fil quboor"
    },
    {
      "index": 2603,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Wa-minan naasi maien yujaadilu fil laahi bighairi 'ilminw Wa-laa hudanw Wa-laa Kitaabim Muneer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2604,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Saaniya 'itfihee liyudilla 'an sabeelil laahi lahoo fiddun yaa khizyunw Wa-nuzeequhoo Yawmal Qiyaamati azaabal hareeq"
    },
    {
      "index": 2605,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bimaa qaddamat yadaaka Wa-annal laaha laisa bizallaamil lil'abeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2606,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Wa-minan naasi maien ya'budul laaha 'alaa harfin fa-in asaabahoo khairunit maanna bihee Wa-in asaabat-hu fitnatunin qalaba 'alaa wajhihee khasirad dunyaa wal-aakhirah; zaalika huwal khusraanul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2607,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Yad'oo min doonil laahi maa laa yadurruhoo Wa-maa laa yanfa'uh' zaalika huwad dalaalul ba'ed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2608,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Yad'oo laman darruhooo aqrabu min naf'ih; labi' salmawlaa Wa-labi'sal 'asheer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2609,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha yudkhilul lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaar; innal laaha yaf'alu maa yureed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2610,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Man kaana yazunnu al laien yansurahul laahu fid dunyaa wal-aakhirati fal-yamdud bisababin ilas samaaa'i summal yaqta' falyanzur hal yuzhibanna kaiduhoo maa yagheez"
    },
    {
      "index": 2611,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika anzalnaahu aayaatim baiyinaatinw Wa-annal laaha yahdee mai yureed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2612,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo wallazeena haadoo was-saabi'eena wan-nasaaraa wal-Majoosa wallazeena ashrakooo innal laaha yafsilu bainahum yawmal qiyaamah; innal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in shaheed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2613,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annal laaha yasjudu lahoo man fis samaawaati Wa-man fil ardi wash-shamsu walqamaru wan-nu-joomu wal-jibaalu wash-shajaru wad-dawaaabbu Wa-kaseerum minan naasi Wa-kaseerun haqqa 'alaihil 'azaab; Wa-maien yuhinil laahu famaa lahoo mim mukrim; innal laaha yaf'alu maa yashaaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2614,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Haazaani khasmaanikh tasamoo fee Rabbihim fal-lazeena kafaroo qutti'at lahum siyaabum min naar; yusabbu min fawqi ru'oosihimul hameem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2615,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 20,
      "text": "Yusharu bihee maa fee butoonihim waljulood"
    },
    {
      "index": 2616,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 21,
      "text": "Wa-lahum maqaami'u min hadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2617,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Kullamaa araadooo any yakhrujoo minhaa min ghammin u'eedoo feeha Wa-zooqoo 'azaabal hareeq"
    },
    {
      "index": 2618,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha yudkhilul lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru yuhallawna feehaa min asaawira min zahabinw Wa-lu'lu'aa; Wa-libaasuhum feehaa hareer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2619,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Wa-hudooo ilat taiyibi minal qawli Wa-hudooo ilaaa siraatil hameed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2620,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena kafaroo Wa-yasuddoona 'an sabeelil laahi wal-Masjidil Haraamil lazee ja'alnaahu linnaasi sawaaa'anil 'aakifu feehi walbaad; Wa-maien yurid feehi bi-ilhaadim bizulmin nuziqhu min 'azaabin aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2621,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz bawwaanaa li-Ibraaheema makaanal Baiti al laa tushrik bee shai'anw Wa-tahhir Baitiya litaaa'ifeena walqaaa'-imeena warrukka-'is sujood"
    },
    {
      "index": 2622,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wa-azzin fin naasi bil-Hajji yaatooka rijaalanw Wa-'alaa kulli daamirien yaateena min kulli fajjin 'ameeq"
    },
    {
      "index": 2623,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Li yashhadoo manaafi'a lahum Wa-yazkurus mal laahi feee ayyaamimma'loomaatin 'alaa maa razaqahum mim baheematil an'aami fakuloo minhaa Wa-at'imul baaa'isal faqeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2624,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Summal yaqdoo tafasahum wal-yoofoo nuzoorahum wal-yattawwafoo bil-Baitil 'Ateeq"
    },
    {
      "index": 2625,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Zaalika Wa-maien yu'azzim hurumaatil laahi fahuwa khairul lahoo 'inda Rabbih; Wa-uhillat lakumul an'aamu illaa maa yutlaa 'alaikum fajtanibur rijsa minal awsaani wajtaniboo qawlaz zoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 2626,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Hunafaaa'a lillaahi ghaira mushrikeena bih; Wa-maien yushrik billaahi faka-annamaa kharra minas samaaa'i fatakh-tafuhut tairu aw tahwee bihir reehu bee makaanin saheeq"
    },
    {
      "index": 2627,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Zaalika Wa-mai yu'azzim sha'aaa'iral laahi fa-innahaa min taqwal quloob"
    },
    {
      "index": 2628,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Lakum feehaa manaafi'u ilaaa ajalim musamman summa mahilluhaaa ilal Baitil 'Ateeq"
    },
    {
      "index": 2629,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-likulli ummatin ja'alnaa mansakal liyazkurus mal laahi 'alaa maa razaqahum mim baheematil an'aam; failaahukum ilaahunw Waahidun falahooo aslimoo; Wa-bashshiril mukhbiteen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2630,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Allazeena izaa zukiral laahu wajilat quloobuhum wassaabireena 'alaa maaa asaabahum walmuqeemis Salaati Wa-mimmaa razaqnaahum yunfiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2631,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Walbudna ja'alnaahaa lakum min sha'aaa'iril laahi lakum feehaa khairun fazkurus mal laahi 'alaihaa sawaaff; fa-izaa wajabat junoobuhaa fakuloo minhaa Wa-at'imul qaani'a walmu'tarr; kazaalika sakhkharnaahaa lakum la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2632,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Laien yanaalal laaha luhoo-muhaa Wa-laa dimaaa'uhaa Wa-laakiny yanaaluhut taqwaa minkum; kazaalika sakhkharhaa lakum litukabbirul laaha 'alaa ma hadaakum; Wa-bashshirul muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2633,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha yudaafi' 'anil lazeena aamanoo; innal laaha laa yuhibbu kulla khawwaanin kafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 2634,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Uzina lillazeena yuqaataloona bi-annahum zulimoo; Wa-innal laaha 'alaa nasrihim la-Qaderr"
    },
    {
      "index": 2635,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Allazeena ukhrijoo min diyaarihim bighairi haqqin illaaa any yaqooloo rabbunallaah; Wa-law laa daf'ul laahin naasa ba'dahum biba'dil lahuddimat sawaami'u Wa-biya'unw Wa-salawaatunw Wa-masaajidu yuzkaru feehasmul laahi kaseeraa; Wa-layansurannal laahu mai yansuruh; innal laaha la qawiyyun 'Azeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 2636,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Allazeena im makkan-naahum fil ardi aqaamus Salaata Wa-aatawuz Zakaata Wa-amaroo bilma'roofi Wa-nahaw 'anil munkar; Wa-lillaahi 'aaqibatul umoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 2637,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-ien yukazzibooka faqad kazzabat qablahum qawmu Nooinw Wa-Aadunw Wa-Samood"
    },
    {
      "index": 2638,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 43,
      "text": "Wa-qawmu Ibraaheema Wa-qawmu Loot"
    },
    {
      "index": 2639,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Wa-as-haabu Madyana Wa-kuzziba Moosaa fa-amlaitu lilkaafireena summa akhaztuhum fakaifa kaana nakeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2640,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Faka-ayyim min qaryatin ahlaknaahaa Wa-hiya zaalimatun fahiya khaawiyatun 'alaa 'urooshihaa Wa-bi'rim mu'at-talatinw Wa-qasrim masheed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2641,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Afalam yaseeroo fil ardi fatakoona lahum quloobuien ya'qiloona bihaaa aw aazaanunien yasma'oona bihaa fa-innahaa laa ta'mal absaaru Wa-laakin ta'mal quloobul latee fis sudoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 2642,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-yasta'juloonaka bil'azaabi Wa-lany yukhlifal laahu wa'dah; Wa-inna yawman 'inda Rabbika ka'alfi sanatim mimmaa ta'uddoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2643,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-ka-ayyim min qaryatin amlaitu lahaa Wa-hiya zaalimatun summa akhaztuhaa Wa-ilaiyal maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2644,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 49,
      "text": "Qul yaaa-ayyuhan naasu innamaaa ana lakum nazeerum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2645,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Fallazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilu saalihaati lahum maghfiratunw Wa-rizqun kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2646,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena sa'aw feee Aayaatinaa mu'aajizeena ulaaa-ika As-haabul jaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2647,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaa min qablika mir Rasoolinnw Wa-laa Nabiyyin illaaa izaaa tamannaaa alqash Shaitaanu feee umniy-yatihee fa-yansakhul laahu maa yulqish Shaitaanu summa yuhkimul laahu aayaatih; wallaahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2648,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Liyaj'ala maa yulqish Shaitaanu fitnatal lillazeena fee quloobihim maradunw walqaasiyati quloobuhum; Wa-innaz zaalimeena lafee shiqaaqim ba'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2649,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wa-liya'lamal lazeena ootul 'ilma annahul haqqu mir Rabbika fa-yu'minoo bihee fatukhbita lahoo quloobuhum; Wa-innal laaha lahaadil lazeena aamanoo ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2650,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yazaalul lazeena kafaroo fee miryatim minhu hattaa taatiyahumus Saa'atu baghtatan aw yaatiyahum 'azaabu Yawmin 'aqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2651,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Almulku Yawma'izil lillaahi yahkumu bainahum; fallazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati fee jannaatin Na'eem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2652,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kafaroo Wa-kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa fa-ulaaa'ika lahum 'azaabum muheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2653,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena haajaroo fee sabeelil laahi summa qutilooo aw maatoo la-yarzuqan-nahumul laahu rizqan hasanaa; Wa-innal laaha la-Huwa khairur raaziqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2654,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "La-yudkhilan-nahum mud-khalaien yardawnah; Wa-innal laaha la-'Aleemun Haleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2655,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Zaalika Wa-man 'aaqaba bimisli maa 'ooqiba bihee summa bughiya 'alaihi la-yansurannahul laah; innal laaha la-'Afuwwun Ghafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 2656,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bi-annal laaha yoolijul laila fin nahaari Wa-yoolijun nahaara fil laili Wa-annal laaha Samee'um Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2657,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bi-annal laaha Huwal haqqu Wa-anna maa yad'oona min doonihee huwal baatilu Wa-annal laaha Huwal 'Aliyyul kabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2658,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annal laaha anzala minas samaaa'i maaa'an fatusbihul ardu mukhdarrah; innal laaha Lateefun Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2659,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Lahoo ma fis samaawaati Wa-ma fil ard; Wa-innal laaha la-Huwal Ghaniyyul Hameed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2660,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annal laaha sakhkhara lakum maa fil ardi wal-fulka tajree fil bahri bi-amrihee Wa-yumsikus samaaa'a an taqa'a 'alal ardi illaa biiznih; innal laaha binnaasi la-Ra'oofur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2661,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee ahyaakum summa yumeetukum summa yuhyeekum; innal insaana la-kafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 2662,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Likulli ummatin ja'alnaa mansakan hum naasikoohu falaa yunaazi-'unnaka fil amr; wad'u ilaa Rabbika innaka la-'alaa hudan mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2663,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 68,
      "text": "Wa-in jaadalooka faqulil laahu a'lamu bimaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2664,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Allaahu yahkumu bainakum Yawmal Qiyaamati feemaa kuntum feehi takhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2665,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Alam ta'lam annal laaha ya'lamu maa fis samaaa'i wal-ard; inna zaalika fee kitaab; inna zaalika 'alal laahi yaseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2666,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wa-ya'budoona min doonil laahi maa lam yunazzil bihee sultaananw Wa-maa laisa lahum bihee 'ilm; Wa-maa lizzaalimeena min naseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2667,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa tutlaa 'laihim Aayaatunaa baiyyinaatin ta'rifu fee wujoohil lazeena kafarul munkara yakaadoona yastoona bil-lazeena yatloona 'alaihim Aayaatinaa; qul afa-unab-bi'ukum bisharrim min zaalikum; an-Naaru Wa-'adahal laahul lazeena kafaroo Wa-bi'sal maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2668,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhan naasu duriba masalun fastami'oo lah; innal lazeena tad'oona min doonil laahi laien yakhluqoo zubaabanw Wa-lawi ijtama'oo lahoo Wa-ien yaslub-humuz zubaabu shai'an laa yastanqizoohu minh; da'ufat taalibu wal-matloob"
    },
    {
      "index": 2669,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 74,
      "text": "Maa qadrul laaha haqqa qadrih; innal laaha la-Qawiyyun 'Azeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 2670,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Allahu yastafee minal malaaa'ikati Rusulanw Wa-minan naas; innal laaha Samee'un Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2671,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Ya'lamu maa baina aydeehim Wa-maa khalfahum; Wa-ilal laahi turja'ul umoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 2672,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhal lazeena aamanur ka'oo wasjudoo wa'budoo Rabbakum waf'alul khaira la'allakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2673,
      "sura": 22,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaahidoo fil laahi haqqa jihaadih; Huwaj tabaakum Wa-maa ja'ala 'alaikum fid deeni min haraj; Millata abeekum Ibraaheem; Huwa sammaakumul muslimeena min qablu Wa-fee haaza li-yakoonar Rasoolu shaheedan 'alaikum Wa-takoonoo shuhadaaa'a 'alan naas; fa-aqeemus salaata Wa-aatuz zakaata wa'tasimoo billaahi Huwa mawlaakum fani'mal mawlaa Wa-ni'man naseer"
    },
    {"index": 2674, "sura": 23, "aya": 1, "text": "Qad aflahal mu'minoon"},
    {
      "index": 2675,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Allazeena hum fee Salaatihim khaashi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2676,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "Wallazeena hum 'anil laghwi mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2677,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 4,
      "text": "Wallazeena hum liz-Zakaati faa'iloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2678,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 5,
      "text": "Wallazeena hum lifuroo-jihim haafizoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2679,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Illaa 'alaaa azwaajihim aw maa malakat aimaanuhum fa-innahum ghairu maloomeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2680,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 7,
      "text": "Famanib taghaa waraaa'a zaalika fa-ulaaa'ika humul 'aadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2681,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 8,
      "text": "Wallazeena hum li-amaanaatihim Wa-'ahdihim raa'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2682,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 9,
      "text": "Wallazeena hum 'alaa Salawaatihim yuhaafizoon"
    },
    {"index": 2683, "sura": 23, "aya": 10, "text": "Ulaaa'ika humul waarisoon"},
    {
      "index": 2684,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 11,
      "text": "Allazeena yarisoonal Firdawsa hum feehaa khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2685,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 12,
      "text": "Wa-laqad khalaqnal insaana min sulaalatim min teen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2686,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 13,
      "text": "Summa ja'alnaahu nutfatan fee qaraarim makeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2687,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Summa khalaqnan nutfata 'alaqatan fakhalaqnal 'alaqata mudghatan fakhalaq-nal mudghata 'izaaman fakasawnal 'izaama lahman summa anshaanaahu khalqan aakhar; fatabaarakal laahu ahsanul khaaliqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2688,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 15,
      "text": "Summa innakum ba'da zaalika la-maaiyitoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2689,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 16,
      "text": "Summa innakum Yawmal Qiyaamati tub'asoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2690,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad khalaqnaa fawqakum sab'a taraaa'iqa Wa-maa kunnaa 'anil khalqi ghaafileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2691,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-anzalnaa minas samaaa'i maaa'am biqadarin fa-askannaahu fil ardi Wa-innaa 'alaa zahaabim bihee laqaa-diroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2692,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Fa-anshaanaa lakum bihee Jannaatim min nakheelinw Wa-a'naab; lakum feehaa fawaakihu kaseeratunw Wa-minhaa taakuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2693,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-shajaratan takhruju min Toori Sainaaa'a tambutu bidduhni Wa-sibghil lil-aakileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2694,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-inna lakum fil an'aami la'ibrah; nusqeekum mimmaa fee butoonihaa Wa-lakum feehaa manaafi'u kaseeratunw Wa-minhaa taakuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2695,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 22,
      "text": "Wa-'alaihaa wa'alal fulki tuhmaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2696,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad arsalnaa Noohan ilaa qawmihee faqaala yaa qawmi'budul laaha maa lakum min ilahin ghairuhoo afalaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2697,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Faqaalal mala'ul lazeena kafaroo min qawmihee maa haazaaa illaa basharum mislukum yureedu aien yatafaddala 'alaikum Wa-law shaaa'al laahu la-anzala malaaa'ikatam maa sami'naa bihaazaa feee aabaaa'inal awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2698,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "In huwa illaa rajulum bihee jinnatun fatarabbasoo bihee hattan heen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2699,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 26,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbin surnee bimaa kazzaboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2700,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Fa-awhainaaa ilaihi anis na'il fulka bi-a'yuninaa Wa-wahyinaa fa-izaa jaaa'a amrunaa Wa-faarat tannooru fasluk feehaa min kullin zawjainis naini Wa-ahlaka illaa man sabaqa 'alaihil qawlu minhum Wa-laa tukhaat-ibnee fil lazeena zalamooo innaahum mughraqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2701,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Fa-izas tawaita ata Wa-mam ma'aka 'alal fulki faqulil hamdu lillaahil lazee najjaanaa minal qawmiz zalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2702,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Wa-qur Rabbi anzilnee munzalam mubaarakanw Wa-Anta khairul munzileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2703,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 30,
      "text": "Inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatinw Wa-in kunnaa lamubtaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2704,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 31,
      "text": "Summaa anshaana mim ba'dihim qarnan aakhareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2705,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Fa-arsalnaa feehim Rasoolam minhum ani 'budul laaha maa lakum min ilaahin ghairuhoo afalaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2706,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal mala-u min qawmihil lazeena kafaroo Wa-kazzaboo bi-liqaaa'il Aakhirati Wa-atrafnaahum fil hayaatid dunyaa maa haazaaa illaa basharum mislukum yaakulu mimmaa taakuloona minhu Wa-yashrabu mimmaa tashraboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2707,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 34,
      "text": "Wa-la'in at'atum basharam mislakum innakum izal lakhaasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2708,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "A-Ya'idukum annakum izaa mittum Wa-kuntum turaabanw Wa-izaaman annakum mukhrajoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2709,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 36,
      "text": "Haihaata haihaata limaa too'adoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2710,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "In hiya illaa hayaatunad dunyaa namootu Wa-nahyaa Wa-maa nahnu bimab'ooseen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2711,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "In huwa illaa rajulunif taraa 'alal laahi kazibanw Wa-maa nahnuu lahoo bimu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2712,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 39,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbin surnee bimaa kazzaboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2713,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 40,
      "text": "Qaala 'ammaa qaleelil la-yusbihunna naadimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2714,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Fa-akhazat-humus saihatu bilhaqqi faja'alnaahum ghusaaa'aa; fabu;dal lilqaw-miz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2715,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 42,
      "text": "Summa anshaanaa mim ba'dihim quroonan aakhareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2716,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 43,
      "text": "Maa tasbiqu min ummatin ajalahaa Wa-maa yastaakhiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2717,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Summa arsalnaa Rusulanaa tatraa kulla maa jaaa'a ummatar Rasooluhaa kazzabooh; fa-atba'naa ba'dahum ba'danw Wa-ja'alnaahum ahaadees; fabu'dal liqawmil laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2718,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Summa arsalnaa Moosaa Wa-akhaahu Haaroona bi-Aayaatinaa Wa-sultaanim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2719,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 46,
      "text": "Ilaa Fir'awna Wa-mala'ihee fastakbaroo Wa-kaanoo qawman 'aaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2720,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Faqaaloo annu'minu libasharaini mislinaa Wa-qawmuhumaa lanaa 'aabidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2721,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 48,
      "text": "Fakazzaboohumaa fakaanoo minal muhlakeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2722,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 49,
      "text": "Wa-laqad aatainaa Moosal Kitaaba la'allahum yahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2723,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnab na Maryama Wa-ummahooo aayatannw Wa-aawainaahumaaa ilaa rabwatin zaati qaraarinw Wa-ma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 2724,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyuhar Rusulu kuloo minat taiyibaati wa'maloo saalihan innee bimaa ta'maloona 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2725,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-inna haaziheee ummatukum ummatanw waahidatanw Wa-Ana Rabbukum fattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2726,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Fataqatta'ooo amrahum bainahum zuburaa; kullu hizbim bimaa ladaihim farihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2727,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 54,
      "text": "Fazarhum fee ghamratihim hattaa heen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2728,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 55,
      "text": "A-yahsaboona annnamaa numiduhum bihee mim maalinw Wa-baneen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2729,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 56,
      "text": "Nusaari'u lahum fil khairaat; bal laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2730,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 57,
      "text": "Innal lazeena hum min khashyati Rabbihim mushfiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2731,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 58,
      "text": "Wallazeena hum bi-Aayaati Rabbihim yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2732,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 59,
      "text": "Wallazeena hum bi-Rabbihim laa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2733,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yu'toona maaa aataw Wa-quloobuhum wajilatun annahum ilaa Rabbihim raaji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2734,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 61,
      "text": "Ulaaa'ika yusaari'oona fil khairaati Wa-hum lahaa saabiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2735,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa nukallifu nafsan illaa wus'ahaa Wa-ladainaa kitaabuny yantiqu bilhaqqi Wa-ahum la yuzlamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2736,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Bal quloobuhum fee ghamratim min haazaa Wa-lahum a'maalum min dooni zaalika hum lahaa 'aamiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2737,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 64,
      "text": "Hattaaa izaaa akhaznaa mutrafeehim bil'azaabi izaa hum yaj'aroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2738,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 65,
      "text": "Laa taj'arul yawma innakum minnaa laa tunsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2739,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Qad kaanat Aayaatee tutlaa 'alaikum fakuntum 'alaaa a'qaabikum tankisoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2740,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 67,
      "text": "Mustakbireena bihee saamiran tahjuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2741,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Afalam yaddabbarrul qawla am jaaa'ahum maa lam yaati aabaaa'ahumul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2742,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 69,
      "text": "Am lam ya'rifoo Rasoolahum fahum lahoo munkiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2743,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Am yaqooloona bihee jinnnah; bal jaaa'ahum bilhaqqi Wa-aksaruhum lil-haqqi kaarihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2744,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wa-lawit taba'al haqqu ahwaaa'ahum lafasadatis samaawaatu wal-ardu Wa-man feehinnn; bal atainaahum bizikrihim fahum 'an zikrihim mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2745,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Am tas'aluhum kharjan fakharaaju Rabbika khairunw Wa-Huwa khairur raaziqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2746,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 73,
      "text": "Wa-innaka latad'oohum ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2747,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wa-innnal lazeena laa yu'minoona bil-Aakhirati 'anis siraati lanaakiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2748,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Wa-law rahimnaahum Wa-kashafnaa maa bihim min durril lalajjoo fee tughyaanihim ya'mahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2749,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad akhaznaahum bil'azaabi famas takaanoo li-Rabbihim Wa-maa yatadarra'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2750,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Hattaaa izaa fatahnaa 'alaihim baaban zaa 'azaabin shadeedin izaa hum feehi mublisoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2751,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazeee ansha-a lakumus sam'a wal-absaara wal-af'idah; qaleelam maa tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2752,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 79,
      "text": "Wa-Huwal lazee zara-akum fil ardi Wa-ilaihi tuhsharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2753,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee yuhyee Wa-yumeetu Wa-lahukh tilaaful laili wannahaar; afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2754,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 81,
      "text": "Bal qaaloo misla maa qaalal awwaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2755,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Qaalooo 'a-izaa mitnaa Wa-kunnaa turaabanw Wa-'izaaman 'a-innaa lamab-'oosoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2756,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Laqad wu'idnaa nahnu Wa-aabaaa'unaa haazaa min qablu in haazaaa illaaa asaateerul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2757,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 84,
      "text": "Qul limanil ardu Wa-man feehaaa in kuntum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2758,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 85,
      "text": "Sa-yaqooloona lillaah; qul afalaa tazakkkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2759,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 86,
      "text": "Qul mar Rabbus samaawaatis sab'i Wa-Rabbul 'Arshil 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2760,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 87,
      "text": "Sa-yaqooloona lillaah; qul afalaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2761,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Qul mam bi-yadihee malakootu kulli shai'inw Wa-Huwa yujeeru Wa-laa yujaaru 'alaihi in kuntum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2762,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 89,
      "text": "Sa-yaqooloona lillaah; qul fa-annaa tus-haroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2763,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 90,
      "text": "Bal atainaahum bil-haqqi Wa-innahum lakaaziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2764,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Mat takhazal laahu minw waladinw Wa-maa kaana ma'ahoo min ilaah; izal lazahaba kullu ilaahim bimaa khalaqa Wa-la'alaa ba'duhum 'alaa ba'd; Subhaannal laahi 'ammaa yasifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2765,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 92,
      "text": "Aalimil Ghaibi wash-shahhaadati fata'aalaa 'ammaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2766,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 93,
      "text": "Qur Rabbi immmaa turiyannee maa yoo'adoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2767,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 94,
      "text": "Rabbi falaa taj'alnee fil qawmiz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2768,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 95,
      "text": "Wa-innaa 'alaaa an nuriyaka maa na'iduhum laqaadiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2769,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 96,
      "text": "Idfa' billate hiya ahsanus saiyi'ah; nahnu a'lamu bimaa yasifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2770,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 97,
      "text": "Wa-qur Rabbi a'oozu bika min hamazaatish Shayaateen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2771,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 98,
      "text": "Wa-a'oozu bika Rabbi aien yahduroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2772,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 99,
      "text": "Hattaaa izaa jaaa'a ahada-humul mawtu qaala Rabbir ji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2773,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 100,
      "text":
          "La'alleee a'malu saalihan feemaa taraktu kallaa; innahaa kalimatun huwa qaaa'iluhaa Wa-minw waraaa'ihim barzakhun ilaa Yawmi yub'asoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2774,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 101,
      "text":
          "Fa-izaa nufikha fis Soori falaaa ansaaba bainahum yawma'izinw Wa-laa yatasaaa'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2775,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 102,
      "text": "Faman saqulat mawaazee-nuhoo fa-ulaaa'ika humul muflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2776,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 103,
      "text":
          "Wa-man khaffat mawaa-zeenuhoo fa-ulaaa'ikal lazeena khasiroo 'anfusahum fee Jahannama khaalidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2777,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 104,
      "text": "Talfahu wujoohahumun Naaru Wa-hum feehaa kaalihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2778,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 105,
      "text": "Alam takun Aayaatee tutlaa 'alaikum fakuntum bihaa tukazziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2779,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 106,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo Rabbanaa ghalabat 'alainaa shiqwatunaa Wa-kunnaa qawman daaalleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2780,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 107,
      "text": "Rabbanaa akhrijnaa minhaa fa-in 'udnaa fa-innaa zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2781,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 108,
      "text": "Qaalakh sa'oo feehaa Wa-laa tukallimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2782,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Innahoo kaana fareequm min 'ibaadee yaqooloona Rabbanaaa aamannaa faghfir lanaa warhamnaa Wa-Anta khairur raahimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2783,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 110,
      "text":
          "Fattakhaztumoohum sikhriyyan hattaaa ansawkum zikree Wa-kuntum minhum tadhakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2784,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 111,
      "text": "Inee jazaituhumul Yawma bimaa sabarooo annahum humul faaa'izoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2785,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 112,
      "text": "Qaala kam labistum fil ardi 'adada sineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2786,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 113,
      "text": "Qaaloo labisnaa yawman aw ba'da yawmin fas'alil 'aaaddeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2787,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 114,
      "text": "Qaala il labistum illaa qaleelal law annakum kuntum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2788,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 115,
      "text":
          "Afahsibtum annamaa khalaqnaakum 'abasanw Wa-annakum ilainaa laa turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2789,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 116,
      "text":
          "Fata'aalal laahul Malikul Haqq; laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa Rabbul 'Arshil Kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2790,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 117,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yad'u ma'allaahi ilaahan aakhara laa burhaana lahoo bihee fa-inna maa hisaabuhoo 'inda Rabbih; innahoo laa yuflihul kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2791,
      "sura": 23,
      "aya": 118,
      "text": "Wa-qul Rabbigh fir warham Wa-Anta khairur raahimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2792,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Sooratun anzalnaahaa Wa-faradnaahaa Wa-anzalnaa feehaaa Aayaatim baiyinaatil la'allakum tazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2793,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Azzaaniyatu wazzaanee fajlidoo kulla waahidim minhumaa mi'ata jaldatinw Wa-laa taakhuzkum bihimaa raafatun fee deenil laahi in kuntum tu'minoona billaahi wal-Yawmil Aakhiri wal-yashhad 'azaabahumaa taaa'ifatum minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2794,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Azzaanee laa yankihu illaa zaaniyatan aw mushrikatanw wazzaaniyatu laa yankihuhaaa illaa zaanin aw mushrik; Wa-hurrima zaalika 'alal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2795,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yarmoonal muhsanaati summa lam yaatoo bi-arba'ati shuhadaaa'a fajlidoohum samaaneena jaldatanw Wa-laa taqbaloo lahum shahaadatan abadaa; Wa-ulaaa'ika humul faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2796,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Illal lazeena taaboo mim ba'di zaalika Wa-aslahoo fa-innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2797,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yarmoona azwaajahum Wa-lam yakul lahum shuhadaaa'u illaaa anfusuhum fashahaadatu ahadihim arba'u shahaadaatim billaahi innahoo laminas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2798,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wal-khaamisatu anna la'natal laahi 'alaihi in kaana minal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2799,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Wa-yadra'u anhal 'azaaba an tashhada arba'a shahaa-daatim billaahi innahoo laminal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2800,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wal-khaamisata anna ghadabal laahi 'alaihaaa in kaana minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2801,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-law-laa fadlul laahi 'alaikum Wa-rahmatuhoo Wa-annal laaha Tawwaabun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2802,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena jaaa'oo bilifki 'usbatum minkum; laa tahsaboohu sharral lakum bal huwa khairul lakum; likul limri'im minhum mak tasaba minal ism; wallazee tawallaa kibrahoo minhum lahoo 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2803,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Law-laaa iz sami'tumoohu zannal mu'minoona walmu'minaatu bi-anfusihim khairanw Wa-qaaloo haazaaa ifkum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2804,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Law-laa jaaa'oo 'alaihi bi-arba'ati shuhadaaa'; fa-iz lam yaatoo bishshuhadaaa'i fa-ulaaa-'ika 'indal laahi humul kaaziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2805,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-law-laa fadlul laahi 'alaikum Wa-rahmatuhoo fiddunyaa wal aakhirati lamassakum fee maaa afadtum feehi 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2806,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Iz talaqqawnahoo bi-alsinatikum Wa-taqooloona bi-afwaahikum maa laisa lakum bihee 'ilmunw Wa-tahsaboo-nahoo haiyinanw Wa-huwa 'indal laahi 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2807,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wa-law-laaa iz sami'tu-moohu qultum maa yakoonu lanaaa an natakallama bihaazaa Subhaanaka haaza buhtaanun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2808,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Ya'izukumul laahu an ta'oodoo limisliheee abadan in kuntum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2809,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 18,
      "text": "Wa-yubaiyinul laahu lakumul Aayaat; wallaahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2810,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yuhibboona an tashee'al faahishatu fil lazeena aamanoo lahum 'azaabun aleemun fid dunyaa wal-Aakhirah; wallaahu ya'lamu Wa-antum laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2811,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-law-laa fadlul laahi 'alaikum Wa-rahmatuhoo Wa-annal laaha Ra'oofur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2812,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Yaaa aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tattabi'oo khutuwaatish Shaitaan; Wa-many-yattabi' khutuwaatish Shaitaani fa-innahoo yaamuru bilfahshaaa'i walmunkar; Wa-law laa fadlul laahi 'alaikum Wa-rahmatuhoo maa zakaa minkum min ahadin abadanw Wa-laakinnal laaha yuzakkee many-yashaaa'; wallaahu Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2813,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yaatali ulul fadli minkum wassa'ati ai yu'tooo ulil qurbaa walmasaakeena walmuhaajireena fee sabeelillaahi walya'foo walyasfahoo; alaa tuhibboona aien yaghfiral laahu lakum; wal laahu Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2814,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yarmoonal muhsanaatil ghaafilaatil mu'minaati lu'inoo fid dunyaa wal-Aakhirati Wa-lahum 'azaabun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2815,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Yawma tashhhadu 'alaihim alsinatuhum Wa-aideehim Wa-arjuluhum bimaa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2816,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Yawma'izien yuwaf-feehimul laahu deenahumul haqqa Wa-ya'lamoona annal laaha Huwal Haqqul Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2817,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Al-khabeesaatu lil-khabeeseena wal-khabeesoona lil-khabeesaati wat-taiyibaatu lit-taiyibeena wat-taiyiboona lit-taiyibaat; ulaaa'ika mubarra'oona mimma yaqooloona lahum maghfiratunw Wa-rizqun kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2818,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tadkhuloo buyootan ghaira buyootikum hatta tastaanisoo Wa-tusallimoo 'allaa ahlihaa; zaalikum khairul lakum la'allakum tazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2819,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Fa-il lam tajidoo feehaaa ahadan falaa tadkhuloohaa hattaa yu'zana lakum Wa-in qeela lakumur ji'oo farji'oo huwa azkaa lakum; wallaahu bimaa ta'maloona 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2820,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Laisa 'alaikum junaahun ann tadkhuloo buyootan ghaira maskoonatin feeha mataa'ul lakum; wallaahu ya'lamu maa tubdoona Wa-maa taktumoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2821,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Qul lilmu' mineena yaghuuddoo min absaarihim Wa-yahfazoo furoojahum; zaalika azkaa lahum; innallaaha khabeerum bimaa yasna'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2822,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa qul lilmu'minaati yaghdudna min absaarihinna Wa-yahfazna furoojahunna Wa-laa yubdeena zeenatahunna illaa maa zahara minhaa walyadribna bikhumurihinna 'alaa juyoobihinna Wa-laa yubdeena zeenatahunna illaa libu'oolatihinna aw aabaaa'i hinna aw aabaaa'i bu'oolati hinna aw abnaaa'ihinaa aw abnaaa'i bu'oolatihinnna aw ikhwaanihinnna aw baneee ikhwaanihinna aw banee akhawaatihinna aw nisaaa'i hinna aw maa malakat aimaanuhunna awit taabi'eena ghairi ilil irbati minar rijaali awit tiflillazeena lam yazharoo 'alaa 'awraatin nisaaa'i wala yadribnna bi arjulihinna min zeenatihinn; Wa-toobooo ilallaahi jammee'an aiyuhal mu'minoona la'allakum tuflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2823,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wa-ankihul ayaamaa minkum was-saaliheena min 'ibaadikum Wa-imaa'kum; ien yakoonoo fuqaraaa'a yughni-himul laahu min fadlih; wal-laahu Waasi'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2824,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wal-yasta'fifil lazeena laa yajidoona nikaahan hatta yughniyahumul laahu min fadlih; wallazeena yabtaghoonal kitaaba mimmaa malakat aimaanukum fakaatiboohum in 'alimtum feehim khairanw Wa-aatoohum mim maalil laahil lazeee aataakum; Wa-laa tukrihoo fatayaatikum 'alal bighaaa'i in aradna tahassunal litabtaghoo 'aradal hayaatid dunyaa; Wa-mai yukrihhunna fa-innal laaha mim ba'di ikraahihinna Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2825,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad anzalnaaa ilaikum Aayaatim mubaiyinaatinw Wa-masalam minnal lazeena khalaw min qablikum Wa-maw'izatal lilmuttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2826,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Allaahu noorus samaawaati wal-ard; masalu noorihee kamishkaatin feehaa misbaah; almisbaahu fee zujaajatin azzujaajatu ka-annahaa kawkabun durriyyuien yooqadu min shajaratim mubaarakatin zaitoonatil laa shariqiyyatinw Wa-laa gharbiyyatien yakaadu zaituhaa yudeee'u Wa-law lam tamsashu naar; noorun 'alaa noor; yahdil laahu linoorihee mai yashaaa'; Wa-yadribul laahul amsaala linnaas; wallaahu bikulli shai'in Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2827,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Fee buyootin azinal laahu an turfa'a Wa-yuzkara feehas muhoo yusabbihu lahoo feehaa bilghuduwwi wal-aasaal"
    },
    {
      "index": 2828,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Rijaalul laa tulheehim tijaaratunw Wa-laa bai'un 'an zikril laahi Wa-iqaamis Salaati Wa-eetaaa'iz Zakaati yakhaafoona Yawman tataqallabu feehil quloobu wal-absaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 2829,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Liyajziyahumul laahu ahsana maa 'amiloo Wa-yazeedahum min fadlih; wal-laahu yarzuqu maien yashaaa'u bighairi hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 2830,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kafarooo a'maaluhum kasaraabim biqee'atien yahsabuhuz zamaanu maaa'an hattaaa izaa jaaa'ahoo lam yajid-hu shai'anw Wa-wajadal laaha 'indahoo fa-waffaahu hisaabah; wallaahu saree'ul hisaab"
    },
    {
      "index": 2831,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Aw kazulumaatin fee bahril lujjiyyiny yaghshaahu mawjun min fawqihee mawjun min fawqihee sahaab; zulumatun ba'duhaa fawqa ba'din izaaa akhraja yadahoo lam yakad yaraahaa Wa-man lam yaj'alil laahu lahoo nooran famaa lahoo min noor"
    },
    {
      "index": 2832,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annal laaha yusabbihu lahoo man fissamaawaati wal-ardi wat tairu saaaffaatim kullun qad 'alima Salaatahoo Wa-tasbeehah; wallaahu 'aleemum bimaa yaf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2833,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 42,
      "text": "Wa-lillaahi mulkus samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-ilal laahil maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2834,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annal laaha yuzjee sahaaban summa yu'allifu bainahoo summa yaj'aluhoo rukaaman fataral wadqa yakhruju min khilaalihee Wa-yunazzilu minas samaaa'i min jibaalin feehaa mim baradin fa-yuseebu bihee maien yashaaa'u Wa-yasrifuhoo 'am maien yashaaa'u yakaadu sanaa barqihee yazhabu bil-absaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 2835,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Yuqallibul laahul laila wannahaar; inna fee zaalika la'ibratal li-ulil absaar"
    },
    {
      "index": 2836,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu khalaqa kulla daaabbatim mim maaa'in faminhum mai yamshee 'alaa batnihee Wa-minhum mai yamshee 'alaa rijlaine Wa-minhum maien yamshee 'alaaa arba'; yakhluqul laahu maa yashaaa'; innal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2837,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Laqad anzalnaaa Aayaatim mubaiyinaat; wallaahu yahdee mai yashaaa'u ilaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2838,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaqooloona aamannaa billaahi Wa-bir-Rasooli Wa-ata'naa summa yatawallaa fareequm minhum mim ba'di zaalik; Wa-maaa ulaaa'ika bilmu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2839,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa du'ooo ilal laahi Wa-Rasoolihee li-yahkuma bainahum izaa fareequm minhum mu'ridoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2840,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 49,
      "text": "Wa-ien yakul lahumul haqqu yaatooo ilaihi muz'ineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2841,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Afee quloobihim ma-radun amir taabooo am yakhaafoona aien yaheefal laahu 'alaihim Wa-Rasooluh; bal ulaaa'ika humuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2842,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Innamaa kaana qawlal mu'mineena izaa du'ooo ilal laahi Wa-Rasoolihee li-yahkuma bainahum ai yaqooloo sami'naa Wa-ata'naa; Wa-ulaaa'ika humul muflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2843,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yuti'il laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo Wa-yakhshal laaha Wa-yattaqhi fa-ulaaa'ika humul faaa'izoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2844,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-aqsamoo billaahi jahda aimaanihim la'in amartahum la-yakhrujunna qul laa tuqsimoo taa'atum ma'roofah innal laaha khabeerum bimaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2845,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Qul atee'ul laaha Wa-atee'ur Rasoola fa-in tawallaw fa-innamaa 'alaihi maa hummila Wa-'alaikum maa hummiltum Wa-in tutee'oohu tahtadoo; Wa-maa 'alar Rasooli illal balaaghul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2846,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Wa'adal laahul lazeena aamanoo minkum Wa-'amilus saalihaati la-yastakh-lifan-nahum fil ardi kamastakh lafal lazeena min qablihim Wa-la-yumakki-nanna lahum deenahumul lazir tadaa lahum Wa-la-yubaddi-lannahum mim ba'di khawfihim amnaa; ya'budoona-nee laa yushrikoona bee shai'aa; Wa-man kafara ba'da zaalika fa-ulaaa'ika humul faasiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2847,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Wa-aqeemus Salaata Wa-aatuz Zakaata Wa-atee'ur Rasoola la'allakum turhamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2848,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Laa tahsabannal lazeena kafaroo mu'jizeena fil ard; Wa-maawaahumun Naaru Wa-labi'sal maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 2849,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo li-yasta'zinkumul lazeena malakat aimaanukum wallazeena lam yablughul huluma minkum salaasa marraat; min qabli Salaatil Fajri Wa-heena tada'oona siyaa-bakum minaz zaheerati Wa-min ba'di Salaatil Ishaaa'; salaasu 'awraatil lakum; laisa 'alaikum Wa-laa 'alaihim junaahun ba'dahunn; tawwaafoona 'alaikum ba'dukum 'alaa ba'd; kazaalika yubaiyyinul laahu lakumul aayaat; wallahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2850,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa balaghal atfaalu minkumul huluma fal-yasta'zinoo kamas ta'zanal lazeena min qablihim; kazaalika yubaiyinul laahu lakum Aayaatih; wallaahu 'Aleemun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2851,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Walqawaa'idu minan nisaaa'il laatee laa yarjoona nikaahan fa-laisa 'alaihinna junaahun aien yada'na siyaabahunna ghaira mutabarrijaatin bi-zeenah; Wa-aien yasta'fif-na khairul lahunn; wallaahu Samee'un 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2852,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Laisa 'alal a'maa harajunw Wa-laa 'alal a'raji harajunw Wa-laa 'alal mareedi harajun Wa-laa 'alaa anfusikum 'an ta'kuloo min buyootikum aw buyooti aabaaa'ikum aw buyooti ummahaatikum aw buyooti ikhwaanikum aw buyooti akhawaatikum aw buyooti a'maamikum aw buyooti 'ammaatikum aw buyooti akhwaalikum aw buyooti khaalaatikum aw maa malaktum mafaatihahooo aw sadeeqikum; laisa 'alaikum junaahun 'an ta'kuloo jamee'an aw ashtaata; fa-izaa dakhaltum buyootan fa-sallimoo 'alaaa anfusikum tahiyyatan min 'indil laahi mubaarakatan taiyyibah; kazaalika yubai-yyinul laahu lakumul Aayaati la'allakum ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2853,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Innamal mu'minoonal lazeena aamanoo billaahi Wa-Rasoolihee Wa-izaa kaanoo ma'ahoo 'alaaa amrin jaami'il lam yazhaboo hattaa yasta'zinooh; innal lazeena yasta'zinoonaka ulaaa'ikal lazeena yu'minoona billaahi Wa-Rasoolih; fa-izas ta'zanooka li-ba'di sha'nihim fa'zal liman shi'ta minhum wastaghfir lahumul laah; innal laaha Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2854,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Laa taj'aloo du'aaa'ar Rasooli bainakum ka-du'aaa'i ba'dikum ba'daa; qad ya'lamul laahul lazeena yatasallaloona minkum liwaazaa; fal-yahzaril lazeena yukhaalifoona 'an amriheee 'an tuseebahum fitnatun aw yuseebahum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2855,
      "sura": 24,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Alaaa inna lillaahi maa fis samaawaati wal-ardi qad ya'lamu maaa antum 'alaihi Wa-Yawma yurja'oona ilaihi fa-yunabbi'uhum bimaa 'amiloo; wallaahu bikulli shai'in 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2856,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Tabaarakal lazee nazzalal Furqaana 'alaa 'abdihee li-yakoona lil'aalameena nazeera"
    },
    {
      "index": 2857,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Allazee lahoo mulkus samaawaati wal ardi Wa-lam yattakhiz waladanw Wa-lam yakul lahoo shareekun filmulki Wa-khalaqa kulla shai'in faqaddarahoo taqdeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2858,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Wattakhazoo min dooniheee aalihatal laa yakhluqoona shai'anw Wa-hum yukhlaqoona Wa-laa yamlikoona li-anfusihim darranw Wa-laa naf'anw Wa-laa yamlikoona mawtanw Wa-laa hayaatanw Wa-laa nushooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2859,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena kafarooo in haazaaa illaaa ifkunif taraahu Wa-a'aanahoo 'alaihi qawmun aakharoona faqad jaaa'oo zulmanw Wa-zooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2860,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalooo asaateerul awwaleenak tatabahaa fahiya tumlaa 'alaihi bukratanw Wa-aseelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2861,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Qul anzalhul lazee ya'lamus sirra fis samaawaati wal-ard; innahoo kaana Ghafoorar Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2862,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo maa-li haazar Rasooli ya'kulut ta'aama Wa-yamshee fil aswaaq; law-laaa unzila ilaihi malakun fa-yakoona ma'ahoo nazeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2863,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Aw yulqaaa ilaihi kanzun aw takoonu lahoo jannatuien ya'kulu minhaa; Wa-qaalaz zaalimoona in tattabi'oona illaa rajulan mas-hooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2864,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Unzur kaifa daraboo lakal amsaala fadalloo falaa yastatee'oona sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2865,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Tabaarakal lazeee in shaaa'a ja'ala laka khairan min zaalika jannaatin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru Wa-yaj'al laka qusooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2866,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Bal kazzaboo bis-Saa'ati Wa-a'tadnaa liman kazzaba bis-Saa'ati sa'eeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2867,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Izaa ra'at-hum min makaanin ba'eedin sami'oo lahaa taghaiyuzanw Wa-zafeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2868,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaaa ulqoo minhaa makaanan daiyyiqam muqar-raneena da'aw hunaalika thuboora"
    },
    {
      "index": 2869,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 14,
      "text": "Laa tad'ul yawma thubooranw waahidanw wad'oo thubooran kaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2870,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Qul azaalika khairun am Jannatul khuldil latee wu'idal muttaqoon; kaanat lahum jazaaa'anw Wa-maseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2871,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Lahum feehaa maa yashaaa'oona khaalideen; kaana 'alaa Rabbika wa'dan mas'oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2872,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma yahshuruhum Wa-maa ya'budoona min doonil laahi fa-yaqoolu 'a-antum adlaltum 'ibaadee haaa'ulaaa'i am hum dallus sabeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 2873,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo Subhaanaka maa kaana yanbaghee lanaaa an nattakhiza min doonika min awliyaaa'a Wa-laakin matta'tahum Wa-aabaaa'ahum hattaa nasooz zikra Wa-kaanoo qawman booraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2874,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Faqad kazzabookum bimaa taqooloona famaa tastatee'oona sarfanw Wa-laa nasraa; Wa-many yazlim minkum nuziqhu 'azaaban kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2875,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaa qablaka minal mursaleena illaaa innahum la-ya'kuloonat ta'aama Wa-yamshoona fil aswaaq; Wa-ja'alnaa ba'dakum liba'din fitnatan atasbiroon; Wa-kaana Rabbuka Baseera"
    },
    {
      "index": 2876,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena laa yarjoona liqaaa'anaa law-laaa unzila 'alainal malaaa'ikatu aw naraa Rabbanaa; laqadis takbaroo feee anfusihim Wa-'ataw 'utuwwan kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2877,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Yawma yarawnal malaaa-'ikata laa bushraa Yawmaizin lil-mujrimeena Wa-yaqooloona hijran mahjooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2878,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa qadimnaaa ilaa maa 'amiloo min 'amalin faja'alnaahuhabaaa'an manthooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2879,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "As-haabul jannati yawma'izin khairun mustaqar-ranw Wa-ahsanu maqeela"
    },
    {
      "index": 2880,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma tashaqqaqus samaaa'u bilghamaami Wa-nuzzilal malaaa'ikatu tanzeela"
    },
    {
      "index": 2881,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Almulku Yawma'izinil haqqu lir Rahmaan; Wa-kaana Yawman'alal kaafireena 'aseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2882,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma ya'adduz zaalimu 'alaa yadaihi yaqoolu yaa-laitanit takhaztu ma'ar Rasooli sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2883,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 28,
      "text": "Yaa-wailataa laitanee lam attakhiz fulaanan khaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2884,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Laqad adallanee 'aniz zikri ba'da iz jaaa'anee; Wa-kaanash Shaitaanu lil-insaani khazoolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2885,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalar Rasoolu yaa-Rabbi inna qawmit takhazoo haazal Qur'aana mahjooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2886,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika ja'alnaa likulli Nabiyyin 'aduwwan minal mujrimeen; Wa-kafaa bi-Rabbika haadiyanw Wa-naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2887,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena kafaroo law-laa nuzzila 'alaihil Qur'aanu jumlatanw waahidah; kazaalika linusabbita bihee fu'aadaka Wa-rattalnaahu tarteelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2888,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa ya'toonaka bi-masalin illaa ji'naaka bilhaqqi Wa-ahsana tafseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2889,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yuhsharoona 'alaa wujoohihim ilaa jahannama ulaaa'ika sharrun makaananw Wa-adallu sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2890,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Moosal Kitaaba Wa-ja'alnaa ma'ahooo akhaahu Haaroona wazeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2891,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Faqulnaz habaaa ilal qawmil lazeena kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa fadammarnaahum tadmeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2892,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-qawma Noohin lammaa kazzabur Rusula aghraqnaahum Wa-ja'alnaahum linnaasi Aayatanw Wa-a'tadnaa lizzaalimeena 'azaaban aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2893,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wa-'Aadanw Wa-Samooda Wa-As-haabar Rassi Wa-quroonan baina zaalika katheeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2894,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 39,
      "text": "Wa-kullan darabnaa lahul amsaala Wa-kullan tabbarnaa tatbeera"
    },
    {
      "index": 2895,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad ataw 'alal qaryatil lateee umtirat mataras saw'; afalam yakoonoo yarawnahaa; bal kaanoo laa yarjoona nushooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2896,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa ra-awka ien yattakhizoonaka illaa huzuwan ahaazal lazee ba'asal laahu Rasoolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2897,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "In kaada la-yudillunaa 'an aalihatinaa law-laaa an sabarnaa 'alaihaa; Wa-sawfa ya'lamoona heena yarawnal 'azaaba man adallu sabeela"
    },
    {
      "index": 2898,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Ara'aita manit takhaza ilaahahoo hawaahu afa-anta takoonu 'alaihi wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2899,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Am tahsabu anna aksarahum yasma'oona aw ya'qiloon; in hum illaa kal-an'aami bal hum adallu sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2900,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Alam tara ilaa Rabbika kaifa maddaz zilla Wa-law shaaa'a la-ja'alahoo saakinan thumma ja'alnash shamsa 'alaihi daleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2901,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 46,
      "text": "Thumma qabadnaahu ilainaa qabdany yaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2902,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee ja'ala lakumul laila libaasanw wannawma subaatanw Wa-ja'alan nahaara nushooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2903,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazeee arsalar riyaaha bushran baina yadai rahmatih; Wa-anzalnaa minas samaaa'i maaa'an tahooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2904,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Linuhyiya bihee baldatan maitanw-wa nusqiyahoo mimmaa khalaqnaaa an'aamanw Wa-anaasiyya katheeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2905,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad sarrafnaahu bainahum li-yazzakkaroo fa-abaaa aksarun naasi illaa kufooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2906,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 51,
      "text": "Wa-law shi'naa laba'asnaa fee kulli qaryatin nazeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2907,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 52,
      "text": "Falaa tuti'il kaafireena Wa-jaahidhum bihee jihaadan kabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2908,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee marajal bahraini haazaa 'azbun furaatunw Wa-haazaa milhun ujaaj; Wa-ja'ala bainahumaa barzakhanw Wa-hijran mahjooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2909,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee khalaqa minal maaa'i basharan fa-ja'alahoo nasaban Wa-sihraa; Wa-kaana Rabbuka Qadeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2910,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Wa-ya'budoona min doonil laahi maa laa yanfa'uhum Wa-laa yadurruhum; Wa-kaanal kaafiru 'alaa Rabbihee zaheeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2911,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 56,
      "text": "Wa-maa arsalnaaka illaa mubashshiranw Wa-nazeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2912,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Qul maaa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin illaa man shaaa'a ai yattakhiza ilaa Rabbihee sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2913,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-tawakkal 'alal Haiyil lazee laa yamootu Wa-sabbih bihamdih; Wa-kafaa bihee bizunoobi 'ibaadihee khabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2914,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Allazee khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda Wa-maa bainahumaa fee sittati aiyaamin thumma stawaa 'alal 'Arsh; ar-Rahmaanu fas'al bihee khabeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2915,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahumus judoo lir-Rahmaani qaaloo Wa-mar Rahmaanu 'a-nasjudu limaa ta'murunaa Wa-zaadahum nufooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2916,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Tabaarakal lazee ja'ala fis samaaa'i buroojanw Wa-ja'ala feehaa siraajanw Wa-qamaran muneeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2917,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Wa-huwal lazee ja'alal laila wannahaara khilfatan liman araada 'any yazzakkara aw araadaa shukooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2918,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Wa-'ibaadur Rahmaanil lazeena yamshoona 'alal ardi hawnanw Wa-izaa khaata-bahumul jaahiloona qaaloo salaamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2919,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 64,
      "text": "Wallazeena yabeetoona li-Rabbihim sujjadanw Wa-qiyaamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2920,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yaqooloona Rabbanas rif 'annaa 'azaaba Jahannama inna 'azaabahaa kaana gharaamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2921,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 66,
      "text": "Innahaa saaa'at mustaqarranw Wa-muqaamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2922,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena izaaa anfaqoo lam yusrifoo Wa-lam yaqturoo Wa-kaana baina zaalika qawaamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2923,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena laa yad'oona ma'al laahi ilaahan aakhara Wa-laa yaqtuloonan nafsal latee harramal laahu illaa bilhaqqi Wa-laa yaznoon; Wa-mai yaf'al zaalika yalqa 'athaamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2924,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Yudaa'af lahul 'azaabu Yawmal Qiyaamati Wa-yakhlud feehee muhaanaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2925,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Illaa man taaba Wa-'aamana Wa-'amila 'amalan saalihan fa-ulaaa'ika yubad-dilul laahu saiyyi-aatihim hasanaat; Wa-kaanal laahu Ghafoorar Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2926,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Wa-man taaba Wa-'amila saalihan fa-innahoo yatoobu ilal laahi mataabaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2927,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena laa yash-hadoonaz zoora Wa-izaa marroo billaghwi marroo kiraamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2928,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena izaa zukkiroo bi-Aayaati Rabbihim lam yakhirroo 'alaihaa summanw wa'umyaanaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2929,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yaqooloona Rabbanaa hab lanaa min azwaajinaa Wa-zurriyaatinaa qurrata a'yuninw waj-'alnaa lilmuttaqeena Imaamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2930,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika yujzawnal ghurfata bimaa sabaroo Wa-yulaqqawna feehaa tahiyyatanw Wa-salaamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2931,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 76,
      "text": "Khaalideena feehaa; hasunat mustaqarranw Wa-muqaamaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 2932,
      "sura": 25,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Qul maa ya'ba'u bikum Rabbee law-laa du'aaa'ukum faqad kazzabtum fasawfa yakoonu lizaamaa"
    },
    {"index": 2933, "sura": 26, "aya": 1, "text": "Taa-Seeen-Meeem"},
    {
      "index": 2934,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Tilka Aayaatul Kitaabil Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2935,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "La'allaka baakhi'un nafsaka allaa yakoonoo mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2936,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "In nashaa nunazzil 'alaihim minas samaaa'i Aayatan fazallat a'naaquhum lahaa khaadi'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 2937,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa yaateehim min zikrim minar Rahmaani muhdasin illaa kaanoo 'anhu mu'rideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2938,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Faqad kazzaboo fasa-yaateehim ambaaa'u maa kaanoo bihee yastahzi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2939,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Awa-lam yaraw ilal ardi kam ambatnaa feehaa min kulli zawjin kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2940,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 8,
      "text": "Inna fee zaalika la-Aayah; Wa-maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2941,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 9,
      "text": "Wa-inna Rabbaka la-Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2942,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 10,
      "text": "Wa-iz naadaa Rabbuka Moosaaa ani' til qawmaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2943,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 11,
      "text": "Qawma Fir'awn; alaa yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2944,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 12,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbi inneee akhaafu ai yukazziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2945,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-yadeequ sadree Wa-laa yantaliqu lisaanee fa-arsil ilaa Haaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2946,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 14,
      "text": "Wa-lahum 'alaiya zambun fa-akhaafu ai yaqtuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2947,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 15,
      "text": "Qaala kallaa fazhabaa bi-Aayaatinaaa innaa ma'akum mustami'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2948,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 16,
      "text": "Faatiyaa Fir'awna faqoolaaa innaa Rasoolu Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2949,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 17,
      "text": "An arsil ma'anaa Baneee Israaa'eel"
    },
    {
      "index": 2950,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Qaala alam nurabbika feenaa waleedanw Wa-labista feenaa min 'umurika sineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2951,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 19,
      "text": "Wa-fa'alta fa'latakal latee fa'alta Wa-anta minal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2952,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 20,
      "text": "Qaala fa'altuhaaa izanw Wa-ana minad daaaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2953,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Fafarartu minkum lam-maa khiftukum fawahaba lee Rabbee hukmanw Wa-ja'alanee minal mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2954,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-tilka ni'matun tamun-nuhaa 'alaiya an 'abbatta Baneee Israaa'eel"
    },
    {
      "index": 2955,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 23,
      "text": "Qaala Fir'awnu Wa-maa Rabbul 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2956,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbus samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-maa bainahumaa in kuntum mooqineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2957,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 25,
      "text": "Qaala liman hawlahooo alaa tastami'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2958,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 26,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbukum Wa-Rabbu aabaaa'ikumul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2959,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 27,
      "text": "Qaala inna Rasoolakumul lazee ursila ilaikum lamajnoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2960,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbul mashriqi wal-maghribi Wa-maa baina-humaa in kuntum ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2961,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Qaala la'init takhazta ilaahan ghairee la-aj'alannaka minal masjooneen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2962,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 30,
      "text": "Qaala awalaw ji'tuka bishai'im mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2963,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 31,
      "text": "Qaala faati biheee in kunta minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2964,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 32,
      "text": "Fa-alqaa 'asaahu fa-izaaa hiya su'baanum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2965,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 33,
      "text": "Wa-naza'a yadahoo faizaa hiya baidaaa'u linnaa-zireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2966,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 34,
      "text": "Qaala lilmala-i hawlahooo inna haazaa lasaahirun 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2967,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Yureedu aien yukhrijakum min ardikum bisihrihee famaazaa taamuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2968,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 36,
      "text": "Qaalooo arjih Wa-akhaahu wab'as fil madaaa'ini haashireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2969,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 37,
      "text": "Yaatooka bikulli sah-haarin 'aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2970,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 38,
      "text": "Fa-jumi'as saharatu limeeqaati Yawmim ma'loom"
    },
    {
      "index": 2971,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 39,
      "text": "Wa-qeela linnaasi hal antum mujtami'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2972,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 40,
      "text": "La'allanaa nattabi'us saharata in kaanoo humul ghaalibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2973,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'as saharatu qaaloo li-Fir'awna a'inna lanaa la-ajjran in kunnaa nahnul ghaalibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2974,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 42,
      "text": "Qaala na'am Wa-innakum izal laminal muqarrabeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2975,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 43,
      "text": "Qaala lahum Moosaaa alqoo maaa antum mulqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2976,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Fa-alqaw hibaalahum Wa-'isiyyahum Wa-qaaloo bi'izzati Fir'awna innaa lanahnul ghaaliboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2977,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 45,
      "text": "Fa-alqaa Moosaa 'asaahu fa-izaa hiya talqafu maa yaafikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2978,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 46,
      "text": "Fa-ulqiyas saharatu saajideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2979,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 47,
      "text": "Qaalooo aamannaa bi-Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {"index": 2980, "sura": 26, "aya": 48, "text": "Rabbi Moosaa Wa-Haaroon"},
    {
      "index": 2981,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Qaala aamantum lahoo qabla an aazana lakum innahoo lakabeerukumul lazee 'alla-makumus sihra falasawfa ta'lamoon; la-uqatti'anna aidiyakum Wa-arjulakum min khilaafinw Wa-la-usallibanna-kum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 2982,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 50,
      "text": "Qaaloo la daira innaaa ilaa Rabbinaa munqalliboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2983,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Innaa natma'u aien yaghfira lanaa Rabbunna khataa-yaanaaa an kunnaaa awwalal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2984,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-awhainaaa ilaa Moosaaa an asri bi'ibaadeee innakum muttaba'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2985,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 53,
      "text": "Fa-arsala Fir'awnu fil madaaa'ini haashireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2986,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 54,
      "text": "Inna haaa'ulaaa'i lashir-zimatun qaleeloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2987,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 55,
      "text": "Wa-innahum lanaa laghaaa'izoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2988,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 56,
      "text": "Wa-innaa lajamee'un haaziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2989,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 57,
      "text": "Fa-akhrajnaahum min Jannaatinw Wa-'uyoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2990,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 58,
      "text": "Wa-kunoozinw Wa-ma-qaamin kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2991,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 59,
      "text": "Kazaalika Wa-awrasnaahaa Baneee Israaa'eel"
    },
    {"index": 2992, "sura": 26, "aya": 60, "text": "Fa-atba'oohum mushriqeen"},
    {
      "index": 2993,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Falammaa taraaa'al jam'aani qaala as-haabu Moosaaa innaa lamudrakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 2994,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 62,
      "text": "Qaala kallaaa inna ma'iya Rabbee sa-yahdeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2995,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Fa-awhainaaa ilaa Moosaaa anid rib bi'asaakal bahra fanfalaqa fakaana kullu firqin kattawdil 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 2996,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 64,
      "text": "Wa-azlafnaa sammal aakhareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 2997,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 65,
      "text": "Wa-anjainaa Moosaa Wa-mam ma'ahooo ajma'een"
    },
    {"index": 2998, "sura": 26, "aya": 66, "text": "Summa aghraqnal aakhareen"},
    {
      "index": 2999,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 67,
      "text": "Inna fee zaalika la-Aayaah; Wa-maa kaana aksaru-hu mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3000,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 68,
      "text": "Wa-inna Rabbaka la-Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3001,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 69,
      "text": "Watlu 'alaihim naba-a Ibraaheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3002,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 70,
      "text": "Iz qaala li-abeehi Wa-qawmihee maa ta'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3003,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 71,
      "text": "Qaaloo na'budu asnaaman fanazallu lahaa 'aakifeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3004,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 72,
      "text": "Qaala hal yasma'oona-kum iz tad'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3005,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 73,
      "text": "Aw yanfa'oonakum aw yadurroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3006,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 74,
      "text": "Qaaloo bal wajadnaaa aabaaa-'anaa kazaalika yaf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3007,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 75,
      "text": "Qaala afara-'aitum maa kuntum ta'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3008,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 76,
      "text": "Antum Wa-aabaaa'ukumul aqdamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3009,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 77,
      "text": "Fa-innahum 'aduwwwul leee illaa Rabbal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3010,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 78,
      "text": "Allazee khalaqanee fa-Huwa yahdeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3011,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 79,
      "text": "Wallazee Huwa yut'imunee Wa-yasqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3012,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 80,
      "text": "Wa-izaa maridtu fahuwa yashfeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3013,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 81,
      "text": "Wallazee yumeetunee summa yuhyeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3014,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 82,
      "text": "Wallazeee atma'u aien yaghfira lee khateee'-atee Yawmad Deen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3015,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 83,
      "text": "Rabbi hab lee hukmanw Wa-alhiqnee bis-saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3016,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 84,
      "text": "Waj'al lee lisaana sidqin fil aakhireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3017,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 85,
      "text": "Waj'alnee minw warasati Jannnatin Na'eem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3018,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 86,
      "text": "Waghfir li-abeee innahoo kaana mind daalleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3019,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 87,
      "text": "Wa-laa tukhzinee Yawma yub'asoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3020,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 88,
      "text": "Yawma laa yanfa'u maalunw Wa-laa banoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3021,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 89,
      "text": "Illaa man atal laaha biqalbin saleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3022,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 90,
      "text": "Wa-uzlifatil Jannatu lilmuttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3023,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 91,
      "text": "Wa-burrizatil Jaheemu lilghaaween"
    },
    {
      "index": 3024,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 92,
      "text": "Wa-qeela lahum aina maa kuntum ta'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3025,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 93,
      "text": "Min doonil laahi hal yansuroonakum aw yantasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3026,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 94,
      "text": "Fakubkiboo feehaa hum walghaawoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3027,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 95,
      "text": "Wa-junoodu Ibleesa ajma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3028,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 96,
      "text": "Qaaloo Wa-hum feehaa yakkhtasimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3029,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 97,
      "text": "Tallaahi in kunnaa lafee dalaalim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3030,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 98,
      "text": "Iz nusawweekum bi-Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3031,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 99,
      "text": "Wa-maaa adallanaaa illal mujrimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3032,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 100,
      "text": "Famaa lanaa min shaa-fi'een"
    },
    {"index": 3033, "sura": 26, "aya": 101, "text": "Wa-laa sadeeqin hameem"},
    {
      "index": 3034,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 102,
      "text": "Falaw anna lanaa karratan fanakoona minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3035,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 103,
      "text": "Inna fee zaalika la-Aayatanw Wa-maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3036,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 104,
      "text": "Wa-inna Rabbaka la-Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3037,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 105,
      "text": "Kazzabat qawmu Noohinil Mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3038,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 106,
      "text": "Iz qaala lahum akhoohum Noohun alaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3039,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 107,
      "text": "Innee lakum Rasoolun ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3040,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 108,
      "text": "Fattaqul laaha Wa-atee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3041,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 109,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3042,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 110,
      "text": "Fattaqul laaha Wa-atee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3043,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 111,
      "text": "Qaalooo anu'minu laka wattaba-'akal arzaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3044,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 112,
      "text": "Qaala Wa-maa 'ilmee bimaa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3045,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 113,
      "text": "In hisaabuhum illaa 'alaa Rabbee law tash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3046,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 114,
      "text": "Wa-maaa ana bitaaridil mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3047,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 115,
      "text": "In ana illaa nazeerum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3048,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 116,
      "text": "Qaaloo la'il lam tantahi yaa-Noohu latakoonanna minal marjoomeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3049,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 117,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbi inna qawmee kazzaboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3050,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 118,
      "text":
          "Faftab bainee Wa-bai-nahum fat-hanw Wa-najjinee Wa-mam ma'iya minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3051,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 119,
      "text": "Fa-anjainaahu Wa-mam ma'ahoo fil fulkil mashhoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3052,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 120,
      "text": "Summa aghraqnaa ba'dul baaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3053,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 121,
      "text": "Inna fee zaalika la-Aayaah; Wa-maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3054,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 122,
      "text": "Wa-inna Rabbaka la-huwal 'Azeezur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3055,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 123,
      "text": "Kazzabat 'Aadunil mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3056,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 124,
      "text": "Iz qaala lahum akhoohum Hoodun alaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3057,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 125,
      "text": "Innee lakum Rasoolun ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3058,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 126,
      "text": "Fattaqul laaha Wa-atee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3059,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 127,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3060,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 128,
      "text": "Atabnoona bikulli ree'in aayatan ta'basoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3061,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 129,
      "text": "Wa-tattakhizoona masaani'a la'allakum takhludoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3062,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 130,
      "text": "Wa-izaa batashtum batashtum jabbaareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3063,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 131,
      "text": "Fattaqul laaha Wa-atee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3064,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 132,
      "text": "Wattaqul lazeee amad-dakum bimaa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3065,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 133,
      "text": "Amaddakum bi-an'aa-minw Wa-baneen"
    },
    {"index": 3066, "sura": 26, "aya": 134, "text": "Wa-jannaatinw Wa-'uyoon"},
    {
      "index": 3067,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 135,
      "text": "Innee akhaafu 'alaikum 'azaaba Yawmin 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3068,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 136,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo sawaaa'un 'alainaaa awa-'azta am lam takum minal waa'izeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3069,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 137,
      "text": "In haazaaa illaa khuluqul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3070,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 138,
      "text": "Wa-maa nahnu bimu-'azzabeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3071,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 139,
      "text":
          "Fakazzaboohu fa-ahlaknaahum; inna fee zaalika la-aayah; Wa-maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3072,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 140,
      "text": "Wa-inna Rabbaka la-huwal 'Azeezur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3073,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 141,
      "text": "Kazzabat Samoodul mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3074,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 142,
      "text": "Iz qaala lahum akhoohum Saalihun alaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3075,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 143,
      "text": "Innee lakum Rasoolun ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3076,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 144,
      "text": "Fattaqul laaha Wa-atee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3077,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 145,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3078,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 146,
      "text": "Atutrakoona fee maa haahunnaaa aamineen"
    },
    {"index": 3079, "sura": 26, "aya": 147, "text": "Fee jannaatinw Wa-'uyoon"},
    {
      "index": 3080,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 148,
      "text": "Wa-zuroo-inw Wa-nakhlin tal-'uhaa hadeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3081,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 149,
      "text": "Wa-tanhitoona minal jibaali buyootan faariheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3082,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 150,
      "text": "Fattaqul laaha Wa-atee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3083,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 151,
      "text": "Wa-laa tutee'ooo amral musrifeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3084,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 152,
      "text": "Allazeena yufsidoona fil ardi Wa-laa yuslihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3085,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 153,
      "text": "Qaalooo innamaa anta minal musahhareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3086,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 154,
      "text":
          "Maaa anta illaa basharum mislunaa faati bi-Aayatin in kunta minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3087,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 155,
      "text":
          "Qaala haazihee naaqatul lahaa shirbunw walakum shirbu yawmim ma'loom"
    },
    {
      "index": 3088,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 156,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tamassoohaa bisooo'in fa-yaakhuzakum 'azaabu Yawmin 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3089,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 157,
      "text": "Fa'aqaroohaa fa-asbahoo naadimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3090,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 158,
      "text":
          "Fa-akhazahumul 'azaab; inna fee zaalika la-Aayah; Wa-maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3091,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 159,
      "text": "Wa-inna Rabbaka la-Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3092,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 160,
      "text": "kazzabat qawmu Lootinil mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3093,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 161,
      "text": "Iz qaala lahum akhoohum Lootun alaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3094,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 162,
      "text": "Innee lakum rasoolun ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3095,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 163,
      "text": "Fattaqul laaha Wa-atee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3096,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 164,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3097,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 165,
      "text": "Ataatoonaz zukraana minal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3098,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 166,
      "text":
          "Wa-tazaroona maa khalaqa lakum Rabbukum min azwaajikum; bal antum qawmun 'aadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3099,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 167,
      "text": "Qaloo la'il lam tantahi yaa-Lootu latakoonanna minal mukhrajeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3100,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 168,
      "text": "Qaala innee li'amalikum minal qaaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3101,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 169,
      "text": "Rabbi najjjinee Wa-ahlee mimmmaa ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3102,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 170,
      "text": "Fanajjainaahu Wa-ahlahooo ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 3103,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 171,
      "text": "Illaa 'ajoozan fil ghaabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3104,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 172,
      "text": "Summa dammarnal aa-khareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3105,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 173,
      "text": "Wa-amtarnaa 'alaihim mataran fasaaa'a matarul munzareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3106,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 174,
      "text": "Inna fee zaalika la-Aayah; Wa-maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3107,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 175,
      "text": "Wa-inna Rabbaka la-Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3108,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 176,
      "text": "Kazzaba As-haabul Aykatil mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3109,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 177,
      "text": "Iz qaala lahum Shu'aybun alaa tattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3110,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 178,
      "text": "Innee lakum Rasoolun ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3111,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 179,
      "text": "Fattaqul laaha Wa-atee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3112,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 180,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3113,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 181,
      "text": "Awful kaila Wa-laa takoonoo minal mukhsireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3114,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 182,
      "text": "Wa-zinoo bilqistaasil mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3115,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 183,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tabkhasun naasa ashyaaa-'ahum Wa-laa ta'saw fil ardi mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3116,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 184,
      "text": "Wattaqul lazee khalaqakum waljibillatal awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3117,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 185,
      "text": "Qaalooo innamaa anta minal musahhareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3118,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 186,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa anta illaa basharum mislunaa Wa-in nazunnuka laminal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3119,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 187,
      "text":
          "Fa-asqit 'alainaa kisafam minas samaaa'i in kunta minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3120,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 188,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbeee a'lamu bimaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3121,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 189,
      "text":
          "Fakazzaboohu fa-akhazahum 'azaabu Yawmiz zullah; innahoo kaana 'azaaba Yawmin 'Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3122,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 190,
      "text": "Inna fee zaalika la-Aayah; Wa-maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3123,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 191,
      "text": "Wa-inna Rabbaka la-huwal 'Azeezur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3124,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 192,
      "text": "Wa-innahoo latanzeelu Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3125,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 193,
      "text": "Nazala bihir Roohul Ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3126,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 194,
      "text": "Alaa qalbika litakoona minal munzireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3127,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 195,
      "text": "Bilisaanin 'Arabiyyim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3128,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 196,
      "text": "Wa-innahoo lafee Zuburil awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3129,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 197,
      "text":
          "Awalam yakul lahum Aayatan ai ya'lamahoo 'ulamaaa'u Baneee Israaa'eel"
    },
    {
      "index": 3130,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 198,
      "text": "Wa-law nazzalnaahu 'alaa ba'dil a'jameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3131,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 199,
      "text": "Faqara-ahoo 'alaihim maa kaanoo bihee mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3132,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 200,
      "text": "Kazaalika salaknaahu fee quloobil mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3133,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 201,
      "text": "Laa yu'minoona bihee hattaa yarawul 'azaabal aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3134,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 202,
      "text": "Fayaatiyahum baghtatanw Wa-hum laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3135,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 203,
      "text": "Fa-yaqooloo hal nahnu munzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3136,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 204,
      "text": "Aafabi-'azaabinaa yasta'jiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3137,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 205,
      "text": "Aara'aita im matta'naahum sineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3138,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 206,
      "text": "Summa jaaa'ahum maa kaanoo yoo'adoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3139,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 207,
      "text": "Maaa aghnaaa 'anhum maa kaanoo yumatta'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3140,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 208,
      "text": "Wa-maaa ahlaknaa min qaryatin illaa lahaa munziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3141,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 209,
      "text": "Zikraa Wa-maa kunnaa zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3142,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 210,
      "text": "Wa-maa tanazzalat bihish Shayaateen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3143,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 211,
      "text": "Wa-maa yambaghee lahum Wa-maa yastatee'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3144,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 212,
      "text": "Innahum 'anis sam'i lama'zooloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3145,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 213,
      "text":
          "Falaa tad'u ma'al laahi ilaahan aakhara fatakoona minal mu'azzabeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3146,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 214,
      "text": "Wa-anzir 'asheeratakal aqrabeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3147,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 215,
      "text": "Wakhfid janaahaka limanit taba-'aka minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3148,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 216,
      "text": "Fa-in asawka faqul innee bareee'um mimmmaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3149,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 217,
      "text": "Wa-tawakkal alal 'Azeezir Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3150,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 218,
      "text": "Allazee yaraaka heena taqoom"
    },
    {
      "index": 3151,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 219,
      "text": "Wa-taqallubaka fis saajideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3152,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 220,
      "text": "Innahoo Huwas Samee'ul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3153,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 221,
      "text": "Hal unabbi'ukum 'alaa man tanazzalush Shayaateen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3154,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 222,
      "text": "Tanazzalu 'alaa kulli affaakin aseem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3155,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 223,
      "text": "Yulqoonas sam'a Wa-aksaruhum kaaziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3156,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 224,
      "text": "Washshu-'araaa'u yattabi-'uhumul ghaawoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3157,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 225,
      "text": "Alam tara annahum fee kulli waadiny yaheemoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3158,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 226,
      "text": "Wa-annahum yaqooloona ma laa yaf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3159,
      "sura": 26,
      "aya": 227,
      "text":
          "Illal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati Wa-zakarul laaha kaseeranw wantasaroo min ba'di maa zulimoo; Wa-saya'lamul lazeena zalamooo aiya munqalabiny yanqaliboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3160,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 1,
      "text": "Taa-Seeen; tilka Aayaatul Qur-aani Wa-Kitaabim Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3161,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Hudanw Wa-bushraa lil-mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3162,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yuqeemoonas Salaata Wa-yu'toonaz Zakaata Wa-hum bil-Aakhirati hum yooqinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3163,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena laa yu'minoona bil-Aakhirati zaiyannaa lahum a'maalahum fahum ya'mahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3164,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ikal lazeena lahum sooo'ul 'azaabi Wa-hum fil Aakhirati humul akhsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3165,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 6,
      "text": "Wa-innaka latulaqqal Qur-aana mil ladun Hakeemin 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3166,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Iz qaala Moosaa li-ahliheee inneee aanastu naaran saaateekum minhaa bikhabarin aw aateekum bishihaabin qabasil la'allakum tastaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3167,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'ahaa noodiya am boorika man fin naari Wa-man hawlahaa Wa-Subhaanal laahi Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3168,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 9,
      "text": "Yaa-Moosaaa innahooo Anal laahul 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3169,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-alqi 'asaak; falammmaa ra-aahaa tahtazzu ka-annahaa jaaannunw wallaa mudbiranw Wa-lam yu'aqqib; yaa-Moosaa laa takhaf innee laa yakhaafu ladaiyal mursaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3170,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Illaa man zalama summa baddala husnam ba'da sooo'in fa-innee Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3171,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-adkhil yadaka fee jaibika takhruj baidaaa'a min ghairi sooo'in fee tis'i Aayaatin ilaa Fir'awna Wa-qawmih; innahum kaanoo qawman faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3172,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'at-hum Aayaatunaa mubsiratan qaaloo haazaa sihrum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3173,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-jahadoo bihaa wastaiqanat-haaa anfusuhum zulmanw wa-'uluwwaa; fanzur kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3174,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Daawooda Wa-sulaimaana 'ilmaa; Wa-qaalal hamdu lil-laahil lazee faddalanaa 'alaa kaseerim min 'ibaadihil mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3175,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wa-warisa Sulaimaanu Daawooda Wa-qaala yaaa-aiyuhan naasu 'ullimnaa mantiqat tairi Wa-ooteenaa min kulli shai'in inna haazaa lahuwal fadlul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3176,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Wa-hushira Sulaimaana junooduhoo minal jinni wal-insi wattairi fahum yooza'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3177,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "hattaaa izaaa ataw 'alaa waadin namli qaalat namlatuien yaaa-aiyuhan namlud khuloo masaakinakum laa yahtimannakum Sulaimaanu Wa-junooduhoo Wa-hum laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3178,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Fatabassama daahikam min qawlihaa Wa-qaala Rabbi awzi'nee an ashkura ni'mata-kal lateee an'amta 'alaiyya Wa-'alaa waalidaiyya Wa-an a'mala saalihan tardaahu Wa-adkhilnee birahmatika fee 'ibaadikas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3179,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-tafaqqadat taira faqaala maa liya laaa araa al-hudhuda, am kaana minal ghaaa'ibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3180,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "La-u'azzibanahoo 'azaaban shadeedan aw la-azbahannahoo aw layaatiyannee bisultaanim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3181,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Famakasa ghaira ba'eedin faqaala ahattu bimaa lam tuhit bihee Wa-ji'tuka min Sabaim binaba-iny yaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3182,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Innee wajattum ra-atan tamlikuhum Wa-ootiyat min kulli shai'inw Wa-lahaa 'arshun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3183,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Wajattuhaa Wa-qawmahaa yasjudoona lishshamsi min doonil laahi Wa-zaiyana lahumush Shaitaanu a'maalahum fasaddahum 'anis sabeeli fahum laa yahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3184,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Allaa yasjudoo lillaahil lazee yukhrijul khab'a fis samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-ya'lamu maa tukhfoona Wa-maa tu'linoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3185,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 26,
      "text": "Allaahu laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa Rabbul 'Arshil Azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3186,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 27,
      "text": "Qaala sananzuru asadaqta am kunta minal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3187,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Izhab bikitaabee haaza fa-alqih ilaihim summma tawalla 'anhum fanzur maazaa yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3188,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 29,
      "text": "Qaalat yaaa-aiyyuhal mala'u innee ulqiya ilaiya kitaabun kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3189,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 30,
      "text": "Innahoo min Sulaimaana Wa-innahoo bismil laahir Rahmaanir Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3190,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 31,
      "text": "Allaa ta'loo 'alaiya waa-toonee muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3191,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Qaalat yaaa-aiyyuhal mala'u aftoonee fee amree maa kuntu qaati'atan amran hattaa tashhhaddon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3192,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo nahnu uloo quwwatinw Wa-uloo baasin shadeed; wal-amru ilaiki fanzuree maazaa taamureen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3193,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Qaalat innal mulooka izaa dakhaloo qaryatan afsadoohaa Wa-ja'alooo a'izzata ahlihaaa azillah; Wa-kazaalika yaf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3194,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-innee mursilatun ilaihim bihadiyyatin fanaaziratum bima yarji'ul mursaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3195,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'a Sulaimaana qaala atumiddoonani bimaalin famaaa aataaniyal laahu khairum mimmmaaa aataakum bal antum bihadiy-yatikum tafrahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3196,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Irji' ilaihim falanaatiyan-nahum bijunoodil laa qibala lahum bihaa Wa-lanukhri-jannahum minhaaa azillatanw Wa-hum saaghiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3197,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaaa-aiyyuhal mala'u aiyyukum yaateenee bi'arshihaa qabla aien yaatoonee muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3198,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Qaala 'ifreetum minal jinni ana aateeka bihee qabla an taqooma mim maqaamika Wa-innee 'alaihi laqawiyyun ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3199,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Qaalal lazee indahoo 'ilmum minal Kitaabi ana aateeka bihee qabla aien yartadda ilaika tarfuk; falammaa ra-aahu mustaqirran 'indahoo qaala haazaa min fadli Rabbee li-yabluwaneee 'a-ashkuru am akfuru Wa-man shakara fa-innamaa yashkuru linafsihee Wa-man kafara fa-inna Rabbee Ghaniyyun Kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3200,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Qaala nakkiroo lahaa 'arshahaa nanzur atahtadeee am takoonu minal lazeena laa yahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3201,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'at qeela ahaakaza 'arshuki qaalat kaanna hoo; Wa-ooteenal 'ilma min qablihaa Wa-kunnaa muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3202,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-saddahaa maa kaanat ta'budu min doonil laahi innahaa kaanat min qawmin kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3203,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Qeela lahad khulis sarha falammaa ra-at-hu hasibat-hu lujjatanw Wa-khashafat 'an saaqaihaa; qaala innahoo sarhum mumarradum min qawaareer; qaalat Rabbi innee zalamtu nafsee Wa-aslamtu ma'a Sulaimaana lillaahi Rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3204,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa laqad arsalnaaa ilaa Samooda akhaahum Saalihan ani'budul lahha fa-izaa hum fareeqaani yakhtasimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3205,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Qaala yaa-qawmi lima tasta'jiloona bissaiyi'ati qablal hasanati law-laa tas-taghfiroonal laaha la'allakum turhamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3206,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Qaalut taiyyarnaa bika Wa-bimam ma'ak; qaala taaa'irukum 'indal laahi bal antum qawmun tuftanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3207,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-kaana fil madeenati tis'atu rahtien yufsidoona fil ardi Wa-laa yuslihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3208,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo taqaasamoo billaahi lanubaiyyitannahoo Wa-ahlahoo summaa lanaqoolana liwaliy-yihee maa shahidnaa mahlika ahliee Wa-innaa lasaadiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3209,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 50,
      "text": "Wa-makaroo makranw Wa-makarnaa makranw Wa-hum laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3210,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Fanzur kaifa kaana 'aaqibatu makrihim annaa dammar-naahum Wa-qawmahum ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 3211,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Fatilka buyootuhum khaa-wiyatam bimaa zalamoo; inna fee zaalika la-Aayatal liqaw-mien ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3212,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 53,
      "text": "Wa-anjainal lazeena aamanoo Wa-kaanoo yattaqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3213,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wa-lootan iz qaala liqawmiheee ataatoonal faa-hishata Wa-antum tubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3214,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "A'innakum lataatoonar rijaala shahwatam min doonin nisaaa'; bal antum qawmun tajhaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3215,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Famaa kaana jawaaba qawmiheee illaaa an qaalooo akhrijooo aalaa Lootim min qaryatikum innahum unaasuny yatatahharoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3216,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Fa-anjainaahu Wa-ahlahooo illam ra-atahoo qaddarnaahaa minal ghaabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3217,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 58,
      "text": "Wa-amtarnaa 'alaihimm mataran fasaaa'a matarul munzareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3218,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Qulil hamdu lillaahi Wa-salaamun 'alaa 'ibaadihil lazeenas tafaa; aaallaahu khairun ammmaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3219,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Amman khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda Wa-anzala lakum minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa-anbatnaa bihee hadaaa'iqa zaata bahjah; maa kaana lakum an tunbitoo shajarahaa; 'a-ilaahun ma'al laah; bal hum qawmuien ya'diloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3220,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Ammann ja'alal arda qaraaranw Wa-ja'ala khilaalahaaa anhaaranw Wa-ja'ala lahaa rawaasiya Wa-ja'ala bainal bahraini haajizaa; 'a-ilaahun ma' allah; bal aksaruhum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3221,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Ammaien yujeebul mud-tarra izaa da'aahu Wa-yakshifus sooo'a Wa-yaj'alukum khula-faaa'al ardi 'a-ilaahun ma' allaah qaleelan maa tazak-karoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3222,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Ammaien yahdeekum fee zulumaatil barri wal bahri Wa-maien yursilu riyaaha bushran baina yadai rahmatih; 'a-ilaahun ma'allah; Ta'aalal laahu 'ammaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3223,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Ammaien yabda'ul khalqa thumma yu'eeduhoo Wa-maien yarzuqukum minas sammaaa'i wal ard; 'a-ilaahun ma'allah; qul haatoo burhaanakum in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3224,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Qul laa ya'lamu man fis sammaawaati wal-ardil ghaiba illal laah; Wa-maa yash'uroona aiyaana yub'asoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3225,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Balid daaraka 'ilmuhum fil Aakhirah; bal hum fee shakkin minhaa bal hum minhaa 'amoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3226,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena kafarooo 'a-izaa kunnaa turaabanw Wa-aabaaa'unaaa a'innaa lamukhrajoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3227,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Laqad wu'idnaa haazaa nahnu Wa-aabaaa'unaa min qablu in haazaaa illaaa asaateerul awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3228,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 69,
      "text": "Qul seeroo fil ardi fanzuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3229,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 70,
      "text": "Wa-laa tahzan 'alaihim Wa-laa takun fee daiqin mimmaa yamkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3230,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 71,
      "text": "Wa-yaqooloona mataa haazal wa'du in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3231,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 72,
      "text": "Qul 'asaaa aien yakoona radifa lakum ba'dul lazee tasta'jiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3232,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-inna Rabbaka lazoo fadlin 'alan naasi Wa-laakinna aksarahum laa yashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3233,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wa-inna Rabbaka la-ya'lamu maa tukinnu sudooruhum Wa-maa yu'linoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3234,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa min ghaaa'ibatin fis samaaa'i wal-ardi illaa fee kitaabin mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3235,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Inna haazal Qur-aana yaqussu 'alaa Baneee israaa'eela aksaral lazee hum feehi yakhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3236,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 77,
      "text": "Wa-innahoo lahudanw Wa-rahmatul lilmu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3237,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 78,
      "text": "Inna Rabbaka yaqdee bainahum bihukmih; Wa-Huwal 'Azeezul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3238,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 79,
      "text": "Fatawakkal 'alal laahi innaka 'alal haqqil mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3239,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Innaka laa tusmi'ul mawtaa Wa-laa tusmi'us summad du'aaa izaa wallaw mudbireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3240,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa anta bihaadil-'umyi 'an dalaalatihim in tusmi'u illaa mai yu'minu bi aayaatinaa fahum muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3241,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa waqa'al qawlu 'alaihim akhrajnaa lahum daaabbatan minal ardi tukal-limuhum annan naasa kaanoo bi-aayaatinaa laa yooqinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3242,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma nahshuru min kulli ummatin fawjan mimmaien yukazzibu bi-Aayaatinaa fahum yooza'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3243,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Hattaaa izaa jaaa'oo qaala akazzabtum bi-Aayaatee Wa-lam tuheetoo bihaa 'ilman ammaazaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3244,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 85,
      "text": "Wa-waqa'al qawlu 'alaihim bimaa zalamoo fahum laa yantiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3245,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Alam yaraw annaa ja'alnal laila li-yaskunoo feehi wannahaara mubsiraa; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil liqaw-mien yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3246,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma yunfakhu fis Soori fafazi'a man fis samaawaati Wa-man fil ardi illaa man shaaa'al laah; Wa-kullun atawhu daakhireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3247,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Wa-taral jibaala tahsabuhaa jaamidatanw Wa-hiya tamurru marras sahaab; sun'al laahil lazeee atqana kulla shai'; innahoo khabeerun bimaa taf'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3248,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 89,
      "text":
          "Man jaaa'a bil-hasanati falahoo khairun minhaa Wa-hum min faza'ien Yawma'izin aaminoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3249,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 90,
      "text":
          "Wa-man jaaa'a bissai-yi'ati fakubbat wujoohuhum fin Naari hal tujzawna illaa maa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3250,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 91,
      "text":
          "Innamaaa umirtu an a'buda Rabba haazihil baldatil lazee harramahaa Wa-lahoo kullu shai'inw Wa-umirtu an akoona minal muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3251,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 92,
      "text":
          "Wa-an atluwal Qur-aana famanih tadaa fa-innamaa yahtadee linafsihee Wa-man dalla faqul innamaaa ana minal munzireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3252,
      "sura": 27,
      "aya": 93,
      "text":
          "Wa-qulil hamdu lillaahi sa-yureekum Aayaatihee fa-ta'rifoonahaa; Wa-maa Rabbuka bighaafilin 'ammaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {"index": 3253, "sura": 28, "aya": 1, "text": "Taa-Seeen-Meeem"},
    {
      "index": 3254,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Tilka Aayaatul Kitaabil mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3255,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Natloo 'alaika min naba-i Moosaa Wa-Fir'awna bilhaqqi liqawminy yu'miinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3256,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Inna Fir'awna 'alaa fil ardi Wa-ja'ala ahlahaa shiya'ai yastad'ifu taaa'ifatam minhum yuzabbihu abnaaa'ahum Wa-yastahyee nisaaa'ahum; innahoo kaana minal mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3257,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Wa-nureedu an namunna 'alal lazeenas tud'ifoo fil ardi Wa-naj'alahum a'immatanw Wa-naj'alahumul waariseen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3258,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-numakkina lahum fil ardi Wa-nuriya Fir'awna Wa-Haamaana Wa-junoodahumaa minhum maa kaanoo yahzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3259,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-awhainaaa ilaaa ummi Moosaaa an ardi'eehi faizaa khifti 'alaihi fa-alqeehi fil yammi Wa-laa takhaafee Wa-laa tahzaneee innaa raaaddoohu ilaiki Wa-jaa'iloohu minal mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3260,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Faltaqatahooo Aalu Fir'awna li-yakoona lahum 'aduwwanw Wa-hazanaa; inna Fir'awna Wa-Haamaana Wa-junooda-humaa kaanoo khaati'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 3261,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalatim ra-atu Fir'awna qurratu 'aynil lee Wa-lak; laa taqtuloohu 'asaaa aien yanfa'anaa aw nattakhizahoo waladanw Wa-hum laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3262,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-asbaha fu'aadu ummi Moosaa faarighan in kaadat latubdee bihee law laaa arrabatnaa 'alaa qalbihaa litakoona minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3263,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalat li-ukhtihee qusseehi fabasurat bihee 'an junubinw wahum laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3264,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-harramnaa 'alaihil maraadi'a min qablu faqaalat hal adullukum 'alaaa ahli baitiny yakfuloonahoo lakum Wa-hum lahoo naasihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3265,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Faradadnaahu ilaa ummihee kai taqarra 'ainuhaa Wa-laa tahzana Wa-lita'lama anna wa'dal laahi haqqunw Wa-laakinna aksarahum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3266,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa balagha ashuddahoo wastawaaa aatai-naahu hukmanw Wa-'ilmaa; Wa-kazaalika najzil muhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3267,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wa-dakhalal madeenata 'alaa heene ghaflatim min ahlihaa fawajada feeha raju-laini yaqtatilaani haazaa min shee'atihee Wa-haaza min 'aduwwihee fastaghaasahul lazee min shee'atihee 'alal lazee min 'aduwwihee fawakazahoo Moosaa faqadaa 'alaihi qaala haaza min 'amalish Shaitaani innahoo 'aduwwum mmudillum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3268,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbi innee zalamtu nafsee faghfir lee faghafara lah; innahoo Huwal Ghafoorur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3269,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbi bimaaa an'amta 'alaiya falan akoona zaheeral lilmujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3270,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Fa-asbaha fil madeenati khaaa'ifaien yataraqqabu fa-izal lazis tansarahoo bil-amsi yastasrikhuh; qaala lahoo moosaaa innaka laghawiyyum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3271,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Falammaaa an araada aien yabtisha billazee huwa 'aduwwul lahumaa qaala yaa-Moosaaa atureedu an taqtulanee kamaa qatalta nafsam bil-amsi in tureedu illaaa an takoona jabbaaram fil ardi Wa-maa tureedu an takoona minal musliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3272,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaaa'a rajulum min aqsal madeenati yas'aa qaala yaa-Moosaaa innal mala-a yaa-tamiroona bika liyaqtulooka fakhruj innee laka minan naasiheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3273,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Fakharaja minhaa khaaa 'ifany-yataraqqab; qaala Rabbi najjinee minal qawmiz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3274,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa tawajjaha tilqaaa'a Madyana qaala 'asaa Rabbeee aien yahdiyanee Sawaaa'as Sabeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 3275,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa warada maaa'a Madyana wajada 'alaihi ummatam minannaasi yasqoona Wa-wajada min doonihimum ra ataini tazoodaani qaala maa khatubkumaa qaalataa laa nasqee hataa yusdirar ri'aaa'u Wa-aboonaa shaikhun kabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3276,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Fasaqaa lahumaa summa tawallaaa ilaz zilli faqaala Rabbi innee limaaa anzalta ilaiya min khairin faqeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3277,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Fajaaa'at-hu ihdaahumaa tamshee 'alas tihyaaa'in qaalat inna abee yad'ooka li-yajziyaka ajra maa saqaita lanaa; falammaa jaaa'ahoo Wa-qassa 'alaihil qasasa qaala laa takhaf najawta minal qawmiz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3278,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Qaalat ihdaahumaa yaaa abatis taajirhu inna khaira manistaajartal qawiyyul ameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3279,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Qaala innee ureedu an unkihaka ihdab nataiya haataini 'alaaa an taajuranee samaaniya hijaj; fa-in atmamta 'ashran famin 'indika Wa-maaa ureedu an ashuqqa 'alaik; satajiduneee in shaaa'al laahu minas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3280,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Qaala zaalika bainee Wa-bainaka aiyamal ajalaini qadaitu falaa 'udwaana 'alaiya wallaahu 'alaa ma naqoolu Wakeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 3281,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Falammmaa qadaa Moosal ajala Wa-saara bi-ahliheee aanasa min jaanibit Toori naaran qaala li-ahlihim kusooo inneee aanastu naaral la-'alleee aateekum minhaa bikhabarin aw jazwatim minan naari la-'allakum tastaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3282,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Falammaaa ataahaa noodiya min shaati'il waadil aimani fil buq'atil muubaarakati minash shajarati aien yaa-Moosaaa inneee Anal laahu Rabbul 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3283,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-an alqi 'asaaka falam-maa ra-aahaa tahtazzu ka-annnahaa jaaannunw wallaa mudbiranw Wa-lam yu'aqqib; yaa-Moosaa aqbil Wa-laa takhaf innaka minal aamineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3284,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Usluk yadaka fee jaibika takhruj baidaaa'a min ghairi sooo'inw wadmum ilaika janaahaka minar rahbi fazaanika burhaanaani mir Rabbika ilaa Fir'awna Wa-mala'ih; innahum kaanoo qawman faasiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3285,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Qaala Rabbi innee qataltu minhum nafsan fa-akhaafu aien yaqtuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3286,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-akhee Haaroonu huwa afsahu minnee lisaanan fa-arsilhu ma'iya rid-aien yusaddiquneee innee akhaafu aien yukazziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3287,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Qaala sanashuddu 'adudaka bi-akheeka Wa-naj'alu lakumaa sultaanan falaa yasiloona ilaikumaa; bi-Aayaatinaa antumaa Wa-manit taba'akumal ghaaliboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3288,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'ahum Moosaa bi-Aayaatinaa baiyinaatin qaaloo maa haazaaa illaa sihrum muftaranw Wa-maa sami'naa bihaazaa feee aabaaa'inal awwaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3289,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala Moosaa Rabbeee a'alamu biman jaaa'a bilhudaa min 'indihee Wa-man takoonu lahoo 'aaqibatud daari innahoo laa yuflihuz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3290,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala Fir'awnu yaaa-aiyyuhal mala-u maa 'alimtu lakum min ilaahin ghairee fa-awqid lee yaa-Haamaanu 'alatteeni faj'al lee sarhal la'alleee attali'u ilaaa ilaahi Moosaa Wa-innee la azunnuhoo minal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3291,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wastakbara huwa Wa-junooduhoo fil ardi bighairil haqqi Wa-zannooo annahum ilainaa laa yurja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3292,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Fa-akhaznaahu Wa-junoo-dahoo fanabaznaahum fil yammi fanzur kaifa kaana 'aaqibatuz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3293,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnaahum a'immataien yad'oona ilan Naari Wa-Yawmal Qiyaamati laa yunsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3294,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-atba'naahum fee haazihid dunyaa la'natanw Wa-Yawmal Qiyaamati hum minal maqbooheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3295,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Moosal Kitaaba mim ba'di maaa ahlaknal quroonal oolaa basaaa'ira linnaasi Wa-hudanw Wa-rahmatal la'allahum yata-zakkkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3296,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kunta bijaanibil gharbiyyi iz qadainaaa ilaa Moosal amra Wa-maa kunta minash shaahideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3297,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa-laakinnaa anshaanaa quroonan fatataawala 'alaihimul 'umur; Wa-maa kunta saawiyan feee ahli Madyana tatloo 'alaihim Aayaatinaa Wa-laakinnaa kunnaa mursileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3298,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kunta bijaanibit Toori iz naadainaa Wa-laakir rahmatam mir Rabbika litunzira qawmam maaa ataahum min nazeerim min qablika la'allahum yatazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3299,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-law-laaa an tuseebahum museebatum bimaa qaddamat aideehim fa-yaqooloo Rabbanaa law-laaa arsalta ilainaa Rasoolan fanattabi'a Aayaatika Wa-nakoona minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3300,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Falammaa jaaa'ahumul haqqu min 'indinaa qaaloo law-laa ootiya misla maaa ootiyaa Moosaa; awalam yakfuroo bimaaa ootiya Moosaa min qablu qaaloo sihraani tazaaharaa Wa-qaalooo innaa bikullin kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3301,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Qul faatoo bi-Kitaabim min 'indil laahi huwa ahdaa minhu-maaa attabi'hu in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3302,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Fa-il lam yastajeeboo laka fa'lam annamaa yattabi'oona ahwaaa'ahum; Wa-man adallu mimmanit taba'a hawaahu bighari hudam minal laah; innal laaha laa yahdil qawmaz zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3303,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 51,
      "text": "Wa-laqad wassalnaa lahumul qawla la'allahum yatazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3304,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Allazeena aatainaahu-mul Kitaaba min qablihee hum bihee yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3305,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa yutlaa 'alaihim qaaloo aamannaa biheee innahul haqqu mir rabbinaaa innaa kunnaa min qablihee muslimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3306,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Ulaaa'ika yu'tawna ajrahum marratayni bimaa sabaroo Wa-yadra'oona bil-hasanatis saiyyi'ata Wa-mimmmaa razaq-naahum yunfiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3307,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa sami'ul laghwa a'radoo 'anhu Wa-qaaloo lanaaa a'maalunaa Wa-lakum a'maalukum salaamun 'alaikum laa nabtaghil jaahileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3308,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Innaka laa tahdee man ahbata Wa-laakinna laaha yahdee maien yashaaa'; Wa-Huwaa 'lamu bilmuhtadeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3309,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalooo in nattabi'il hudaa ma'aka nutakhattaf min ardinaa; awalam numakkkil lahum haraman aaminany yujbaaa ilaihi samaraatu kulli shai'ir rizqam mil ladunnaa Wa-laakinna aksarahum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3310,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-kam ahlaknaa min qaryatim batirat ma'eeshatahaa fatilka masaakinuhum lam tuskam mim ba'dihim illaa qaleelaa; Wa-kunnaa Nahnul waariseen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3311,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana Rabbuka muhlikal quraa hattaa yab'asa feee ummihaa Rasoolany yatloo 'alaihim aayaatina; Wa-maa kunnaa muhlikil quraaa illaa Wa-ahluhaa zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3312,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa ooteetum min shai'in famataa'ul hayaatid dunyaa Wa-zeenatuhaa; Wa-maa 'indal laahi khairunw Wa-abqaa; afalaa ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3313,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Afamanw wa'adnaahu wa'dan hasanan fahuwa laaqeehi kamam matta'naahu mataa'al hayaatid dunyaa summa huwa Yawmal Qiyaamati minal muhdareen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3314,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma yunaadeehim fa-yaqoolu aina shurakaaa-'iyal lazeena kuntum taz'umoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3315,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Qaalal lazeena haqqa 'alaihimul qawlu Rabbanaa haaa'ulaaa'il lazeena aghwainaa aghwainaahu kamaa ghawainaa tabarraanaaa ilaika maa kaanoo iyyaanaa ya'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3316,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Wa-qeelad 'oo shurakaaa'akum fada'awhum falam yastajeeboo lahum Wa-ra-awul 'azaab; law annahum kaanoo yahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3317,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 65,
      "text": "Wa-Yawma yunaadeehim fa-yaqoolu maazaaa ajabtumul mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3318,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Fa'amiyat 'alaihimul ambaaa'u Yawma'izin fahum laa yatasaaa'aloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3319,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Fa-ammaa man taaba Wa-aamana Wa-'amila saalihan fa'asaaa ai yakoona minal mufliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3320,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Wa-Rabbuka yakhuluqu maa yashaaa'u Wa-yakhtaar; maa kaana lahumul khiyarah; Subhannal laahi Wa-Ta'aalaa 'ammmaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3321,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 69,
      "text": "Wa-Rabbuka ya'lamu maa tukinnu sudooruhum Wa-maa yu'linoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3322,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal laahu laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa lahul hamdu fil oolaa wal-Aakhirati Wa-lahul hukmu Wa-ilaihi turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3323,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Qul ara'aitum in ja'alal laahu 'alaikumul laila sarmadan ilaa Yawmil Qiyaamati man ilaahun ghairul laahi yaa-teekum bidiyaaa'in afalaa tasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3324,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Qul ara'aitum in ja'alal laahu 'alaikumun nahaara sarmadan ilaa Yawmil Qiyaamati man ilaahun ghairul laahi yaateekum bilailin taskunoona feehi afalaa tubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3325,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Wa-mir rahmatihee ja'ala lakumul laila wannahaara litaskunoo feehi Wa-litabtaghoo min fadlihee Wa-la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3326,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 74,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma yunaadeehim fa-yaqoolu aina shurakaaa'iyal lazeena kuntum tazz'umoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3327,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 75,
      "text":
          "Wa-naza'naa min kulli ummatin shaheedan faqulnaa haatoo burhaanakum fa'alimooo annal haqqa lillaahi Wa-dalla 'anhum maa kaanoo yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3328,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Inna Qaaroona kaana min qawmi Moosaa fabaghaaa 'alaihim Wa-aatainaahu minal kunoozi maaa inna mafaati-hahoo latanooo'u bil'usbati ulil quwwati iz qaala lahoo qawmuhoo laa tafrah innal laahaa laa yuhibbul fariheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3329,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Wabtaghi feemaaa aataakal laahud Daaral Aakhirata Wa-laa tansa naseebaka minad dunyaa Wa-ahsin kamaaa ahsanal laahu ilaika Wa-laa tabghil fasaada fil ardi innal laaha laa yuhibbul mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3330,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Qaala innamaaa ootee-tuhoo 'alaa 'ilmin 'indeee; awalam ya'lam annal laaha qad ahlaka min qablihee minal qurooni man huwa ashaddu minhu quwwatanw Wa-aksaru jam'aa; Wa-laa yus'alu 'an zunoobihimul mujrimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3331,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Fakharaja 'alaa qawmihee fee zeenatih; qaalal lazeena yureedoonal hayaatad dunyaa yaalaita lanaa misla maaa ootiya Qaaroonu innahoo lazoo hazzin 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3332,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena ootul 'ilma wailakum sawaabul laahi khairul liman aamana Wa-'amila saalihaa; Wa-laa yulaq-qaahaaa illas saabiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3333,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Fakhasafnaa bihee Wa-bidaarihil arda famaa kaana laho min fi'atien yansuroo-nahoo min doonil laahi Wa-maa kaana minal muntasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3334,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Wa-asbahal lazeena tamannaw makaanahoo bil-amsi yaqooloona waika-annal laaha yabsutur rizqa limaien ya-shaaa'u min 'ibaadihee Wa-yaqdiru law-laaa am mannal laahu 'alainaa lakhasafa binaa waika-annahoo laa yuflihul kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3335,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Tilkad Daarul Aakhiratu naj'aluhaa lillazeena laa yureedoona 'uluwwan fil ardi Wa-laa fasaadaa; wal-'aaqibatu lilmuttaqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3336,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 84,
      "text":
          "Man jaaa'a bilhasanati falahoo khairum minhaa Wa-man jaaa'a bissaiyi'ati falaa yujzal lazeena 'amilus saiyiaati illaa maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3337,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 85,
      "text":
          "Innal azee farada 'alaikal Qur-aana laraaadduka ilaa ma'aad; qur Rabbeee a'lamu man jjaaa'a bil-hudaa Wa-man huwa fee dalaalim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3338,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 86,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kunta tarjooo aien yulqaaa ilaikal Kitaabu illaa rahmatam mir Rabbika falaa takoonanna zaheeral lilkaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3339,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 87,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa yasuddunnaka 'an Aayaatil laahi ba'da iz unzilat ilaika wad'u ilaa Rabbika Wa-laa takonanna minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3340,
      "sura": 28,
      "aya": 88,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tad'u ma'al laahi ilaahan aakhar; laaa ilaaha illaa Hoo; kullu shai'in haalikun illaa Wajhah; lahul hukkmu Wa-ilaihi turja'oon"
    },
    {"index": 3341, "sura": 29, "aya": 1, "text": "Alif-Laaam-Meeem"},
    {
      "index": 3342,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Ahasiban naasu any yutrakooo any yaqoolooo aamannaa Wa-hum la yuftanoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3343,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad fatannal lazeena min qablihim fala-ya'lamannal laahul lazeena sadaqoo Wa-la-ya'lamannal kaazibeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3344,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Am hasibal lazeena ya'maloonas sayyiaati any yasbiqoonaa; saaa'a maa yahkumoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3345,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Man kaana yarjoo liqaaa 'allaahi fa-inna ajalal laahi laaat; Wa-Huwass Sameeul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3346,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-man jaahada fainnamaa yujaahidu linafsih; innal laaha laghaniyyun 'anil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3347,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati lanukaf-firanna 'anhum saiyiaatihim Wa-lanajziyannahum ahsanal lazee kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3348,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Wa-wassainal insaana biwaalidaihi husnanw Wa-in jaahadaaka litushrika bee maa laisa laka bihee 'ilmun falaa tuti'humaa; ilaiya marji'ukum fa-unabbi'ukum bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3349,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aamanoo wa'amilus saalihaati lanudkhilan-nahum fis saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3350,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-minan naasi maien yaqoolu aamannaa billaahi faizaaa ooziya fil laahi ja'ala fitnatan naasi ka'azaabil laahi Wa-la'in jaaa'a nasrum mir Rabbika la-yaqoolunna innaa kunnaa ma'akum; awa-laisal laahu bi-a'lama bimaa fee sudooril 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3351,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Wa-la-ya'lamannal laahul lazeena aamanoo Wa-la-ya'lamannal munaafiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3352,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena kafaroo lillazeena aamanut tabi'oo sabeelanaa walnahmil khataayaakum Wa-maa hum bihaamileena min khataa-yaahum min shai'in innahum lakaaziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3353,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-la-yahmilunna asqaa-lahum Wa-asqaalam ma'a asqaalihim Wa-la-yus'alunna Yawmal Qiyaamati 'ammaa kaanoo yaftaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3354,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad arsalnaa Noohan ilaa qawmihee falabisa feehim alfa sanatin illaa khamseena 'aaman fa-akhazahumut toofaanu Wa-hum zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3355,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Fa-anjainaahu Wa-as-haabas safeenati Wa-ja'alnaahaaa Aayatal lil'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3356,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wa-Ibraheema iz qaala liqawmihi' budul laaha wattaqoohu zaalikum khayrul lakum in kuntum ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3357,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Innamaa ta'budoona min doonil laahi awsaananw-wa takhluqoona ifkaa; innal lazeena ta'budoona min doonil laahi laa yamlikoona lakum rizqan fabtaghoo 'indal laahir rizqa wa'budoohu washkuroo lahooo ilaihi turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3358,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-in tukazziboo faqad kazzaba umamum min qablikum Wa-maa' alar Rasooli illal balaaghul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3359,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Awa-lam yaraw kaifa yubdi'ul laahul khalqa summa yu'eeduh; inna zaalika 'alal laahi yaseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3360,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Qul seeroo fil ardi fanzuroo kaifa bada'a al-khalqa summal laahu yunshi'-'un nash-atal Aakhirah; innal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3361,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Yu'azzibu many yashaaa'u Wa-yarhamu many yashaaa'; Wa-ilaihi tuqlaboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3362,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa antum bimu'jizeena fil ardi Wa-laa fis samaaa'i Wa-maa lakum min doonil laahi minw waliyyinw Wa-laa naseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3363,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kafaroo bi-Aayaatil laahi Wa-liqaaa'iheee ulaaa'ika ya'isoo mir rahmatee Wa-ulaaa'ika lahum 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3364,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Famaa kaana jawaaba qawmiheee illaaa an qaaluqtuloohu aw harriqoohu fa-anjaahul laahu minan naar; inna fee zaalika la Aayaatil laqawmien yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3365,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaala innamat takhaz-tum min doonil laahi awsaanam mawaddata bainikum fil hayaatid dunyaa summa Yawmal Qiyaamati yakfuru ba'dukum biba'dinw Wa-yal'anu ba'dukum ba'danw Wa-ma'waakumun Naaru Wa-maa lakum min naasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3366,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Fa-aamana lahoo Loot; Wa-qaala innee muhajirun ilaa Rabbee innahoo Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3367,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wa-wahabnaa lahoo Iss-haaqa Wa-Ya'Qooba Wa-ja'alnaa fee zurriyyatihin Nubuwwata wal-Kitaaba Wa-aatainaahu ajrahoo fid dunyaa Wa-innahoo fil aakhirati laminas saaliheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3368,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wa-Lootan iz qaala liqawmiheee innakum ta'toonal faahishata maa sabaqakum bihaa min ahadin minal 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3369,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "A'innakum la-ta'toonar rijaala Wa-taqta'oonas sabeela Wa-ta'toona fee naadeekumul munkara famaa kaana jawaaba qawmiheee illaaa an qaalu' tinaaa bi'azaabil laahi in kunta minas saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3370,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 30,
      "text": "Qaala Rabbin surnee 'alal qawmil mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3371,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa jaaa'at Rusulunaaa Ibraaheema bil-bushraa qaalooo innaa muhlikoo ahli haazihil qaryati inna ahlahaa kaanoo zaalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3372,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Qaala inna feeha Lootaa; qaaloo nahnu a'lamu biman feehaa lanunajjjiyannahoo Wa-ahlahooo illam ra-atahoo kaanat minal ghaabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3373,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaaa an jaaa'at Rusulunaa Lootan seee'a bihim Wa-daaqa bihim zar'anw Wa-qaaloo laa takhaf Wa-laa tahzan innaa munajjooka Wa-ahlaka illam ra-ataka kaanat minal ghaabireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3374,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Innaa munziloona 'alaaa ahli haazihil qaryati rijzan minas samaaa'i bimaa kaanoo yafsuqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3375,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad taraknaa min-haaa aayatan baiyyinatan liqawmien ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3376,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-ilaa Madyana akhaahum Shu'ayban faqaala yaa-qawmi' budul laaha warjul yawmal aakhira Wa-laa ta'saw fil ardi mufsideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3377,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Fakazzaboohu fa-akhazat-humur rajfatu fa-asbahoo fee daarihim jaasimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3378,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wa-'Aadanw Wa-Samooda Wa-qad tabaiyana lakum min masaakinihim Wa-zaiyana lahumush Shaitaanu a'maalahum fasaddahum 'anis sabeeli Wa-kaanoo mustabsireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3379,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wa-Qaaroona Wa-Fir'awna Wa-haamaana Wa-laqad jaaa'ahum Moosa bilbaiyinaati fastakbaroo fil ardi Wa-maa kaanoo saabiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3380,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Fakullan akhaznaa bi-zanbihee faminhum man arsalnaa 'alaihi haasibaa; Wa-minhum man akhazat-hus saihatu Wa-minhum man khasafnaa bihil arda Wa-minhum man aghraqnaa; Wa-maa kaanal laahu li-yazlimahum Wa-laakin kaanoo anfusahum yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3381,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Masalul lazeenat takhazoo min doonil laahi awliyaaa'a kamasalil 'ankaboot, ittakhazat baitaa; Wa-inna awhanal buyooti la-baitul 'ankaboot; law kaanoo ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3382,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha ya'lamu maa yad'oona min doonihee min shai'; Wa-Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3383,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-tilkal amsaalu nadribuhaa linnaasi Wa-maa ya'qiluhaaa illal 'aalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3384,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Khalaqal laahus samaawaati wal-arda bilhaqq; inna fee zaalika la-aayatan lil-mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3385,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Utlu maaa oohiya ilaika minal Kitaabi Wa-aqimis Salaata innas Salaata tanhaa 'anil fahshaaa'i wal-munkar; Wa-lazikrul laahi akbar; wal-laahu ya'lamu maa tasna'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3386,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tujaadilooo Ahlal Kitaabi illaa billatee hiya ahsanu illal lazeena zalamoo minhum Wa-qoolooo aamannaa billazeee unzila ilainaa Wa-unzila ilaikum Wa-illaahunna Wa-illahukum waahidunw-wa nahnu lahoo muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3387,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazaalika anzalnaaa ilaikal Kitaab; fallazeena aatainaahumul kitaaba yu'minoona bihee Wa-min haaa'ulaaa'i many yu'minu bih; Wa-maa yajhadu bi'Aayaatinaa illal kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3388,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kunta tatloo min qablihee min kitaabinw Wa-laa takhuttubhoo bi-yameenika izal lartaabal mubtiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3389,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Bal huwa aayaatum baiyinaatun fee sudooril lazeena ootul 'ilm; Wa-maa yajhadu bi-aayaatinaa illaz zaalimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3390,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo law-laaa unzila 'alaihi aayaatum mir Rabbihee qul innamal aayaatu 'indal laahi Wa-innamaaa ana nazeerum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3391,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Awa-lam yakfihim annaaa anzalnaa 'alaikal kitaaba yutlaa 'alaihim; inna fee zaalika larahmatanw Wa-zikraa liqawmien yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3392,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Qul kafaa billaahi bainee Wa-bainakum shaheedaa; ya'lamu maa fis samaawaati wal-ard; wallazeena aamanoo bil-baatili Wa-kafaroo billaahi ulaaa'ika humul khaasiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3393,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-yasta'jiloonaka bil'azaab; Wa-law-laaa ajalum musammal lajaaa'ahumul a'zaab; Wa-la-ya'tiannahum baghta-tanw Wa-hum laa yash'uroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3394,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Yasta'jiloonaka bil'azaab; Wa-inna Jahannama la-muheetatum bil-kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3395,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Yawma yaghshaahumul 'azaabu min fawqihim Wa-min tahti arjulihim Wa-yaqoolu zooqoo maa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3396,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Yaa-'ibaadiyal lazeena aamanooo inna ardee waasi-'atun fa-iyyaaya fa'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3397,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 57,
      "text": "Kullu nafsin zaaa'iqatul mawti summa ilainaa turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3398,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati la-nubawwi-'annahum minal Jannati ghurafan tajree min tahtihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaa; ni'ma ajrul 'aamileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3399,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 59,
      "text": "Allazeena sabaroo Wa-'alaa Rabbihim yatawakkaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3400,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Wa-ka-ayyim min daaabbatil laa tahmilu rizqahaa; al-laahu yarzuquhaa Wa-iyyaakum; Wa-Huwas Samee'ul Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3401,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 61,
      "text":
          "Wa-la'in sa-altahum man khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda Wa-sakhkharash shamsa wal-qamara la-yaqoolunnal laahu fa-anna yu'fakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3402,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Allaahu yabsutur rizqa limaien yashaaa'u min 'ibaadihee Wa-yaqdiru lah; innal laaha bikulli shai'in Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3403,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Wa-la'in sa-altahum man nazzala minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa-ahyaa bihil arda min ba'di mawtihaa la-yaqoolunnal laah; qulil hamdu lillah; bal aksaruhum laa ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3404,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 64,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa haazihil hayaa-tud dunyaaa illaa lahwunw wa-la'ib; Wa-innad Daaral Aakhirata la-hiyal ha-yawaan; law kaano ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3405,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Fa-izaa rakiboo fil fulki da'awul laaha mukhliseena lahud deena falammaa najjaa-hum ilal barri izaa hum yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3406,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Li-yakfuroo bimaaa aatainaahum Wa-li-yatamatta'oo fasawfa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3407,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaraw annaa ja'alnaa haraman aaminanw Wa-yutakhattafun naasu min haw-lihim; afabil-baatili yu'minoona Wa-bini'matil laahi yakfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3408,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Wa-man azlamu mimma nif-taraa 'alal laahi kaziban aw kazzaba bilhaqqi lammaa jaaa'ah; alaisa fee jahannama maswal lil-kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3409,
      "sura": 29,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena jaahadoo feenaa lanahdiyannahum subulana; Wa-innal laaha lama'al muhsineen"
    },
    {"index": 3410, "sura": 30, "aya": 1, "text": "Alif-Laaam-Meeem"},
    {"index": 3411, "sura": 30, "aya": 2, "text": "Ghulibatir Room"},
    {
      "index": 3412,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "Feee adnal ardi Wa-hum mim ba'di ghalabihim sa-yaghliboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3413,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Fee bid'i sineen; lillaahil amru min qablu Wa-mim ba'd; Wa-yawma'izien yafrahul mu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3414,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 5,
      "text": "Binasril laa; yansuru maien yashaaa'u Wa-Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3415,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa'dal laahi laa yukhliful laahu wa'dahoo Wa-laakin-na aksaran naasi laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3416,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Ya'lamoona zaahiram minal hayaatid dunya Wa-hum 'anil Aakhirati hum ghaafiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3417,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Awalam yatafakkaroo feee anfusihim; maa khalaqal laahus samaawaati wal-arda Wa-maa bainahumaaa illaa bil-haqqi Wa-ajalim musammaa; Wa-inna kaseeram minan naasi biliqaaa'i Rabbihim lakaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3418,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaseeroo fil ardi fa-yanzuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul lazeena min qablihim; kaanooo ashadda minhhum quwwatanw Wa-asaarul arda Wa-'amaroohaaa aksara mimmaa 'amaroohaa Wa-jaaa'athum Rusuluhum bil-baiyyinaati famaa kaanal laahu liyazli-mahum Wa-laakin kaanooo anfusahum yazlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3419,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Summa kaana 'aaqibatal lazeena asaaa'us sooo-aaa an kazzaboo bi-aayaatil laahi Wa-kaanoo bihaa yastahzi'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3420,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 11,
      "text": "Allaahu yabda'ul khalqa summa yu'eeduhoo summa ilaihi turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3421,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 12,
      "text": "Wa-yawma taqoomus Saa'atu yublisul mujrimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3422,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-lam yakul lahum min shurakaaa'ihim shufa'aaa'u Wa-kaanoo bishurakaaa'ihim kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3423,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 14,
      "text": "Wa-Yawma taqoomus Saa'atu Yawma'izien yatafarraqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3424,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Fa-ammal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati fahum fee rawdatien yuhbaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3425,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Wa-ammal lazeena kafaroo Wa-kazzaboo bi-Aayaatinaa Wa-liqaaa'il Aakhirati faulaaa'ika fil 'azaabi muhdaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3426,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 17,
      "text": "Fa-Subhaanal laahi heena tumsoona Wa-heena tusbihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3427,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-lahul hamdu fis samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-'ashiyyanw Wa-heena tuzhiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3428,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Yukhrijul haiyya minal maiyyiti Wa-yukhrijul maiyyita minal haiyyi Wa-yuhyil arda ba'da mawtihaa; Wa-kazaalika tukhrajoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3429,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-min Aayaatiheee an khalaqakum min turaabin summa izaaa antum basharun tantashiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3430,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-min Aayaatiheee an khalaqa lakum min anfusikum azwaajal litaskunooo ilaihaa Wa-ja'ala bainakum mawad-datanw Wa-rahmah; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil liqawmien yatafakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3431,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-min Aayaatihee khalqus samaawaati wal-aardi wakhtilaafu alsinatikum Wa-alwaanikum; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil lil'aalimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3432,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa-min Aayaatihee manaamukum bil-laili wannahaari wabtighaaa'ukum min fadlih; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil liqawmien yasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3433,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Wa-min Aayaatihee yureekumul barqa khawfanw Wa-tama'anw Wa-yunazzilu minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa-yuhyee bihil arda ba'da mawtihaaa inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil liqawmien ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3434,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-min Aayaatihee an taqoomas samaaa'u wal-ardu bi-amrih; summa izaa da'aakum da'watam minal ardi izaaa antum takhrujoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3435,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 26,
      "text": "Wa-lahoo man fis samaawaati wal-ardi kullul lahoo qaanitoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3436,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wa-Huwal lazee yabda'ul khalqa summa yu'eeduhoo Wa-huwa ahwanu 'alaih; Wa-lahul masalul la'laa fis samaawaati wal-ard; Wa-Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3437,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Daraba lakum masalam min anfusikum hal lakum mimmaa malakat aymaanukum min shurakaaa'a fee maa razaqnaakum fa-antum feehi sawaaa'un takhaafoonahum kakheefa tikum anfusakum; kazaalika nufassilul Aayaati liqawminy ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3438,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Balit taba'al lazeena zalamooo ahwaaa'ahum bighairi 'ilmin famai yahdee man adallal laahu Wa-maa lahum min naasireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3439,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Fa-aqim wajhaka liddeeni Haneefaa; fitratal laahil latee fataran naasa 'alaihaa; laa taabdeela likhalqil laah; zaalikad deenul qaiyimu Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3440,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Muneebeena ilaihi wattaqoohu Wa-aqeemus Salaata Wa-laa takoonoo minal mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3441,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Minal lazeena farraqoo deenahum Wa-kaanoo shiya'an kullu hizbim bimaa ladaihim farihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3442,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa massan naasa durrun da'aw Rabbahum muneebeena ilaihi summa izaaa azaqahum minhu rahmatan izaa fareequm minhum bi-Rabbihim yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3443,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 34,
      "text": "Li-yakfuroo bimaaa aatainaahum; fatamatta'oo fasawfa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3444,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Am anzalnaa 'alaihim sultaanan fahuwa yatakallamu bimaa kaanoo bihee yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3445,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaaa azaqnan naasa rahmatan farihoo bihaa Wa-in tusibhum sayyi'atum bimaa qaddamat aydeehim izaa hum yaqnatoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3446,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaraw annal laaha yabsutur rizqa limaien yashaaa'u Wa-yaqdir; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil liqawmien yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3447,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Fa-aati zal qurbaa haqqahoo walmiskeena wabnassabeel; zaalika khairul lil lazeena yureedoona Wajhal laahi Wa-ulaaa'ika humul muflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3448,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa aataitum mir ribal li-yarbuwa feee amwaalin naasi falaa yarboo 'indal laahi Wa-maaa aataitum min zaakaatin tureedoona wajhal laahi fa-ulaaa'ika humul mud'ifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3449,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Allaahul lazee khalaqa-kum summa razaqakum summa yumeetukum summa yuhyeekum hal min shurakaaa'ikum maien yaf'alu min zaalikum min shai'; Sub-haanahoo Wa-Ta'aalaa 'ammaa yushrikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3450,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Zaharal fasaadu fil barri wal-bahri bimaa kasabat aydin naasi li-yuzeeqahum ba'dal lazee 'amiloo la'allahum yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3451,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Qul seeroo fil ardi fanzuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul lazeena min qabl; kaana aksaruhum mushrikeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3452,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Fa-aqim wajhaka lid-deenil qaiyyimi min qabli aien yaatiya Yawmul laa maradda lahoo minal laahi Yawma'izien yassadda'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3453,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Man kafara fa'alaihi kufruhoo Wa-man 'amila saalihan fali-anfusihim yamhadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3454,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Li-yajziyal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati min fadlih; innahoo laa yuhibbul kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3455,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-min Aayaatiheee aien yursilar riyaaha mubashshi-raatinw Wa-li-yuzeeqakum mir rahmatihee Wa-litajriyal fulku bi-amrihee Wa-litabtaghoo min fadlihee Wa-la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3456,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad arsalnaa min qablika Rusulan ilaa qawmihim fajaaa'oohum bil-baiyyinaati fantaqamnaa minal lazeena ajramoo Wa-kaana haqqan 'alainaa nasrul mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3457,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Allaahul lazee yursilur riyaaha fatuseeru sahaaban fa-yabsutuhoo fis samaaa'i kaifa yashaaa'u Wa-yaj'aluhoo kisafan fataral wadqa yakhruju min khilaalihee fa-izaaa asaaba bihee mai yashaaa'u min 'ibaadiheee izaa hum yastabshiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3458,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Wa-in kaanoo min qabli aien yunazzala 'alaihim min qablihee lamubliseen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3459,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Fanzur ilaaa aasaari rahmatil laahi kaifa yuhyil arda ba'da mawtihaa; inna zaalika lamuhyil mawtaa Wa-Huwa 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3460,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Wa-la'in arsalnaa reehan fara-awhu musfarral lazalloo mim ba'dihee yakfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3461,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Fa-innaka laa tusmi'ul mawtaa Wa-laa tusmi'us summad du'aaa'a izaa wallaw mudbireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3462,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa anta bihaadil 'umyi 'an dalaalatihim in tusmi'u illaa maien yuminu bi-aayaatinaa fahum muslimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3463,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Allahul lazee khalaqa-kum min du'fin summa ja'ala mim ba'di du'fin quwwatan summa ja'ala mim ba'di quwwatin du'fanw Wa-shaibah; yakhluqu maa yashaaa'u Wa-Huwal 'Aleemul Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3464,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Wa-Yawma taqoomus Saa'atu yuqsimul mujrimoona maa labisoo ghaira saa'ah; kazaalika kaanoo yu'fakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3465,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena ootul 'ilma wal-eemaana laqad labistum fee kitaabil laahi ilaa yawmil ba'si fahaazaa yawmul ba'si Wa-laakinnakum kuntum laa ta'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3466,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Fa-Yawma'izil laa yanfa'ul lazeena zalamoo ma'ziratu-hum Wa-laa hum yusta'taboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3467,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad darabnaa linnaasi fee haazal Quraani min kulli masal; Wa-la'in ji'tahum bi-aayatil la-yaqoolannal lazeena kafaroo in antum illaa mubtiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3468,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 59,
      "text": "Kazaalika yatba'ul laahu 'alaa quloobil lazeena laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3469,
      "sura": 30,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Fasbir inna wa'dal laahi haqqunw Wa-laa yastakhif-fannakal lazeena laa yooqinoon"
    },
    {"index": 3470, "sura": 31, "aya": 1, "text": "Alif-Laaam-Meeem"},
    {
      "index": 3471,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Tilka Aayaatul Kitaabil Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3472,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "Hudanw Wa-rahmatal lilmuhsineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3473,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yuqeemoonas Salaata Wa-yu'toonaz Zakaata Wa-hum bil-Aakhirati hum yooqinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3474,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 5,
      "text": "Ulaaa'ika 'alaa hudam mir Rabbihim Wa-ulaaa'ika humul muflihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3475,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-minan naasi maien yashtaree lahuwal hadeesi li-yudilla 'an sabeelil laahi bighairi 'ilminw Wa-yattakhizahaa huzuwaa; ulaaa'ika lahum 'azaabum muheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3476,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa tutlaa 'alayhi Aayaatunaa wallaa mustakbiran ka-al lam yasma'haa ka-anna feee uzunaihi waqran fabash-shiru bi'azaabin aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3477,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati lahum Janaatun Na'eem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3478,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 9,
      "text": "Khaalideena feeha wa'dal laahi haqqaa; Wa-Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3479,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Khalaqas samaawaati bi-ghairi 'amadin tarawnahaa Wa-alqaa fil ardi rawaasiya an tameeda bikum Wa-bassa feehaa min kulli daaabbah; Wa-anzalnaa minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa-ambatnaa feeha min kulli zawjin kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3480,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Haazaa khalqul laahi fa-aroonee maazaa khalaqal lazeena min doonih; baliz zaalimoona fee dalalim Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3481,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Luqmaanal hikmata anish kur lillaah; Wa-maien yashkur fa-innamaa yashkuru linafsihee Wa-man kafara fa-innal laaha Ghaniyyun Hameed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3482,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaala luqmaanu libnihee Wa-huwa ya'izuhoo ya-bunaiya laa tushrik billaah; innash shirka lazulmun 'azeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3483,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Wa-wassainal insaana bi-waalidaihi hamalat hu ummuhoo wahnan 'alaa wahninw Wa-fisaaluhoo fee 'aamaini anishkur lee Wa-liwaalidaika ilaiyal maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3484,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wa-in jaahadaaka 'alaaa an tushrika bee maa laisa laka bihee 'ilmun falaa tuti'humaa Wa-saahib-humaa fid dunyaa ma'roofanw wattabi' sabeela man anaaba ilayy; summa ilaiyya marji'ukum fa-unabbi'ukum bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3485,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Ya-bunaiya innahaaa in taku misqaala habbatim min khardalin fatakun fee sakhratin aw fis samaawaati aw fil ardi yaati bihal laa; innal laaha lateefun Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3486,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Yaa bunaiya aqimis-Salaata waamur bilma'roofi wanha 'anil munkari wasbir 'alaa maaa asaabaka inna zaalika min 'azmil umoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3487,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tusa'-ir khaddaka linnaasi Wa-laa tamshi fil ardi maarahan innal laaha laa yuhibbu kulla mukhtaalin fakhoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3488,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Waqsid fee mashyika waghdud min sawtik; inna ankaral aswaati lasawtul hameer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3489,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Alam taraw annal laaha sakhkhara lakum maa fis sa-maawaati Wa-maa fil ardi Wa-asbaha 'alaikum ni'amahoo zaahiratanw Wa-baatinah; Wa-minan naasi many yujaadilu fil laahi bighayri 'ilminw Wa-laa hudanw Wa-laa Kitaabim muneer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3490,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahumut tabi'oo maaa anzalal laahu qaaloo bal nattabi'u maa wajadnaa 'alaihi aabaaa'anaa; awalaw kaanash Shaitaanu yad'oohum ilaa 'azaabis sa'eer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3491,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yuslim wajha-hooo ilal laahi Wa-huwa muhsinun faqadistamsaka bil'ur watil wusqaa; Wa-ilal laahi 'aaqibatul umoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3492,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa-man kafara falaa yahzunka kufruh; ilainaa marji'uhum fanunabbi'uhum bimaa 'amiloo; innal laaha 'aleemum bizaatis sudoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3493,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 24,
      "text": "Numatti'uhum qaleelan summa nadtarruhum ilaa 'azaabin ghaleez"
    },
    {
      "index": 3494,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-la'in sa-altahum man khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda la-yaqoolunnal laah; qulil hamdu lillaah; bal aksaruhum laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3495,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Lilaahi ma fis samaa-waati wal-ard; innal laaha Huwal Ghaniyyul Hameed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3496,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wa-law annamaa fil ardi min shajaratin aqlaamunw wal-bahru yamudduhoo mim ba'dihee sab'atu abhurim maa nafidat Kalimaatul laah; innal laaha 'azeezun Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3497,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Maa khalqukum Wa-laa ba'sukum illaa kanafsinw-waa hidah; innal laaha Samee'um Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3498,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annal laaha yoolijul laila fin nahaari Wa-yoolijun nahaara fil laili Wa-sakhkharash shamsa wal-qamara kulluny yajreee ilaaa ajalim musammanw Wa-annal laaha bimaa ta'maloona Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3499,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Zaalika bi-annal laaha Huwal Haqqu Wa-anna maa yad'oona min doonihil baatilu Wa-annal laaha Huwal 'Aliyyul Kabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3500,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annal fulka tajree fil bahri bini'matil laahi li-yuriyakum min Aayaatih; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil likulli sabbaarin shakoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3501,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa ghashiyahum mawjun kazzulali da'a-wul laaha mukhliseena lahud deena fa-lammaa najjaahum ilal barri faminhum muqtasid; Wa-maa yajhadu bi-Aayaatinaa illaa kullu khattaarin kafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3502,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhan naasut taqoo Rabbakum wakhshaw Yawmal laa yajzee waalidun 'anw waladihee Wa-laa mawloodun huwa jaazin 'anw waalidihee shai'aa; innaa wa'dal laahi haqqun falaa taghurran-nakumul hayaatud dunyaa Wa-laa yaghur-rannakum billaahil gharoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3503,
      "sura": 31,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha 'indahoo 'ilmus saa'ati Wa-yunazzilul ghaisa Wa-ya'lamu maa fil arhaami Wa-maa tadree nafsum maazaa taksibu ghadaa; Wa-maa tadree nafsum bi-ayyi ardin tamoot; innal laaha 'Aleemun Khabeer"
    },
    {"index": 3504, "sura": 32, "aya": 1, "text": "Alif-Laaam-Meeem"},
    {
      "index": 3505,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 2,
      "text": "Tanzeelul Kitaabi laa raiba feehi mir rabbil 'aalameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3506,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Am yaqooloonaf taraahu bal huwal haqqu mir rabbika litunzira qawma maaa ataahum min nazeerim min qablika la'allahum yahtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3507,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Allaahul lazee khalaqas samaawaati wal-arda Wa-maa bainahumaa fee sittati ayyaamin thummas tawaa 'alal 'arsh; maa lakum min doonihee minw waliyyinw wala shafee'; afalaa tatazakkaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3508,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Yudabbirul amra minas samaaa'i ilal ardi thumma ya'ruju ilaihi fee yawmin kaana miqdaaruhooo alfa sanatim mimmaa ta'uddoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3509,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 6,
      "text": "Zaalika 'aalimul ghaybi Wa-shahaadatil 'azeezur raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3510,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Allazee ahsana kulla shai-in khalaqa; Wa-bada-a khalqal insaani min teen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3511,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 8,
      "text": "Thumma ja'ala naslahoo min sulaalatim mim maaa'im maheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3512,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Thumma sawwaahu Wa-nafakha feehi mir roohihih; Wa-ja'ala lakumus sam'a wal-absaara wal-af'idah; qaleelam maa tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3513,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalooo 'a-izaa dalalnaa fil ardi 'a-innaa lafee khalqin jadeed; bal hum biliqaaa'i rabbihim kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3514,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Qul yatawaffaakum malakul mawtil lazee wukkila bikum Thumma ilaa rabbikum turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3515,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-law taraaa izil mujrimoona naakisoo ru'oosihim 'inda rabbihim rabbanaaa absarnaa Wa-sami'naa farji'naa na'mal saalihan innaa mooqinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3516,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-law shi'naa la-aatainaa kulla nafsin hudaahaa Wa-laakin haqqal qawlu minnee la-amla'anna jahannama minal jinnati wannaasi ajma'een"
    },
    {
      "index": 3517,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Fazooqoo bimaa naseetum liqaaa'a yawminkum haaza innaa naseenaakum Wa-zooqoo 'azaabal khuldi bimaa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3518,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Innamaa yu'minu bi-aayaatinal lazeena izaa zukkiroo bihaa kharroo sujjadanw Wa-sabbahoo bihamdi rabbihim Wa-hum laa yastakbiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3519,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Tatajaafaa junoobuhum 'anil madaaji'i yad'oona rabbahum khawfanw Wa-tama'anw Wa-mimmaa razaqnaahum yunfiqoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3520,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Falaa ta'lamu nafsum maaa ukhfiya lahum min qurrati a'yunin jazaaa'am bimaa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3521,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 18,
      "text": "Afaman kaana mu'minan kaman kaana faasiqaa; laa yasta-woon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3522,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Ammal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati falahum jannaatul ma'waa nuzulam bimaa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3523,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-ammal lazeena fasaqoo fama'waahumun Naaru kullamaaa araadooo any yakhrujoo minhaaa u'eedoo feehaa Wa-qeela lahum zooqoo 'azaaaban Naaril lazee kuntum bihee tukazziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3524,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-lanuzeeqan-nahum minal 'azaabil ladnaa doonal 'azaabil akbari la'allahum yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3525,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-man azlamu mimman zukkira bi-aayaati rabbihee summa a'rada 'anhaa; innaa minal mujrimeena muntaqimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3526,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Moosal Kitaaba falaa takun fee miryatim mil liqaaa'ihee Wa-ja'alnaahu hudal li-Baneee Israaa'eel"
    },
    {
      "index": 3527,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnaa minhum a'immataien yahdoona bi-amrinaa lammaa sabaroo Wa-kaanoo bi-aayaatinaa yooqinoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3528,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Inna rabbaka huwa yafsilu bainahum yawmal qiyaamati feemaa kaanoo feehi yakhtalifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3529,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Awalam yahdi lahum kam ahlaknaa min qablihim minal qurooni yamshoona fee masaakinihim; inna fee zaalika la-aayaatin afalaa yasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3530,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaraw annaa nasooqul maaa'a ilal ardil juruzi fanukhriju bihee zar'an ta'kulu minhu an'aamuhum Wa-anfusuhum afalaa yubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3531,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 28,
      "text": "Wa-yaqooloona mataa haazal fath-hu in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3532,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Qul yawmal fath-hi laa yanfa'ul lazeena kafarooo eemaanuhum Wa-laa hum yunzaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3533,
      "sura": 32,
      "aya": 30,
      "text": "Fa-a'rid 'anhum wantazir innahum muntaziroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3534,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Yaa-aiyuhan Nabiyyut taqil laaha Wa-laa tuti'il kaafireena wal-munaafiqeen; innal laaha kaana 'aleeman Hakeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3535,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Wattabi' maa yoohaaa ilaika mir Rabbik; innal laaha kaana bimaa ta'maloona Khabeera"
    },
    {
      "index": 3536,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 3,
      "text": "Wa-tawakkal 'alal laah; Wa-kafaa billaahi Wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3537,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Maa ja'alal laahu lirajulim min qalbaini fee jawfih; Wa-maa ja'ala azwaajakumul laaa'ee tuzaahiroona minhunna ummahaatikum; Wa-maa ja'ala ad'iyaaa'akum abnaaa'akum; zaalikum qawlukum bi-afwaa-hikum wallaahu yaqoolul haqqa Wa-Huwa yahdis sabeel"
    },
    {
      "index": 3538,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Ud'oohum li-aabaaa'ihim huwa aqsatu 'indal laah; fa-il lam ta'lamooo aabaaa'ahum fa-ikhwaanukum fid deeni Wa-mawaaleekum; Wa-laisa 'alaikum junaahun feemaaa akhtaatum bihee Wa-laakim maa ta'ammadat quloobukum; Wa-kaanal laahu Ghafoorar Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3539,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "An-Nabiyyu awlaa bil-mu'mineena min anfusihim Wa-azwaajuhoo ummahatuhum Wa-ulul arhaami ba'duhum awlaa biba'din fee Kitaabil laahi minal mu'meneena wal-Muhaajireena illaaa an taf'alooo ilaaa awliyaaa'ikum ma'roofaa; kaana zaalika fil kitaabi mastooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3540,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz akhaznaa minan Nabiyyeena meesaaqahum Wa-minka Wa-min Noohinw Wa-Ibraaheema Wa-Moosaa Wa-Eesab ni Maryama Wa-akhaznaa minhum meesaaqan ghaleezaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3541,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Liyas'alas saadiqeena 'an sidqihim; Wa-a'adda lilkaa-fireena 'azaaban aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3542,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanuz kuroo ni'matal laahi 'alaikum iz jaaa'atkum junoodun fa-arsalnaa 'alaihim reehanw Wa-junoodal lam tarawhaa; Wa-kaanal laahu bimaa ta'maloona Baseera"
    },
    {
      "index": 3543,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Iz jaaa'ookum min fawqikum Wa-min asfala minkum Wa-iz zaaghatil absaaru Wa-balaghatil quloobul hanaajira Wa-tazunnoona billaahiz zunoonaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3544,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 11,
      "text": "Hunaalikab tuliyal mu'minoona Wa-zulziloo zilzaalan shadeedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3545,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz yaqoolul munaafiqoona wallazeena fee quloobihim maradum maa wa'adanal laahu Wa-Rasooluhooo illaa ghurooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3546,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz qaalat taaa'ifatum minhum yaaa-ahla Yasriba laa muqaamaa lakum farji'oo; Wa-yastaazinu fareequm minhumun Nabiyya yaqooloona inna buyootanaa 'awrah; Wa-maa hiya bi'awratin iny yureedoona illaa firaaraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3547,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "wa-law dukhilat 'alaihim min aqtaarihaa summa su'ilul fitnata la-aatawhaa Wa-maa talabbasoo bihaaa illaa yaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3548,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad kaanoo 'aahadul laaha min qablu laa yuwal-loonal adbaar; Wa-kaana 'ahdul laahi mas'oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3549,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Qul laien yanfa'akumul firaaru in farartum minal mawti awil qatli Wa-izal laa tumatta'oona illaa qaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3550,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 17,
      "text":
          "Qul man zal lazee ya'simukum minal laahi in araada bikum sooo'an aw araada bikum rahmah; Wa-laa yajidoona lahum min doonil laahi waliyyanw Wa-laa naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3551,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Qad ya'lamul laahul mu'awwiqeena minkum walqaaa'ileena li-ikhwaanihim halumma ilainaa, Wa-laa yaatoonal baasa illaa qaleelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3552,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Ashihhatan 'alaikum faizaa jaaa'al khawfu ra-aytahum yanzuroona ilaika tadooru a'yunuhum kallazee yughshaa 'alaihi minal mawti fa-izaa zahabal khawfu salqookum bi-alsinatin hidaadin ashibbatan 'alal khayr; ulaaa'ika lam yu'minoo fa-ahbatal laahu a'maalahum; Wa-kaana zaalika 'alal laahi yaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3553,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Yahsaboonal Ahzaaba lam yazhaboo Wa-ien yaatil Ahzaabu yawaddoo law annahum baadoona fil A'raabi yasaloona 'an ambaaa'ikum Wa-law kaanoo feekum maa qaatalooo illaa qaleela"
    },
    {
      "index": 3554,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Laqad kaana lakum fee Rasoolil laahi uswatun hasanatul liman kaana yarjul laaha wal-yawmal Aakhira Wa-azkaral laaha kaseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3555,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-lammaa ra al-mu'minoonal Ahzaaba qaaloo haazaa maa wa'adanal laahu Wa-Rasooluh; Wa-sadaqal laahu Wa-Rasooluh; Wa-maa zaadahum illaaa eemaananw Wa-tasleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3556,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Minal mu'mineena rijaalun sadaqoo maa 'aahadul laaha 'alaihi faminhum man qadaa nahbahoo Wa-minhum mai yantaziru Wa-maa baddaloo tabdeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3557,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Li-yajziyal aahus saadiqeena bisidqihim Wa-yu'azzibal munaafiqeena in shaaa'a aw yatooba 'alaihim; innal laaha kaana Ghafoorar Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3558,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-raddal laahul lazeena kafaroo bighaizihim lam yanaaloo khairaa; Wa-kafal laahul mu'mineenal qitaal; Wa-kaanal laahu Qawiyyan 'Azeezaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3559,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Wa-anzalal lazeena zaaha-roohum min Ahlil Kitaabi min sa-yaaseehim Wa-qazafa fee quloobihimm mur-ru'ba fareeqan taqtuloona Wa-taasiroona fareeqaaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3560,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Wa-awrasakum ardahum Wa-diyaarahum Wa-amwaalahum Wa-ardal lam tata'oohaa; Wa-kaanal laahu 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3561,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhan Nabiyyu qul li-azwaajika in kuntunna turidnal hayaatad dunyaa Wa-zeenatahaa fata'aalaina umatti'kunna Wa-usarrihkunna saraahan jameela"
    },
    {
      "index": 3562,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Wa-in kuntunna turidnal laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo wad-Daaral Aakhirata fa-innal laaha a'adda lil-muhsinaati min-kunna ajjran 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3563,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Yaa-nisaaa'an Nabiyyi maien yaati minkunna bifaa-hishatim mubaiyyinatien yudaa'af lahal 'azaabu di'faini Wa-kaana zaalika 'alal laahi yaseera"
    },
    {
      "index": 3564,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-maien yaqnut minkunna lillaahi Wa-Rasoolihee Wa-ta'mal saalihan nu'tihaaa ajrahaa marratayni Wa-a'tadnaa lahaa rizqan kareema"
    },
    {
      "index": 3565,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Yaa-nisaaa'an Nabiyyi lastunna ka-ahadim minan nisaaa'i init taqaitunna falaa takhda'na bilqawli fa-yatma'al lazee fee qalbihee maradunw Wa-qulna qawlam ma'roofaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3566,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-qarna fee bu-yoo-tikunna Wa-laa tabarrajna tabarrujal Jaahiliyyatil oolaa Wa-aqimnas Salaata Wa-aaateenaz Zakaata Wa-ati'nal laaha Wa-Rasoolah; innamaa yureedul laahu liyuzhiba 'ankumur rijsa Ahlal Bayti Wa-yutahhirakum tatheeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3567,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wazkurna maa yutlaa fee bu-yootikunna min aayaatil laahi wal-Hikmah; innal laaha kaana lateefan Khabeera"
    },
    {
      "index": 3568,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Innal muslimeena wal-muslimaati wal-mu'mineena wal-mu'minaati walqaaniteena walqaanitaati wassaadiqeena wassaadiqaati wassaabireena wassaabiraati walkhaashi'eena walkhaashi'aati walmutasaddiqeena walmutasaddiqaati wassaaa'imeena wassaaa'imaati walhaafizeena furoojahum walhaafizaati waz-zaakireenal laaha kaseeranw waz-zaakiraati a'addal laahu lahum maghfiratanw Wa-ajran 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3569,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana limu'mininw Wa-laa mu'minatin izaa qadal laahu Wa-Rasooluhooo amran aien yakoona lahumul khiyaratu min amrihim; Wa-maien ya'sil laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo faqad dalla dalaalam mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3570,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-iz taqoolu lillazeee an'amal laahu 'alaihi Wa-an'amta 'alaihi amsik 'alaika zawjaka wattaqil laaha Wa-tukhfee fee nafsika mal laahu mubdeehi Wa-takhshan naasa wallaahu ahaqqu an takhshaah; falammaa qadaa Zaidum minhaa wataran zawwajnaa-kahaa likay laa yakoona 'alal mu'mineena harajun feee azwaaji ad'iyaaa'ihim izaa qadaw minhunna wataraa; Wa-kaana amrul laahi maf'oolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3571,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Maa kaana 'alan nabiyyyi min harajin feemaa faradal laahu lahoo sunnatal laahi fil lazeena khalaw min qabl; Wa-kaana amrul laahi qadaram maqdooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3572,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Allazeena yuballighoona Risaalaatil laahi Wa-yakhshaw-nahoo Wa-laa yakkhshawna ahadan illal laah; Wa-kafaa billaahi Haseebaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3573,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Maa kaana Muhammmadun abaaa ahadim mir rijaalikum Wa-laakir Rasoolal laahi Wa-Khaataman Nabiyyeen; Wa-kaanal laahu bikulli shai'in 'Aleema"
    },
    {
      "index": 3574,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 41,
      "text": "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanuz kurul laaha zikran kaseera"
    },
    {
      "index": 3575,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 42,
      "text": "Wa-sabbihoohu bukratanw Wa-aseela"
    },
    {
      "index": 3576,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazee yusallee 'alaikum Wa-malaaa'ikatuhoo liyukhrijakum minaz zulumaati ilan noor Wa-kaana bilmu'mineena Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3577,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Tahiyyatuhum Yawma yalqawnahoo salaamunw Wa-a'adda lahum ajran kareemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3578,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhan Nabiyyu innaaa arsalnaaka shaahidanw Wa-mubashshiranw Wa-nazeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3579,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 46,
      "text": "Wa-daa'iyan ilal laahi bi-iznihee Wa-siraajam muneeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3580,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-bashshiril mu'mineena bi-annna lahum minal laahi fadlan kabeera"
    },
    {
      "index": 3581,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 48,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tuti'il kaafireena walmunaafiqeena Wa-da 'azaahum Wa-tawakkal 'alal laah; Wa-kafaa billaahi Wakeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3582,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanooo izaa nakahtumul mu'minaati summa tallaqtu-moohunna min qabli an tamas-soohunna famaa lakum 'alaihinna min 'iddatin ta'taddoonahaa famatti'oohunna Wa-sarri-hoohunna saraahan jameelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3583,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhan Nabiyyu innaaa ahlalnaa laka azwaa-jakal laatee aataiyta ujoora-hunna Wa-maa malakat yameenuka mimmaaa afaaa'al laahu 'alaika Wa-banaati 'ammika Wa-banaati 'ammaatika Wa-banaati khaalika Wa-banaati khaalaa-tikal laatee haajarna ma'aka wamra'-atan mu'minatan inw wahabat nafsahaa lin-Nabiyyi in araadan Nabiyyu aien yastan-kihahaa khaalisatan laka min doonil mu'mineen; qad 'alimnaa maa faradnaa 'alaihim feee azwaajihim Wa-maa malakat aimaanuhum li-kailaa yakoona 'alaika haraj; Wa-kaanal laahu Ghafoorar Raheema"
    },
    {
      "index": 3584,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Turjee man tashaaa'u minhunna Wa-tu'weee ilaika man tashaaa'u Wa-manib ta-ghaita mimman 'azalta falaa junaaha 'alaik; zaalika adnaaa an taqarra a'yunuhunna Wa-laa yahzanna Wa-yardaina bimaa aataitahunna kulluhunn; wal-laahu ya'lamu maa fee quloo-bikum; Wa-kaanal laahu 'Aleeman haleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3585,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Laa yahillu lakan nisaaa'u mim ba'du Wa-laaa an tabaddala bihinna min azwaajinw Wa-law ajabaka husnuhunna illaa maa malakat yameenukk; Wa-kaanal laahu 'alaa kulli shai'ir Raqeeba"
    },
    {
      "index": 3586,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo laa tadkhuloo bu-yootan Nabiyyi ilaaa aien yu'zana lakum ilaa ta'aamin ghaira naazireena inaahu Wa-laakin izaa du'eetum fadkhuloo fa-izaa ta'imtum fantashiroo Wa-laa mustaaniseena lihadees; inna zaalikum kaana yu'zin Nabiyya fa-yastahyee minkum wallaahu laa yastahyee minal haqq; Wa-izaa sa-altumoohunna mataa'an fas'aloohunna minw waraaa'i hijaab; zaalikum atharu liquloobikum Wa-quloobihinn; Wa-maa kaana lakum an tu'zoo Rasoolal laahi Wa-laaa an tankihooo azwaajahoo mim ba'diheee abadaa; inna zaalikum kaana 'indal laahi 'azeema"
    },
    {
      "index": 3587,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "In tubdoo shai'an aw tukhfoohu fa-innal laaha kaana bikulli shai'in 'Aleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3588,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 55,
      "text":
          "Laa junaaha 'alaihinna feee aabaaa'ihinna Wa-laaa abnaaa'ihinna Wa-laaa ikhwaanihinnna Wa-laaa abnaaa'i ikhwaanihinna Wa-laaa abnaaa'i akhawaatihinna Wa-laa nisaaa'i-hinna Wa-laa Maa malakat aimaanuhunn; wattaqeenal laah; innal laaha kaana 'alaa kulli shai'in Shaheedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3589,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 56,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha Wa-malaaa'i-katahoo yusalloona 'alan Nabiyy; yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo salloo 'alaihi Wa-sallimoo tasleemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3590,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 57,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yu'zoonal laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo la'anahumul laahu fid dunyaa wal-Aakhirati Wa-a'adda lahum 'azaabam muheenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3591,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 58,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yu'zoonal mu'mineena almu'manaati bighairi mak tasaboo faqadih tamaloo buhtaananw Wa-ismam mubeenaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3592,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 59,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhan Nabiyyu qul li-azwaajika Wa-banaatika Wa-nisaaa'il mu'mineena yudneena 'alaihinna min jalaabee-bihinn; zaalika adnaaa aien yu'rafna falaa yu'zain; Wa-kaanal laahu Ghafoorar Raheemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3593,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "La'il lam yantahil munaafiqoona wallazeena fee quloobihim maradunw walmur-jifoona fil madeenati lanughri-yannaka bihim summa laa yujaawiroonaka feehaaa illaa qaleela"
    },
    {
      "index": 3594,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 61,
      "text": "Mal'ooneena ainamaa suqifoo ukhizoo Wa-quttiloo taqteelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3595,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Sunnatal laahi fil lazeena khalaw min qablu Wa-lan tajida lisunnatil laahi tabdeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3596,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 63,
      "text":
          "Yas'alukan naasu 'anis Saa'ati qul innamaa 'ilmuhaa 'indal laah; Wa-maa yudreeka la'allas Saa'ata takoonu qareebaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3597,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 64,
      "text": "Innal laaha la'anal kaafireena Wa-a'adda lahum sa'eeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3598,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Khaalideena feehaaa abadaa, laa yajidoona waliyyanw Wa-laa naseeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3599,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Yawma tuqallabu wujoohuhum fin Naari yaqooloona yaa-laitanaaa ata'nal laaha Wa-ata'nar Rasoolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3600,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo Rabbanaaa innaaa ata'naa saadatanaa Wa-kubaraaa'anaa fa-adalloonas sabeelaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3601,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 68,
      "text":
          "Rabbanaaa aatihim di'fai-ni minal 'azaabi wal'anhum la-nan kabeera"
    },
    {
      "index": 3602,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "yaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanoo las takoonoo kalla-zeena aazaw Moosaa fa-barra-ahul laahu mimmmaa qaaloo; Wa-kaana 'indal laahi wajeehaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3603,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 70,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-aiyyuhal lazeena aamanut taqul laaha Wa-qooloo qawlan sadeedaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3604,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Yuslih lakum a'maalakum Wa-yaghfir lakum zunoobakum; Wa-mai yuti'il laaha Wa-Rasoolahoo faqad faaza fawzan 'azeemaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3605,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 72,
      "text":
          "Innaa 'aradnal amaanata 'alas samaawaati walardi wal-jibaali fa-abaina aien yahmil-nahaa Wa-ashfaqna minhaa Wa-hamalahal insaanu innahoo kaana zalooman jahoolaa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3606,
      "sura": 33,
      "aya": 73,
      "text":
          "Liyu-'azzibal laahul munaafiqeena wal-munaafiqaati walmushrikeena wal-mushrikaati Wa-yatoobal laahu 'alal mu'mineena walmu'minaat; Wa-kaanal laahu Ghafoorar Raheema"
    },
    {
      "index": 3607,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Alhamdu lillaahil lazee lahoo maa fis samaawaati Wa-maa fil ardi Wa-lahul hamdu fil aakhirah; Wa-Huwal Hakeemul Khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3608,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Ya'lamu maa yaliju fil ardi Wa-maa yakhruju minhaa Wa-maa yanzilu minas samaaa'i Wa-maa ya'ruju feehaa; Wa-Huwar Raheemul Ghafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3609,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena kafaroo laa taateenas Saa'ah; qul balaa Wa-Rabbee lataatiyannakum 'Aalimul Ghaib; laa ya'zubu 'anhu misqaalu zarratin fis samaawaati Wa-laa fil ardi Wa-laaa asgharu min zaalika Wa-laaa akbaru illaa fee kitaabim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3610,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Liyajziyal lazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaat; ulaaa'ika lahum maghfiratunw Wa-rizqun kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3611,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena sa'aw feee aayaatinaa mu'aajizeena ulaaa-'ika lahum 'azaabum mir rijzin aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3612,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Wa-yaral lazeena ootul 'ilmal lazeee unzila ilaika mir Rabbika huwal haqqa Wa-yahdeee ilaaa siraatil 'Azeezil Hameed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3613,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena kafaroo hal nadullukum 'alaa rajuliny yanabbi-'ukum izaa muzziqtum kulla mumazzaqin innakum lafee khalqin jadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3614,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Aftaraa 'alal laahi kaziban am bihee jinnah; balil lazeena laa yu'minoona bil-Aakhirati fil'azaabi wad dalaalil ba'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3615,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Afalam yaraw ilaa maa baina aydeehim Wa-maa khalfahum minas samaaa'i wal-ard; in nashad nakhsif bihimul arda aw nusqit 'alaihim kisafam minas samaaa'; inna fee zaalika la-Aayatal likulli 'abdim muneeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 3616,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad aatainaa Daawooda minnaa fadlaien yaa-jibaalu awwibee ma'ahoo wattaira Wa-alannaa lahul hadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3617,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Ani 'mal saabighaatinw Wa-qaddir fis sardi wa'maloo saalihan innee bimaa ta'maloona Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3618,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-li-Sulaimaanar reeha ghuduwwuhaa shahrunw Wa-ra-waahuhaa shahrunw Wa-asalnaa lahoo 'ainal qitr; Wa-minal jinni maien ya'malu baina yadaihi bi-izni Rabbih; Wa-maien yazigh minhum 'an amrinaa nuziqhu min 'azaabis sa'eer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3619,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Ya'maloona lahoo ma yashaaa'u mim mahaareeba Wa-tamaaseela Wa-jifaanin kaljawaabi Wa-qudoorir raasiyaat; i'maloo aala Daawooda shukraa; Wa-qaleelum min 'ibaadiyash shakoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3620,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Falammaa qadainaa 'alaihil mawta ma dallahum 'alaa mawtiheee illaa daaabbatul ardi taakulu minsa-atahoo falammaa kharra tabaiyyanatil jinnu al law kaanoo ya'lamoonal ghaiba maa labisoo fil 'azaabil muheen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3621,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Laqad kaana li-Saba-in fee maskanihim Aayatun jannataani 'aien yameeninw Wa-shimaalin kuloo mir rizq Rabbikum washkuroo lah; baldatun taiyyibatunw Wa-Rabbun Ghafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3622,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 16,
      "text":
          "Fa-a'radoo fa-arsalnaa 'alaihim Sailal 'Arimi Wa-baddalnaahum bijannataihim jannataini zawaatai ukulin khamtinw Wa-aslinw Wa-shai'im min sidrin qaleel"
    },
    {
      "index": 3623,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 17,
      "text": "Zaalika jazainaahum bimaa kafaroo Wa-hal nujaazeee illal kafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3624,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnaa bainahum Wa-bainal qural latee baaraknaa feehaa quran zaahiratanw Wa-qaddamaa feehas sayr; seeroo feehaa la-yaalirya Wa-aiyaaman aamineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3625,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Faqaaloo Rabbanaa baa'id baina asfaarinaa Wa-zalamooo anfusahum faja'alnaahum ahaadeesa Wa-mazzaq-naahum kulla mumazzaq; inna fee zaalika la-Aayaatil likulli sabbaarin shakoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3626,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad saddaq 'alaihim Ibleesu zannnabhoo fattaba'oohu illaa fareeqam minal mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3627,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 21,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa kaana lahoo 'alaihim min sultaanin illaa lina'lama maien yu-minu bil-Aakhirati mimman huwa minhaa fee shakk; Wa-Rabbuka 'alaa kulli shai'in Hafeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 3628,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Qulid 'ul lazeena za'amtum min doonil laahi laa yamlikoona misqaala zarratin fis samaawaati Wa-laa fil ardi Wa-maa lahum feehimaa min shirkinw Wa-maa lahoo minhum min zaheer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3629,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa tanfa'ush shafaa'atu 'indahooo illaa liman azina lah; hattaaa izaa fuzzi'a 'an quloobihim qaaloo maazaa qaala Rabbukum; qaalul haqq, Wa-Huwal 'Aliyul Kabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3630,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Qul maien yarzuqukum minas samaawaati wal-ardi qulil laahu Wa-innaaa aw iyyaakum la'alaa hudan aw fee dalaalim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3631,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Qul laa tus'aloona 'ammaaa ajramnaa Wa-laa nus'alu 'ammaa ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3632,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 26,
      "text":
          "Qul yajma'u bainanaa Rabbunaa summa yaftahu bainanaa bilhaqq; Wa-Huwal Fattaahul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3633,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Qul arooniyal lazeena alhaqtum bihee shurakaaa'a kallaa; bal Huwal Laahul 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3634,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaaka illaa kaaffatal linnaasi basheeranw Wa-nazeeranw Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3635,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 29,
      "text": "Wa-yaqooloona mataa haazal wa'du in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3636,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Qul lakum mee'aadu Yawmil laa tasta'khiroona 'anhu saa'atanw Wa-laa tastaqdimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3637,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeena kafaroo lan nu'mina bihaazal Quraani Wa-laa billazee baina yadayh; Wa-law taraaa iziz zaalimoona mawqoofoona 'inda Rabbihim yarji'u ba'duhum ilaa ba'dinil qawla yaqoolul lazeenas tud'ifoo lillazeenas takbaroo law-laaa antum lakunnaa mu'mineen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3638,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Qaalal lazeenas takbaroo lillazeenas tud'ifooo anahnu sadadnaakum 'anil hudaa ba'da iz jaaa'akum bal kuntum mujrimeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3639,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalal lazeenastud'ifoo lillazeenas takbaroo bal makrul laili wannahaari iz ta'muroonanaaaa an nakfura billaahi Wa-naj'ala lahooo andaadaa; Wa-asarrun nadaamata lammaa ra awul 'azaab; Wa-ja'alnal aghlaala feee a'naaqil lazeena kafaroo; hal yujzawna illaa maa kaanoo ya'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3640,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa arsalnaa' fee qaryatim min nazeerin illaa qaala mutrafooaa innaa bimaaa ursiltum bihee kaafiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3641,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo nahnu aksaru amwaalanw Wa-awlaadanw Wa-maa nahnu bimu-'azzabeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3642,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Qul inna Rabbee yabsutur rizqa limaien yashaaa'u Wa-yaqdiru Wa-laakinna aksaran naasi laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3643,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa amwaalukum Wa-laaa awlaadukum billatee tuqarribukum 'indanaa zulfaaa illaa man aamana Wa-'amila saalihan fa-ulaaa'ika lahum jazaaa'ud di'fi bimaa 'amiloo Wa-hum fil ghurufaati aaminoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3644,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena yas'awna feee Aayaatinaa mu'aajizeena ulaaa'ika fil 'azaabi muhdaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3645,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Qul inna Rabbee yabsutur rizqa limai yashaaa'u min 'ibaadihee Wa-yaqdiru lah; Wa-maaa anfaqtum min shai'in fahuwa yukhlifuhoo Wa-Huwa khairur raaziqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3646,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Wa-yawma yahshuruhum jamee'an summa yaqoolu lilmalaaa'ikati a-haaa'ulaaa'i iyyaakum kaanoo ya'budoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3647,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo Subhaanaka Anta waliyyunaa min doonihim bal kaanoo ya'budoonal jinna aksaruhum bihim mu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3648,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Fal-Yawma laa yamliku ba'dukum liba'din naf'anw Wa-laa darraa; Wa-naqoolu lil-lazeena zalamoo zooqoo 'azaaban Naaril latee kuntum bihaa tukazziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3649,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa tutlaa 'alaihim Aayaatunaa baiyinaatin qaaloo maa haazaa illaa rajuluien yureedu aien yasuddakum 'ammaa kaana ya'budu aabaaa'ukum Wa-qaaloo maa haazaaa illaaa ifkum muftaraa; Wa-qaalal lazeena kafaroo lilhaqqi lammaa jaaa'ahum in haazaaa illaa sihrum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3650,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa aatainaahum min Kutubiny yadrusoonahaa Wa-maaa arsalnaaa ilaihim qablaka min nazeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3651,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa-kazzabal lazeena min qablihim Wa-maa balaghoo mi'shaara maaa aatainaahum fakazzaboo Rusulee; fakaifa kaana nakeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3652,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Qul innamaaa a'izukum biwaahidatin an taqoomoo lillaahi masnaa Wa-furaadaa summa tatafakkaroo; maa bisaahibikum min jinnah; in huwa illaa nazeerul lakum baina yadai 'azaabin shadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3653,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Qul maa sa-altukum min ajrin fahuwa lakum in ajriya illaa 'alal laahi Wa-Huwa 'alaa kullin shai-in Shaheed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3654,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 48,
      "text": "Qul inna Rabbee yaqzifu bilhaqq 'Allaamul Ghuyoob"
    },
    {
      "index": 3655,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 49,
      "text": "Qul jaaa'al haqqu Wa-maa yubdi'ul baatilu Wa-maa yu'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3656,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 50,
      "text":
          "Qul in dalaltu fainnamaaa adillu 'alaa nafsee Wa-inih tadaitu fabimaa yoohee ilaiyya Rabbee; innahoo Samee'un Qareeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 3657,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Wa-law taraaa iz fazi'oo falaa fawta Wa-ukhizoo mim makaanin qareeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 3658,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaaloo aamannaa bihee Wa-annaa lahumut tanaawushu min makaanin ba'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3659,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "Wa-qad kafaroo bihee min qablu Wa-yaqzifoona bilghaibi min makaanin ba'eed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3660,
      "sura": 34,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Wa-heela bainahum Wa-baina maa yashtahoona kamaa fu'ila bi-ashyaa'ihim min qabl; innahum kaanoo fee shakkin mureeb"
    },
    {
      "index": 3661,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 1,
      "text":
          "Alhamdu lillaahi faatiris samaawaati wal-ardi jaa'ilil malaaa'ikati rusulan uleee ajnihatim masnaa Wa-sulaasa Wa-rubaa'; yazeedu fil khalqi maa yashaaa'; innal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3662,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 2,
      "text":
          "Maa yaftahil laahu linnaaasi mir rahmatin falaa mumsika lahaa Wa-maa yumsik falaa mursila lahoo mim ba'dihi; Wa-Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3663,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 3,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhan naasuzkuroo ni'matal laahi 'alaikum; hal min khaaliqin ghairul laahi yarzuqukum minas samaaa'i wal ard; laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa fa-annaa tu'fakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3664,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 4,
      "text":
          "Wa-ien yukazzibooka faqad kuzzibat Rusulum min qablik; Wa-ilal laahi turja'ul umoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3665,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 5,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyuhan naasu inna wa'dal laahi haqqun falaa taghurrannakumul hayaatud dunyaa; Wa-laa yaghurran-nakum billaahil gharoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3666,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 6,
      "text":
          "Innash shaitaana lakum 'aduwwun fattakhizoohu 'aduwwaa; innamaa yad'oo hizbahoo liyakoonoo min ashaabis sa'eer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3667,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 7,
      "text":
          "Allazeena kafaroo lahum 'azaabun shadeed; wallazeena aamanoo Wa-'amilus saalihaati lahum maghfiratunw Wa-ajrun kabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3668,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Afaman zuyyina lahoo sooo'u 'amalihee fara-aahu hasanaa; fa-innal laaha yudillu mai yashaaa'u Wa-yahdee mai yashaaa'u falaa tazhab nafsuka 'alaihim hasaraat; innal laaha 'aleemun bimaa yasna'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3669,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wallaahul lazeee arsalar riyaaha fatuseeru sa-haaban fasuqnaahu ilaa baladim maiyitin fa-ahyaynaa bihil arda ba'da mawtihaa; kazaalikan nushoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3670,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Man kaana yureedul 'izzata falillaahil 'izzatu jamee'aa; ilaihi yas'adul kalimut taiyibu wal'amalus saalihu yarfa'uh; wallazeena yamkuroonas sayyiaati lahum 'azaabun shadeed; Wa-makru ulaaa'ika huwa yaboor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3671,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Wallaahu khalaqakum min turaabin summa min nutfatin summa ja'alakum azwaajaa; Wa-maa tahmilu min unsaa Wa-laa tada'u illaa bi'ilmih; Wa-maa yu'ammaru mim mu'ammarinw Wa-laa yunqasu min 'umuriheee illaa fee kitaab; inna zaalika 'alal laahi yaseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3672,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa yastawil bahraani haaza 'azbun furaatun saaa'ighun sharaabuhoo Wa-haazaa milhun ujaaj; Wa-min kullin ta'kuloona lahman tariyyanw Wa-tastakhrijoona hilyatan talbasoonahaa Wa-taral fulka feehi mawaakhira litabtaghoo min fadlihee Wa-la'allakum tashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3673,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 13,
      "text":
          "Yoolijul laila fin nahaari Wa-yoolijun nahaara fil laili Wa-sakhkharash shamsa wal-qamara kulluien yajree li-ajalim musammaa; zaalikumul laahu Rabbukum lahul mulk; wallazeena tad'oona min doonihee maa yamlikoona min qitmeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3674,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "In tad'oohum laa yasma'oo du'aaa'akum Wa-law sami'oo mas tajaaboo lakum; Wa-Yawmal Qiyaamati Yakfuroona bishirkikum; Wa-laa yunabbi'uka mislu khabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3675,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Yaaa-ayyunhan naasu antumul fuqaraaa'u ilal laahi wallaahu Huwal Ghaniyyul Hameed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3676,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 16,
      "text": "Ien yasha' yuzhibkum Wa-ya'ti bikhalqin jadeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3677,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 17,
      "text": "Wa-maa zaalika 'alal laahi bi'azeez"
    },
    {
      "index": 3678,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Wa-laa taziru waaziratun wizra ukhraa; Wa-in tad'u musqalatun ilaa himlihaa laa yuhmal minhu shai'unw Wa-law kaana zaa qurbaa; innamaa tunzirul lazeena yakhshawna Rabbahum bilghaibi Wa-aqaamus Salaah; Wa-man tazakkaa fa-innamaa yatazakkaa linafsih; Wa-ilal laahil maseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3679,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 19,
      "text": "Wa-maa yastawil a'maa wal-baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3680,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 20,
      "text": "Wa-laz zulumaatu Wa-lan noor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3681,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 21,
      "text": "Wa-laz zillu Wa-lal haroor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3682,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 22,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa yastawil ahyaaa'u Wa-lal amwaat; innal laaha yusmi'u maien yashaaa'u Wa-maaa anta bi-musmi'im man fil quboor"
    },
    {"index": 3683, "sura": 35, "aya": 23, "text": "In anta illaa nazeer"},
    {
      "index": 3684,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 24,
      "text":
          "Innaa arsalnaaka bil-haqqi basheeranw Wa-nazeeraa; Wa-im min ummatin illaa khalaa feehaa nazeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3685,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 25,
      "text":
          "Wa-ien yukazzibooka faqad kazzabal lazeena min qablihim jaaa'at-hum Rusuluhum bilbaiyyinaati Wa-biz-Zuburi Wa-bil-Kitaabil Muneer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3686,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 26,
      "text": "Summa akhaztul lazeena kafaroo fakaifa kaana nakeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3687,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 27,
      "text":
          "Alam tara annal laaha anzala minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa-akhrajnaa bihee samaraatim mukhtalifan alwaanuhaa; Wa-minal jibaali judadum beedunw Wa-humrum mukhtalifun alwaanuhaa Wa-gharaabeebu sood"
    },
    {
      "index": 3688,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wa-minan naasi wadda-waaabbi wal-an'aami mukhtalifun alwaanuhoo kazalik; innamaa yakhshal laaha min 'ibaadihil 'ulamaaa'; innal laaha 'Azeezun Ghafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3689,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 29,
      "text":
          "Innal lazeena yatloona Kitabbal laahi Wa-aqaamus Salaata Wa-anfaqoo mimmaa razaqnaahum sirranw Wa-'alaa-niyataien yarjoona tijaaratal lan taboor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3690,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Liyuwaffiyahum ujoorahum Wa-yazeedahum min fadlih; innahoo Ghafoorun Shakoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3691,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Wallazeee awhainaaa ilaika minal Kitaabi huwal haqqu musaddiqal limaa baina yadayh; innal laaha bi'ibaadihee la-khabeerum Baseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3692,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 32,
      "text":
          "Summa awrasnal Kitaabal lazeenas tafainaa min 'ibaadinaa faminhum zaalimul linafsihee Wa-minhum muqtasidu, Wa-minhum saabiqum bilkhairaati bi-iznil laah; zaalika huwal fadlul kabeer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3693,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Jannaatu 'adnien yad-khuloonahaa yuhallawna feeha min asaawira min zahabinw Wa-lu'lu'anw Wa-libaa-suhum feehaa hareer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3694,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-qaalul hamdu lillaahil lazeee azhaba 'annal hazan; inna Rabbanaa la-Ghafoorun Shakoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3695,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Allazeee ahallanaa daaral muqaamati min fadlihee laa yamassunaa feehaa nasabunw Wa-laa yamassunaa feehaa lughoob"
    },
    {
      "index": 3696,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Wallazeena kafaroo lahum naaru Jahannama laa yuqdaa 'alaihim fa-yamootoo Wa-laa yukhaffafu 'anhum min 'azaabihaa; kazaalika najzee kulla kafoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3697,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-hum yastarikhoona feehaa Rabbanaa akhrijnaa na'mal saalihan ghairal lazee kunnaa na'mal; awa-lamnu 'ammirkum maa yatazak-karu feehi man tazakkara Wa-jaaa'akumun nazeeru fazooqoo famaa lizzaalimeena min naseer"
    },
    {
      "index": 3698,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha 'aalimu ghaibis samaawaati wal-ard; innahoo 'aleemum bizaatis sudoor"
    },
    {
      "index": 3699,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Huwal lazee ja'alakum khalaaa'ifa fil ard; faman kafara fa'alaihi kufruhoo; Wa-laa yazeedul kaafireena kufruhum 'inda Rabbihim illaa maqtanw Wa-laa yazeedul kaafireena kufruhum illaa khasaaraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3700,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Qul ara'aytum shurakaaa'a-kumul lazeena tad'oona min doonil laahi; aroonee maazaa khalaqoo minal ardi am lahum shirkun fis samaawaati am aatainaahum Kitaaban fahum 'alaa baiyyinatim minh; bal ien ya'iduz zaalimoona ba-'duhum ba'dan illaa ghurooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3701,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 41,
      "text":
          "Innal laaha yumsikus samaawaati wal-arda an tazoolaaa; Wa-la'in zaalataaa in amsa-kahumaa min ahadim mim ba'dih; innahoo kaana Haleeman Ghafooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3702,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 42,
      "text":
          "Wa-aqsamoo billaahi jahda aymaanihim la'in jaaa'ahum nazeerul layakoonunna ahdaa min ihdal umami falam-maa jaaa'ahum nazeerum maa zaadahum illaa nufooraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3703,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Istikbaaran fil ardi Wa-makras sayyi'; Wa-laa yaheequl makrus sayyi'u illaa bi-ahlih; fahal yanzuroona illaa sunnatal awwaleen; falan tajida lisunnatil laahi tabdeelanw Wa-lan tajida lisunnatil laahi tahweela"
    },
    {
      "index": 3704,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 44,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaseeroo fil ardi fa-yanzuroo kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul lazeena min Qablihim Wa-kaanoo ashadda minhum quwwah; Wa-maa kaanal laahu liyu'jizahoo min shai'in fis samaawaati Wa-laa fil ard; innahoo kaana 'Aleeman Qadeeraa"
    },
    {
      "index": 3705,
      "sura": 35,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa-law yu'aakhizul laahun naasa bima kasaboo maa taraka 'alaa zahrihaa min daaabbatinw Wa-laakiny yu'akhkhiruhum ilaaa ajalim musamman fa-izaa jaaa'a ajaluhum fa-innal laaha kaana bi'ibaadihee Baseeraa"
    },
    {"index": 3706, "sura": 36, "aya": 1, "text": "Yaa-Seeen"},
    {"index": 3707, "sura": 36, "aya": 2, "text": "Wal-Qur-aanil Hakeem"},
    {"index": 3708, "sura": 36, "aya": 3, "text": "Innaka laminal mursaleen"},
    {"index": 3709, "sura": 36, "aya": 4, "text": "Alaa Siraatim Mustaqeem"},
    {"index": 3710, "sura": 36, "aya": 5, "text": "Tanzeelal 'Azeezir Raheem"},
    {
      "index": 3711,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 6,
      "text": "Litunzira qawmam maaa unzira aabaaa'uhum fahum ghaafiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3712,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 7,
      "text": "Laqad haqqal qawlu 'alaaa aksarihim fahum laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3713,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 8,
      "text":
          "Innaa ja'alnaa feee a'naaqihim aghlaalan fahiya ilal azqaani fahum muqmahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3714,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 9,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnaa mim baini aydeehim saddanw wa-min khalfihim saddan fa-aghshai-naahum fahum laa yubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3715,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 10,
      "text":
          "Wa-sawaaa'un 'alaihim 'a-anzartahum am lam tunzirhum laa yu'minoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3716,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 11,
      "text":
          "Innamaa tunziru manit taba 'az-Zikra Wa-khashiyar Rahmaana bilghaib, fabashshirhu bimaghfiratinw-wa ajrin kareem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3717,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 12,
      "text":
          "Innaa Nahnu nuhyil mawtaa Wa-naktubu maa qaddamoo Wa-aasaarahum; Wa-kulla shai'in ahsainaahu feee Imaamim Mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3718,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 13,
      "text": "Wadrib lahum masalan Ashaabal Qaryatih; iz jaaa'ahal mursaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3719,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 14,
      "text":
          "Iz arsalnaaa ilaihimus naini fakazzaboohumaa fa'azzaznaa bisaalisin faqaalooo innaaa ilaikum mursaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3720,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 15,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo maaa antum illaa basharum mislunaa Wa-maaa anzalar Rahmaanu min shai'in in antum illaa takziboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3721,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 16,
      "text": "Qaaloo Rabbunaa ya'lamu innaaa ilaikum lamursaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3722,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 17,
      "text": "Wa-maa 'alainaaa illal balaaghul mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3723,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 18,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo innaa tataiyarnaa bikum la'il lam tantahoo lanar-jumannakum Wa-la-yamassan-nakum minnaa 'azaabun aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3724,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 19,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo taaa'irukum ma'akum; a'in zukkirtum; bal antum qawmum musrifoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3725,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 20,
      "text":
          "Wa-jaaa'a min aqsal madeenati rajuluien yas'aa qaala yaa-qawmit tabi'ul mursaleen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3726,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 21,
      "text": "Ittabi'oo mal laa yas'alukum ajranw wa-hum muhtadoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3727,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 22,
      "text": "Wa-maa liya laaa a'budul lazee fataranee Wa-ilaihi turja'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3728,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 23,
      "text":
          "A-attakhizu min dooniheee aalihatan ien yuridnir Rahmaanu bidurril laa tughni 'annee shafaa-'atuhum shai-'anw wa-laa yunqizoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3729,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 24,
      "text": "Inneee izal lafee dalaa-lim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3730,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 25,
      "text": "Inneee aamantu bi-Rabbikum fasma'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3731,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 26,
      "text": "Qeelad khulil Jannnah; qaala yaa-laita qawmee ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3732,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 27,
      "text": "Bimaa ghafara lee Rabbee Wa-ja'alanee minal mukrameen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3733,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 28,
      "text":
          "Wa-maaa anzalnaa 'alaa qawmihee mim ba'dihee min jundim minas samaaa'i Wa-maa kunnaa munzileen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3734,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 29,
      "text": "In kaanat illaa saihatanw waahidatan fa-izaa hum khaamidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3735,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 30,
      "text":
          "Yaa-hasratan 'alal 'ibaaad; maa ya'teehim mir Rasoolin illaa kaanoo bihee yastahzi-'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3736,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 31,
      "text":
          "Alam yaraw kam ahlak-naa qablahum minal qurooni annahum ilaihim laa yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3737,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 32,
      "text": "Wa-in kullul lammaa jamee'ul ladainaa muhdaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3738,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 33,
      "text":
          "Wa-Aayatul lahumul ardul maitatu ahyainaahaa Wa-akhrajnaa minhaa habban faminhu ya'kuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3739,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 34,
      "text":
          "Wa-ja'alnaa feehaa jannaatim min nakheelinw Wa-a'naabinw Wa-fajjarnaa feeha minal 'uyoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3740,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 35,
      "text":
          "Li-ya'kuloo min samarihee Wa-maa 'amilat-hu aideehim; afalaa yashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3741,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 36,
      "text":
          "Subhaanal lazee khalaqal azwaaja kullahaa mimmaa tumbitul ardu Wa-min anfusihim Wa-mimmaa laa ya'lamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3742,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 37,
      "text":
          "Wa-Aayatul lahumul lailu naslakhu minhun nahaara fa-izaa hum muzlimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3743,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 38,
      "text":
          "Wash-shamsu tajree limustaqarril lahaa; zaalika taqdeerul 'Azeezil Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3744,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 39,
      "text":
          "Walqamara qaddarnaahu manaazila hattaa 'aada kal'ur-joonil qadeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3745,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 40,
      "text":
          "Lash shamsu yambaghee lahaaa an tudrikal qamara walal lailu saabiqun nahaar; Wa-kullun fee falaki yasbahoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3746,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 41,
      "text": "Wa-Aayatul lahum annaa hamalnaa zurriyatahum fil fulkil mashhoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3747,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 42,
      "text": "Wa-khalaqnaa lahum mim mislihee maa yarkaboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3748,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 43,
      "text":
          "Wa-in nashaa nughriqhum falaa sareekha lahum Wa-laa hum yunqazoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3749,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 44,
      "text": "Illaa rahmatam minnaa Wa-mataa'an ilaa heen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3750,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 45,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahumut taqoo maa baina aideekum Wa-maa khalfakum la'allakum turhamoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3751,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 46,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa ta'teehim min aayatim min Aayaati Rabbihim illaa kaanoo 'anhaa mu'rideen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3752,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 47,
      "text":
          "Wa-izaa qeela lahum anfiqoo mimmaa razaqakumul laahu qaalal lazeena kafaroo lillazeena aamanooo anut'imu mal law yashaaa'ul laahu at'amahooo in antum illaa fee dalaalim mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3753,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 48,
      "text": "Wa-yaqooloona mataa haazal wa'du in kuntum saadiqeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3754,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 49,
      "text":
          "Maa yanzuroona illaa saihatanw waahidatan ta'khuzuhum Wa-hum yakhissimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3755,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 50,
      "text": "Falaa yastatee'oona taw-siyatanw wa-laaa ilaaa ahlihim yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3756,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 51,
      "text":
          "Wa-nufikha fis soori faizaa hum minal ajdaasi ilaa Rabbihim yansiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3757,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 52,
      "text":
          "Qaaloo yaa-wailanaa mam ba'asanaa mim marqadinaa; haaza maa wa'adar Rahmanu Wa-sadaqal mursaloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3758,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 53,
      "text":
          "In kaanat illaa saihatanw waahidatan fa-izaa hum jamee'ul ladainaa muhdaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3759,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 54,
      "text":
          "Fal-Yawma laa tuzlamu nafsun shai'anw-wa laa tujzawna illaa maa kuntum ta'maloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3760,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 55,
      "text": "Inna Ashaabal jannatil Yawma fee shughulin faakihoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3761,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 56,
      "text": "Hum Wa-azwaajuhum fee zilaalin 'alal araaa'iki muttaki'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3762,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 57,
      "text": "Lahum feehaa faakiha-tunw wa-lahum maa yadda'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3763,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 58,
      "text": "Salaamun qawlam mir Rabbir Raheem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3764,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 59,
      "text": "Wamtaazul Yawma ayyuhal mujrimoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3765,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 60,
      "text":
          "Alam a'had ilaikum yaa Baneee Aadama al-laa ta'budush Shaitaana innahoo lakum 'aduwwum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3766,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 61,
      "text": "Wa-ani 'budoonee; haazaa Siraatum Mustaqeem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3767,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 62,
      "text":
          "Wa-laqad adalla minkum jibillan kaseeraa; afalam takoonoo ta'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3768,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 63,
      "text": "Haazihee Jahannamul latee kuntum too'adoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3769,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 64,
      "text": "Islawhal Yawma bimaa kuntum takfuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3770,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 65,
      "text":
          "Al-Yawma nakhtimu 'alaaa afwaahihim Wa-tukallimunaaa aideehim Wa-tashhadu arjuluhum bimaa kaanoo yaksiboon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3771,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 66,
      "text":
          "Wa-law nashaaa'u lata-masna 'alaaa aiyyunihim fasta-baqus siraata fa-annaa yubsiroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3772,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 67,
      "text":
          "Wa-law nashaaa'u lamasakhnaahum 'alaa makaanatihim famas tataa'oo mudiyyanw-wa laa yarji'oon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3773,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 68,
      "text": "Wa-man nu-'ammirhu nunakkishu fil khalq; afalaa ya'qiloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3774,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 69,
      "text":
          "Wa-maa 'allamnaahush shi'ra Wa-maa yambaghee lah; in huwa illaa zikrunw-wa Qur-aanum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3775,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 70,
      "text": "Liyunzira man kaana haiyyanw wa-yahiqqal qawlu 'alal kaafireen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3776,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 71,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaraw annaa khalaqnaa lahum mimmaa 'amilat aideenaaa an'aaman fahum lahaa maalikoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3777,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 72,
      "text": "Wa-zallalnaahaa lahum faminhaa rakoobuhum Wa-minhaa ya'kuloon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3778,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 73,
      "text": "Wa-lahum feehaa manaa-fi'u Wa-mashaarib; afalaa yashkuroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3779,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 74,
      "text": "Wattakhazoo min doonil laahi aalihatal la'allahum yunsaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3780,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 75,
      "text": "Laa yastatee'oona nasrahum Wa-hum lahum jundum muhdaroon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3781,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 76,
      "text":
          "Falaa yahzunka qawluhum; innaa na'lamu maa yusirroona Wa-maa yu'linoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3782,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 77,
      "text":
          "Awalam yaral insaanu annaa khalaqnaahu min nutfatin fa-izaa huwa khaseemum mubeen"
    },
    {
      "index": 3783,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 78,
      "text":
          "Wa-daraba lanaa maslanw wa-nasiya khalqahoo qaala maien yuhyil 'izaama Wa-hiya rameem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3784,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 79,
      "text":
          "Qul yuh-yeehal lazeee ansha-ahaaa awwala marrah; Wa-Huwa bikulli khalqin 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3785,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 80,
      "text":
          "Allazee ja'ala lakum minash shajaril akhdari naaran fa-izaaa antum minhu tooqidoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3786,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 81,
      "text":
          "Awa-laisal lazee khalaqas samaawaati wal arda biqaadirin 'alaaa ai-yakhluqa mislahum; balaa Wa-Huwal Khallaaqul 'Aleem"
    },
    {
      "index": 3787,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 82,
      "text":
          "Innamaa amruhooo izaaa araada shai'an aien yaqoola lahoo kun fa-yakoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 3788,
      "sura": 36,
      "aya": 83,
      "text":
          "Fa-Subhaanal lazee biyadihee malakootu kulli shai-inw wa-ilaihi turja'oon"
    },
    {"index": 3789, "sura": 37, "aya": 1, "text": "Wassaaaffaati saffaa"},
    {"index": 3790, "sura": 37, "aya": 2, "text": "Fazzaajiraati zajraa"},
    {"index": 3791, "sura": 37, "aya": 3, "text": "Fattaaliyaati Zikra"},
    {"index": 3792, "sura": 37, "aya": 4, "text": "Inna Illaahakum la-Waahid"},
    {
      "index": 3793,
      "sura": 37,
      "aya": 5,
      "text": "Rabbus samaawaati wal-ardi Wa-maa bainahumaa Wa-Rabbul mashaariq"
    },
    {
